  ('229e941c-d560-5ec6-90ab-b891390b2382', NULL, 'Dumbbell Lying Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Extension im Liegen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Lower the dumbbells down towards your forehead, bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Lower the dumbbells down towards your forehead, bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander.","Strecke die Arme gerade über der Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Senke die Kurzhanteln Richtung Stirn ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0351.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0351.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('df657c3c-f505-5bf0-a4f3-a329f7e30c30', NULL, 'Dumbbell Lying Wide Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Curl im Liegen (weiter Griff)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up and arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up and arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1662.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1662.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4d73169f-9921-53b5-9c28-84e2bdf0e5ca', NULL, 'Dumbbell Neutral Grip Bench Press', 'Kurzhantel-Bankdrücken im Neutralgriff', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with a neutral grip (palms facing each other) and your arms extended straight up over your chest. Slowly lower the dumbbells down towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the dumbbells back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with a neutral grip (palms facing each other) and your arms extended straight up over your chest.","Slowly lower the dumbbells down towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the dumbbells back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken auf der Bank.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im neutralen Griff (Handflächen zueinander), die Arme gerade über der Brust gestreckt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte am unteren Punkt kurz inne und drücke die Kurzhanteln dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0352.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0352.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bdb7c7b3-dd7f-5b9a-b144-cc5d6579b00d', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Bench Fly', 'Bank-Fliegende mit Kurzhanteln, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, resting it on top of your thigh. Lie back on the bench, keeping the dumbbell pressed against your thigh. Using your free hand, help lift the dumbbell up to the starting position. Hold the dumbbell directly above your shoulder with your arm extended and palm facing inward. Lower the dumbbell out to the side in a wide arc, keeping a slight bend in your elbow. Pause when your arm is parallel to the ground, then reverse the movement and bring the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, resting it on top of your thigh.","Lie back on the bench, keeping the dumbbell pressed against your thigh.","Using your free hand, help lift the dumbbell up to the starting position.","Hold the dumbbell directly above your shoulder with your arm extended and palm facing inward.","Lower the dumbbell out to the side in a wide arc, keeping a slight bend in your elbow.","Pause when your arm is parallel to the ground, then reverse the movement and bring the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat."]', '["Setze dich auf eine flache Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, auf dem Oberschenkel abgestützt.","Lege dich auf der Bank zurück, die Kurzhantel bleibt gegen den Oberschenkel gedrückt.","Nutze die freie Hand, um die Kurzhantel in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Halte die Kurzhantel direkt über der Schulter, der Arm gestreckt, die Handfläche zeigt nach innen.","Senke die Kurzhantel in einer weiten Bogenbewegung seitlich ab, der Ellbogen bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Halte inne, wenn der Arm parallel zum Boden ist, und kehre die Bewegung um, um die Kurzhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu bringen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1285.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1285.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bf8bc37f-15d2-5745-ae0b-6e51b6d24e91', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Bent-Over Row', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern vorgebeugt, einarmig', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing your body. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Let the dumbbell hang straight down towards the floor, with your arm fully extended. Pull the dumbbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing your body.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Let the dumbbell hang straight down towards the floor, with your arm fully extended.","Pull the dumbbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt zum Körper.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Lass die Kurzhantel gerade Richtung Boden hängen, der Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Brust hoch, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper, ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0292.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0292.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fe789588-7f6c-5912-8810-e2f0fba26b8b', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Chest Fly on Exercise Ball', 'Fliegende mit Kurzhanteln auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in one hand and your feet flat on the ground. Walk your feet forward, rolling the ball until your upper back is supported on the ball and your head, neck, and shoulders are off the ball. Extend your arm with the dumbbell straight up above your chest, palm facing inward. Slowly lower the dumbbell out to the side, keeping a slight bend in your elbow. Pause for a moment when your arm is parallel to the ground. Engage your chest muscles to bring the dumbbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in one hand and your feet flat on the ground.","Walk your feet forward, rolling the ball until your upper back is supported on the ball and your head, neck, and shoulders are off the ball.","Extend your arm with the dumbbell straight up above your chest, palm facing inward.","Slowly lower the dumbbell out to the side, keeping a slight bend in your elbow.","Pause for a moment when your arm is parallel to the ground.","Engage your chest muscles to bring the dumbbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Füsse flach am Boden.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne und rolle den Ball ab, bis dein oberer Rücken vom Ball gestützt wird und Kopf, Nacken und Schultern frei sind.","Strecke den Arm mit der Kurzhantel gerade über die Brust, Handfläche zeigt nach innen.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam seitlich ab, der Ellbogen bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Halte kurz inne, wenn der Arm parallel zum Boden ist.","Spanne die Brustmuskeln an, um die Kurzhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu bringen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1286.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1286.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5834c945-bd5c-5d43-b802-303f3ed9f46e', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Concentration Curl (On Stability Ball)', 'Kurzhantel-Konzentrationscurl auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm extended down towards the floor. Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder while contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm extended down towards the floor.","Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder while contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Stabilitätsball, Füsse flach am Boden, Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach oben, der Arm Richtung Boden gestreckt.","Stütze den Ellbogen an der Innenseite des Oberschenkels ab, direkt über dem Knie.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne, atme dann ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0353.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0353.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('21736b59-5276-5366-8ca5-0b7144fedd02', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Decline Chest Press', 'Kurzhantel-Negativbank-Drücken, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Lie on a decline bench with a dumbbell in one hand, resting on your chest. Place your feet flat on the ground and keep your back pressed against the bench. Extend your arm and push the dumbbell up towards the ceiling, fully extending your elbow. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Lie on a decline bench with a dumbbell in one hand, resting on your chest.","Place your feet flat on the ground and keep your back pressed against the bench.","Extend your arm and push the dumbbell up towards the ceiling, fully extending your elbow.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Lege dich auf eine Negativbank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf der Brust abgestützt.","Stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken an der Bank.","Strecke den Arm und drücke die Kurzhantel Richtung Decke, der Ellbogen wird vollständig gestreckt.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1287.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1287.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b495e4bc-d28d-5c5e-b98d-b59dbe144030', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Fly on Exercise Ball', 'Fliegende mit Kurzhanteln auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in one hand and your feet flat on the ground. Walk your feet forward and roll your body down until your upper back is resting on the exercise ball. Extend your arm with the dumbbell straight up above your chest, palm facing inwards. Slowly lower the dumbbell out to the side, keeping a slight bend in your elbow. Pause for a moment, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in one hand and your feet flat on the ground.","Walk your feet forward and roll your body down until your upper back is resting on the exercise ball.","Extend your arm with the dumbbell straight up above your chest, palm facing inwards.","Slowly lower the dumbbell out to the side, keeping a slight bend in your elbow.","Pause for a moment, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Füsse flach am Boden.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne und rolle den Körper ab, bis dein oberer Rücken auf dem Gymnastikball aufliegt.","Strecke den Arm mit der Kurzhantel gerade über die Brust, Handfläche nach innen.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam seitlich ab, der Ellbogen bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Halte kurz inne und spanne dann die Brustmuskeln an, um die Kurzhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu bringen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1288.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1288.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0dc75158-ad0d-5ef0-9c73-094ec48edd50', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm French Press on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-French-Press auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your arm straight up towards the ceiling, keeping your elbow stationary. Slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your arm straight up towards the ceiling, keeping your elbow stationary.","Slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach oben, der Ellbogen im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke den Arm gerade Richtung Decke, der Ellbogen bleibt ruhig.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1736.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1736.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4c41d943-f6ec-58db-a573-7e81129184d9', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Hammer Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammer-Scott-Curl, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher bench with a dumbbell in one hand and your upper arm resting on the pad. Hold the dumbbell with a neutral grip (palms facing your body). Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher bench with a dumbbell in one hand and your upper arm resting on the pad.","Hold the dumbbell with a neutral grip (palms facing your body).","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Scott-Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, der Oberarm auf dem Polster.","Halte die Kurzhantel im neutralen Griff (Handflächen zum Körper).","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1663.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1663.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('efeec071-910c-504f-b852-4cec734c4c24', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Hammer Press on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Hammerdrücken auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing inwards and your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle. Place your other hand on your hip for stability. Press the dumbbell upwards, extending your arm fully. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing inwards and your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle.","Place your other hand on your hip for stability.","Press the dumbbell upwards, extending your arm fully.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach innen, der Ellbogen im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Lege die andere Hand zur Stabilisierung auf die Hüfte.","Drücke die Kurzhantel nach oben, der Arm wird vollständig gestreckt.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1621.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1621.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('122dad11-0874-5ccd-8922-1327dcf01848', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Incline Chest Press', 'Kurzhantel-Schrägbank-Drücken, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Adjust the incline bench to a 45-degree angle. Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip, resting it on your shoulder. Push the dumbbell up and away from your body, extending your arm fully. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Adjust the incline bench to a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip, resting it on your shoulder.","Push the dumbbell up and away from your body, extending your arm fully.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stelle die Schrägbank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Setze dich auf die Bank, der Rücken am Polster, die Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Obergriff, auf der Schulter abgestützt.","Drücke die Kurzhantel nach oben und vom Körper weg, der Arm wird vollständig gestreckt.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1289.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1289.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('414e5708-0c14-50bf-9f51-fa445ffe82ec', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Kickback, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in your right hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Bring your right elbow up to your side, keeping it bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your right arm straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement. Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in your right hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Bring your right elbow up to your side, keeping it bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your right arm straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement.","Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Bringe den rechten Ellbogen an die Seite, im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke den rechten Arm gerade nach hinten und spanne den Trizeps am oberen Punkt der Bewegung an.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0354.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0354.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b81eb328-8df5-5e6d-91e8-07c09b5193cc', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Lateral Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben, einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing your body. Keep your back straight and your core engaged throughout the exercise. Raise the dumbbell to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down. Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","triceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing your body.","Keep your back straight and your core engaged throughout the exercise.","Raise the dumbbell to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down.","Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt zum Körper.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte während der ganzen Übung angespannt.","Hebe die Kurzhantel seitlich an, der Arm bleibt gestreckt, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten.","Hebe weiter, bis der Arm parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0355.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0355.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('be73baa4-33be-5342-8c28-be95b64e8589', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Lateral Raise with Support', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben mit Unterstützung, einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, with your palm facing your body. Place your other hand on a stable surface, such as a bench or wall, for support. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Raise the dumbbell out to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down. Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rotator cuff"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, with your palm facing your body.","Place your other hand on a stable surface, such as a bench or wall, for support.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Raise the dumbbell out to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down.","Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt zum Körper.","Lege die andere Hand zur Stütze auf eine stabile Fläche, zum Beispiel eine Bank oder Wand.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Kurzhantel seitlich an, der Arm bleibt gestreckt, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten.","Hebe weiter, bis der Arm parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0356.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0356.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c1f4fd46-9181-5ca4-a024-e791ca3aa4fe', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Press on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Drücken auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and position it at shoulder height, with your elbow bent and palm facing forward. Slowly press the dumbbell upward until your arm is fully extended, while keeping your core engaged and maintaining balance on the exercise ball. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and position it at shoulder height, with your elbow bent and palm facing forward.","Slowly press the dumbbell upward until your arm is fully extended, while keeping your core engaged and maintaining balance on the exercise ball.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe, der Ellbogen gebeugt, die Handfläche nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhantel langsam nach oben, bis der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist, halte dabei die Körpermitte angespannt und das Gleichgewicht auf dem Ball.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1290.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1290.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0c7d8dd2-b7ed-54d2-ad22-f8550d3a5157', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Prone Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl in Bauchlage, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie face down on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down. Extend your arm fully, letting it hang straight down towards the floor. Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Lie face down on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down.","Extend your arm fully, letting it hang straight down towards the floor.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Lege dich bäuchlings auf eine flache Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach unten.","Strecke den Arm vollständig, lass ihn gerade Richtung Boden hängen.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, indem du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1665.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1665.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('50e9b872-9a01-57e4-ac2d-a1bfd5624b12', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Prone Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl in Bauchlage, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie face down on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing your body and arm fully extended. Keep your upper arm stationary and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Lie face down on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing your body and arm fully extended.","Keep your upper arm stationary and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Lege dich bäuchlings auf eine flache Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche zum Körper, Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1666.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1666.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8f65ab78-ce30-5091-a3ac-231c8b419449', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Pullover on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Überzüge auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a dumbbell with one hand and extend your arm straight up above your chest. Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head while keeping your arm straight. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","latissimus dorsi","rhomboids"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a dumbbell with one hand and extend your arm straight up above your chest.","Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head while keeping your arm straight.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit einer Hand und strecke den Arm gerade über die Brust.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf ab, der Arm bleibt gestreckt.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1291.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1291.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('fbfa9804-c3ba-56bc-aa22-4c7ecb919eca', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Reverse Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Handgelenk-Curl, einarmig', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip, palm facing down. Rest your forearm on your thigh, with your wrist hanging off the edge. Slowly lower the dumbbell towards the ground by flexing your wrist. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly curl your wrist back up towards your body. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'wrist extensors', '["wrist extensors"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip, palm facing down.","Rest your forearm on your thigh, with your wrist hanging off the edge.","Slowly lower the dumbbell towards the ground by flexing your wrist.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly curl your wrist back up towards your body.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Obergriff, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten.","Lege den Unterarm auf den Oberschenkel, das Handgelenk hängt über die Kante.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam Richtung Boden ab, indem du das Handgelenk beugst.","Halte am unteren Punkt kurz inne und ziehe das Handgelenk dann langsam zurück Richtung Körper.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0358.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0358.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8dad9490-a6df-5ef8-aa3b-a2d295025c90', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Reverse Fly (With Support)', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Fly mit Unterstützung, einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing inwards. Lean forward and place your free hand on the bench for support. Keep your arm slightly bent and raise it out to the side until it is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arm back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing inwards.","Lean forward and place your free hand on the bench for support.","Keep your arm slightly bent and raise it out to the side until it is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arm back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach innen.","Lehne dich nach vorne und stütze die freie Hand zur Unterstützung auf der Bank ab.","Halte den Arm leicht gebeugt und hebe ihn seitlich an, bis er parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke den Arm dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0359.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0359.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ff499cd6-3975-5c9b-8ec3-22994f955607', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Reverse Grip Press', 'Kurzhantel-Drücken im Untergriff, einarmig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing towards your body. Place your feet flat on the ground and keep your back straight. Raise the dumbbell to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body. Press the dumbbell upwards until your arm is fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing towards your body.","Place your feet flat on the ground and keep your back straight.","Raise the dumbbell to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Press the dumbbell upwards until your arm is fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setze dich auf eine flache Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt zum Körper.","Stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Hebe die Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper.","Drücke die Kurzhantel nach oben, bis der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1622.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1622.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('85bc0e51-683e-58bc-b008-07890582eb11', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Reverse Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse-Scott-Curl, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher bench with your chest against the pad and your arm extended over the edge of the bench, holding a dumbbell with an underhand grip. Lower the dumbbell slowly until your arm is fully extended. Curl the dumbbell back up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary. Squeeze your biceps at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher bench with your chest against the pad and your arm extended over the edge of the bench, holding a dumbbell with an underhand grip.","Lower the dumbbell slowly until your arm is fully extended.","Curl the dumbbell back up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Squeeze your biceps at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Scott-Bank, die Brust am Polster, der Arm über die Bankkante gestreckt, halte eine Kurzhantel im Untergriff.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam ab, bis der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist.","Ziehe die Kurzhantel zurück Richtung Schulter hoch, der Oberarm bleibt ruhig.","Spanne den Bizeps am oberen Punkt der Bewegung an und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1414.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1414.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9098b874-4552-5a47-b01f-4c29e026690a', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Reverse Spider Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse-Spider-Curl, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down and arm fully extended. Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by flexing your elbow. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down and arm fully extended.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by flexing your elbow.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten, der Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, indem du den Ellbogen beugst.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1667.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1667.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('63e09cc9-09f4-59f8-a321-fa611149bf18', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Seated Bicep Curl on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm fully extended. Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm fully extended.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach oben, der Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, indem du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1668.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1668.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a36e1696-83ee-5275-9323-dc2a9a1d169b', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Seated Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl im Sitzen, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with a neutral grip (palms facing each other). Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with a neutral grip (palms facing each other).","Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im neutralen Griff (Handflächen zueinander).","Stütze den Ellbogen an der Innenseite des Oberschenkels ab, direkt über dem Knie.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1669.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1669.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2cc0bbdc-e0c0-56a4-902d-1edd2779a388', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Seated Neutral Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl im Neutralgriff im Sitzen, einarmig', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up. Rest your forearm on your thigh, allowing your wrist to hang off the edge. Keeping your forearm stationary, curl your wrist upward as far as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your wrist back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other hand.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up.","Rest your forearm on your thigh, allowing your wrist to hang off the edge.","Keeping your forearm stationary, curl your wrist upward as far as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your wrist back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other hand."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach oben.","Lege den Unterarm auf den Oberschenkel, das Handgelenk hängt über die Kante.","Halte den Unterarm ruhig und ziehe das Handgelenk so weit wie möglich nach oben.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke das Handgelenk dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zur anderen Hand."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1415.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1415.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6986ecfb-ab4c-5baa-837c-ca8660c6e3b8', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Shoulder Press', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken, einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder level, palm facing forward. Press the dumbbell upward until your arm is fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder level, palm facing forward.","Press the dumbbell upward until your arm is fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe, die Handfläche zeigt nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhantel nach oben, bis der Arm vollständig über dem Kopf gestreckt ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0361.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0361.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b1110564-c283-56df-a3dc-81eafa8676bc', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Shoulder Press V. 2', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken, einarmig (Variante 2)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder level, palm facing forward. Engage your core and press the dumbbell straight up overhead, fully extending your arm. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder level, palm facing forward.","Engage your core and press the dumbbell straight up overhead, fully extending your arm.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe, die Handfläche zeigt nach vorne.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und drücke die Kurzhantel gerade nach oben über den Kopf, der Arm wird vollständig gestreckt.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann zurück auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0360.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0360.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3d7c73bc-2f12-55a5-b6be-576b324b4d95', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Snatch', 'Kurzhantel-Snatch, einarmig', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Lower the dumbbell towards the ground, keeping it close to your body. Explosively extend your hips, knees, and ankles, driving the dumbbell upwards in a straight line. As the dumbbell reaches shoulder height, quickly rotate your hand and punch it overhead, fully extending your arm. Catch the dumbbell overhead with a slight bend in your knees and hips. Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position in a controlled manner. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Lower the dumbbell towards the ground, keeping it close to your body.","Explosively extend your hips, knees, and ankles, driving the dumbbell upwards in a straight line.","As the dumbbell reaches shoulder height, quickly rotate your hand and punch it overhead, fully extending your arm.","Catch the dumbbell overhead with a slight bend in your knees and hips.","Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position in a controlled manner.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust raus.","Senke die Kurzhantel Richtung Boden ab, nah am Körper.","Strecke Hüfte, Knie und Sprunggelenke explosiv und führe die Kurzhantel in einer geraden Linie nach oben.","Sobald die Kurzhantel Schulterhöhe erreicht, drehst du schnell die Hand und drückst sie über Kopf, der Arm wird vollständig gestreckt.","Fange die Kurzhantel über Kopf auf, mit leichter Beugung in Knien und Hüfte.","Senke die Kurzhantel kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3888.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3888.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('87f06b63-8459-5463-adeb-34fff8ef9180', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Standing Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl im Stehen, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing forward and arm fully extended. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the weight upward while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing forward and arm fully extended.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the weight upward while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, die Handfläche zeigt nach vorne, der Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhantel weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe ist.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1670.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1670.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0a35dcf4-0b2e-506d-9ac0-457fbb748914', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Standing Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl im Stehen, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary. Exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary.","Exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1671.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1671.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e0f3a536-0f93-5215-a7d7-7567dcfcc047', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Triceps Extension (On Bench)', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Extension auf der Bank, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place your other hand on the bench for support. Raise the dumbbell overhead, keeping your upper arm close to your head and your elbow pointing forward. Lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm stationary. Extend your arm back up to the starting position, fully straightening your elbow. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place your other hand on the bench for support.","Raise the dumbbell overhead, keeping your upper arm close to your head and your elbow pointing forward.","Lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Extend your arm back up to the starting position, fully straightening your elbow.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand und stütze die andere Hand zur Unterstützung auf der Bank ab.","Hebe die Kurzhantel über Kopf, der Oberarm bleibt nah am Kopf, der Ellbogen zeigt nach vorne.","Senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf ab, indem du den Ellbogen beugst, der Oberarm bleibt ruhig.","Strecke den Arm zurück in die Ausgangsposition, der Ellbogen wird vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0362.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0362.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('99c3967a-7fd3-5afe-8948-f094b37ff116', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Upright Row', 'Kurzhantel-Aufrechtes Rudern, einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip. Let the dumbbell hang at arm''s length in front of your thighs, with your palm facing your body. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbell straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbow. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Let the dumbbell hang at arm''s length in front of your thighs, with your palm facing your body.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbell straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbow.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Lass die Kurzhantel in Armlänge vor den Oberschenkeln hängen, die Handfläche zeigt zum Körper.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel gerade Richtung Kinn hoch, der Ellbogen führt die Bewegung an.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne, atme dann ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0363.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0363.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6dffd4c8-f905-541d-b9e5-ac37635460f9', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl, einarmig', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your forearm on your thigh. Allow your wrist to extend, letting the dumbbell roll down towards your fingers. Slowly curl your wrist back up, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other hand.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your forearm on your thigh.","Allow your wrist to extend, letting the dumbbell roll down towards your fingers.","Slowly curl your wrist back up, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other hand."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Untergriff, der Unterarm liegt auf dem Oberschenkel.","Lass das Handgelenk strecken, sodass die Kurzhantel Richtung Finger abrollt.","Ziehe das Handgelenk langsam zurück nach oben und führe die Kurzhantel Richtung Unterarm.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zur anderen Hand."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0364.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0364.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('51cf9e3f-a9c3-5723-86f9-9e70a0ee1a50', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Arm Zottman Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Zottman-Scott-Curl, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher curl bench and hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip. Rest your upper arm on the preacher bench pad, allowing your arm to fully extend. Curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary. At the top of the curl, rotate your wrist so that your palm faces up. Slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position, rotating your wrist back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher curl bench and hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip.","Rest your upper arm on the preacher bench pad, allowing your arm to fully extend.","Curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.","At the top of the curl, rotate your wrist so that your palm faces up.","Slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position, rotating your wrist back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Scott-Bank und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Untergriff.","Lege den Oberarm auf das Polster der Scott-Bank, sodass der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist.","Ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, der Oberarm bleibt ruhig.","Drehe am oberen Punkt der Bewegung das Handgelenk, sodass die Handfläche nach oben zeigt.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab und drehe das Handgelenk zurück in die Ausgangsstellung.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1672.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1672.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('416501d3-7a5d-5aae-8757-b020320d7b71', NULL, 'Dumbbell One Leg Fly on Exercise Ball', 'Fliegende mit Kurzhanteln auf dem Gymnastikball, einbeinig', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Place one foot on the ground and extend the other leg straight out in front of you. Lean forward slightly and bring your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Slowly lower the dumbbells down and out to the sides, feeling a stretch in your chest. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the dumbbells back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Place one foot on the ground and extend the other leg straight out in front of you.","Lean forward slightly and bring your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Slowly lower the dumbbells down and out to the sides, feeling a stretch in your chest.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the dumbbells back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander.","Stelle einen Fuss auf den Boden und strecke das andere Bein gerade vor dir aus.","Lehne dich leicht nach vorne und führe die Arme seitlich, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam seitlich ab, du spürst eine Dehnung in der Brust.","Halte am unteren Punkt kurz inne und spanne dann die Brustmuskeln an, um die Kurzhanteln zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu bringen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1292.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1292.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('53e4a281-a7fb-5f52-b03d-faba050a047d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench Neutral Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl im Neutralgriff auf der Bank', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up. Rest your forearms on the bench, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up.","Rest your forearms on the bench, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Bank, die Handgelenke hängen über die Kante.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Schultern hoch.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne, atme dann ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0365.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0365.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ced2588b-ab70-53ae-a429-7366b68ffbcc', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench One Arm Neutral Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl im Neutralgriff auf der Bank, einarmig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in one hand and your arm extended over the bench, palm facing up. Keep your upper arm stationary and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, keeping your wrist in a neutral position. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in one hand and your arm extended over the bench, palm facing up.","Keep your upper arm stationary and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, keeping your wrist in a neutral position.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, der Arm über die Bank gestreckt, Handfläche nach oben.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, das Handgelenk bleibt neutral.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0366.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0366.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('856775e1-aafb-5b65-8bf4-b6016225b6ae', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench One Arm Reverse Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Handgelenk-Curl auf der Bank, einarmig', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down. Rest your forearm on the bench with your wrist hanging off the edge. Slowly curl your wrist upwards, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down.","Rest your forearm on the bench with your wrist hanging off the edge.","Slowly curl your wrist upwards, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach unten.","Lege den Unterarm auf die Bank, das Handgelenk hängt über die Kante.","Ziehe das Handgelenk langsam nach oben und führe die Kurzhantel Richtung Unterarm.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1441.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1441.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e843cd9d-704e-50fe-8fa3-60c097d9b821', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench One Arm Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl auf der Bank, einarmig', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down. Rest your forearm on the bench with your wrist hanging off the edge. Slowly curl your wrist upwards, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing down.","Rest your forearm on the bench with your wrist hanging off the edge.","Slowly curl your wrist upwards, bringing the dumbbell towards your forearm.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach unten.","Lege den Unterarm auf die Bank, das Handgelenk hängt über die Kante.","Ziehe das Handgelenk langsam nach oben und führe die Kurzhantel Richtung Unterarm.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann zum anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0367.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0367.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7569735e-ac87-5913-9582-c06907f0499b', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench Reverse Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Handgelenk-Curl auf der Bank', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing down. Rest your forearms on the bench, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge. Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the dumbbells towards your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing down.","Rest your forearms on the bench, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge.","Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the dumbbells towards your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach unten.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Bank, die Handgelenke hängen über die Kante.","Ziehe die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und führe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Körper.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0368.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0368.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('12b7723d-eb4b-59b6-a08f-4b1df1c90087', NULL, 'Dumbbell Over Bench Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenk-Curl auf der Bank', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your forearms resting on the bench and your palms facing up, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Allow your wrists to hang over the edge of the bench. Slowly curl your wrists upward, squeezing your forearms at the top of the movement. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower your wrists back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench with your forearms resting on the bench and your palms facing up, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Allow your wrists to hang over the edge of the bench.","Slowly curl your wrists upward, squeezing your forearms at the top of the movement.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower your wrists back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, die Unterarme auf der Bank abgestützt, Handflächen nach oben, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Lass die Handgelenke über die Bankkante hängen.","Ziehe die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und spanne dabei die Unterarme am oberen Punkt der Bewegung an.","Halte kurz inne und senke die Handgelenke dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0369.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0369.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('485e9ced-9729-5223-903f-b1b3eb193d7e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Palm Rotational Bent Over Row', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern vorgebeugt mit Rotation', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent. Let your arms hang straight down, palms facing your body. Engage your core and pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. As you pull the dumbbells up, rotate your palms so they face away from your body. Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the top of the movement. Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position, rotating your palms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent.","Let your arms hang straight down, palms facing your body.","Engage your core and pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","As you pull the dumbbells up, rotate your palms so they face away from your body.","Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the top of the movement.","Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position, rotating your palms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Lass die Arme gerade herabhängen, die Handflächen zum Körper.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Brust hoch, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Drehe beim Hochziehen die Handflächen, sodass sie vom Körper weg zeigen.","Ziehe die Schulterblätter am oberen Punkt der Bewegung zusammen.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab und drehe die Handflächen zurück in die Ausgangsstellung.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1329.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1329.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('97587742-4885-56ed-9e19-45938dede1d6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Palms in Incline Bench Press', 'Kurzhantel-Schrägbank-Bankdrücken im Neutralgriff', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Sit on the bench with your back against the backrest and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing inwards. Extend your arms straight up above your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Lower the dumbbells slowly towards your shoulders, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then press the dumbbells back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the bench with your back against the backrest and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing inwards.","Extend your arms straight up above your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Lower the dumbbells slowly towards your shoulders, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then press the dumbbells back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank im 45-Grad-Winkel auf.","Setze dich auf die Bank, der Rücken an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff, Handflächen nach innen.","Strecke die Arme gerade über der Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam Richtung Schultern ab, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte am unteren Punkt kurz inne und drücke die Kurzhanteln dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1623.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1623.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fe51e057-945e-5f64-8f76-f20a67a80eff', NULL, 'Dumbbell Preacher Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammer-Scott-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso. Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate the palms of your hands until they are facing forward. This will be your starting position. Now, keeping the upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Then, inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the recommended amount of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate the palms of your hands until they are facing forward.","This will be your starting position.","Now, keeping the upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Then, inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the recommended amount of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper und drehe die Handflächen, bis sie nach vorne zeigen.","Das ist deine Ausgangsposition.","Halte nun die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme dann ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die empfohlene Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0370.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0370.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('69c9c096-49e1-5276-be6c-6ac6cb86ba52', NULL, 'Dumbbell Plyo Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Sprungkniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides. Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. As you reach the bottom of the squat, explode upward, jumping off the ground. While in the air, quickly switch the position of your feet, landing with your opposite foot forward. Immediately lower your body back into a squat position and repeat the jump, switching your feet again. Continue alternating the position of your feet with each jump for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides.","Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","As you reach the bottom of the squat, explode upward, jumping off the ground.","While in the air, quickly switch the position of your feet, landing with your opposite foot forward.","Immediately lower your body back into a squat position and repeat the jump, switching your feet again.","Continue alternating the position of your feet with each jump for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel an den Seiten.","Senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Explodiere am unteren Punkt der Kniebeuge nach oben und springe vom Boden ab.","Wechsle in der Luft schnell die Fussposition und lande mit dem entgegengesetzten Fuss vorne.","Senke den Körper sofort wieder in eine Kniebeuge ab und wiederhole den Sprung, wechsle dabei erneut die Füsse.","Wechsle die Fussposition mit jedem Sprung fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0371.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0371.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0676aaac-24e0-5434-85d4-e56e32d5fc95', NULL, 'Dumbbell Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Scott-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher curl bench with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against it. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing up and your arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher curl bench with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against it.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing up and your arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Scott-Bank, die Oberarme auf dem Polster, die Brust dagegen.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0372.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0372.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a1c94b56-751c-598c-a416-ccb0748f979e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Preacher Curl Over Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Scott-Curl über dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your elbow on the exercise ball. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your elbow on the exercise ball.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Untergriff, der Ellbogen auf dem Gymnastikball abgestützt.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne, atme dann ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1673.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1673.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a7bd39cf-62e7-5c5e-af3d-20e78a5063dc', NULL, 'Dumbbell Press on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Drücken auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and dumbbells in each hand, resting on your thighs. Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the exercise ball until your lower back is supported on the ball and your knees are at a 90-degree angle. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and dumbbells in each hand, resting on your thighs.","Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the exercise ball until your lower back is supported on the ball and your knees are at a 90-degree angle.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, auf den Oberschenkeln abgestützt.","Gehe langsam mit den Füssen nach vorne und rolle den Gymnastikball ab, bis dein unterer Rücken auf dem Ball gestützt ist und die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel sind.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1293.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1293.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fa6c3d9a-c5b9-5bc5-842b-4552d92b52c3', NULL, 'Dumbbell Pronate-Grip Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Extension im Pronationsgriff', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell with both hands, palms facing down, and extend your arms straight up overhead. Keeping your upper arms close to your head and elbows pointing forward, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands, palms facing down, and extend your arms straight up overhead.","Keeping your upper arms close to your head and elbows pointing forward, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen, Handflächen nach unten, und strecke die Arme gerade über den Kopf.","Halte die Oberarme nah am Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach vorne, senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0373.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0373.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('64e1338f-2f67-5460-8daa-62352fa887b3', NULL, 'Dumbbell Prone Incline Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Schrägbank-Bizepscurl in Bauchlage', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Adjust the bench to a 45-degree incline. Lie face down on the bench with your chest and stomach resting against it. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing down and your arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the bench to a 45-degree incline.","Lie face down on the bench with your chest and stomach resting against it.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing down and your arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Bank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Lege dich bäuchlings auf die Bank, Brust und Bauch liegen auf.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach unten, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0374.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0374.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a03e02d8-ffea-55c2-932c-55f5bf1d245d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Prone Incline Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Schrägbank-Hammercurl in Bauchlage', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Adjust the bench to a 45-degree incline. Lie face down on the bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Allow your arms to hang straight down towards the floor, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the bench to a 45-degree incline.","Lie face down on the bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Allow your arms to hang straight down towards the floor, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Bank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Lege dich bäuchlings auf die Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander.","Lass die Arme gerade Richtung Boden hängen, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1674.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1674.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('75185803-0531-5805-b3b5-3b0c41c572b2', NULL, 'Dumbbell Pullover', 'Kurzhantel-Überzüge', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet on the floor. Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight above your chest. Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head until you feel a stretch in your chest and shoulders. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'latissimus dorsi', '["latissimus dorsi","triceps"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet on the floor.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight above your chest.","Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head until you feel a stretch in your chest and shoulders.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, der Kopf an einem Ende, die Füsse auf dem Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust.","Halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt und senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf ab, bis du eine Dehnung in Brust und Schultern spürst.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0375.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0375.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dff6f285-a601-5ec2-9b1a-7c74902a08d9', NULL, 'Dumbbell Pullover Hip Extension on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Überzüge mit Hüftstreckung auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and the dumbbell resting on your thighs. Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the exercise ball down your back until your head, neck, and upper back are supported on the ball. Hold the dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your arms straight and maintaining control. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. While keeping your arms extended, lift your hips off the ground, squeezing your glutes and engaging your core. Lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and the dumbbell resting on your thighs.","Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the exercise ball down your back until your head, neck, and upper back are supported on the ball.","Hold the dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your arms straight and maintaining control.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","While keeping your arms extended, lift your hips off the ground, squeezing your glutes and engaging your core.","Lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, die Kurzhantel auf den Oberschenkeln abgestützt.","Gehe langsam mit den Füssen nach vorne und rolle den Gymnastikball deinen Rücken hinunter, bis Kopf, Nacken und oberer Rücken vom Ball gestützt werden.","Halte die Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf ab, die Arme bleiben gestreckt und kontrolliert.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Hebe bei gestreckten Armen die Hüfte vom Boden ab, spanne dabei Gesäss und Körpermitte an.","Senke die Hüfte dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1294.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1294.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eabe1a41-76e0-5a3c-af85-2fdfb3c43a21', NULL, 'Dumbbell Pullover on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Überzüge auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball and hold a dumbbell with both hands above your chest, arms extended. Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head while keeping your arms straight. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","latissimus dorsi"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball and hold a dumbbell with both hands above your chest, arms extended.","Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head while keeping your arms straight.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball und halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen über der Brust, Arme gestreckt.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf ab, die Arme bleiben gestreckt.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1295.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1295.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('89734b95-ce72-509e-b08d-78d3fd096f22', NULL, 'Dumbbell Push Press', 'Kurzhantel-Stossdrücken', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level. Bend your knees slightly and dip your body down, then explosively extend your legs and press the dumbbells overhead. Lock out your arms at the top of the movement, then lower the dumbbells back to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level.","Bend your knees slightly and dip your body down, then explosively extend your legs and press the dumbbells overhead.","Lock out your arms at the top of the movement, then lower the dumbbells back to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und senke den Körper ab, strecke dann die Beine explosiv und drücke die Kurzhanteln über Kopf.","Strecke die Arme am oberen Punkt der Bewegung vollständig und senke die Kurzhanteln dann zurück auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1700.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1700.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d22a4e8b-4765-50ee-8fcd-604478c4b7d7', NULL, 'Dumbbell Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Armheben', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the floor, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the floor, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0376.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0376.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('452945ec-af8a-5b7d-94e2-9ae02e992a1e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Delt Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Reverses Seitheben', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2292.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2292.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dd60af34-3f31-5c80-80c4-b8ea6e9fbd47', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Delt Row', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern für die hintere Schulter', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Extend your arms straight down towards the floor, with a slight bend in your elbows. Raise the dumbbells out to the sides, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Extend your arms straight down towards the floor, with a slight bend in your elbows.","Raise the dumbbells out to the sides, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Strecke die Arme gerade Richtung Boden, die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln seitlich an und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0377.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0377.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('89b8a00e-165d-5915-a12b-186aa612ef3f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Fly', 'Kurzhantel-Reverses Fliegende', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Extend your arms straight down towards the ground, palms facing each other. Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, lift your arms out to the sides and squeeze your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arms straight down towards the ground, palms facing each other.","Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, lift your arms out to the sides and squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Strecke die Arme gerade Richtung Boden, Handflächen zueinander.","Halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt und hebe die Arme seitlich an, ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0378.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0378.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2e4ef0f4-2e0a-5118-bc9f-598b01b02ca7', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Lateral Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Reverses Seitheben', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and core engaged. Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0380.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0380.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3bbce414-028a-5aa3-8415-734b5500232b', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Lateral Raise (Support Head)', 'Kurzhantel-Reverses Seitheben mit Kopfstütze', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0379.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0379.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dbae517e-8212-5c6f-bd2e-93c16b2cadf9', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rear Lunge', 'Kurzhantel-Ausfallschritt rückwärts', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Take a step backward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. Bend your left knee and lower your body until your left thigh is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push through your left heel to return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side, stepping back with your left foot.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Take a step backward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","Bend your left knee and lower your body until your left thigh is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push through your left heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side, stepping back with your left foot."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Trete mit dem rechten Fuss nach hinten und senke den Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Beuge das linke Knie und senke den Körper ab, bis der linke Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann durch die linke Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite, trete mit dem linken Fuss nach hinten."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0381.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0381.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9a064227-1157-506f-b514-4b1a1cb0c32e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Grip Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing down and arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing down and arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach unten, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0382.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0382.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9ad9e317-7a20-54a3-a15a-db16da9514ce', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Bench Press', 'Kurzhantel-Bankdrücken im Untergriff', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing towards your feet. Extend your arms straight up towards the ceiling, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Slowly lower the dumbbells towards your chest, allowing your elbows to flare out to the sides. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the dumbbells back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing towards your feet.","Extend your arms straight up towards the ceiling, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Slowly lower the dumbbells towards your chest, allowing your elbows to flare out to the sides.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the dumbbells back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, Füsse flach am Boden, Knie gebeugt.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff, Handflächen zu den Füssen.","Strecke die Arme gerade Richtung Decke, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam Richtung Brust ab und lass die Ellbogen dabei seitlich ausklappen.","Halte am unteren Punkt kurz inne und drücke die Kurzhanteln dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1624.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1624.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cb5b7899-cd86-5a0d-b291-a8598af09de6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Fly', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Fly', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Extend your arms straight down in front of you, palms facing each other. Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arms straight down in front of you, palms facing each other.","Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir nach unten, Handflächen zueinander.","Halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt und hebe die Arme seitlich an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0383.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0383.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d6a1753f-ce61-5416-b1c5-638f7fb90de6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Grip Incline Bench One Arm Row', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern im Untergriff auf der Schrägbank, einarmig', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Place a dumbbell on the floor next to the bench. Stand facing the bench with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend at the waist and place your left knee and left hand on the bench for support. Pick up the dumbbell with your right hand using a reverse grip (palm facing down). Keep your back straight and your core engaged. Pull the dumbbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body. Squeeze your back muscles at the top of the movement. Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position in a controlled manner. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions. Switch sides and repeat the exercise with your left arm.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Place a dumbbell on the floor next to the bench.","Stand facing the bench with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend at the waist and place your left knee and left hand on the bench for support.","Pick up the dumbbell with your right hand using a reverse grip (palm facing down).","Keep your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull the dumbbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Squeeze your back muscles at the top of the movement.","Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position in a controlled manner.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.","Switch sides and repeat the exercise with your left arm."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank im 45-Grad-Winkel auf.","Lege eine Kurzhantel neben der Bank auf den Boden.","Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen mit dem Gesicht zur Bank.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte und stütze das linke Knie und die linke Hand auf der Bank ab.","Nimm die Kurzhantel mit der rechten Hand im umgekehrten Griff (Handfläche nach unten).","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Kurzhantel Richtung Brust hoch, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper.","Spanne die Rückenmuskeln am oberen Punkt der Bewegung an.","Senke die Kurzhantel kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen.","Wechsle die Seite und wiederhole die Übung mit dem linken Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1330.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1330.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9fae3d47-8636-563d-b34a-f7bf3f13ec1d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Grip Incline Bench Two Arm Row', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern im Untergriff auf der Schrägbank, beidarmig', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Sit on the bench with your chest against the backrest and your feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip. Lean forward and let your arms hang straight down, fully extended. Pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the bench with your chest against the backrest and your feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip.","Lean forward and let your arms hang straight down, fully extended.","Pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank im 45-Grad-Winkel auf.","Setze dich auf die Bank, die Brust an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Untergriff.","Lehne dich nach vorne und lass die Arme gerade herabhängen, vollständig gestreckt.","Ziehe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Brust hoch und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1331.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1331.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('9fc9614f-d11c-5906-b101-776abcb48c86', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Grip Row (Female)', 'Kurzhantel-Rudern im Untergriff (Frauen)', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing your body. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Let your arms hang straight down, fully extended, with a slight bend in your elbows. Pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing your body.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Let your arms hang straight down, fully extended, with a slight bend in your elbows.","Pull the dumbbells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff, Handflächen zum Körper.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Lass die Arme gerade herabhängen, vollständig gestreckt, die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Ziehe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Brust hoch und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2327.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2327.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e2c83fe3-26e0-5867-804f-60bffae716e0', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse-Scott-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher bench with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against the support. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells as you contract your biceps. Continue to curl the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher bench with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against the support.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells as you contract your biceps.","Continue to curl the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Scott-Bank, die Oberarme auf dem Polster, die Brust an der Stütze.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhanteln hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Ziehe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0384.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0384.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('af54c2a6-84ab-53cf-973f-46facadbd7e5', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Spider Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse-Spider-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body and arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body and arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe sind.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1675.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1675.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d697a14a-e663-544d-afe8-2a0496d85b56', NULL, 'Dumbbell Reverse Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Handgelenk-Curl', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing down. Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge. Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the dumbbells towards your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing down.","Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge.","Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the dumbbells towards your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff, Handflächen nach unten.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Oberschenkel, die Handgelenke hängen über die Kante.","Ziehe die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und führe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Körper.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0385.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0385.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5de2aed5-d085-55c6-9db5-7247bd1d8182', NULL, 'Dumbbell Romanian Deadlift', 'Kurzhantel-Rumänisches Kreuzheben', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing your knees to bend slightly. Lower the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, then push through your heels and engage your glutes to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing your knees to bend slightly.","Lower the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, then push through your heels and engage your glutes to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, beuge dich in der Hüfte und senke die Kurzhanteln Richtung Boden ab, die Knie beugen sich dabei leicht.","Senke die Kurzhanteln, bis du eine Dehnung in den Beinbeugern spürst, drücke dich dann durch die Fersen ab und spanne das Gesäss an, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1459.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1459.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('71bc4f09-9291-5730-a315-5b1f37d80875', NULL, 'Dumbbell Rotation Reverse Fly', 'Kurzhantel-Reverse Fly mit Rotation', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor. Rotate your arms so that your palms are facing downwards. Slowly lower your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows, until they are parallel to the floor.","Rotate your arms so that your palms are facing downwards.","Slowly lower your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreiten Füssen, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach innen.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust raus.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Drehe die Arme, sodass die Handflächen nach unten zeigen.","Senke die Arme langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0386.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0386.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('60ecb90b-bec0-5bcb-ad80-186be23d1f67', NULL, 'Dumbbell Scott Press', 'Kurzhantel-Scott-Drücken', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, die Ellbogen gebeugt, die Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2397.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2397.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('775f3884-db94-5eac-886c-d7f6cdb37f04', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Alternate Front Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Frontheben im Sitzen, wechselseitig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and arms extended down by your sides. Keeping your arms straight, raise one dumbbell in front of you until it is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat with the other arm. Alternate between arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","biceps"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and arms extended down by your sides.","Keeping your arms straight, raise one dumbbell in front of you until it is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat with the other arm.","Alternate between arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper, Arme neben dem Körper nach unten gestreckt.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und hebe eine Kurzhantel vor dir an, bis sie parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle den Arm fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0387.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0387.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('23fe779d-e778-570c-8bc7-396426c8a363', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Alternate Hammer Curl on Exercise Ball', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball, wechselseitig', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and your arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl one dumbbell up towards your shoulder while keeping your palm facing your body. Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat the movement with the opposite arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and your arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl one dumbbell up towards your shoulder while keeping your palm facing your body.","Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat the movement with the opposite arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, Füsse flach am Boden, Rücken gerade.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und ziehe eine Kurzhantel Richtung Schulter hoch, die Handfläche bleibt zum Körper gerichtet.","Ziehe die Kurzhantel weiter, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und die Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe ist.","Halte die kontrahierte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle den Arm fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1676.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1676.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b0b73d33-114b-5a9a-b1ee-9f951b6d28f6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Alternate Press', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken im Sitzen, wechselseitig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward. Press one dumbbell up overhead, fully extending your arm. Lower the dumbbell back down to shoulder height. Repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward.","Press one dumbbell up overhead, fully extending your arm.","Lower the dumbbell back down to shoulder height.","Repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, die Ellbogen gebeugt, die Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke eine Kurzhantel über Kopf, der Arm wird vollständig gestreckt.","Senke die Kurzhantel zurück auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle den Arm fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0388.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0388.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3d07af9c-d9aa-58ca-b036-07d83901ba02', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Alternate Shoulder', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken im Sitzen, wechselseitig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards, and raise them to shoulder height. Press one dumbbell up overhead while keeping the other dumbbell at shoulder height. Lower the raised dumbbell back to shoulder height while simultaneously pressing the other dumbbell up overhead. Continue alternating between arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards, and raise them to shoulder height.","Press one dumbbell up overhead while keeping the other dumbbell at shoulder height.","Lower the raised dumbbell back to shoulder height while simultaneously pressing the other dumbbell up overhead.","Continue alternating between arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach innen, und hebe sie auf Schulterhöhe.","Drücke eine Kurzhantel über Kopf, während die andere auf Schulterhöhe bleibt.","Senke die gedrückte Kurzhantel zurück auf Schulterhöhe ab, während du gleichzeitig die andere über Kopf drückst.","Wechsle den Arm fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3546.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3546.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('abe33803-d5df-5fe7-9d4a-6603df1ac9cb', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Bench Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Extension im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up above your head. Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your elbows close to your ears. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up above your head.","Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your elbows close to your ears.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über den Kopf.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf ab, die Ellbogen bleiben nah an den Ohren.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0389.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0389.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('09d388b1-ccb4-56bc-92a1-965236afeeb2', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Bent Arm Lateral Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben mit gebeugten Armen im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and your arms bent at a 90-degree angle. Keeping your elbows bent, raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body and your arms bent at a 90-degree angle.","Keeping your elbows bent, raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, Rücken gerade, Füsse flach am Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper, Arme im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, die Ellbogen bleiben gebeugt, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte am oberen Punkt kurz inne und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2317.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2317.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7fd52f4-2f88-54bb-b33d-f1aae170e172', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Bent Over Alternate Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Kickback vorgebeugt im Sitzen, wechselseitig', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground. Extend one arm straight back, keeping it close to your body, until your arm is fully extended. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","back"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inwards.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground.","Extend one arm straight back, keeping it close to your body, until your arm is fully extended.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank, in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach innen.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade und parallel zum Boden.","Strecke einen Arm gerade nach hinten, nah am Körper, bis der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist.","Halte kurz inne und senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle den Arm fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1730.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1730.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9ae023e5-50f0-5003-861c-d2384581ce2d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Bent Over Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken vorgebeugt im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your head up. Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your head. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","back"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your head up.","Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your head.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und den Kopf oben.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach hinten und halte die Ellbogen nah am Kopf.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1737.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1737.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4b44d499-b44e-5ad1-908f-2361217d274a', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up. Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your torso. Exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up.","Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your torso.","Exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper.","Atme aus und curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1677.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1677.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('aa491765-6a26-5ad1-b79f-a4a4211810dd', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Biceps Curl (on Stability Ball)', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl im Sitzen (auf dem Gymnastikball)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing forward and your arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing forward and your arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbells while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhanteln hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0390.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0390.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('65b5528f-81f9-5ff9-95f6-f4faa514a673', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Biceps Curl to Shoulder Press', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl mit Schulterdrücken im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing forward and arms fully extended. Keeping your elbows close to your sides, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders. Once your forearms are vertical, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing forward. Press the dumbbells overhead until your arms are fully extended. Lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position by reversing the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing forward and arms fully extended.","Keeping your elbows close to your sides, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders.","Once your forearms are vertical, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing forward.","Press the dumbbells overhead until your arms are fully extended.","Lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position by reversing the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper und curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch.","Sobald die Unterarme senkrecht stehen, drehe die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen nach vorne zeigen.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln über den Kopf, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Senke die Kurzhanteln in umgekehrter Bewegungsreihenfolge zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3547.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3547.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8ecf6151-671a-5bb0-a90b-31a709e59905', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Calf Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben im Sitzen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your thighs. Place the balls of your feet on a raised surface such as a step or block, with your heels hanging off the edge. Hold onto the dumbbell for stability. Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your thighs.","Place the balls of your feet on a raised surface such as a step or block, with your heels hanging off the edge.","Hold onto the dumbbell for stability.","Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Stelle die Fussballen auf eine erhöhte Fläche wie eine Stufe oder einen Block, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Halte die Kurzhantel zur Stabilisierung fest.","Hebe die Fersen so hoch wie möglich und verlagere dein Körpergewicht auf die Fussballen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1379.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1379.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bc288a5d-078d-5506-b07d-4d4f073f9680', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Curl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your torso. Exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your torso.","Exhale and curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper.","Atme aus und curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0391.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0391.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cd28a4b1-98fb-5c8f-8495-ba65894bc5ec', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Front Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Frontheben im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs. Keep your back straight and core engaged. Raise the dumbbells in front of you, with your palms facing down, until they are at shoulder level. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","biceps"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs.","Keep your back straight and core engaged.","Raise the dumbbells in front of you, with your palms facing down, until they are at shoulder level.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln vor dir an, Handflächen nach unten, bis sie sich auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0392.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0392.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b198066f-0350-59a6-933d-6023c13ea395', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Hammer Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso and arms extended straight down. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso and arms extended straight down.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet, Arme gerade nach unten gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Gewichte hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1678.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1678.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ea56a6d1-9404-5ec6-8c20-c7f5344154ae', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Inner Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Innen-Bizepscurl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up. Rest your upper arms on your thighs, allowing the dumbbells to hang down. Keeping your upper arms stationary, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up.","Rest your upper arms on your thighs, allowing the dumbbells to hang down.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Oberarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die Kurzhanteln nach unten hängen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und curle die Kurzhanteln durch Anspannen des Bizeps zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0393.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0393.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a2283e41-734b-5f88-9b01-7af4450281d3', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Kickback im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight. Bring your upper arms close to your sides and keep your elbows bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your arms straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight.","Bring your upper arms close to your sides and keep your elbows bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your arms straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und lehne dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Bringe die Oberarme nah an den Körper und halte die Ellbogen in einem 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach hinten und spanne am Ende der Bewegung den Trizeps an.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0394.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0394.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('71506b90-5bc7-546d-b67a-dc1c4d515ca9', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Lateral Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs. Keep your back straight and core engaged. Raise the dumbbells to your sides with a slight bend in your elbows, until your arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs.","Keep your back straight and core engaged.","Raise the dumbbells to your sides with a slight bend in your elbows, until your arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln seitlich an, mit leicht gebeugten Ellbogen, bis die Arme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0396.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0396.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e8af6271-cb58-549b-8a02-f864979fa0c8', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Lateral Raise V. 2', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben im Sitzen (Variante 2)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs. Keep your back straight and core engaged. Raise the dumbbells to your sides with a slight bend in your elbows, until your arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","triceps"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs.","Keep your back straight and core engaged.","Raise the dumbbells to your sides with a slight bend in your elbows, until your arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln seitlich an, mit leicht gebeugten Ellbogen, bis die Arme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0395.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0395.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('857b4112-3100-5f7a-b88e-83f12d867cd5', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Neutral Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenkscurl im Sitzen (neutraler Griff)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing the dumbbells to hang down. Keeping your wrists in a neutral position, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing the dumbbells to hang down.","Keeping your wrists in a neutral position, curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die Kurzhanteln nach unten hängen.","Halte die Handgelenke in neutraler Position und curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0397.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0397.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d571b2a1-e399-5789-8002-bfe4cfd54808', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Arm Biceps Curl on Exercise Ball with Leg Raised', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl einarmig im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball mit angehobenem Bein', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm fully extended. Place your other hand on your hip for stability. Slowly curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your bicep. Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions. Switch arms and repeat the exercise.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing up and your arm fully extended.","Place your other hand on your hip for stability.","Slowly curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your bicep.","Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.","Switch arms and repeat the exercise."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach oben, Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Lege die andere Hand zur Stabilisierung auf die Hüfte.","Curle die Kurzhantel langsam zur Schulter hoch, während der Oberarm ruhig bleibt.","Halte am oberen Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen.","Wechsle die Seite und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1679.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1679.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b79a9d5b-ba2f-5806-88dd-f2bca775ad40', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Arm Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Kickback einarmig im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand. Bend your torso forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground. Extend your arm straight back, keeping your elbow close to your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand.","Bend your torso forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground.","Extend your arm straight back, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Beuge den Oberkörper in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und parallel zum Boden.","Strecke den Arm gerade nach hinten und halte den Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, dann wechsle den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0398.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0398.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b5bd859c-8628-509a-aed4-a760cb7e7842', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Arm Rotate', 'Kurzhantel-Unterarmrotation einarmig im Sitzen', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and hold a dumbbell in one hand, resting it on your thigh. Raise the dumbbell up to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body. Rotate your forearm outward, away from your body, while keeping your upper arm stationary. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly rotate your forearm back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","biceps"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and hold a dumbbell in one hand, resting it on your thigh.","Raise the dumbbell up to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Rotate your forearm outward, away from your body, while keeping your upper arm stationary.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly rotate your forearm back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und lege eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf den Oberschenkel.","Hebe die Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe an und halte den Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Drehe den Unterarm nach aussen, vom Körper weg, während der Oberarm ruhig bleibt.","Halte oben kurz inne, drehe den Unterarm dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0399.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0399.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b9462e4c-e155-5fff-9543-0a1156e52d9f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Leg Calf Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben einbeinig im Sitzen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your right thigh. Extend your left leg straight out in front of you, keeping your foot flexed. Place the ball of your right foot on an elevated surface, such as a step or weight plate. Using your calf muscles, raise your right heel as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your right thigh.","Extend your left leg straight out in front of you, keeping your foot flexed.","Place the ball of your right foot on an elevated surface, such as a step or weight plate.","Using your calf muscles, raise your right heel as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege eine Kurzhantel auf den rechten Oberschenkel.","Strecke das linke Bein gerade nach vorne aus und halte den Fuss angezogen.","Stelle den Ballen des rechten Fusses auf eine erhöhte Fläche, zum Beispiel eine Stufe oder Gewichtsscheibe.","Hebe die rechte Ferse mit der Wadenmuskulatur so hoch wie möglich an.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Ferse dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0400.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0400.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('087c9224-09e0-5906-81bf-4bc202161186', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Leg Calf Raise - Hammer Grip', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben einbeinig im Sitzen (Hammergriff)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your thighs. Place one foot on a raised surface, such as a step or block, with your heel hanging off the edge. Hold the dumbbell with a hammer grip, meaning your palms are facing each other and your fingers are wrapped around the handle. Keeping your core engaged and your back straight, slowly raise your heel as high as possible by pushing through the ball of your foot. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and a dumbbell resting on your thighs.","Place one foot on a raised surface, such as a step or block, with your heel hanging off the edge.","Hold the dumbbell with a hammer grip, meaning your palms are facing each other and your fingers are wrapped around the handle.","Keeping your core engaged and your back straight, slowly raise your heel as high as possible by pushing through the ball of your foot.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und lege eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Stelle einen Fuss auf eine erhöhte Fläche wie eine Stufe oder einen Block, die Ferse hängt über die Kante hinaus.","Halte die Kurzhantel im Hammergriff, das heisst die Handflächen zeigen zueinander und die Finger umschliessen den Griff.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, halte den Rücken gerade und hebe die Ferse langsam so hoch wie möglich, indem du dich über den Fussballen abdrückst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Ferse dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1380.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1380.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ba1ff4b5-7163-5fbe-b7ea-cb9cbab8dc72', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated One Leg Calf Raise - Palm Up', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben einbeinig im Sitzen (Handfläche oben)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench or chair with your back straight and your feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place it on top of your thigh, palm facing up. Lift one leg off the ground and extend it in front of you, keeping your knee slightly bent. Raise your heel as high as possible by pushing through the ball of your foot. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Sit on a bench or chair with your back straight and your feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place it on top of your thigh, palm facing up.","Lift one leg off the ground and extend it in front of you, keeping your knee slightly bent.","Raise your heel as high as possible by pushing through the ball of your foot.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank oder einen Stuhl, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand und lege sie auf den Oberschenkel, Handfläche nach oben.","Hebe ein Bein vom Boden ab und strecke es vor dir aus, das Knie bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Hebe die Ferse so hoch wie möglich an, indem du dich über den Fussballen abdrückst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Ferse dann langsam wieder ab.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, wechsle dann das Bein und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1381.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1381.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3c8f8490-12ed-5ebf-bf4f-1f73e642fe03', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Palms Up Wrist Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Handgelenkscurl im Sitzen (Handflächen oben)', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up. Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge. Slowly curl your wrists upward, squeezing your forearms at the top of the movement. Pause for a moment, then lower your wrists back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up.","Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge.","Slowly curl your wrists upward, squeezing your forearms at the top of the movement.","Pause for a moment, then lower your wrists back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die Handgelenke über die Kante hinausragen.","Curle die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und spanne am Ende der Bewegung die Unterarme an.","Halte kurz inne und senke die Handgelenke dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0401.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0401.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e1f94ad4-379a-58ec-8032-d4ccd7238887', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Scott-Curl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher curl bench with your feet flat on the floor. Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your upper arm against the preacher pad. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher curl bench with your feet flat on the floor.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand with an underhand grip, resting your upper arm against the preacher pad.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Scott-Bank und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Untergriff und lege den Oberarm auf die Polster der Scott-Bank.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel zur Schulter hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0402.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0402.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d1b53517-5678-580d-875d-76fe44272515', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Reverse Grip Concentration Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Konzentrationscurl im Sitzen (Obergriff)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up. Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up.","Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach oben.","Stütze den Ellbogen auf der Innenseite des Oberschenkels ab, knapp über dem Knie.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel zur Schulter hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0403.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0403.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fe37f94d-6b1f-510f-a99c-4cbc90c9e29a', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Reverse Grip One Arm Overhead Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Überkopf-Trizepsstrecken einarmig im Sitzen (Obergriff)', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell with an underhand grip and extend your arm straight up overhead. Lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm stationary. Pause for a moment, then extend your arm back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell with an underhand grip and extend your arm straight up overhead.","Lower the dumbbell behind your head by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arm back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel im Untergriff und strecke den Arm gerade über den Kopf.","Senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf, indem du den Ellbogen beugst, während der Oberarm ruhig bleibt.","Halte kurz inne und strecke den Arm dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1738.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1738.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2beaf071-2c8b-589b-8860-10b51132081b', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Shoulder Press', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, resting on your thighs.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank und lege in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf die Oberschenkel.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0405.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0405.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fbf2b2a1-58d4-5afa-9456-ca997e4beed8', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Shoulder Press (Parallel Grip)', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterdrücken im Sitzen (paralleler Griff)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inward. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, elbows bent and palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing inward.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, elbows bent and palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, Ellbogen gebeugt, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0404.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0404.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('69b7ffe8-183d-5387-9275-f8e1af05b44f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Seated Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up overhead. Bend your elbows and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arms close to your ears. Pause for a moment, then straighten your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up overhead.","Bend your elbows and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arms close to your ears.","Pause for a moment, then straighten your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über den Kopf.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf, die Oberarme bleiben nah an den Ohren.","Halte kurz inne, strecke die Arme dann wieder und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2188.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2188.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8160f25e-3c13-5a29-acd7-be7fa8a661e1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Shrug', 'Kurzhantel-Schulterheben', 'back', 'traps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Keep your arms straight and let the dumbbells hang by your sides. Raise your shoulders as high as possible, as if you are trying to touch your ears with your shoulders. Hold the contraction for a second, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Keep your arms straight and let the dumbbells hang by your sides.","Raise your shoulders as high as possible, as if you are trying to touch your ears with your shoulders.","Hold the contraction for a second, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und lass die Kurzhanteln seitlich am Körper hängen.","Hebe die Schultern so hoch wie möglich an, als wolltest du mit den Schultern die Ohren berühren.","Halte die Anspannung eine Sekunde, senke die Schultern dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0406.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0406.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('805e00c2-a421-559d-9932-34c70230cd3e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Side Bend', 'Kurzhantel-Seitbeuge', 'waist', 'abs', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, letting it hang down by your side. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, slowly bend sideways at the waist towards the opposite side of the dumbbell, lowering the weight as far as you comfortably can. Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, letting it hang down by your side.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, slowly bend sideways at the waist towards the opposite side of the dumbbell, lowering the weight as far as you comfortably can.","Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, seitlich am Körper hängend.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, beuge dich langsam seitlich zur gegenüberliegenden Seite der Kurzhantel und senke das Gewicht so weit ab, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0407.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0407.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b69f4ca1-bc4e-5eaf-b255-5f717bec3564', NULL, 'Dumbbell Side Lying One Hand Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Seitheben im Seitliegen (einarmig)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Lie on your side with your legs extended and your head supported by your arm. Hold a dumbbell in your top hand with your palm facing down. Keeping your arm straight, raise the dumbbell up to shoulder height. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs extended and your head supported by your arm.","Hold a dumbbell in your top hand with your palm facing down.","Keeping your arm straight, raise the dumbbell up to shoulder height.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, strecke die Beine aus und stütze den Kopf mit dem Arm ab.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in der oberen Hand, Handfläche nach unten.","Halte den Arm gestreckt und hebe die Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0408.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0408.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e44f4cb5-2176-5c7e-92a4-82175262dd38', NULL, 'Dumbbell Side Plank with Rear Fly', 'Kurzhantel-Seitplank mit rückwärtigen Fliegenden', 'back', 'upper back', 'dumbbell', 'Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other. Place your forearm on the ground directly below your shoulder, keeping your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a dumbbell in your top hand, with your arm extended straight down towards the ground. Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your heels. While maintaining the side plank position, lift the dumbbell up towards the ceiling, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other.","Place your forearm on the ground directly below your shoulder, keeping your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a dumbbell in your top hand, with your arm extended straight down towards the ground.","Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your heels.","While maintaining the side plank position, lift the dumbbell up towards the ceiling, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, strecke die Beine aus und lege sie übereinander.","Stelle den Unterarm direkt unter der Schulter auf den Boden, der Ellbogen bleibt im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in der oberen Hand, der Arm ist gerade nach unten zum Boden gestreckt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Hebe in der Seitstütz-Position die Kurzhantel zur Decke und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Senke die Kurzhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3664.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3664.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7b1cffcc-64fe-5f3a-ac1a-2d985e9ac7d1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Arm Overhead Carry', 'Kurzhantel-Überkopftragen einarmig', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand. Raise the dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm. Engage your core and keep your back straight as you walk forward, maintaining the dumbbell overhead. Continue walking for the desired distance or time. Switch hands and repeat the exercise.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","core"]', '["Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand.","Raise the dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm.","Engage your core and keep your back straight as you walk forward, maintaining the dumbbell overhead.","Continue walking for the desired distance or time.","Switch hands and repeat the exercise."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Hebe die Kurzhantel über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken gerade, während du nach vorne gehst und die Kurzhantel über dem Kopf hältst.","Gehe die gewünschte Distanz oder Zeit weiter.","Wechsle die Hand und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3548.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3548.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e9b0d02e-c816-52df-ae57-a3bd0ca3eca1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Leg Calf Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben einbeinig', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand on the edge of a step or platform with your heels hanging off and your toes on the step. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place your other hand on a wall or railing for support. Raise your heel as high as possible, lifting your body up onto your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down below the step. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles"]', '["Stand on the edge of a step or platform with your heels hanging off and your toes on the step.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and place your other hand on a wall or railing for support.","Raise your heel as high as possible, lifting your body up onto your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down below the step.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg."]', '["Stell dich an den Rand einer Stufe oder Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei, die Zehen stehen auf der Stufe.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand und stütze dich mit der anderen an einer Wand oder einem Geländer ab.","Hebe die Ferse so hoch wie möglich an und hebe den Körper auf die Zehenspitzen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Ferse dann langsam unter das Niveau der Stufe ab.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0409.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0409.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bffec48b-5b17-5f99-9dfc-cc9364d1022b', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Leg Deadlift', 'Kurzhantel-Kreuzheben einbeinig', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a dumbbell in your right hand. Shift your weight onto your left leg and lift your right foot slightly off the ground. Keeping your back straight, hinge forward at the hips and lower the dumbbell towards the ground. At the same time, extend your right leg straight behind you, maintaining a slight bend in your left knee. Lower the dumbbell until your torso and right leg are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then engage your glutes and hamstrings to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a dumbbell in your right hand.","Shift your weight onto your left leg and lift your right foot slightly off the ground.","Keeping your back straight, hinge forward at the hips and lower the dumbbell towards the ground.","At the same time, extend your right leg straight behind you, maintaining a slight bend in your left knee.","Lower the dumbbell until your torso and right leg are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then engage your glutes and hamstrings to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich hüftbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand.","Verlagere das Gewicht auf das linke Bein und hebe den rechten Fuss leicht vom Boden ab.","Halte den Rücken gerade, beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne und senke die Kurzhantel Richtung Boden.","Strecke gleichzeitig das rechte Bein gerade nach hinten aus, das linke Knie bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhantel, bis Oberkörper und rechtes Bein parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und kehre durch Anspannen von Gesäss und Beinbeugern in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1757.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1757.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a702d1b0-eafd-506f-b5b7-494f5d676370', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Leg Deadlift with Stepbox Support', 'Kurzhantel-Kreuzheben einbeinig mit Stepbox-Unterstützung', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a dumbbell in your right hand. Place your left foot on a stepbox or elevated surface behind you. Keeping your back straight and core engaged, hinge forward at the hips, lowering the dumbbell towards the ground. As you lower the dumbbell, simultaneously lift your left leg behind you, maintaining a straight line from head to heel. Lower the dumbbell until you feel a stretch in your right hamstring, then return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a dumbbell in your right hand.","Place your left foot on a stepbox or elevated surface behind you.","Keeping your back straight and core engaged, hinge forward at the hips, lowering the dumbbell towards the ground.","As you lower the dumbbell, simultaneously lift your left leg behind you, maintaining a straight line from head to heel.","Lower the dumbbell until you feel a stretch in your right hamstring, then return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich hüftbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand.","Stelle den linken Fuss auf eine Stepbox oder erhöhte Fläche hinter dir.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne und senke die Kurzhantel Richtung Boden.","Hebe beim Absenken der Kurzhantel gleichzeitig das linke Bein nach hinten an, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Senke die Kurzhantel, bis du eine Dehnung im rechten Beinbeuger spürst, und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2805.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2805.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('60f1589a-9c7b-52b4-979f-64c9837f71da', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Leg Split Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Split-Kniebeuge einbeinig', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Take a step forward with one foot and position your feet so that your front foot is flat on the ground and your back foot is elevated on a bench or step. Lower your body by bending your front knee and hip, keeping your back knee slightly bent and your back heel off the ground. Continue lowering until your front thigh is parallel to the ground, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Take a step forward with one foot and position your feet so that your front foot is flat on the ground and your back foot is elevated on a bench or step.","Lower your body by bending your front knee and hip, keeping your back knee slightly bent and your back heel off the ground.","Continue lowering until your front thigh is parallel to the ground, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Mache mit einem Fuss einen Schritt nach vorne und positioniere dich so, dass der vordere Fuss flach auf dem Boden steht und der hintere Fuss auf einer Bank oder Stufe erhöht liegt.","Senke den Körper, indem du das vordere Knie und die Hüfte beugst, das hintere Knie bleibt leicht gebeugt und die hintere Ferse vom Boden abgehoben.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis der vordere Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden ist, und drücke dich dann über die vordere Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, wechsle dann das Bein und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0410.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0410.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ff777a9c-c28e-520e-984f-46d3bb94c167', NULL, 'Dumbbell Single Leg Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Kniebeuge einbeinig', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Extend one leg forward and keep it off the ground throughout the exercise. Bend your standing leg and lower your body down as if sitting back into a chair. Keep your chest up and your back straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Extend one leg forward and keep it off the ground throughout the exercise.","Bend your standing leg and lower your body down as if sitting back into a chair.","Keep your chest up and your back straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Strecke ein Bein nach vorne aus und halte es während der gesamten Übung vom Boden abgehoben.","Beuge das Standbein und senke den Körper ab, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte die Brust oben und den Rücken gerade.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0411.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0411.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('b1574b20-dae8-5d9c-a143-635cc1cdfec4', NULL, 'Dumbbell Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides. Keeping your chest up and core engaged, lower your body down by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides.","Keeping your chest up and core engaged, lower your body down by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel seitlich am Körper.","Halte die Brust oben und die Körpermitte angespannt, senke den Körper durch Beugen von Knien und Hüfte ab, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0413.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0413.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9059090f-14a5-5576-b4b7-0003e096851c', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Alternate Hammer Curl and Press', 'Kurzhantel-Hammercurl mit Drücken im Wechsel stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your back straight. Exhale and curl the dumbbell in your right hand towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary. Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat the curl with your left hand. After completing the curl with your left hand, exhale and press the dumbbell in your right hand overhead. Extend your arm fully and hold for a moment at the top. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat the press with your left hand. Continue alternating between curls and presses for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your back straight.","Exhale and curl the dumbbell in your right hand towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat the curl with your left hand.","After completing the curl with your left hand, exhale and press the dumbbell in your right hand overhead.","Extend your arm fully and hold for a moment at the top.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat the press with your left hand.","Continue alternating between curls and presses for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper und den Rücken gerade.","Atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand zur Schulter hoch, der Oberarm bleibt ruhig.","Hebe die Kurzhantel weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hantel auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole den Curl mit der linken Hand.","Atme nach dem Curl mit der linken Hand aus und drücke die Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand über den Kopf.","Strecke den Arm vollständig und halte oben kurz inne.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole den Press mit der linken Hand.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter zwischen Curls und Press ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3560.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3560.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fcd2336f-e832-5673-83b0-450c780ca248', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Alternate Overhead Press', 'Kurzhantel-Überkopfdrücken im Wechsel stehend', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward. Press one dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm. Lower the dumbbell back to shoulder level. Repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward.","Press one dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm.","Lower the dumbbell back to shoulder level.","Repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke eine Kurzhantel über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Senke die Kurzhantel zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0414.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0414.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dde12226-24c1-5edb-b9f5-41273b8bc60f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Alternate Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Heben im Wechsel stehend', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Keep your back straight and your core engaged. Raise one dumbbell to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down. Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat with the other arm. Alternate between arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Keep your back straight and your core engaged.","Raise one dumbbell to the side, keeping your arm straight and your palm facing down.","Continue lifting until your arm is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat with the other arm.","Alternate between arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Hebe eine Kurzhantel seitlich an, der Arm bleibt gestreckt, Handfläche nach unten.","Hebe weiter an, bis der Arm parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen zwischen den Armen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0415.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0415.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5879edcc-e6c3-5e2b-9f48-e55e15a6281f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Alternating Triceps Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Kickback im Wechsel stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat with the other arm, alternating sides with each repetition.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat with the other arm, alternating sides with each repetition."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach hinten und halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm und wechsle bei jeder Wiederholung die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1739.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1739.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6804a902-57f2-5e86-b919-27c559911d50', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Around the World', 'Kurzhantel-Around the World stehend', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Extend your arms straight out to the sides at shoulder height, palms facing down. Keeping your arms straight, slowly rotate your arms in a circular motion, bringing the dumbbells in front of your body and then overhead. Continue the circular motion, bringing the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Extend your arms straight out to the sides at shoulder height, palms facing down.","Keeping your arms straight, slowly rotate your arms in a circular motion, bringing the dumbbells in front of your body and then overhead.","Continue the circular motion, bringing the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Strecke die Arme seitlich auf Schulterhöhe aus, Handflächen nach unten.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und drehe sie langsam kreisförmig, sodass die Kurzhanteln vor dem Körper und dann über den Kopf geführt werden.","Führe die Kreisbewegung weiter aus, bis die Kurzhanteln wieder in die Ausgangsposition zurückkehren.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2143.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2143.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('12a125f7-4233-5fab-81c2-2c04b67e2cca', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Bent Over One Arm Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken vorgebeugt einarmig stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground. Extend your arm straight back, keeping your elbow close to your body. Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and parallel to the ground.","Extend your arm straight back, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und parallel zum Boden.","Strecke den Arm gerade nach hinten und halte den Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1740.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1740.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('95fcda82-0da3-5de1-93c5-e0f160fe9123', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Bent Over Two Arm Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken vorgebeugt beidarmig stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent. Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your body. Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent.","Extend your arms straight back, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach hinten und halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1741.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1741.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('692c698a-b8a1-5700-80b1-90abc3316849', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Bizepscurl stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward and arms fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward and arms fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne, Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Gewichte hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0416.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0416.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8a382154-eb36-5af6-8f04-0429e5f03d70', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Calf Raise', 'Kurzhantel-Wadenheben stehend', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand. Raise your heels off the ground as high as possible, using your calves. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand.","Raise your heels off the ground as high as possible, using your calves.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Hebe die Fersen mithilfe der Wadenmuskulatur so hoch wie möglich vom Boden ab.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0417.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0417.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d485e054-cf0a-5c08-999b-aca0002ca209', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Concentration Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Konzentrationscurl stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, with your arm fully extended and palm facing inwards. Place your opposite hand on your thigh for support. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, with your arm fully extended and palm facing inwards.","Place your opposite hand on your thigh for support.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, der Arm ist vollständig gestreckt, Handfläche nach innen gerichtet.","Stütze die andere Hand auf dem Oberschenkel ab.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel durch Anspannen des Bizeps zur Schulter hoch.","Hebe die Kurzhantel weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hantel auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0418.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0418.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('46abafa0-9c63-5fdc-9337-d132a7e96555', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Front Raise Above Head', 'Kurzhantel-Frontheben über Kopf stehend', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Keep your arms straight and lift the dumbbells in front of you, raising them above your head. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Keep your arms straight and lift the dumbbells in front of you, raising them above your head.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und hebe die Kurzhanteln vor dir bis über den Kopf.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0419.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0419.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3ba29c5c-530a-58bc-9b25-654f64399eb6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Inner Biceps Curl V. 2', 'Kurzhantel-Innen-Bizepscurl stehend (Variante 2)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso. Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate the palms of your hands until they are facing forward. While holding your upper arms stationary, curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Slowly begin to bring the dumbbells back to the starting position as your breathe in. Repeat for the recommended amount of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your torso.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate the palms of your hands until they are facing forward.","While holding your upper arms stationary, curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Slowly begin to bring the dumbbells back to the starting position as your breathe in.","Repeat for the recommended amount of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Oberkörper gerichtet.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper und drehe die Handflächen, bis sie nach vorne zeigen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und curle die Gewichte hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Gewichte weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und bringe die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die empfohlene Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2321.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2321.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('70b3a755-6839-55c3-b2c4-b4d2e66c4994', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Kickback', 'Kurzhantel-Kickback stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Extend your arms straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arms straight back, squeezing your triceps at the top of the movement.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach hinten und spanne am Ende der Bewegung den Trizeps an.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0420.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0420.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5311b747-2402-509a-89b8-c028360ff4b9', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Concentration Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Konzentrationscurl einarmig stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up. Place your free hand on your thigh for support. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand, palm facing up.","Place your free hand on your thigh for support.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach oben.","Stütze die freie Hand auf dem Oberschenkel ab.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel durch Anspannen des Bizeps zur Schulter hoch.","Hebe die Kurzhantel weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hantel auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0421.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0421.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('67de8734-abfc-5dc8-810d-2ad57ca1fc36', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Curl (Over Incline Bench)', 'Kurzhantel-Curl einarmig stehend (über Schrägbank)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing forward. Place your other hand on an incline bench for support. Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand with your palm facing forward.","Place your other hand on an incline bench for support.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, exhale and curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand, Handfläche nach vorne.","Stütze die andere Hand auf einer Schrägbank ab.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig, atme aus und curle die Kurzhantel durch Anspannen des Bizeps zur Schulter hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0422.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0422.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fc6501dc-61b2-52b7-8544-a6025ff9771d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Curl Over Incline Bench', 'Kurzhantel-Curl einarmig stehend über Schrägbank', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand. Place your other hand on an incline bench for support. Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand.","Place your other hand on an incline bench for support.","Keeping your upper arm stationary, curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Stütze die andere Hand auf einer Schrägbank ab.","Halte den Oberarm ruhig und curle die Kurzhantel durch Anspannen des Bizeps zur Schulter hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1680.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1680.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('57fa32f7-6ff6-5bd7-9148-7d4cbc37857e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken einarmig stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand. Raise the dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm. Keep your upper arm close to your head and perpendicular to the ground. Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, bending your elbow. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand.","Raise the dumbbell overhead, fully extending your arm.","Keep your upper arm close to your head and perpendicular to the ground.","Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, bending your elbow.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Hebe die Kurzhantel über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Halte den Oberarm nah am Kopf und senkrecht zum Boden.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf, indem du den Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0423.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0423.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9894184b-0460-54b7-b5dc-b9907bfd7656', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Palm In Press', 'Kurzhantel-Drücken einarmig stehend (Handfläche innen)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder height with your palm facing inwards. Engage your core and keep your back straight. Press the dumbbell upwards until your arm is fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in one hand at shoulder height with your palm facing inwards.","Engage your core and keep your back straight.","Press the dumbbell upwards until your arm is fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe, Handfläche nach innen gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken gerade.","Drücke die Kurzhantel nach oben, bis der Arm vollständig gestreckt ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0424.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0424.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8e5ac951-a868-5fbc-bb7d-0b8aad501ab1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing One Arm Reverse Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverscurl einarmig stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip. Keep your arm fully extended and close to your body, with your palm facing down. Slowly curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Keep your arm fully extended and close to your body, with your palm facing down.","Slowly curl the dumbbell up towards your shoulder, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Halte den Arm vollständig gestreckt und nah am Körper, Handfläche nach unten.","Curle die Kurzhantel langsam zur Schulter hoch, während der Oberarm ruhig bleibt.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0425.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0425.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f76e9b87-2ac3-596e-8728-791e3d0fd76c', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Overhead Press', 'Kurzhantel-Überkopfdrücken stehend', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0426.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0426.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1c2fc35c-0ac8-569b-9c38-822be204613d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Palms In Press', 'Kurzhantel-Drücken stehend (Handflächen innen)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing inwards. Keeping your core engaged and your back straight, press the dumbbells upwards until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing inwards.","Keeping your core engaged and your back straight, press the dumbbells upwards until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, halte den Rücken gerade und drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0427.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0427.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6e8a6cff-a5b7-5888-b354-e541a23c9bb6', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Scott-Curl stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Rest the back of your upper arms against the preacher bench or an incline bench, with your elbows slightly bent. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Rest the back of your upper arms against the preacher bench or an incline bench, with your elbows slightly bent.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the dumbbells until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Lege die Rückseite der Oberarme auf die Scott-Bank oder eine Schrägbank, die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Gewichte hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Hanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0428.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0428.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('182ed005-9a47-5032-85e4-c720adf792bf', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Reverse Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Reverscurl stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the weights until your biceps are fully contracted and the dumbbells are at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Gewichte hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst. Hebe die Gewichte weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0429.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0429.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('22e93d81-5f41-56ea-a9a6-a502292462b9', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand. Raise the dumbbell overhead, keeping your arm straight. Bend your elbow and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arm stationary. Extend your arm back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand.","Raise the dumbbell overhead, keeping your arm straight.","Bend your elbow and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arm stationary.","Extend your arm back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Hebe die Kurzhantel über den Kopf, der Arm bleibt gestreckt.","Beuge den Ellbogen und senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf, der Oberarm bleibt ruhig.","Strecke den Arm zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0430.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0430.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('34ef8def-6497-58e7-83fa-daae40e36119', NULL, 'Dumbbell Standing Zottman Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Zottman-Scott-Curl stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Place your upper arms against the preacher bench and keep your elbows slightly bent. Curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders while keeping your upper arms stationary. At the top of the movement, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing downward. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position, rotating your wrists back to the starting position as well. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Place your upper arms against the preacher bench and keep your elbows slightly bent.","Curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders while keeping your upper arms stationary.","At the top of the movement, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing downward.","Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position, rotating your wrists back to the starting position as well.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Lege die Oberarme auf die Scott-Bank und halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch, während die Oberarme ruhig bleiben.","Drehe am Ende der Bewegung die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen nach unten zeigen.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition und drehe die Handgelenke dabei ebenfalls zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2293.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2293.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c110a4ae-831f-5cc3-b591-d03718c1d48e', NULL, 'Dumbbell Step-Up Single Leg Balance with Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Step-up mit Balance einbeinig und Bizepscurl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand in front of a step or platform with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Place your right foot on the step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface. Engage your core and push through your right heel to lift your body up onto the step, bringing your left knee up towards your chest. At the top of the movement, perform a bicep curl by bending your elbows and bringing the dumbbells towards your shoulders. Lower the dumbbells back down and simultaneously lower your left foot back to the ground. Repeat the movement on the opposite side, stepping up with your left foot and curling the dumbbells. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Stand in front of a step or platform with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Place your right foot on the step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface.","Engage your core and push through your right heel to lift your body up onto the step, bringing your left knee up towards your chest.","At the top of the movement, perform a bicep curl by bending your elbows and bringing the dumbbells towards your shoulders.","Lower the dumbbells back down and simultaneously lower your left foot back to the ground.","Repeat the movement on the opposite side, stepping up with your left foot and curling the dumbbells.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich vor eine Stufe oder Plattform und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Stelle den rechten Fuss vollständig auf die Stufe.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, drücke dich über die rechte Ferse ab und hebe den Körper auf die Stufe, während du das linke Knie Richtung Brust ziehst.","Führe am Ende der Bewegung einen Bizeps-Curl aus, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hochziehst.","Senke die Kurzhanteln ab und stelle gleichzeitig den linken Fuss zurück auf den Boden.","Wiederhole die Bewegung auf der anderen Seite, indem du mit dem linken Fuss hochsteigst und die Kurzhanteln curlst.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1684.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1684.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a7357a31-995c-552d-9015-5fbdba51b1b0', NULL, 'Dumbbell Step-Up', 'Kurzhantel-Step-up', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand in front of a bench or step with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Place your right foot on the bench or step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface. Push through your right heel and lift your body up onto the bench or step, straightening your right leg. Bring your left foot up onto the bench or step, standing fully upright. Step back down with your left foot, followed by your right foot, returning to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand in front of a bench or step with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Place your right foot on the bench or step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface.","Push through your right heel and lift your body up onto the bench or step, straightening your right leg.","Bring your left foot up onto the bench or step, standing fully upright.","Step back down with your left foot, followed by your right foot, returning to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stell dich vor eine Bank oder Stufe und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Stelle den rechten Fuss vollständig auf die Bank oder Stufe.","Drücke dich über die rechte Ferse ab, hebe den Körper auf die Bank oder Stufe und strecke das rechte Bein.","Bringe den linken Fuss ebenfalls auf die Bank oder Stufe, sodass du vollständig aufrecht stehst.","Steige mit dem linken Fuss zuerst wieder ab, gefolgt vom rechten Fuss, und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0431.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0431.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c1417f66-1702-5c70-be31-458c5813e346', NULL, 'Dumbbell Step-Up Lunge', 'Kurzhantel-Step-up-Ausfallschritt', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'dumbbell', 'Stand in front of a step or platform with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your sides. Place your right foot on the step, ensuring your entire foot is on the surface. Push through your right heel and lift your body up onto the step, bringing your left foot up as well. Once both feet are on the step, lower your left foot back down to the starting position, keeping your right foot on the step. Repeat the movement, alternating which foot you step up with each time. Continue for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand in front of a step or platform with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your sides.","Place your right foot on the step, ensuring your entire foot is on the surface.","Push through your right heel and lift your body up onto the step, bringing your left foot up as well.","Once both feet are on the step, lower your left foot back down to the starting position, keeping your right foot on the step.","Repeat the movement, alternating which foot you step up with each time.","Continue for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich vor eine Stufe oder Plattform und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zur Seite gerichtet.","Stelle den rechten Fuss vollständig auf die Stufe.","Drücke dich über die rechte Ferse ab, hebe den Körper auf die Stufe und bringe den linken Fuss ebenfalls hoch.","Sobald beide Füsse auf der Stufe stehen, senke den linken Fuss zurück in die Ausgangsposition, der rechte Fuss bleibt auf der Stufe.","Wiederhole die Bewegung und wechsle dabei jedes Mal den Fuss, mit dem du hochsteigst.","Führe die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen aus."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2796.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2796.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('40998d08-d8d9-5066-9651-eec5c5e458a1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Step-Up Split Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Step-up-Split-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'dumbbell', 'Stand in front of a bench or step with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Place your right foot on the bench or step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface. Step up onto the bench or step with your right foot, pushing through your heel to lift your body up. As you step up, simultaneously lift your left knee towards your chest. Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your left foot back to the ground while keeping your right foot on the bench or step. Repeat the movement with your left foot on the bench or step. Continue alternating between your right and left foot for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand in front of a bench or step with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Place your right foot on the bench or step, ensuring your entire foot is in contact with the surface.","Step up onto the bench or step with your right foot, pushing through your heel to lift your body up.","As you step up, simultaneously lift your left knee towards your chest.","Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your left foot back to the ground while keeping your right foot on the bench or step.","Repeat the movement with your left foot on the bench or step.","Continue alternating between your right and left foot for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich vor eine Bank oder Stufe und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Stelle den rechten Fuss vollständig auf die Bank oder Stufe.","Steige mit dem rechten Fuss auf die Bank oder Stufe und drücke dich über die Ferse ab, um den Körper hochzuheben.","Ziehe beim Hochsteigen gleichzeitig das linke Knie Richtung Brust.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und senke den linken Fuss dann langsam zurück auf den Boden, der rechte Fuss bleibt auf der Bank oder Stufe.","Wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem linken Fuss auf der Bank oder Stufe.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter zwischen rechtem und linkem Fuss ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2812.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2812.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5c186c42-8ba0-53bf-885a-100200fcd24f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Stiff Leg Deadlift', 'Kurzhantel-Kreuzheben mit gestreckten Beinen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing a slight bend in your knees. Lower the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, then squeeze your glutes and push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing a slight bend in your knees.","Lower the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, then squeeze your glutes and push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, beuge dich aus der Hüfte und senke die Kurzhanteln Richtung Boden, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln, bis du eine Dehnung in den Beinbeugern spürst, spanne dann das Gesäss an und drücke dich über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0432.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0432.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('370bd422-5de9-5109-9829-c58437898374', NULL, 'Dumbbell Straight Arm Pullover', 'Kurzhantel-Überzug mit gestreckten Armen', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet planted firmly on the ground. Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight above your chest. Keeping your arms straight, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head in an arc-like motion. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'latissimus dorsi', '["latissimus dorsi","triceps"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet planted firmly on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight above your chest.","Keeping your arms straight, slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head in an arc-like motion.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, der Kopf am einen Ende, die Füsse fest auf dem Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und senke die Kurzhantel in einer Bogenbewegung langsam hinter den Kopf.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0433.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0433.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d55cd43f-ac66-554d-af25-deb059e3069a', NULL, 'Dumbbell Straight Leg Deadlift', 'Kurzhantel-Kreuzheben mit gestreckten Beinen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing your torso to lean forward. Continue lowering the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, keeping your knees slightly bent. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then engage your glutes and hamstrings to lift your torso back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, hinge at the hips and lower the dumbbells towards the ground, allowing your torso to lean forward.","Continue lowering the dumbbells until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, keeping your knees slightly bent.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then engage your glutes and hamstrings to lift your torso back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, beuge dich aus der Hüfte und senke die Kurzhanteln Richtung Boden, während sich der Oberkörper nach vorne neigt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln weiter, bis du eine Dehnung in den Beinbeugern spürst, die Knie bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte unten kurz inne und richte den Oberkörper durch Anspannen von Gesäss und Beinbeugern zurück in die Ausgangsposition auf.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0434.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0434.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('625d57a5-1223-52ba-8313-bc33cc04353f', NULL, 'Dumbbell Sumo Pull Through', 'Kurzhantel-Sumo-Pull-Through', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointed outwards. Hold a dumbbell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended. Bend your knees and lower your hips down into a squat position, keeping your back straight. Lower the dumbbell down between your legs, keeping your arms straight. Drive through your heels and extend your hips forward, pulling the dumbbell up and in front of your body. Squeeze your glutes at the top of the movement, then lower the dumbbell back down between your legs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointed outwards.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended.","Bend your knees and lower your hips down into a squat position, keeping your back straight.","Lower the dumbbell down between your legs, keeping your arms straight.","Drive through your heels and extend your hips forward, pulling the dumbbell up and in front of your body.","Squeeze your glutes at the top of the movement, then lower the dumbbell back down between your legs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich breiter als schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen nach aussen.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen vor dem Körper, die Arme gestreckt.","Beuge die Knie und senke die Hüfte in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Senke die Kurzhantel zwischen die Beine, die Arme bleiben gestreckt.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab und strecke die Hüfte nach vorne, während du die Kurzhantel nach oben vor den Körper ziehst.","Spanne am Ende der Bewegung das Gesäss an und senke die Kurzhantel dann zurück zwischen die Beine.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2808.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2808.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ddbe6077-f9d7-5906-814c-3d3cb8aea8a1', NULL, 'Dumbbell Supported Squat', 'Kurzhantel-Kniebeuge mit Abstützung', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides. Keeping your chest up and core engaged, slowly lower your body down by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides.","Keeping your chest up and core engaged, slowly lower your body down by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel seitlich am Körper.","Halte die Brust oben und die Körpermitte angespannt, senke den Körper langsam ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2803.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2803.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ccfb3db1-8763-5659-9320-8c94552a3e1a', NULL, 'Dumbbell Tate Press', 'Kurzhantel-Tate-Press', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, then rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing away from you. Press the dumbbells up until your arms are fully extended, then lower them back down to shoulder height. Rotate your wrists back to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a flat bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, then rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing away from you.","Press the dumbbells up until your arms are fully extended, then lower them back down to shoulder height.","Rotate your wrists back to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine flache Bank und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe und drehe die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen von dir weg zeigen.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, und senke sie dann zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Drehe die Handgelenke zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0436.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0436.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0f8ded74-78d6-5c2e-8b27-c491adf34790', NULL, 'Dumbbell Triceps Kickback with Stork Stance', 'Kurzhantel-Trizeps-Kickback im Storchenstand', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in your right hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Bring your right elbow up to your side, keeping it bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your right arm straight back, squeezing your triceps. Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in your right hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Bring your right elbow up to your side, keeping it bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your right arm straight back, squeezing your triceps.","Pause for a moment, then slowly lower the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in der rechten Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Bringe den rechten Ellbogen an die Seite und halte ihn im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke den rechten Arm gerade nach hinten und spanne den Trizeps an.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Kurzhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1742.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1742.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('40ab0ceb-df75-5aff-8bd7-763037a9b482', NULL, 'Dumbbell Twisting Bench Press', 'Kurzhantel-Bankdrücken mit Drehung', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing away from you. Extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Lower the dumbbells down towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. As you lower the dumbbells, twist your wrists so that your palms face towards you at the bottom of the movement. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then reverse the movement by pressing the dumbbells back up to the starting position. As you press the dumbbells up, twist your wrists back to the starting position with palms facing away from you. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip, palms facing away from you.","Extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Lower the dumbbells down towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","As you lower the dumbbells, twist your wrists so that your palms face towards you at the bottom of the movement.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then reverse the movement by pressing the dumbbells back up to the starting position.","As you press the dumbbells up, twist your wrists back to the starting position with palms facing away from you.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und drücke den Rücken gegen die Bank.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln Richtung Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Drehe beim Absenken die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen am unteren Ende der Bewegung zu dir zeigen.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke die Kurzhanteln dann in umgekehrter Bewegung zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Drehe beim Hochdrücken die Handgelenke zurück in die Ausgangsposition, Handflächen wieder von dir weg gerichtet.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1743.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1743.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a9f0a627-48bb-5c6d-ae57-61ce6aea38ca', NULL, 'Dumbbell Upright Row', 'Kurzhantel-Aufrechtes Rudern', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Let the dumbbells hang in front of your thighs, with your arms fully extended. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbells straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Let the dumbbells hang in front of your thighs, with your arms fully extended.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbells straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Lass die Kurzhanteln vor den Oberschenkeln hängen, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhanteln, angeführt von den Ellbogen, gerade Richtung Kinn hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0437.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0437.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('be96b298-5bd0-521d-aa36-ef3e30023980', NULL, 'Dumbbell Upright Row (Back POV)', 'Kurzhantel-Aufrechtes Rudern (Rückenansicht)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Let the dumbbells hang in front of your thighs, with your arms fully extended and your palms facing your body. Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbells straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbows. Continue lifting until the dumbbells are at shoulder height, with your elbows pointing out to the sides. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Let the dumbbells hang in front of your thighs, with your arms fully extended and your palms facing your body.","Keeping your back straight and your core engaged, exhale and lift the dumbbells straight up towards your chin, leading with your elbows.","Continue lifting until the dumbbells are at shoulder height, with your elbows pointing out to the sides.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel im Obergriff.","Lass die Kurzhanteln vor den Oberschenkeln hängen, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, atme aus und ziehe die Kurzhanteln, angeführt von den Ellbogen, gerade Richtung Kinn hoch.","Ziehe weiter hoch, bis sich die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe befinden und die Ellbogen seitlich nach aussen zeigen.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1765.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1765.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c2babb28-1a25-5209-86c0-a43f217f100d', NULL, 'Dumbbell Upright Shoulder External Rotation', 'Kurzhantel-Aussenrotation der Schulter im Stehen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Rotate your arms externally, bringing the dumbbells up towards your head while keeping your elbows in the same position. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'rotator cuff', '["rotator cuff","trapezius"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the ground, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Rotate your arms externally, bringing the dumbbells up towards your head while keeping your elbows in the same position.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Drehe die Arme nach aussen und führe die Kurzhanteln Richtung Kopf, während die Ellbogen in Position bleiben.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0864.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0864.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2f35f174-a26c-50f0-9cb1-33647acb4f62', NULL, 'Dumbbell Waiter Biceps Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Kellner-Bizepscurl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Keep your upper arms close to your body and your elbows tucked in. Slowly curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, keeping your wrists straight. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Keep your upper arms close to your body and your elbows tucked in.","Slowly curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, keeping your wrists straight.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Halte die Oberarme nah am Körper und die Ellbogen eng am Körper.","Curle die Kurzhanteln langsam zu den Schultern hoch, die Handgelenke bleiben gerade.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kurzhanteln dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/5201.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/5201.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('41eccb7f-eb9c-5c18-9ba1-7c12623cc13d', NULL, 'Dumbbell W-Press', 'Kurzhantel-W-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, elbows bent and palms facing forward. Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Sit on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Raise the dumbbells to shoulder height, elbows bent and palms facing forward.","Press the dumbbells upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Lower the dumbbells back to shoulder height.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne.","Hebe die Kurzhanteln auf Schulterhöhe, Ellbogen gebeugt, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kurzhanteln nach oben, bis die Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Senke die Kurzhanteln zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0438.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0438.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3625c0b7-4867-5270-87f1-a296a55e4109', NULL, 'Dumbbell Zottman Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Zottman-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body. Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate your palms to face forward. Curl the dumbbells up to your shoulders while keeping your upper arms stationary. At the top of the movement, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing away from your body. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position, rotating your palms back to facing your body. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your body.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and rotate your palms to face forward.","Curl the dumbbells up to your shoulders while keeping your upper arms stationary.","At the top of the movement, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing away from your body.","Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position, rotating your palms back to facing your body.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper und drehe die Handflächen nach vorne.","Curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch, während die Oberarme ruhig bleiben.","Drehe am Ende der Bewegung die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen vom Körper weg zeigen.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition und drehe die Handflächen dabei wieder zum Körper.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0439.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0439.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1373b265-210f-562b-891a-48797df6ea38', NULL, 'Dumbbell Zottman Preacher Curl', 'Kurzhantel-Zottman-Scott-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a preacher bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up and elbows resting on the pad. Curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, keeping your upper arms stationary and your palms facing up. At the top of the curl, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing down. Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position, rotating your wrists back to the starting position as you do so. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing up and elbows resting on the pad.","Curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, keeping your upper arms stationary and your palms facing up.","At the top of the curl, rotate your wrists so that your palms are facing down.","Slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position, rotating your wrists back to the starting position as you do so.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Scott-Bank und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach oben, die Ellbogen auf dem Polster.","Curle die Kurzhanteln zu den Schultern hoch, die Oberarme bleiben ruhig, Handflächen nach oben.","Drehe am Ende des Curls die Handgelenke, sodass die Handflächen nach unten zeigen.","Senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition und drehe die Handgelenke dabei wieder zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2294.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2294.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cfb2caba-1965-52a6-946d-027d18e33106', NULL, 'Dumbbells Seated Triceps Extension', 'Kurzhantel-Trizepsstrecken im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in both hands with an overhand grip, and raise it above your head. Bend your elbows and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arms close to your ears. Extend your arms and raise the dumbbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a dumbbell in both hands with an overhand grip, and raise it above your head.","Bend your elbows and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arms close to your ears.","Extend your arms and raise the dumbbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen im Obergriff und hebe sie über den Kopf.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf, die Oberarme bleiben nah an den Ohren.","Strecke die Arme und hebe die Kurzhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2189.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2189.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8b4cb5c9-0f75-58a8-809a-40436ef25a10', NULL, 'Dynamic Chest Stretch (Male)', 'Dynamische Brustdehnung (Mann)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend your arms straight out to the sides, parallel to the ground. Slowly bring your arms forward, crossing them in front of your body. Feel the stretch in your chest muscles. Hold the stretch for 10-30 seconds. Return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend your arms straight out to the sides, parallel to the ground.","Slowly bring your arms forward, crossing them in front of your body.","Feel the stretch in your chest muscles.","Hold the stretch for 10-30 seconds.","Return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand.","Strecke die Arme seitlich aus, parallel zum Boden.","Führe die Arme langsam nach vorne und kreuze sie vor dem Körper.","Spüre die Dehnung in der Brustmuskulatur.","Halte die Dehnung 10 bis 30 Sekunden.","Kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1167.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1167.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c032a626-e946-5a46-a9a7-95dc0748daa2', NULL, 'Elbow Dips', 'Ellbogen-Dips', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge next to your hips. Slide your hips forward off the bench and straighten your legs, keeping your heels on the ground. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to straighten your arms and lift your body back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge next to your hips.","Slide your hips forward off the bench and straighten your legs, keeping your heels on the ground.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to straighten your arms and lift your body back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich an den Rand einer Bank oder eines Stuhls und greife die Kante neben der Hüfte.","Schiebe die Hüfte nach vorne von der Bank und strecke die Beine, die Fersen bleiben auf dem Boden.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke den Körper Richtung Boden, der Rücken bleibt nah an der Bank.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich über die Hände ab, um die Arme zu strecken und den Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3287.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3287.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('da58a4a3-2f8c-5677-9334-114b371f25dd', NULL, 'Elbow Lift - Reverse Push-Up', 'Ellbogenheben - Liegestütz rückwärts', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Start by lying face down on the ground with your legs extended and your hands placed directly under your shoulders. Engage your core and press through your palms to lift your upper body off the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides. Pause at the top for a moment, squeezing your upper back muscles. Slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start by lying face down on the ground with your legs extended and your hands placed directly under your shoulders.","Engage your core and press through your palms to lift your upper body off the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides.","Pause at the top for a moment, squeezing your upper back muscles.","Slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Boden, strecke die Beine aus und platziere die Hände direkt unter den Schultern.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, um den Oberkörper vom Boden zu heben, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne die obere Rückenmuskulatur an.","Senke den Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1772.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1772.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ded4400c-5185-5680-9895-1d4e68c67b01', NULL, 'Elbow-to-Knee', 'Ellbogen-zu-Knie', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by lying flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee. At the same time, bring your left knee towards your right elbow, creating a twisting motion. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and extend your legs back to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time bringing your left elbow towards your right knee and your right knee towards your left elbow. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Start by lying flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee.","At the same time, bring your left knee towards your right elbow, creating a twisting motion.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and extend your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time bringing your left elbow towards your right knee and your right knee towards your left elbow.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper vom Boden, während du den rechten Ellbogen zum linken Knie führst.","Ziehe gleichzeitig das linke Knie zum rechten Ellbogen, sodass eine Drehbewegung entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam ab und strecke die Beine zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal mit dem linken Ellbogen zum rechten Knie und dem rechten Knie zum linken Ellbogen.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0443.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0443.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('00e8066a-2de0-597b-9ef1-0a1160d1fe50', NULL, 'Elevator', 'Elevator', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Place your hands on your hips or cross them in front of your chest. Keeping your back straight, slowly bend forward at the waist, lowering your upper body towards the ground. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly raise your upper body back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","trapezius"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Place your hands on your hips or cross them in front of your chest.","Keeping your back straight, slowly bend forward at the waist, lowering your upper body towards the ground.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly raise your upper body back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Lege die Hände auf die Hüfte oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Halte den Rücken gerade und beuge dich langsam in der Hüfte nach vorne, wobei du den Oberkörper Richtung Boden senkst.","Halte unten kurz inne und richte den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition auf.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3292.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3292.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('58807d50-00b7-59ef-9518-1adccc295829', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Alternating Arm Ups', 'Gymnastikball-Armheben im Wechsel', 'back', 'lats', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing inwards and your arms extended down by your sides. Engage your core and slowly lift one arm up towards your shoulder, keeping your elbow slightly bent. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arm back down to the starting position. Repeat the movement with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing inwards and your arms extended down by your sides.","Engage your core and slowly lift one arm up towards your shoulder, keeping your elbow slightly bent.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arm back down to the starting position.","Repeat the movement with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet, die Arme seitlich nach unten gestreckt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe langsam einen Arm Richtung Schulter, der Ellbogen bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Arm dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1332.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1332.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b9241d64-d55b-5b96-a576-d3a6097dea25', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Back Extension with Arms Extended', 'Rückenstrecken auf dem Gymnastikball mit gestreckten Armen', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it, with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability. Extend your arms straight out in front of you, with your palms facing down. Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, keeping your back straight and your neck in line with your spine. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it, with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability.","Extend your arms straight out in front of you, with your palms facing down.","Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, keeping your back straight and your neck in line with your spine.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten darauf, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Ball, die Füsse stützen sich zur Stabilisierung an einer Wand ab.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus, Handflächen nach unten.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, der Rücken bleibt gerade und der Nacken in Verlängerung der Wirbelsäule.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1333.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1333.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fc1d2a53-25c6-5018-b886-e57f1c0bf19d', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Back Extension with Hands Behind Head', 'Rückenstrecken auf dem Gymnastikball mit Händen hinter dem Kopf', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it with your hips resting on the ball. Position your feet against a wall or other stable surface for support. Cross your arms behind your head, with your hands touching the back of your head. Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your hips. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it with your hips resting on the ball.","Position your feet against a wall or other stable surface for support.","Cross your arms behind your head, with your hands touching the back of your head.","Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your hips.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten darauf, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Ball.","Stütze die Füsse zur Unterstützung an einer Wand oder einer anderen stabilen Fläche ab.","Verschränke die Arme hinter dem Kopf, die Hände berühren den Hinterkopf.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, bis eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Hüfte entsteht.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1334.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1334.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c77284d7-45a1-5259-a4a1-dbca94adf15c', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Back Extension with Knees off Ground', 'Rückenstrecken auf dem Gymnastikball mit angehobenen Knien', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it, with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability. Position your hands behind your head or crossed over your chest. Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your heels. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and lie face down on top of it, with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability.","Position your hands behind your head or crossed over your chest.","Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your heels.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten darauf, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Ball, die Füsse stützen sich zur Stabilisierung an einer Wand ab.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, bis eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1335.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1335.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('77f62d9f-c207-5038-9a9a-3a8b6fdfd9bf', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Back Extension with Rotation', 'Rückenstrecken auf dem Gymnastikball mit Rotation', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Start by lying face down on the stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your feet firmly planted on the ground. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your heels. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly rotate your torso to one side, keeping your hips and legs stable. Return to the center and repeat the rotation to the other side. Lower your upper body back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Start by lying face down on the stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your feet firmly planted on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line from your head to your heels.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly rotate your torso to one side, keeping your hips and legs stable.","Return to the center and repeat the rotation to the other side.","Lower your upper body back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Gymnastikball, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Ball, die Füsse stehen fest auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, bis eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne und drehe den Oberkörper dann langsam zur einen Seite, Hüfte und Beine bleiben stabil.","Kehre zur Mitte zurück und wiederhole die Drehung zur anderen Seite.","Senke den Oberkörper zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1336.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1336.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e42db030-ba97-5704-b53e-7de1824c56b6', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Dip', 'Dip auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Place your hands on the ball beside your hips, fingers pointing forward. Engage your triceps and push through your hands to lift your body off the ball, straightening your arms. Lower your body back down by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Place your hands on the ball beside your hips, fingers pointing forward.","Engage your triceps and push through your hands to lift your body off the ball, straightening your arms.","Lower your body back down by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden, die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Stütze die Hände neben der Hüfte auf dem Ball ab, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Spanne den Trizeps an und drücke dich über die Hände ab, um den Körper vom Ball zu heben, die Arme strecken sich dabei.","Senke den Körper zurück ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, sie bleiben nah am Körper.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1744.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1744.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('38ba9095-c865-53c7-b063-56fc3267d936', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Hip Flexor Stretch', 'Hüftbeuger-Dehnung auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and kneel in front of it. Place your right foot on top of the stability ball, with your knee bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your left leg behind you, keeping it straight. Lean forward, pushing your hips towards the stability ball, until you feel a stretch in your right hip flexor. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and kneel in front of it.","Place your right foot on top of the stability ball, with your knee bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your left leg behind you, keeping it straight.","Lean forward, pushing your hips towards the stability ball, until you feel a stretch in your right hip flexor.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und knie dich davor hin.","Stelle den rechten Fuss oben auf den Gymnastikball, das Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke das linke Bein gerade nach hinten aus.","Lehne dich nach vorne und schiebe die Hüfte Richtung Gymnastikball, bis du eine Dehnung im rechten Hüftbeuger spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1559.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1559.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9c64b4ac-df7f-5e53-9e01-011ba79dd1c7', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Hug', 'Gymnastikball-Umarmung (Rückendehnung)', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold the stability ball with both hands, hugging it close to your chest. Engage your core muscles and slowly lean back, keeping your back straight and your feet planted on the ground. Continue leaning back until you feel a stretch in your back muscles. Hold the position for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold the stability ball with both hands, hugging it close to your chest.","Engage your core muscles and slowly lean back, keeping your back straight and your feet planted on the ground.","Continue leaning back until you feel a stretch in your back muscles.","Hold the position for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Umfasse den Gymnastikball mit beiden Händen und halte ihn nah an die Brust gedrückt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und lehne dich langsam zurück, der Rücken bleibt gerade und die Füsse stehen fest auf dem Boden.","Lehne dich weiter zurück, bis du eine Dehnung in der Rückenmuskulatur spürst.","Halte die Position einige Sekunden und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1338.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1338.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f081b8e1-c280-5793-abc1-f79341c3440d', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Lat Stretch', 'Latissimus-Dehnung auf dem Gymnastikball', 'back', 'lats', 'stability ball', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and extend your arm straight up overhead. Slowly lean to the opposite side, feeling a stretch in your lat muscle. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and extend your arm straight up overhead.","Slowly lean to the opposite side, feeling a stretch in your lat muscle.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand und strecke den Arm gerade über den Kopf.","Lehne dich langsam zur gegenüberliegenden Seite und spüre die Dehnung im Latissimus.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1339.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1339.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3b82f253-17d2-51db-a861-bb577f6a1b48', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Lower Back Stretch (Pyramid)', 'Dehnung des unteren Rückens auf dem Gymnastikball (Pyramide)', 'back', 'lats', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the ball down your back until your lower back is resting on the ball. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your core and slowly lower your upper body towards the ground, allowing your lower back to stretch over the ball. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Slowly walk your feet forward, rolling the ball down your back until your lower back is resting on the ball.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your core and slowly lower your upper body towards the ground, allowing your lower back to stretch over the ball.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden, die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Gehe mit den Füssen langsam nach vorne und rolle den Ball dabei den Rücken hinunter, bis der untere Rücken auf dem Ball liegt.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke den Oberkörper langsam Richtung Boden, sodass sich der untere Rücken über den Ball dehnt.","Halte die Dehnung einige Sekunden und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1341.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1341.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('49e1659d-1236-5197-875e-390d21c0688a', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Lying Side Lat Stretch', 'Latissimus-Dehnung seitlich liegend auf dem Gymnastikball', 'back', 'lats', 'stability ball', 'Lie on your side with your legs extended and your head supported by the stability ball. Place your top arm on the ball for stability. Reach your top arm overhead and allow your torso to rotate slightly. Feel the stretch in your lat muscles on the side of your body. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs extended and your head supported by the stability ball.","Place your top arm on the ball for stability.","Reach your top arm overhead and allow your torso to rotate slightly.","Feel the stretch in your lat muscles on the side of your body.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, strecke die Beine aus und stütze den Kopf auf dem Gymnastikball ab.","Lege den oberen Arm zur Stabilisierung auf den Ball.","Strecke den oberen Arm über den Kopf und lass den Oberkörper leicht mitdrehen.","Spüre die Dehnung im Latissimus an der Körperseite.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1342.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1342.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c95cc1ac-9fea-59c6-a698-02269e9cfed4', NULL, 'Exercise Ball on the Wall Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben mit Gymnastikball an der Wand', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your back against a wall and place an exercise ball between your lower back and the wall. Position your feet shoulder-width apart, with your toes pointing forward. Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides. Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Stand with your back against a wall and place an exercise ball between your lower back and the wall.","Position your feet shoulder-width apart, with your toes pointing forward.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides.","Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit dem Rücken gegen eine Wand und platziere einen Gymnastikball zwischen unterem Rücken und Wand.","Stelle die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, die Arme seitlich gestreckt.","Hebe die Fersen vom Boden ab und verlagere das Körpergewicht auf die Fussballen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1382.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1382.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('84c03f95-b286-5002-8ac7-444c19f28af9', NULL, 'Exercise Ball on the Wall Calf Raise (Tennis Ball Between Ankles)', 'Wadenheben mit Gymnastikball an der Wand (Tennisball zwischen den Knöcheln)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand facing a wall with your feet shoulder-width apart. Place an exercise ball between the wall and your lower back. Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides. Place a tennis ball between your ankles. Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Stand facing a wall with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place an exercise ball between the wall and your lower back.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides.","Place a tennis ball between your ankles.","Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit dem Gesicht zu einer Wand, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Platziere einen Gymnastikball zwischen Wand und unterem Rücken.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, die Arme seitlich gestreckt.","Klemme einen Tennisball zwischen die Knöchel.","Hebe die Fersen vom Boden ab und hebe den Körper auf die Zehenspitzen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3241.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3241.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('aae58258-93b4-530f-bd39-0d2bf1beabb9', NULL, 'Exercise Ball on the Wall Calf Raise (Tennis Ball Between Knees)', 'Wadenheben mit Gymnastikball an der Wand (Tennisball zwischen den Knien)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your back against a wall and place an exercise ball between your lower back and the wall. Position your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly in front of you. Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides. Place a tennis ball between your knees. Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings"]', '["Stand with your back against a wall and place an exercise ball between your lower back and the wall.","Position your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly in front of you.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand, with your arms extended by your sides.","Place a tennis ball between your knees.","Raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit dem Rücken gegen eine Wand und platziere einen Gymnastikball zwischen unterem Rücken und Wand.","Stelle die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander und leicht vor dem Körper.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, die Arme seitlich gestreckt.","Klemme einen Tennisball zwischen die Knie.","Hebe die Fersen vom Boden ab und hebe den Körper auf die Zehenspitzen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3240.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3240.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('543a200e-2338-5d43-a2bd-eac8c76dc54f', NULL, 'Exercise Ball One Leg Prone Lower Body Rotation', 'Unterkörperrotation einbeinig in Bauchlage auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'stability ball', 'Lie face down on the stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your legs extended straight behind you. Place your hands on the ground in front of you for support. Engage your glutes and core muscles to stabilize your body. Slowly lift one leg off the ground, keeping it straight and parallel to the floor. Rotate your leg outward, away from your body, while keeping your hips and upper body stable. Pause for a moment at the end of the rotation, then slowly return your leg to the starting position. Repeat the rotation with the other leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","core"]', '["Lie face down on the stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your legs extended straight behind you.","Place your hands on the ground in front of you for support.","Engage your glutes and core muscles to stabilize your body.","Slowly lift one leg off the ground, keeping it straight and parallel to the floor.","Rotate your leg outward, away from your body, while keeping your hips and upper body stable.","Pause for a moment at the end of the rotation, then slowly return your leg to the starting position.","Repeat the rotation with the other leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Gymnastikball, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Ball, die Beine gerade nach hinten gestreckt.","Stütze die Hände vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Spanne Gesäss und Körpermitte an, um den Körper zu stabilisieren.","Hebe langsam ein Bein vom Boden ab, es bleibt gestreckt und parallel zum Boden.","Drehe das Bein nach aussen, vom Körper weg, während Hüfte und Oberkörper stabil bleiben.","Halte am Ende der Drehung kurz inne und führe das Bein dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Drehung mit dem anderen Bein.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Beine ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1416.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1416.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d423a8ab-ed93-595b-b360-b6fe45314cfb', NULL, 'Exercise Ball One Legged Diagonal Kick Hamstring Curl', 'Beincurl mit diagonalem Kick einbeinig auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'stability ball', 'Start by lying on your back with your legs extended and your heels resting on top of the stability ball. Place your arms by your sides for stability. Engage your glutes and core muscles to lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your shoulders to your heels. Bend your right knee and bring it towards your chest, keeping your left leg extended and your foot flexed. Kick your right leg diagonally across your body, extending it fully and engaging your hamstrings. Slowly return your right leg to the starting position, maintaining control and stability. Repeat the movement with your left leg, alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start by lying on your back with your legs extended and your heels resting on top of the stability ball.","Place your arms by your sides for stability.","Engage your glutes and core muscles to lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your shoulders to your heels.","Bend your right knee and bring it towards your chest, keeping your left leg extended and your foot flexed.","Kick your right leg diagonally across your body, extending it fully and engaging your hamstrings.","Slowly return your right leg to the starting position, maintaining control and stability.","Repeat the movement with your left leg, alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt, die Fersen liegen oben auf dem Gymnastikball.","Lege die Arme zur Stabilisierung seitlich an den Körper.","Spanne Gesäss und Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden, sodass eine gerade Linie von Schultern bis Fersen entsteht.","Beuge das rechte Knie und ziehe es Richtung Brust, das linke Bein bleibt gestreckt, der Fuss angezogen.","Strecke das rechte Bein diagonal über den Körper, vollständig gestreckt, und spanne dabei die Beinbeuger an.","Führe das rechte Bein langsam und kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem linken Bein und wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1417.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1417.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('460e2359-fcc2-5f7e-b870-696f8589ef6e', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Pike Push-Up', 'Pike-Liegestütz auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'stability ball', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands on the floor and your shins resting on the stability ball. Engage your core and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, rolling the ball towards your hands. Keep your legs straight and your body in a pike position, forming an inverted V shape. Bend your elbows and lower your upper body towards the floor, keeping your head in line with your hands. Push through your hands and extend your arms to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands on the floor and your shins resting on the stability ball.","Engage your core and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, rolling the ball towards your hands.","Keep your legs straight and your body in a pike position, forming an inverted V shape.","Bend your elbows and lower your upper body towards the floor, keeping your head in line with your hands.","Push through your hands and extend your arms to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände auf dem Boden, die Schienbeine liegen auf dem Gymnastikball.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte Richtung Decke, während der Ball zu den Händen rollt.","Halte die Beine gestreckt und den Körper in der Pike-Position, sodass ein umgekehrtes V entsteht.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke den Oberkörper Richtung Boden, der Kopf bleibt in Linie mit den Händen.","Drücke dich über die Hände ab und strecke die Arme, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1296.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1296.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bb522cb1-c77c-5088-b08e-93465943f260', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Prone Leg Raise', 'Beinheben in Bauchlage auf dem Gymnastikball', 'back', 'spine', 'stability ball', 'Lie face down on a mat with your legs extended and your toes resting on top of the stability ball. Place your hands on the ground, shoulder-width apart, and engage your core muscles. Keeping your legs straight, slowly lift them off the ground, using your lower back and glutes to raise them as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'abdominals', '["abdominals","glutes"]', '["Lie face down on a mat with your legs extended and your toes resting on top of the stability ball.","Place your hands on the ground, shoulder-width apart, and engage your core muscles.","Keeping your legs straight, slowly lift them off the ground, using your lower back and glutes to raise them as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf eine Matte, die Beine gestreckt, die Zehen liegen oben auf dem Gymnastikball.","Stütze die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Boden ab und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Halte die Beine gestreckt und hebe sie langsam vom Boden, so hoch wie möglich, mithilfe von unterem Rücken und Gesäss.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1343.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1343.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0d156090-7533-53c7-aaaa-1434719d70bc', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Seated Hamstring Stretch', 'Beinbeuger-Dehnung im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Slowly roll the ball forward, walking your feet out until your upper back is resting on the ball and your legs are extended straight in front of you. Place your hands on your hips for support. Engage your core and slowly lower your upper body towards the ground, keeping your back straight and your chest lifted. Stop when you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, and hold the position for 20-30 seconds. Slowly return to the starting position by pushing through your heels and using your hamstrings to pull yourself back up. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","lower back"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Slowly roll the ball forward, walking your feet out until your upper back is resting on the ball and your legs are extended straight in front of you.","Place your hands on your hips for support.","Engage your core and slowly lower your upper body towards the ground, keeping your back straight and your chest lifted.","Stop when you feel a stretch in your hamstrings, and hold the position for 20-30 seconds.","Slowly return to the starting position by pushing through your heels and using your hamstrings to pull yourself back up.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden, die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Rolle den Ball langsam nach vorne, indem du die Füsse weiter vorschiebst, bis der obere Rücken auf dem Ball liegt und die Beine gerade vor dir ausgestreckt sind.","Stütze die Hände an der Hüfte ab.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke den Oberkörper langsam Richtung Boden, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust oben.","Stoppe, sobald du eine Dehnung in den Beinbeugern spürst, und halte die Position 20 bis 30 Sekunden.","Kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du dich über die Fersen abdrückst und dich mit den Beinbeugern zurückziehst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1560.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1560.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b78a9daf-16fe-5608-b23c-4d49ea616a33', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Seated Triceps Stretch', 'Trizeps-Dehnung im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'stability ball', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a dumbbell in one hand and extend your arm straight up above your head. Bend your elbow and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arm close to your ear. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then return to the starting position. Repeat with the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a dumbbell in one hand and extend your arm straight up above your head.","Bend your elbow and lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your upper arm close to your ear.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then return to the starting position.","Repeat with the other arm."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand und strecke den Arm gerade über den Kopf.","Beuge den Ellbogen und senke die Kurzhantel hinter den Kopf, der Oberarm bleibt nah am Ohr.","Halte die Dehnung einige Sekunden und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1745.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1745.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dab284dd-eb63-527a-ab31-6c8a9aaac7bd', NULL, 'Exercise Ball Supine Triceps Extension', 'Trizepsstrecken in Rückenlage auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up towards the ceiling. Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your elbows close to your ears. Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms straight up towards the ceiling.","Slowly lower the dumbbell behind your head, keeping your elbows close to your ears.","Pause for a moment, then raise the dumbbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden, die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade Richtung Decke.","Senke die Kurzhantel langsam hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen bleiben nah an den Ohren.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Kurzhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1746.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1746.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8be42667-60fe-5693-8024-d217875e6d41', NULL, 'EZ Bar French Press on Exercise Ball', 'SZ-Stange-French-Press auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on an exercise ball and hold an EZ barbell with an overhand grip. Extend your arms straight up, keeping your elbows close to your head. Slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on an exercise ball and hold an EZ barbell with an overhand grip.","Extend your arms straight up, keeping your elbows close to your head.","Slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Gymnastikball und halte eine SZ-Stange im Obergriff.","Strecke die Arme gerade nach oben, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Kopf.","Senke die Stange langsam hinter den Kopf, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1747.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1747.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2e5c73a4-402a-51f2-b944-8316db118514', NULL, 'EZ Bar Lying Bent Arms Pullover', 'SZ-Stange-Überzug im Liegen mit gebeugten Armen', 'back', 'lats', 'ez barbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet on the floor. Hold the EZ barbell with a pronated grip (palms facing away from you) and your hands shoulder-width apart. Extend your arms straight above your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Lower the barbell in an arc motion behind your head, maintaining the slight bend in your elbows. Pause for a moment, then return the barbell to the starting position by reversing the arc motion. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your head at one end and your feet on the floor.","Hold the EZ barbell with a pronated grip (palms facing away from you) and your hands shoulder-width apart.","Extend your arms straight above your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Lower the barbell in an arc motion behind your head, maintaining the slight bend in your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then return the barbell to the starting position by reversing the arc motion.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, der Kopf am einen Ende, die Füsse auf dem Boden.","Halte die SZ-Stange im Pronationsgriff (Handflächen von dir weg), die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Stange in einer Bogenbewegung hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte kurz inne und führe die Stange in umgekehrter Bogenbewegung zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3010.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3010.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f27ad356-d309-5703-9cad-782a3703d0ae', NULL, 'EZ Bar Lying Close Grip Triceps Extension Behind Head', 'SZ-Stange-Trizepsstrecken im Liegen eng gegriffen hinter dem Kopf', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your head at the end of the bench. Hold the ez barbell with a close grip, palms facing up, and extend your arms straight up over your chest. Keeping your upper arms stationary, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your head at the end of the bench.","Hold the ez barbell with a close grip, palms facing up, and extend your arms straight up over your chest.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden, der Kopf liegt am Ende der Bank.","Halte die SZ-Stange im engen Griff, Handflächen nach oben, und strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und senke die Stange langsam hinter den Kopf, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1748.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1748.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('91478d6e-6ff7-51f5-ac1a-1418f35c4fa0', NULL, 'EZ Bar Reverse Grip Bent Over Row', 'SZ-Stange-Rudern vorgebeugt im Obergriff', 'back', 'upper back', 'ez barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and hands shoulder-width apart. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up, until your torso is almost parallel to the floor. Pull the ez barbell towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the ez barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and hands shoulder-width apart.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up, until your torso is almost parallel to the floor.","Pull the ez barbell towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the ez barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und die Brust oben, bis der Oberkörper fast parallel zum Boden ist.","Ziehe die SZ-Stange Richtung unteren Brustbereich und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die SZ-Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1344.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1344.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('881a5a56-b03a-56ec-8197-0f8a252e6f19', NULL, 'EZ Bar Seated Close Grip Concentration Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Konzentrationscurl eng gegriffen im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold an EZ barbell with an underhand grip. Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee. Curl the barbell up towards your shoulder while keeping your upper arm stationary. Squeeze your biceps at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold an EZ barbell with an underhand grip.","Rest your elbow on the inside of your thigh, just above the knee.","Curl the barbell up towards your shoulder while keeping your upper arm stationary.","Squeeze your biceps at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte eine SZ-Stange im Untergriff.","Stütze den Ellbogen auf der Innenseite des Oberschenkels ab, knapp über dem Knie.","Curle die Stange zur Schulter hoch, während der Oberarm ruhig bleibt.","Spanne am Ende der Bewegung den Bizeps an und senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1682.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1682.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('020f536f-e6b4-5324-aa61-fae9e3d0f380', NULL, 'EZ Bar Standing French Press', 'SZ-Stange-French-Press stehend', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip. Raise the barbell above your head, fully extending your arms. Keeping your upper arms close to your head, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip.","Raise the barbell above your head, fully extending your arms.","Keeping your upper arms close to your head, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die SZ-Stange im Obergriff.","Hebe die Stange über den Kopf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme nah am Kopf und senke die Stange langsam hinter den Kopf, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1749.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1749.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('619066cc-945a-5a74-b06c-b3b44476a66a', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Anti Gravity Press', 'SZ-Stange-Schulterdrücken (Anti-Gravity-Press)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'ez barbell', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and holding the ez barbell with an overhand grip. Raise the barbell to shoulder height, keeping your elbows slightly bent and your palms facing forward. Press the barbell overhead, extending your arms fully. Lower the barbell back to shoulder height and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and holding the ez barbell with an overhand grip.","Raise the barbell to shoulder height, keeping your elbows slightly bent and your palms facing forward.","Press the barbell overhead, extending your arms fully.","Lower the barbell back to shoulder height and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die SZ-Stange im Obergriff.","Hebe die Stange auf Schulterhöhe, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt, die Handflächen zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke die Stange über den Kopf und strecke die Arme vollständig.","Senke die Stange zurück auf Schulterhöhe und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0445.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0445.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('65f33d57-dcd1-5007-9a94-2d4f1b14fc62', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Close Grip Preacher Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Scott-Curl eng gegriffen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on a preacher curl bench and place your upper arms on the pad, gripping the ez barbell with an underhand grip. Rest your triceps on the pad and fully extend your arms, keeping your back straight. Slowly curl the barbell towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Lower the barbell back to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher curl bench and place your upper arms on the pad, gripping the ez barbell with an underhand grip.","Rest your triceps on the pad and fully extend your arms, keeping your back straight.","Slowly curl the barbell towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Lower the barbell back to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Scott-Bank, lege die Oberarme auf das Polster und greife die SZ-Stange im Untergriff.","Lege den Trizeps auf das Polster und strecke die Arme vollständig, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Curle die Stange langsam zu den Schultern hoch und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Senke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1627.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1627.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7b37d1af-4d14-5937-a270-ae29b75409d3', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Close-Grip Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Curl eng gegriffen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement. Curl the barbell up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement.","Curl the barbell up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Halte die Ellbogen während der gesamten Bewegung nah am Oberkörper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Curle die Stange zu den Schultern hoch und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0446.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0446.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8cc0dbbb-112e-5a6c-bc3b-57a1237e3f11', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement. Exhale as you curl the barbell up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale as you slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement.","Exhale as you curl the barbell up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale as you slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Halte die Ellbogen während der gesamten Bewegung nah am Oberkörper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Atme aus, während du die Stange zu den Schultern hochcurlst und den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0447.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0447.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9438ed9a-de5d-5059-9f00-7096a118f628', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Decline Close Grip Face Press', 'SZ-Stange-Face-Press eng gegriffen auf der Negativbank', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Lie on a decline bench with your head lower than your feet. Grasp the ez barbell with a close grip, palms facing each other. Extend your arms straight up above your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Lower the barbell towards your forehead by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then press the barbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie on a decline bench with your head lower than your feet.","Grasp the ez barbell with a close grip, palms facing each other.","Extend your arms straight up above your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Lower the barbell towards your forehead by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then press the barbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf eine Negativbank, der Kopf tiefer als die Füsse.","Greife die SZ-Stange im engen Griff, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Senke die Stange Richtung Stirn, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und drücke die Stange dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0448.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0448.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b1c76e78-32dd-5e2c-a30d-35048fbd6408', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Decline Triceps Extension', 'SZ-Stange-Trizepsstrecken auf der Negativbank', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Lie on a decline bench with your head lower than your feet and your feet secured. Hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Extend your arms fully, keeping your elbows close to your head. Lower the barbell slowly towards your forehead, bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Lie on a decline bench with your head lower than your feet and your feet secured.","Hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Extend your arms fully, keeping your elbows close to your head.","Lower the barbell slowly towards your forehead, bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf eine Negativbank, der Kopf tiefer als die Füsse, die Füsse sind fixiert.","Halte die SZ-Stange im Obergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Strecke die Arme vollständig, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Kopf.","Senke die Stange langsam Richtung Stirn, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2186.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2186.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2d5516ea-026e-5a1d-8485-48e7c7db88d3', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Incline Triceps Extension', 'SZ-Stange-Trizepsstrecken auf der Schrägbank', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip. Extend your arms fully overhead, keeping your elbows close to your head. Lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows, keeping your upper arms stationary. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip.","Extend your arms fully overhead, keeping your elbows close to your head.","Lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows, keeping your upper arms stationary.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Setz dich auf die Bank, der Rücken liegt am Polster, und halte die SZ-Stange im Obergriff.","Strecke die Arme vollständig über den Kopf, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Kopf.","Senke die Stange hinter den Kopf, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, die Oberarme bleiben ruhig.","Halte kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0449.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0449.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d8972063-54cb-51e0-a20e-b7dd4448b8d3', NULL, 'EZ Barbell JM Bench Press', 'SZ-Stange-JM-Bankdrücken', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench. Grasp the ez barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lower the barbell to your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in close to your body. Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench.","Grasp the ez barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lower the barbell to your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in close to your body.","Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und drücke den Rücken gegen die Bank.","Greife die SZ-Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Senke die Stange zur Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben eng am Körper.","Drücke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0450.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0450.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6ee373b4-d81a-56b4-a945-150b8156915a', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Reverse Grip Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Curl im Obergriff', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the exercise. Curl the barbell upwards by contracting your biceps, while exhaling. Continue to raise the barbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the barbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Slowly begin to bring the barbell back to the starting position as you inhale. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the exercise.","Curl the barbell upwards by contracting your biceps, while exhaling.","Continue to raise the barbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the barbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Slowly begin to bring the barbell back to the starting position as you inhale.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff.","Halte die Ellbogen während der gesamten Übung nah am Oberkörper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Curle die Stange durch Anspannen des Bizeps nach oben, während du ausatmest.","Hebe die Stange weiter an, bis der Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Stange auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke den Bizeps zusammen.","Atme ein und führe die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0451.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0451.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b8499d45-b6de-5587-b44e-3a8dfbc9a783', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Reverse Grip Preacher Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Scott-Curl im Obergriff', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on a preacher bench with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Rest your upper arms on the pad, allowing your forearms to hang down. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a preacher bench with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Rest your upper arms on the pad, allowing your forearms to hang down.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Scott-Bank, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Lege die Oberarme auf das Polster, sodass die Unterarme nach unten hängen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Stange zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0452.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0452.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a076eb02-60ab-571e-9cc5-84f837ae7936', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Seated Curls', 'SZ-Stange-Curl im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and your hands shoulder-width apart. Rest your upper arms on your thighs, allowing the ez barbell to hang down in front of you. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the ez barbell upwards towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the ez barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and your hands shoulder-width apart.","Rest your upper arms on your thighs, allowing the ez barbell to hang down in front of you.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the ez barbell upwards towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the ez barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte den Rücken gerade.","Halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Lege die Oberarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die SZ-Stange vor dir herunterhängt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Stange nach oben zu den Schultern.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1458.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1458.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2bf499a1-77b3-5fe4-8aaf-4d96f8bdc3ea', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Seated Triceps Extension', 'SZ-Stange-Trizepsstrecken im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Raise the barbell overhead, fully extending your arms. Keeping your upper arms stationary, lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then raise the barbell back to the starting position by extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the ez barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Raise the barbell overhead, fully extending your arms.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then raise the barbell back to the starting position by extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte die SZ-Stange im Obergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Hebe die Stange über den Kopf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und senke die Stange hinter den Kopf, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Stange durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0453.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0453.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4f874b09-a666-553c-9006-90183ec2ecfc', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Spider Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Spider-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Rest your upper arms on a preacher bench or stability ball, allowing your elbows to hang down. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Rest your upper arms on a preacher bench or stability ball, allowing your elbows to hang down.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Oberarme auf eine Scott-Bank oder einen Gymnastikball, sodass die Ellbogen nach unten hängen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Stange zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0454.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0454.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5d86dbd0-e6e0-5318-bf49-c0203bd398dc', NULL, 'EZ Barbell Spider Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Spider-Curl', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Rest your upper arms on a preacher bench or stability ball, allowing your elbows to hang down. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Rest your upper arms on a preacher bench or stability ball, allowing your elbows to hang down.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Oberarme auf eine Scott-Bank oder einen Gymnastikball, sodass die Ellbogen nach unten hängen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Stange zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1628.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1628.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c0fee57c-b454-582a-a8d8-7aa41520c2ad', NULL, 'EZ-Bar Biceps Curl (with Arm Blaster)', 'SZ-Stange-Bizepscurl (mit Arm Blaster)', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Place your upper arms against the arm blaster, keeping them stationary throughout the exercise. Keeping your elbows close to your body, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Place your upper arms against the arm blaster, keeping them stationary throughout the exercise.","Keeping your elbows close to your body, exhale and curl the barbell up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Oberarme an den Arm-Blaster an und halte sie während der gesamten Übung ruhig.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper, atme aus und curle die Stange zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2404.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2404.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c908a81e-6a3b-5ff0-a409-dd9a1a5870b1', NULL, 'EZ-Bar Close-Grip Bench Press', 'SZ-Stange-Bankdrücken eng gegriffen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'ez barbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench. Grasp the ez barbell with a close grip, hands shoulder-width apart, palms facing forward. Lift the barbell off the rack and hold it directly above your chest with your arms fully extended. Slowly lower the barbell towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest. Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and your back pressed against the bench.","Grasp the ez barbell with a close grip, hands shoulder-width apart, palms facing forward.","Lift the barbell off the rack and hold it directly above your chest with your arms fully extended.","Slowly lower the barbell towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest.","Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und drücke den Rücken gegen die Bank.","Greife die SZ-Stange im engen Griff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander, Handflächen nach vorne.","Hebe die Stange von der Ablage und halte sie mit vollständig gestreckten Armen direkt über der Brust.","Senke die Stange langsam Richtung Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne, sobald die Stange die Brust berührt.","Drücke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2432.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2432.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a4b37beb-a291-5439-b7d7-8f39ef04e14e', NULL, 'EZ-Barbell Standing Wide Grip Biceps Curl', 'SZ-Stange-Bizepscurl breit gegriffen stehend', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'ez barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement. Curl the barbell up towards your shoulders by contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the ez barbell with an underhand grip, hands wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and your upper arms stationary throughout the movement.","Curl the barbell up towards your shoulders by contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand und halte die SZ-Stange im Untergriff, die Hände breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte die Ellbogen während der gesamten Bewegung nah am Oberkörper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Curle die Stange durch Anspannen des Bizeps zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2741.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2741.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7c75cb56-e467-584f-bab5-3c4d3d1be6a1', NULL, 'Farmer''s Walk', 'Kurzhantel-Farmer''s Walk', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'dumbbell', 'Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your sides. Keep your back straight and your shoulders back. Take small, controlled steps forward, maintaining an upright posture. Continue walking for the desired distance or time. To finish, stop walking and carefully lower the dumbbells to your sides.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","forearms","core"]', '["Stand up straight with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing your sides.","Keep your back straight and your shoulders back.","Take small, controlled steps forward, maintaining an upright posture.","Continue walking for the desired distance or time.","To finish, stop walking and carefully lower the dumbbells to your sides."]', '["Steh aufrecht und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zur Seite gerichtet.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Schultern zurück.","Mache kleine, kontrollierte Schritte nach vorne und halte eine aufrechte Haltung.","Gehe die gewünschte Distanz oder Zeit weiter.","Bleibe zum Abschluss stehen und senke die Kurzhanteln vorsichtig seitlich ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2133.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2133.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1bdd76c9-62da-5314-836f-1592db08c7b5', NULL, 'Finger Curls', 'Langhantel-Fingercurl', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'barbell', 'Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge. Slowly curl your fingers towards your palms, squeezing the barbell tightly. Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly release your fingers back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'wrist flexors', '["wrist flexors","grip muscles"]', '["Sit on a bench with your feet flat on the ground and hold a barbell with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off the edge.","Slowly curl your fingers towards your palms, squeezing the barbell tightly.","Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly release your fingers back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden und halte eine Langhantel im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Unterarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die Handgelenke über die Kante hinausragen.","Curle die Finger langsam zu den Handflächen und umschliesse die Stange fest.","Halte die Anspannung kurz und öffne die Finger dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0455.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0455.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9c9d8a49-db55-5fb6-9665-1355c2b4a1a3', NULL, 'Flag', 'Human Flag', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by gripping a vertical pole with both hands, palms facing each other, and arms fully extended. Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight. Using your core and upper body strength, raise your legs until they are parallel to the ground. Hold this position for as long as you can, maintaining a straight body line. Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","shoulders"]', '["Start by gripping a vertical pole with both hands, palms facing each other, and arms fully extended.","Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight.","Using your core and upper body strength, raise your legs until they are parallel to the ground.","Hold this position for as long as you can, maintaining a straight body line.","Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife eine senkrechte Stange mit beiden Händen, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine gestreckt vom Boden ab.","Hebe die Beine mithilfe von Körpermitte und Oberkörperkraft, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte diese Position so lange wie möglich und behalte eine gerade Körperlinie bei.","Senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3303.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3303.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8760b96e-a7e9-5f7e-897b-727372cfceb3', NULL, 'Flexion Leg Sit-Up (Bent Knee)', 'Sit-up mit Beinbeugung (Knie gebeugt)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. At the same time, lift your legs off the ground, bending your knees and bringing them towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","At the same time, lift your legs off the ground, bending your knees and bringing them towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden, bis er in einem 45-Grad-Winkel steht.","Hebe gleichzeitig die Beine vom Boden, beuge die Knie und ziehe sie Richtung Brust.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke Oberkörper und Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0456.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0456.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5b60e460-311b-5d93-bb62-8e3d9f4eb025', NULL, 'Flexion Leg Sit-Up (Straight Arm)', 'Sit-up mit Beinbeugung (gestreckter Arm)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and arms straight above your head. Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground while simultaneously lifting your legs towards your chest. Reach your hands towards your toes as you lift your upper body and legs. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","quadriceps"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and arms straight above your head.","Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground while simultaneously lifting your legs towards your chest.","Reach your hands towards your toes as you lift your upper body and legs.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt, die Arme gerade über den Kopf.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper vom Boden, während du gleichzeitig die Beine Richtung Brust hebst.","Strecke die Hände beim Anheben von Oberkörper und Beinen Richtung Zehen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke Oberkörper und Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0457.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0457.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('d2739f7b-705f-5345-904c-3063bc7777eb', NULL, 'Floor Fly (with Barbell)', 'Langhantel-Fliegende am Boden', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'barbell', 'Lie flat on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold a barbell with an overhand grip, arms extended straight up over your chest. Slowly lower the barbell out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Lower the barbell until your arms are parallel to the floor, feeling a stretch in your chest. Pause for a moment, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'deltoids', '["deltoids","triceps"]', '["Lie flat on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a barbell with an overhand grip, arms extended straight up over your chest.","Slowly lower the barbell out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Lower the barbell until your arms are parallel to the floor, feeling a stretch in your chest.","Pause for a moment, then squeeze your chest muscles to bring the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken auf den Boden, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte eine Langhantel im Obergriff, die Arme gerade über die Brust gestreckt.","Senke die Stange langsam seitlich ab, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Stange, bis die Arme parallel zum Boden sind, und spüre die Dehnung in der Brust.","Halte kurz inne und spanne die Brustmuskulatur an, um die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu bringen.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0458.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0458.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7b727b6-1b9b-5807-8c00-4cda63d2d5eb', NULL, 'Flutter Kicks', 'Flutter Kicks', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your hands by your sides. Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground about 6 inches. Keeping your legs straight, alternate lifting one leg slightly higher than the other. Continue this fluttering motion for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower abs"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your hands by your sides.","Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground about 6 inches.","Keeping your legs straight, alternate lifting one leg slightly higher than the other.","Continue this fluttering motion for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt, die Hände seitlich am Körper.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine etwa 15 Zentimeter vom Boden ab.","Halte die Beine gestreckt und hebe abwechselnd ein Bein leicht höher als das andere.","Führe diese Flatterbewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen fort."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0459.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0459.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a69cb180-85f3-5e73-8bfa-9a4b475be346', NULL, 'Forward Jump', 'Sprung vorwärts', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body into a squat position. Swing your arms back for momentum. Jump forward explosively, extending your hips, knees, and ankles. Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next jump. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees and lower your body into a squat position.","Swing your arms back for momentum.","Jump forward explosively, extending your hips, knees, and ankles.","Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next jump.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Beuge die Knie und senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab.","Schwinge die Arme für Schwung nach hinten.","Springe explosiv nach vorne und strecke dabei Hüfte, Knie und Fussgelenke.","Lande weich auf den Fussballen und gehe sofort in den nächsten Sprung über.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1472.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1472.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f9769d84-8e1f-5e27-af3f-dcebf6b95a1a', NULL, 'Forward Lunge (Male)', 'Ausfallschritt vorwärts (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart and hands on your hips. Take a big step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. Bend your right knee to about 90 degrees, keeping your knee aligned with your ankle. Push off with your right foot and return to the starting position. Repeat with your left leg, alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart and hands on your hips.","Take a big step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","Bend your right knee to about 90 degrees, keeping your knee aligned with your ankle.","Push off with your right foot and return to the starting position.","Repeat with your left leg, alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich hüftbreit hin, die Hände an der Hüfte.","Mache mit dem rechten Fuss einen grossen Schritt nach vorne und senke den Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Beuge das rechte Knie auf etwa 90 Grad, das Knie bleibt in Linie mit dem Fussgelenk.","Drücke dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole mit dem linken Bein und wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3470.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3470.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('69dfe5c7-b246-574b-a502-56359d0c24ff', NULL, 'Frankenstein Squat', 'Langhantel-Frankenstein-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell in front of your body with straight arms. Keeping your back straight, lower your body by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell in front of your body with straight arms.","Keeping your back straight, lower your body by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die Langhantel mit gestreckten Armen vor dem Körper.","Halte den Rücken gerade und senke den Körper durch Beugen von Knien und Hüfte, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3194.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3194.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1aeedb42-1dee-5aa8-85f6-5c1c20ef2265', NULL, 'Frog Crunch', 'Frosch-Crunch', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper vom Boden, bis er in einem 45-Grad-Winkel steht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2429.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2429.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('af4b89ee-0c86-5571-ba73-62b5d480b877', NULL, 'Frog Planche', 'Frosch-Planche', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back straight. As you lower your body, lift your feet off the ground and bring your knees towards your chest. Hold this position for a few seconds, then extend your legs back out and push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","triceps"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back straight.","As you lower your body, lift your feet off the ground and bring your knees towards your chest.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then extend your legs back out and push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander, die Füsse zusammen.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke den Körper Richtung Boden, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Hebe beim Absenken die Füsse vom Boden und ziehe die Knie Richtung Brust.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden, strecke die Beine dann wieder aus und drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3301.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3301.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ff4fb076-1eb9-52d5-8ea0-ca1b395d50b0', NULL, 'Front Lever', 'Front Lever', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back. Bend your knees and tuck them towards your chest. Simultaneously, lift your legs up and extend them straight out in front of you, keeping your body parallel to the ground. Hold this position for as long as you can, aiming for a full front lever position. To release, slowly lower your legs back down and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'lats', '["lats","shoulders","forearms"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back.","Bend your knees and tuck them towards your chest.","Simultaneously, lift your legs up and extend them straight out in front of you, keeping your body parallel to the ground.","Hold this position for as long as you can, aiming for a full front lever position.","To release, slowly lower your legs back down and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich mit Obergriff an eine Klimmzugstange, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter nach unten und hinten.","Beuge die Knie und ziehe sie Richtung Brust.","Hebe gleichzeitig die Beine an und strecke sie gerade vor dir aus, der Körper bleibt parallel zum Boden.","Halte diese Position so lange wie möglich, mit dem Ziel einer vollständigen Front-Lever-Position.","Senke die Beine zum Lösen langsam ab und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3296.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3296.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('94ce77fd-dc82-59dd-ba69-d80591cb2e86', NULL, 'Front Lever Reps', 'Front Lever (Wiederholungen)', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, palms facing away from you. Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back. Keeping your body straight, lift your legs up until they are parallel to the ground. Hold this position for as long as you can, aiming for 10-20 seconds. Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","shoulders"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back.","Keeping your body straight, lift your legs up until they are parallel to the ground.","Hold this position for as long as you can, aiming for 10-20 seconds.","Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich mit Obergriff an eine Klimmzugstange, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter nach unten und hinten.","Halte den Körper gerade und hebe die Beine an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte diese Position so lange wie möglich, mit dem Ziel von 10 bis 20 Sekunden.","Senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3295.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3295.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9ed5b59a-c76e-5cce-96d2-85df047a475f', NULL, 'Front Plank with Twist', 'Plank mit Drehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line from head to toe. Engage your core and glutes to maintain a stable position. Rotate your torso to the right, lifting your right arm and extending it towards the ceiling. Keep your hips and legs stable as you twist. Hold for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat the twist on the left side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Engage your core and glutes to maintain a stable position.","Rotate your torso to the right, lifting your right arm and extending it towards the ceiling.","Keep your hips and legs stable as you twist.","Hold for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the twist on the left side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in den hohen Unterarmstütz (Plank), die Hände direkt unter den Schultern, der Körper bildet eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Spanne Körpermitte und Gesäss an, um eine stabile Position zu halten.","Drehe den Oberkörper nach rechts, hebe den rechten Arm und strecke ihn Richtung Decke.","Halte Hüfte und Beine bei der Drehung stabil.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Drehung auf der linken Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0464.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0464.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f1d8807f-28e9-551d-b86a-a13bb1f5bd86', NULL, 'Full Maltese', 'Full Maltese', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended straight out to the sides. Slowly lean forward, keeping your arms straight, until your upper body is parallel to the ground. Engage your core and hold this position for a few seconds. Return to the starting position by pushing through your feet and standing back up. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended straight out to the sides.","Slowly lean forward, keeping your arms straight, until your upper body is parallel to the ground.","Engage your core and hold this position for a few seconds.","Return to the starting position by pushing through your feet and standing back up.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und strecke die Arme seitlich gerade aus.","Lehne dich langsam nach vorne, die Arme bleiben gestreckt, bis der Oberkörper parallel zum Boden ist.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte diese Position einige Sekunden.","Kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du dich über die Füsse abdrückst und wieder aufrichtest.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3315.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3315.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b2fc1a8a-c80a-5c7f-8d74-6c15a3aa857c', NULL, 'Full Planche', 'Full Planche', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your fingers pointing forward. Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, lifting your feet off the ground. Continue shifting your weight forward until your body is parallel to the ground, balancing on your hands. Hold this position for as long as you can, maintaining a straight body line. Slowly lower your feet back to the ground and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","triceps"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your fingers pointing forward.","Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, lifting your feet off the ground.","Continue shifting your weight forward until your body is parallel to the ground, balancing on your hands.","Hold this position for as long as you can, maintaining a straight body line.","Slowly lower your feet back to the ground and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und verlagere das Gewicht langsam nach vorne, während du die Füsse vom Boden hebst.","Verlagere das Gewicht weiter nach vorne, bis der Körper parallel zum Boden ist und du auf den Händen balancierst.","Halte diese Position so lange wie möglich und behalte eine gerade Körperlinie bei.","Senke die Füsse langsam zurück auf den Boden und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3299.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3299.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3ec9abc2-f3d9-5e20-b842-eb75a1a87857', NULL, 'Full Planche Push-Up', 'Full-Planche-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands placed slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and lower your body down towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides. As you lower yourself, lean your body forward and lift your feet off the ground, balancing on your hands. Continue to lower your body until your chest is just above the ground. Push through your hands and extend your arms to lift your body back up to the starting position. Maintain a straight line from your head to your heels throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands placed slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and lower your body down towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides.","As you lower yourself, lean your body forward and lift your feet off the ground, balancing on your hands.","Continue to lower your body until your chest is just above the ground.","Push through your hands and extend your arms to lift your body back up to the starting position.","Maintain a straight line from your head to your heels throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke den Körper Richtung Boden, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Lehne den Körper beim Absenken nach vorne und hebe die Füsse vom Boden, sodass du auf den Händen balancierst.","Senke den Körper weiter ab, bis die Brust knapp über dem Boden ist.","Drücke dich über die Hände ab und strecke die Arme, um den Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Halte während der gesamten Bewegung eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3327.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3327.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d536d59b-0ca8-58d9-a0a7-f4dcb7fadceb', NULL, 'Gironda Sternum Chin', 'Gironda-Sternum-Klimmzug (Untergriff)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a high bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Reach up and grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your lats and biceps to pull your chest up towards the bar, leading with your sternum. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Stand facing a high bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Reach up and grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your lats and biceps to pull your chest up towards the bar, leading with your sternum.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich vor eine hohe Stange, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge an der Stange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, der Körper gerade.","Spanne Latissimus und Bizeps an und ziehe die Brust, angeführt vom Brustbein, zur Stange hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0466.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0466.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c6423816-ced7-5796-ba55-f87a74cb2fbe', NULL, 'Glute Bridge March', 'Hüftheben marschierend', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. While keeping your hips lifted, lift one foot off the ground and bring your knee towards your chest. Lower your foot back to the ground and repeat the movement with the other leg. Continue alternating legs in a marching motion while maintaining the bridge position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","While keeping your hips lifted, lift one foot off the ground and bring your knee towards your chest.","Lower your foot back to the ground and repeat the movement with the other leg.","Continue alternating legs in a marching motion while maintaining the bridge position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Spanne das Gesäss an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden, sodass eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern entsteht.","Hebe bei angehobener Hüfte einen Fuss vom Boden und ziehe das Knie Richtung Brust.","Setze den Fuss zurück auf den Boden und wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem anderen Bein.","Wechsle die Beine in einer Marschbewegung ab, während du die Brücken-Position hältst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3561.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3561.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9d84b3ea-49dd-59a9-b384-34e6dadf5f1c', NULL, 'Glute Bridge Two Legs on Bench (Male)', 'Hüftheben beidbeinig mit Bank (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a bench with your back against it and your feet flat on the ground. Place your hands on the bench beside your hips for support. Engage your glutes and hamstrings, then lift your hips off the bench until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","core"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench with your back against it and your feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands on the bench beside your hips for support.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings, then lift your hips off the bench until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich an den Rand einer Bank, der Rücken lehnt daran, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Stütze die Hände neben der Hüfte auf der Bank ab.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und hebe die Hüfte von der Bank, bis eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Hüfte dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3523.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3523.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f495db7b-e5d6-5e22-bb0c-3229c9248e3a', NULL, 'Glute-Ham Raise', 'Glute-Ham-Raise', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Adjust the glute-ham raise machine to fit your body. Position yourself face down on the machine with your ankles secured. Place your hands on your chest or cross them over your chest. Engage your hamstrings and glutes to lift your upper body up towards the ceiling. Continue lifting until your body is in a straight line from your head to your heels. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","lower back"]', '["Adjust the glute-ham raise machine to fit your body.","Position yourself face down on the machine with your ankles secured.","Place your hands on your chest or cross them over your chest.","Engage your hamstrings and glutes to lift your upper body up towards the ceiling.","Continue lifting until your body is in a straight line from your head to your heels.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Glute-Ham-Raise-Gerät auf deine Körpergrösse ein.","Positioniere dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf dem Gerät, die Knöchel fixiert.","Lege die Hände auf die Brust oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne Beinbeuger und Gesäss an und hebe den Oberkörper Richtung Decke.","Hebe weiter an, bis der Körper eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse bildet.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3193.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3193.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f7effdb2-3291-5997-aa15-1fa3d464d85b', NULL, 'Gorilla Chin', 'Gorilla-Klimmzug (Untergriff)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, bringing your chin above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, bringing your chin above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife eine Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge an der Stange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe den Körper zur Stange hoch, bis das Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0467.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0467.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('198717cb-8558-5469-a71f-95240ff23bb7', NULL, 'Groin Crunch', 'Leisten-Crunch', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the ground, bringing your knees towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","inner thighs"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the ground, bringing your knees towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe die Beine vom Boden, während du die Knie Richtung Brust ziehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0469.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0469.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7afc9500-452c-5bfc-9cc7-5c8e235abdd1', NULL, 'Hack Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben an der Hackenschmidt-Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight. Stand on the sled machine with your toes on the platform and your heels hanging off. Hold onto the handles for stability. Raise your heels as high as possible by pushing through the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight.","Stand on the sled machine with your toes on the platform and your heels hanging off.","Hold onto the handles for stability.","Raise your heels as high as possible by pushing through the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Schlitten-Gerät auf ein angenehmes Gewicht ein.","Stell dich auf das Gerät, die Zehen auf der Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen fest.","Hebe die Fersen so hoch wie möglich an, indem du dich über die Fussballen abdrückst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1383.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1383.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('42644f80-9785-587a-8a90-68c8881d4e5c', NULL, 'Hack One Leg Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben einbeinig an der Hackenschmidt-Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to an appropriate weight. Stand on the sled machine with one foot, keeping the other foot off the ground. Hold onto the handles for stability. Raise your heel as high as possible, lifting your body up on the ball of your foot. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions. Switch legs and repeat the exercise.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to an appropriate weight.","Stand on the sled machine with one foot, keeping the other foot off the ground.","Hold onto the handles for stability.","Raise your heel as high as possible, lifting your body up on the ball of your foot.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.","Switch legs and repeat the exercise."]', '["Stelle das Schlitten-Gerät auf ein passendes Gewicht ein.","Stell dich mit einem Fuss auf das Gerät, der andere Fuss bleibt in der Luft.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen fest.","Hebe die Ferse so hoch wie möglich und hebe den Körper auf den Fussballen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Ferse dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen.","Wechsle das Bein und wiederhole die Übung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1384.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1384.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8d08595b-1f55-530a-a8ef-f6254fc11ac0', NULL, 'Half Knee Bends (Male)', 'Halbe Kniebeugen (Mann)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body down as if you were sitting back into a chair. Keep your chest up and your weight in your heels. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees and lower your body down as if you were sitting back into a chair.","Keep your chest up and your weight in your heels.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Beuge die Knie und senke den Körper ab, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte die Brust oben und das Gewicht auf den Fersen.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3221.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3221.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4a866e16-f8fb-5330-9d17-eee800393f51', NULL, 'Half Sit-Up (Male)', 'Halber Sit-up (Mann)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden, bis er in einem 45-Grad-Winkel steht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3202.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3202.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eaee27e3-312a-542c-86b9-01eb8aff50d7', NULL, 'Hamstring Stretch', 'Beinbeuger-Dehnung', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Step forward with your right foot and shift your weight onto your right leg. Keeping your back straight, slowly bend forward at the hips, reaching towards your right foot with both hands. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Step forward with your right foot and shift your weight onto your right leg.","Keeping your back straight, slowly bend forward at the hips, reaching towards your right foot with both hands.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Mache einen Schritt nach vorne mit dem rechten Fuss und verlagere das Gewicht auf das rechte Bein.","Halte den Rücken gerade und beuge dich langsam aus der Hüfte nach vorne, die Hände greifen Richtung rechten Fuss.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1511.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1511.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('74ddba72-7d78-570d-98d0-83c53e49d2e6', NULL, 'Hands Bike', 'Handbike (Armergometer)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'upper body ergometer', 'Adjust the seat height and handlebar position to a comfortable level. Sit on the ergometer with your back straight and feet on the pedals. Grasp the handles with your hands and position your arms at a 90-degree angle. Start pedaling with your hands, pushing and pulling the handles in a controlled motion. Continue pedaling for the desired duration or number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and handlebar position to a comfortable level.","Sit on the ergometer with your back straight and feet on the pedals.","Grasp the handles with your hands and position your arms at a 90-degree angle.","Start pedaling with your hands, pushing and pulling the handles in a controlled motion.","Continue pedaling for the desired duration or number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Lenkerposition auf ein angenehmes Niveau ein.","Setz dich auf das Ergometer, halte den Rücken gerade, die Füsse auf den Pedalen.","Greife die Griffe mit den Händen und positioniere die Arme im 90-Grad-Winkel.","Beginne mit den Händen zu kurbeln, indem du die Griffe kontrolliert drückst und ziehst.","Kurble für die gewünschte Dauer oder Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2139.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2139.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e71eb171-949c-56be-9795-fa1a4628c4d9', NULL, 'Hands Clasped Circular Toe Touch (Male)', 'Kreisende Zehenberührung mit gefalteten Händen (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your hands clasped together in front of your chest. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Lower your hands towards your toes in a circular motion, reaching as far as you can without straining. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your hands clasped together in front of your chest.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Lower your hands towards your toes in a circular motion, reaching as far as you can without straining.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und falte die Hände vor der Brust.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Senke die Hände in einer Kreisbewegung Richtung Zehen, so weit wie möglich, ohne dich zu überdehnen.","Halte unten kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3218.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3218.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('608c0cf9-ef02-559d-996e-1122d1eb8964', NULL, 'Hands Reversed Clasped Circular Toe Touch (Male)', 'Kreisende Zehenberührung mit umgekehrt gefalteten Händen (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended to the sides. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent. Reach down with your hands and clasp them together behind your legs. Slowly raise your hands up and over your head in a circular motion, keeping your legs straight. Continue the circular motion until your hands touch your toes. Reverse the motion and bring your hands back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended to the sides.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent.","Reach down with your hands and clasp them together behind your legs.","Slowly raise your hands up and over your head in a circular motion, keeping your legs straight.","Continue the circular motion until your hands touch your toes.","Reverse the motion and bring your hands back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und strecke die Arme seitlich aus.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife mit den Händen nach unten und falte sie hinter den Beinen zusammen.","Hebe die Hände langsam in einer Kreisbewegung über den Kopf, die Beine bleiben gestreckt.","Führe die Kreisbewegung fort, bis die Hände die Zehen berühren.","Kehre die Bewegung um und führe die Hände zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3215.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3215.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('643de1b3-e1b9-52a8-a98c-9d41c63c6261', NULL, 'Handstand', 'Handstand', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Find an open space with enough room to perform a handstand. Place your hands on the ground shoulder-width apart, fingers pointing forward. Kick your legs up towards the wall, using your core and shoulders to maintain balance. Once in a handstand position, engage your triceps to support your body weight. Hold the handstand for as long as you can maintain balance. To come down, slowly lower your legs back to the ground. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Find an open space with enough room to perform a handstand.","Place your hands on the ground shoulder-width apart, fingers pointing forward.","Kick your legs up towards the wall, using your core and shoulders to maintain balance.","Once in a handstand position, engage your triceps to support your body weight.","Hold the handstand for as long as you can maintain balance.","To come down, slowly lower your legs back to the ground.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Suche dir einen freien Platz mit ausreichend Raum für einen Handstand.","Stütze die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Boden ab, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schwinge die Beine Richtung Wand hoch und halte mit Körpermitte und Schultern das Gleichgewicht.","Spanne im Handstand den Trizeps an, um das Körpergewicht zu tragen.","Halte den Handstand, solange du das Gleichgewicht halten kannst.","Senke die Beine zum Beenden langsam zurück auf den Boden.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3302.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3302.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ba547013-24ee-54c6-89b3-cfc5c35b3c36', NULL, 'Handstand Push-Up', 'Handstand-Liegestütz', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Find a wall and face away from it, standing a few feet away. Place your hands on the ground shoulder-width apart and kick your feet up against the wall, coming into a handstand position. Bend your elbows and lower your head towards the ground, keeping your body in a straight line. Push through your hands and extend your arms to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","core"]', '["Find a wall and face away from it, standing a few feet away.","Place your hands on the ground shoulder-width apart and kick your feet up against the wall, coming into a handstand position.","Bend your elbows and lower your head towards the ground, keeping your body in a straight line.","Push through your hands and extend your arms to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit dem Rücken zu einer Wand, einige Schritte davon entfernt.","Stütze die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Boden ab und schwinge die Füsse gegen die Wand hoch in eine Handstand-Position.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke den Kopf Richtung Boden, der Körper bleibt in einer geraden Linie.","Drücke dich über die Hände ab und strecke die Arme, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0471.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0471.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('335dcd05-9457-5c36-b05d-d7dc05bc2cbb', NULL, 'Hanging Leg Hip Raise', 'Hängendes Bein- und Hüftheben', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up by flexing your hips and knees until your thighs are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up by flexing your hips and knees until your thighs are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine, indem du Hüfte und Knie beugst, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1764.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1764.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8dd94d51-5bb3-5738-9fb0-5e5fd51918d4', NULL, 'Hanging Leg Raise', 'Hängendes Beinheben', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight. Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or as high as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight.","Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or as high as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine gestreckt vor dir an.","Hebe weiter an, bis die Beine parallel zum Boden sind oder so hoch, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0472.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0472.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9b480063-0634-570c-921f-323ec990d7f3', NULL, 'Hanging Oblique Knee Raise', 'Hängendes seitliches Knieheben', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your knees towards your chest, twisting your torso to the side as you do so. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat on the other side, twisting your torso in the opposite direction. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your knees towards your chest, twisting your torso to the side as you do so.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side, twisting your torso in the opposite direction.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Knie Richtung Brust, während du den Oberkörper dabei zur Seite drehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite und drehe den Oberkörper in die entgegengesetzte Richtung.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1761.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1761.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cc6b2c95-6c25-535e-b99a-2443fdec9cd6', NULL, 'Hanging Pike', 'Hängender Pike', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up towards the bar, keeping them straight. Continue lifting until your body forms a ''V'' shape, with your legs parallel to the ground. Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","shoulders"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up towards the bar, keeping them straight.","Continue lifting until your body forms a ''V'' shape, with your legs parallel to the ground.","Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die gestreckten Beine Richtung Stange.","Hebe weiter an, bis der Körper ein V bildet und die Beine parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte die Position kurz, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0473.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0473.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('63596f2a-0095-53df-8b5b-9e5cd3ee0a7b', NULL, 'Hanging Straight Leg Hip Raise', 'Hängendes Beckenheben mit gestreckten Beinen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine vor dir an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0474.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0474.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cb8f69b1-24b7-5516-a12f-2d66fb323199', NULL, 'Hanging Straight Leg Raise', 'Hängendes Beinheben mit gestreckten Beinen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight. Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or as high as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight.","Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or as high as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, Handflächen von dir weg gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine gestreckt vor dir an.","Hebe weiter an, bis die Beine parallel zum Boden sind oder so hoch, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0475.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0475.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('11dd3f5b-f310-55ce-a913-6a5569ac6f6e', NULL, 'Hanging Straight Twisting Leg Hip Raise', 'Hängendes Beckenheben mit gestreckten Beinen und Drehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your legs straight. Engage your core and lift your legs up towards your chest, keeping them straight. Once your legs are parallel to the ground, twist your hips to one side, bringing your legs towards that side. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat the movement, but this time twist your hips to the opposite side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your legs straight.","Engage your core and lift your legs up towards your chest, keeping them straight.","Once your legs are parallel to the ground, twist your hips to one side, bringing your legs towards that side.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, but this time twist your hips to the opposite side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, die Beine gerade.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die gestreckten Beine Richtung Brust.","Sobald die Beine parallel zum Boden sind, drehe die Hüfte zu einer Seite und führe die Beine dorthin.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal mit Drehung der Hüfte zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0476.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0476.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b734e808-f7ea-54c3-8d73-29a2eb18f0c7', NULL, 'High Knee Against Wall', 'Kniehebelauf an der Wand', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a wall with your feet hip-width apart. Place your hands on the wall for support. Engage your core and lift your right knee up towards your chest, while keeping your left foot on the ground. Quickly switch legs, bringing your left knee up towards your chest and lowering your right foot back down. Continue alternating legs in a running motion, bringing your knees up as high as possible. Maintain a fast pace and keep your upper body stable throughout the exercise. Repeat for the desired duration or number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Stand facing a wall with your feet hip-width apart.","Place your hands on the wall for support.","Engage your core and lift your right knee up towards your chest, while keeping your left foot on the ground.","Quickly switch legs, bringing your left knee up towards your chest and lowering your right foot back down.","Continue alternating legs in a running motion, bringing your knees up as high as possible.","Maintain a fast pace and keep your upper body stable throughout the exercise.","Repeat for the desired duration or number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit dem Gesicht zu einer Wand, die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander.","Stütze die Hände zur Unterstützung an der Wand ab.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe das rechte Knie Richtung Brust, der linke Fuss bleibt am Boden.","Wechsle schnell die Beine, ziehe das linke Knie Richtung Brust und setze den rechten Fuss zurück ab.","Wechsle die Beine weiter in einer Laufbewegung ab und ziehe die Knie so hoch wie möglich.","Halte ein zügiges Tempo und den Oberkörper während der gesamten Übung stabil.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Dauer oder Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3636.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3636.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2b87b4b1-a6f6-5fea-a4f6-180753ea959a', NULL, 'Hip Raise (Bent Knee)', 'Hüftheben (Beine gebeugt)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands by your sides, palms facing down. Engage your core and glutes, then lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands by your sides, palms facing down.","Engage your core and glutes, then lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände seitlich an den Körper, Handflächen nach unten.","Spanne Körpermitte und Gesäss an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden, bis eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Hüfte dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0484.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0484.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a190a4a6-5e80-5c41-b135-bb45422ef002', NULL, 'Hug Knees to Chest', 'Knie zur Brust ziehen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body down into a squat position. As you squat down, bring your knees up towards your chest and hug them with your arms. Hold this position for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees and lower your body down into a squat position.","As you squat down, bring your knees up towards your chest and hug them with your arms.","Hold this position for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Beuge die Knie und senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab.","Ziehe beim Absenken die Knie Richtung Brust und umarme sie mit den Armen.","Halte diese Position kurz und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1418.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1418.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('13ee2d1f-c457-51e2-a9bb-a0cd3e6326f1', NULL, 'Hyght Dumbbell Fly', 'Hyght-Fliegende mit Kurzhanteln', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'dumbbell', 'Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other. Extend your arms straight up over your chest, with a slight bend in your elbows. Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, lower the dumbbells out to the sides in a wide arc until you feel a stretch in your chest. Pause for a moment, then reverse the movement and bring the dumbbells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing each other.","Extend your arms straight up over your chest, with a slight bend in your elbows.","Keeping a slight bend in your elbows, lower the dumbbells out to the sides in a wide arc until you feel a stretch in your chest.","Pause for a moment, then reverse the movement and bring the dumbbells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Bank und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Strecke die Arme gerade über die Brust, die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Senke die Kurzhanteln bei leicht gebeugten Ellbogen in einem weiten Bogen seitlich ab, bis du eine Dehnung in der Brust spürst.","Halte kurz inne und führe die Kurzhanteln in umgekehrter Bewegung zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3234.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3234.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a23dd8a1-0d80-55a6-98d3-8ce7ad7f46d8', NULL, 'Hyperextension', 'Hyperextension', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Adjust the hyperextension bench so that your upper thighs are resting on the pad and your feet are secured. Cross your arms over your chest or place your hands behind your head. Lower your upper body towards the ground while keeping your back straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then raise your upper body back up until it is in line with your legs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the hyperextension bench so that your upper thighs are resting on the pad and your feet are secured.","Cross your arms over your chest or place your hands behind your head.","Lower your upper body towards the ground while keeping your back straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then raise your upper body back up until it is in line with your legs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Hyperextensionsbank so ein, dass die Oberschenkel auf dem Polster liegen und die Füsse fixiert sind.","Verschränke die Arme vor der Brust oder lege die Hände hinter den Kopf.","Senke den Oberkörper Richtung Boden, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Halte unten kurz inne und richte den Oberkörper dann wieder auf, bis er mit den Beinen eine Linie bildet.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0489.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0489.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('557631b2-4001-5592-be31-0f28cb21a3bb', NULL, 'Hyperextension (on Bench)', 'Hyperextension auf der Bank', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Adjust the hyperextension bench so that your hips are resting comfortably on the pad and your feet are secured. Cross your arms over your chest or place your hands behind your head. Slowly lower your upper body towards the ground while keeping your back straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then raise your upper body back up until it is in line with your legs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the hyperextension bench so that your hips are resting comfortably on the pad and your feet are secured.","Cross your arms over your chest or place your hands behind your head.","Slowly lower your upper body towards the ground while keeping your back straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then raise your upper body back up until it is in line with your legs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Hyperextensionsbank so ein, dass die Hüfte bequem auf dem Polster liegt und die Füsse fixiert sind.","Verschränke die Arme vor der Brust oder lege die Hände hinter den Kopf.","Senke den Oberkörper langsam Richtung Boden, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Halte unten kurz inne und richte den Oberkörper dann wieder auf, bis er mit den Beinen eine Linie bildet.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0488.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0488.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e79e1f9e-1753-5ce7-99a3-65690527ba55', NULL, 'Impossible Dips', 'Impossible Dips', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body suspended in the air. Bend your knees and cross your ankles. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body suspended in the air.","Bend your knees and cross your ankles.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich zwischen zwei Dip-Barren, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, der Körper frei schwebend.","Beuge die Knie und kreuze die Fussgelenke.","Senke den Körper, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis die Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3289.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3289.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('544200a0-7d12-5ded-8d45-4e4de2e7711a', NULL, 'Inchworm', 'Inchworm', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a standing position with your feet hip-width apart. Bend forward at the waist and place your hands on the ground in front of you. Walk your hands forward until you are in a high plank position, with your body in a straight line from head to toe. Pause for a moment, then walk your hands back towards your feet, keeping your legs as straight as possible. Once your hands reach your feet, stand back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","hamstrings"]', '["Start in a standing position with your feet hip-width apart.","Bend forward at the waist and place your hands on the ground in front of you.","Walk your hands forward until you are in a high plank position, with your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Pause for a moment, then walk your hands back towards your feet, keeping your legs as straight as possible.","Once your hands reach your feet, stand back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich hüftbreit hin.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne und stütze die Hände vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Gehe mit den Händen nach vorne, bis du im hohen Stütz bist, der Körper bildet eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Halte kurz inne und gehe mit den Händen dann zurück zu den Füssen, die Beine bleiben möglichst gestreckt.","Sobald die Hände die Füsse erreichen, richte dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition auf.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1471.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1471.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9d44bdf3-ebee-545d-8408-fb52102383dd', NULL, 'Inchworm V. 2', 'Inchworm V. 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a standing position with your feet hip-width apart. Bend forward at the waist and place your hands on the ground in front of you. Walk your hands forward until you are in a high plank position, with your body in a straight line from head to toe. Keeping your legs straight, walk your feet towards your hands, bringing your hips up towards the ceiling. Continue walking your hands forward, repeating the movement for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","hamstrings"]', '["Start in a standing position with your feet hip-width apart.","Bend forward at the waist and place your hands on the ground in front of you.","Walk your hands forward until you are in a high plank position, with your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Keeping your legs straight, walk your feet towards your hands, bringing your hips up towards the ceiling.","Continue walking your hands forward, repeating the movement for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich hüftbreit hin.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne und stütze die Hände vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Gehe mit den Händen nach vorne, bis du im hohen Stütz bist, der Körper bildet eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Halte die Beine gestreckt und gehe mit den Füssen zu den Händen, die Hüfte hebt sich Richtung Decke.","Gehe mit den Händen weiter nach vorne und wiederhole die Bewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3698.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3698.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('69ff9873-49ba-59f6-8e22-d99c23405932', NULL, 'Incline Close-Grip Push-Up', 'Schrägbank-Liegestütz mit engem Griff', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Place your hands on an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, with your body forming a straight line from head to heels. Lower your chest towards the elevated surface by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Place your hands on an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, with your body forming a straight line from head to heels.","Lower your chest towards the elevated surface by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stütze die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf einer erhöhten Fläche wie einer Bank oder Stufe ab.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Fussballen, der Körper bildet eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Senke die Brust Richtung erhöhter Fläche, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, sie bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0490.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0490.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8ea67340-a3b0-5f89-9828-4dd218a2e6aa', NULL, 'Incline Leg Hip Raise (Leg Straight)', 'Schrägbank-Beinheben mit gestrecktem Bein', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie on an incline bench with your back flat against the bench and your legs extended straight out in front of you. Place your hands on the sides of the bench for support. Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the bench, raising them as high as you can while keeping them straight. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie on an incline bench with your back flat against the bench and your legs extended straight out in front of you.","Place your hands on the sides of the bench for support.","Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the bench, raising them as high as you can while keeping them straight.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf eine Schrägbank, der Rücken liegt flach an, die Beine gerade vor dir ausgestreckt.","Stütze die Hände seitlich an der Bank ab.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe die gestreckten Beine so hoch wie möglich von der Bank.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0491.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0491.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d3507d74-570b-5dbc-9049-599b29500624', NULL, 'Incline Push-Up Depth Jump', 'Schrägbank-Liegestütz mit Tiefensprung', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Find an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, and place your hands shoulder-width apart on the edge. Step your feet back, keeping your body in a straight line from head to heels. Lower your chest towards the edge of the surface, bending your elbows and keeping your body aligned. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Jump off the edge of the surface, landing softly with your knees slightly bent. Repeat the push-up and depth jump for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Find an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, and place your hands shoulder-width apart on the edge.","Step your feet back, keeping your body in a straight line from head to heels.","Lower your chest towards the edge of the surface, bending your elbows and keeping your body aligned.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Jump off the edge of the surface, landing softly with your knees slightly bent.","Repeat the push-up and depth jump for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Suche eine erhöhte Fläche wie eine Bank oder Stufe und stütze die Hände schulterbreit an der Kante ab.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach hinten, der Körper bildet eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Senke die Brust Richtung Kante, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, der Körper bleibt in Linie.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Springe von der Kante ab und lande weich mit leicht gebeugten Knien.","Wiederhole Liegestütz und Tiefsprung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0492.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0492.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1241a1a2-7764-5015-a1c9-fab768786445', NULL, 'Incline Push-Up', 'Schrägbank-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Place your hands on an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels. Lower your chest towards the elevated surface by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Place your hands on an elevated surface, such as a bench or step, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels.","Lower your chest towards the elevated surface by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stütze die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf einer erhöhten Fläche wie einer Bank oder Stufe ab.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Fussballen, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Senke die Brust Richtung erhöhter Fläche, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, der Körper bleibt in einer geraden Linie.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0493.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0493.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ac4330ab-d2b9-5cab-b773-1c55f34669e2', NULL, 'Incline Push-Up (on Box)', 'Schrägbank-Liegestütz auf der Box', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Place your hands on the edge of a box or elevated surface, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels. Lower your chest towards the box by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Place your hands on the edge of a box or elevated surface, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels.","Lower your chest towards the box by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stütze die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf der Kante einer Box oder erhöhten Fläche ab.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Fussballen, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Senke die Brust Richtung Box, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, der Körper bleibt in einer geraden Linie.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3785.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3785.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('dfcc53a8-0ab4-52cd-b8d3-10f1adee8f35', NULL, 'Incline Reverse Grip Push-Up', 'Schrägbank-Liegestütz mit Untergriff', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Place your hands on the edge of a bench or elevated surface, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels. Lower your chest towards the bench by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Place your hands on the edge of a bench or elevated surface, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, creating a straight line from your head to your heels.","Lower your chest towards the bench by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stütze die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf der Kante einer Bank oder erhöhten Fläche ab.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Fussballen, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse entsteht.","Senke die Brust Richtung Bank, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, sie bleiben nah am Körper.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0494.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0494.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('146dc475-5bb0-535e-bd01-370231d5d6e8', NULL, 'Incline Scapula Push-Up', 'Schrägbank-Schulterblatt-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'serratus anterior', 'body weight', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Place your hands on the bench slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Position your feet on the ground, hip-width apart. Lower your chest towards the bench, keeping your elbows tucked in. As you lower, retract your shoulder blades, squeezing your scapulae together. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Place your hands on the bench slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Position your feet on the ground, hip-width apart.","Lower your chest towards the bench, keeping your elbows tucked in.","As you lower, retract your shoulder blades, squeezing your scapulae together.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Stütze die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf der Bank ab.","Stelle die Füsse hüftbreit auf den Boden.","Senke die Brust Richtung Bank, die Ellbogen bleiben eng am Körper.","Ziehe beim Absenken die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3011.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3011.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4e7763d8-776d-58e8-95b9-cdabf2b462a6', NULL, 'Incline Twisting Sit-Up', 'Schrägbank-Sit-up mit Drehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle. Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Place your hands behind your head or across your chest. Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the bench, curling forward. As you curl up, twist your torso to one side, bringing your elbow towards the opposite knee. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time twisting your torso to the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Set up an incline bench at a 45-degree angle.","Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Place your hands behind your head or across your chest.","Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the bench, curling forward.","As you curl up, twist your torso to one side, bringing your elbow towards the opposite knee.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time twisting your torso to the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Schrägbank auf einen 45-Grad-Winkel ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper von der Bank, indem du dich nach vorne einrollst.","Drehe den Oberkörper beim Aufrollen zu einer Seite und führe den Ellbogen Richtung gegenüberliegendes Knie.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal mit Drehung zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0495.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0495.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('aecab326-9896-5254-ad9c-fef61af8304f', NULL, 'Intermediate Hip Flexor and Quad Stretch', 'Hüftbeuger- und Quadrizepsdehnung (mittlere Stufe)', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'rope', 'Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart. Hold onto a stable object for support. Bend your right knee and bring your right foot towards your glutes, grabbing the rope with your right hand. Slowly pull your right foot towards your glutes, feeling a stretch in your right quad. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Release the stretch and repeat on the left side.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Hold onto a stable object for support.","Bend your right knee and bring your right foot towards your glutes, grabbing the rope with your right hand.","Slowly pull your right foot towards your glutes, feeling a stretch in your right quad.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Release the stretch and repeat on the left side."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreitem Stand.","Halte dich zur Unterstützung an einem stabilen Gegenstand fest.","Beuge das rechte Knie und ziehe den rechten Fuss Richtung Gesäss, greife dabei mit der rechten Hand nach dem Seil.","Ziehe den rechten Fuss langsam Richtung Gesäss und spüre die Dehnung im rechten Quadrizeps.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden.","Löse die Dehnung und wiederhole auf der linken Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1564.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1564.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('87fc20e4-27fd-5754-874e-35763ef565b2', NULL, 'Inverse Leg Curl (Bench Support)', 'Inverser Beincurl (Bankstütze)', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on a bench with your hips at the edge and your legs extended straight behind you. Hold onto the bench for support. Keeping your upper body still, bend your knees and curl your legs towards your glutes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","calves"]', '["Lie face down on a bench with your hips at the edge and your legs extended straight behind you.","Hold onto the bench for support.","Keeping your upper body still, bend your knees and curl your legs towards your glutes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf eine Bank, die Hüfte an der Kante, die Beine gerade nach hinten gestreckt.","Halte dich an der Bank fest.","Halte den Oberkörper ruhig, beuge die Knie und curle die Beine Richtung Gesäss.","Halte oben kurz inne und strecke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0496.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0496.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eeb5605c-fcd2-5573-9bf3-952aa82393c0', NULL, 'Inverse Leg Curl (on Pull-Up Cable Machine)', 'Inverser Beincurl am Klimmzug-Kabelzug', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Adjust the cable machine so that the ankle straps are at the lowest setting. Lie face down on the bench with your legs extended and the ankle straps attached to your feet. Hold onto the handles of the bench for stability. Bend your knees and curl your legs towards your glutes, squeezing your hamstrings. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","calves"]', '["Adjust the cable machine so that the ankle straps are at the lowest setting.","Lie face down on the bench with your legs extended and the ankle straps attached to your feet.","Hold onto the handles of the bench for stability.","Bend your knees and curl your legs towards your glutes, squeezing your hamstrings.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Kabelzug so ein, dass sich die Fesselgurte auf der untersten Position befinden.","Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf die Bank, die Beine gestreckt, die Fesselgurte an den Füssen befestigt.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen der Bank fest.","Beuge die Knie und curle die Beine Richtung Gesäss, während du die Beinbeuger anspannst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2400.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2400.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('41c505f1-45b9-5bb3-8393-0c3198703a4b', NULL, 'Inverted Row', 'Invertiertes Rudern', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a bar at waist height or use a suspension trainer. Stand facing the bar or suspension trainer, with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grab the bar or handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lean back, keeping your body straight and your heels on the ground. Pull your chest towards the bar or handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up a bar at waist height or use a suspension trainer.","Stand facing the bar or suspension trainer, with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grab the bar or handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lean back, keeping your body straight and your heels on the ground.","Pull your chest towards the bar or handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Stange auf Hüfthöhe ein oder verwende ein Schlingentrainer-System.","Stell dich vor die Stange oder das Schlingentrainer-System, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Greife die Stange oder die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Lehne dich zurück, der Körper bleibt gerade, die Fersen bleiben am Boden.","Ziehe die Brust Richtung Stange oder Griffe und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0499.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0499.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4ff27310-fc19-5263-badd-479cc1a56ab8', NULL, 'Inverted Row (Bent Knees)', 'Invertiertes Rudern mit gebeugten Knien', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a bar at waist height and lie underneath it. Grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Position your body so that your heels are on the ground and your body is straight. Pull your chest up towards the bar by squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up a bar at waist height and lie underneath it.","Grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Position your body so that your heels are on the ground and your body is straight.","Pull your chest up towards the bar by squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Stange auf Hüfthöhe ein und lege dich darunter.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Positioniere den Körper so, dass die Fersen am Boden sind und der Körper gerade ist.","Ziehe die Brust zur Stange hoch, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2300.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2300.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('154013b4-a055-513d-85bf-78a14ba51fa1', NULL, 'Inverted Row (on Bench)', 'Invertiertes Rudern auf der Bank', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a bench at a height that allows your body to hang freely underneath it. Lie face up on the ground with your head towards the bench. Reach up and grab the bench with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Position your body so that your heels are on the ground and your arms are fully extended. Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull your chest up towards the bench. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up a bench at a height that allows your body to hang freely underneath it.","Lie face up on the ground with your head towards the bench.","Reach up and grab the bench with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Position your body so that your heels are on the ground and your arms are fully extended.","Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull your chest up towards the bench.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Bank auf eine Höhe ein, bei der der Körper frei darunter hängen kann.","Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach oben auf den Boden, der Kopf zeigt zur Bank.","Greife nach oben und fasse die Bank im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Positioniere den Körper so, dass die Fersen am Boden sind und die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen, während du die Brust Richtung Bank hochziehst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2298.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2298.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a358bf12-a8df-59d5-b133-57e68b01787d', NULL, 'Inverted Row V. 2', 'Invertiertes Rudern V. 2', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a bar at waist height on a Smith machine or use a suspension trainer. Stand facing the bar or suspension trainer and grab it with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Walk your feet forward, leaning back until your body is at a slight angle. Keep your body straight and pull your chest up towards the bar or handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up a bar at waist height on a Smith machine or use a suspension trainer.","Stand facing the bar or suspension trainer and grab it with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Walk your feet forward, leaning back until your body is at a slight angle.","Keep your body straight and pull your chest up towards the bar or handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle eine Stange in einer Multipresse auf Hüfthöhe ein oder verwende ein Schlingentrainer-System.","Stell dich davor und greife im Obergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne und lehne dich zurück, bis der Körper einen leichten Winkel bildet.","Halte den Körper gerade und ziehe die Brust Richtung Stange oder Griffe, während du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0497.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0497.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8f0ce11c-a0ec-5865-8239-36c8cc7d900a', NULL, 'Inverted Row with Straps', 'Invertiertes Rudern mit Schlaufen', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a suspension trainer or straps at chest height. Stand facing the anchor point and grab the handles with an overhand grip. Walk your feet forward, leaning back until your body is at an angle. Keep your body straight and engage your core. Pull your chest towards the handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up a suspension trainer or straps at chest height.","Stand facing the anchor point and grab the handles with an overhand grip.","Walk your feet forward, leaning back until your body is at an angle.","Keep your body straight and engage your core.","Pull your chest towards the handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle ein Schlingentrainer-System oder Gurte auf Brusthöhe ein.","Stell dich vor den Befestigungspunkt und greife die Griffe im Obergriff.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne und lehne dich zurück, bis der Körper einen Winkel bildet.","Halte den Körper gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Brust Richtung Griffe und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0498.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0498.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cd63d56a-ea20-5b3e-81b3-b2c27899c6ac', NULL, 'Iron Cross Stretch', 'Iron-Cross-Dehnung', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your arms extended out to the sides. Raise your legs up towards the ceiling, keeping them straight. Slowly lower your legs to one side, aiming to touch the floor with your feet. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then return your legs to the starting position. Repeat the stretch on the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your arms extended out to the sides.","Raise your legs up towards the ceiling, keeping them straight.","Slowly lower your legs to one side, aiming to touch the floor with your feet.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then return your legs to the starting position.","Repeat the stretch on the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken und strecke die Arme seitlich aus.","Hebe die gestreckten Beine Richtung Decke.","Senke die Beine langsam zu einer Seite ab, mit dem Ziel, den Boden mit den Füssen zu berühren.","Halte die Dehnung einige Sekunden und führe die Beine dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Dehnung auf der anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1419.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1419.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c19e834a-f052-586a-90b2-e98113ade64a', NULL, 'Isometric Chest Squeeze', 'Isometrisches Brustpressen', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Extend your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground, with your palms facing each other. Squeeze your chest muscles together as hard as you can, while keeping your arms straight. Hold this position for a few seconds, focusing on contracting your chest muscles. Release the squeeze and relax your chest muscles. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Extend your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground, with your palms facing each other.","Squeeze your chest muscles together as hard as you can, while keeping your arms straight.","Hold this position for a few seconds, focusing on contracting your chest muscles.","Release the squeeze and relax your chest muscles.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus, parallel zum Boden, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Spanne die Brustmuskulatur so stark wie möglich an, die Arme bleiben gestreckt.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden und konzentriere dich auf die Anspannung der Brustmuskulatur.","Löse die Anspannung und entspanne die Brustmuskulatur.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1297.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1297.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6d62f023-a6ad-573d-b8d8-d138656d0547', NULL, 'Isometric Wipers', 'Isometrische Wischer', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start by lying flat on your back on a mat or bench. Extend your arms straight out to the sides, perpendicular to your body. Engage your core and lift both legs off the ground, keeping them together and straight. Slowly lower your legs to one side, aiming to touch the ground with your feet while maintaining control. Pause for a moment, then use your core to lift your legs back to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time lowering your legs to the opposite side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Start by lying flat on your back on a mat or bench.","Extend your arms straight out to the sides, perpendicular to your body.","Engage your core and lift both legs off the ground, keeping them together and straight.","Slowly lower your legs to one side, aiming to touch the ground with your feet while maintaining control.","Pause for a moment, then use your core to lift your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time lowering your legs to the opposite side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken auf eine Matte oder Bank.","Strecke die Arme seitlich aus, im rechten Winkel zum Körper.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe beide Beine gestreckt und geschlossen vom Boden ab.","Senke die Beine kontrolliert zu einer Seite ab, mit dem Ziel, den Boden mit den Füssen zu berühren.","Halte kurz inne und hebe die Beine mithilfe der Körpermitte zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal mit Absenken der Beine zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0500.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0500.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9cbd3c60-456c-5cbd-8b08-e5613e780d5f', NULL, 'Jack Burpee', 'Jack-Burpee', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start in a standing position with your feet shoulder-width apart. Lower your body into a squat position, placing your hands on the ground in front of you. Kick your feet back, landing in a push-up position. Perform a push-up, lowering your chest to the ground and then pushing back up. Jump your feet forward, landing in a squat position. Jump up explosively, reaching your arms overhead. Land softly and immediately lower back into the squat position to begin the next repetition.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves","shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Start in a standing position with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body into a squat position, placing your hands on the ground in front of you.","Kick your feet back, landing in a push-up position.","Perform a push-up, lowering your chest to the ground and then pushing back up.","Jump your feet forward, landing in a squat position.","Jump up explosively, reaching your arms overhead.","Land softly and immediately lower back into the squat position to begin the next repetition."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab und stütze die Hände vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Schwinge die Füsse nach hinten und lande in der Liegestütz-Position.","Führe einen Liegestütz aus, senke die Brust zum Boden und drücke dich dann wieder hoch.","Springe mit den Füssen nach vorne und lande in einer Kniebeuge-Position.","Springe explosiv hoch und strecke die Arme über den Kopf.","Lande weich und senke dich sofort wieder in die Kniebeuge-Position, um die nächste Wiederholung zu beginnen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0501.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0501.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8fb3dd7e-fe27-5bb4-8d5b-5f43fb668adc', NULL, 'Jack Jump (Male)', 'Hampelmann-Sprung (männlich)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet together and your arms by your sides. Jump up, spreading your feet apart and raising your arms above your head. As you land, quickly jump back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet together and your arms by your sides.","Jump up, spreading your feet apart and raising your arms above your head.","As you land, quickly jump back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit geschlossenen Füssen hin, die Arme seitlich am Körper.","Springe hoch, spreize dabei die Füsse und hebe die Arme über den Kopf.","Springe beim Landen schnell zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3224.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3224.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a0ca5447-8fbd-577f-9ce4-59875c556883', NULL, 'Jackknife Sit-Up', 'Klappmesser-Sit-up', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms overhead. Engage your core and lift your legs and upper body simultaneously, reaching your hands towards your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs and upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms overhead.","Engage your core and lift your legs and upper body simultaneously, reaching your hands towards your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs and upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt, die Arme über dem Kopf.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe gleichzeitig Beine und Oberkörper, die Hände greifen Richtung Zehen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke Beine und Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0507.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0507.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5a16b8fd-0ff5-54d4-bf59-8b184dadf52a', NULL, 'Janda Sit-Up', 'Janda-Sit-up', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden, bis er in einem 45-Grad-Winkel steht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0508.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0508.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c7c7da2c-3cce-5875-a123-11fe158a8e63', NULL, 'Jump Rope', 'Seilspringen', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'rope', 'Hold the handles of the jump rope with your hands, palms facing inward. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Swing the rope over your head and jump over it as it comes towards your feet. Land softly on the balls of your feet and repeat the jump as the rope comes around again. Continue jumping for the desired duration or number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Hold the handles of the jump rope with your hands, palms facing inward.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Swing the rope over your head and jump over it as it comes towards your feet.","Land softly on the balls of your feet and repeat the jump as the rope comes around again.","Continue jumping for the desired duration or number of repetitions."]', '["Halte die Griffe des Springseils in den Händen, Handflächen nach innen gerichtet.","Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Schwinge das Seil über den Kopf und springe darüber, sobald es Richtung Füsse kommt.","Lande weich auf den Fussballen und wiederhole den Sprung, sobald das Seil erneut ankommt.","Springe für die gewünschte Dauer oder Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2612.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2612.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8a2cb503-5b36-5b37-a08a-fb7792a7cbaa', NULL, 'Jump Squat', 'Sprungkniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. Jump explosively off the ground, extending your hips, knees, and ankles. While in mid-air, quickly bring your arms forward for balance. Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next repetition. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","Jump explosively off the ground, extending your hips, knees, and ankles.","While in mid-air, quickly bring your arms forward for balance.","Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next repetition.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Springe explosiv vom Boden ab und strecke dabei Hüfte, Knie und Fussgelenke.","Bringe die Arme in der Luft schnell nach vorne, um das Gleichgewicht zu halten.","Lande weich auf den Fussballen und gehe sofort in die nächste Wiederholung über.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0514.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0514.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fccd16f6-97a1-5039-8ead-4fdfd3d0172e', NULL, 'Jump Squat V. 2', 'Sprungkniebeuge V. 2', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. Jump explosively, extending your hips and knees fully. Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately lower your body back into a squat position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","Jump explosively, extending your hips and knees fully.","Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately lower your body back into a squat position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Springe explosiv und strecke dabei Hüfte und Knie vollständig.","Lande weich auf den Fussballen und senke den Körper sofort wieder in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0513.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0513.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('243745ec-5618-5470-a4d4-63c9da175d02', NULL, 'Kettlebell Advanced Windmill', 'Fortgeschrittenes Kettlebell-Windmill', 'waist', 'abs', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward. Hold a kettlebell in your right hand, with your arm extended overhead and your palm facing forward. Rotate your left foot slightly to the right, and shift your weight onto your left leg. Bend your left knee and hinge at the hip, lowering your torso towards the left side. Keep your right arm extended overhead and your eyes on the kettlebell. As you lower your torso, allow your right leg to straighten and your right foot to pivot slightly. Lower your torso until you feel a stretch in your left hamstring and your right arm is pointing towards the ground. Pause for a moment, then engage your core and push through your left heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold a kettlebell in your right hand, with your arm extended overhead and your palm facing forward.","Rotate your left foot slightly to the right, and shift your weight onto your left leg.","Bend your left knee and hinge at the hip, lowering your torso towards the left side.","Keep your right arm extended overhead and your eyes on the kettlebell.","As you lower your torso, allow your right leg to straighten and your right foot to pivot slightly.","Lower your torso until you feel a stretch in your left hamstring and your right arm is pointing towards the ground.","Pause for a moment, then engage your core and push through your left heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich breiter als schulterbreit hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte eine Kettlebell in der rechten Hand, der Arm über den Kopf gestreckt, Handfläche nach vorne.","Drehe den linken Fuss leicht nach rechts und verlagere das Gewicht auf das linke Bein.","Beuge das linke Knie und beuge dich aus der Hüfte, während du den Oberkörper zur linken Seite senkst.","Halte den rechten Arm über dem Kopf gestreckt und den Blick auf die Kettlebell gerichtet.","Lass beim Absenken des Oberkörpers das rechte Bein strecken und den rechten Fuss leicht mitdrehen.","Senke den Oberkörper, bis du eine Dehnung im linken Beinbeuger spürst und der rechte Arm Richtung Boden zeigt.","Halte kurz inne, spanne dann die Körpermitte an und drücke dich über die linke Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0517.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0517.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8b5fd917-5dd5-5ced-b52b-327fde84534d', NULL, 'Kettlebell Alternating Hang Clean', 'Wechselseitiges Kettlebell-Hang-Clean', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Allow the kettlebells to hang in front of your body with your arms fully extended. In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips, shrug your shoulders, and pull the kettlebells up towards your shoulders. As the kettlebells reach shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebells in the rack position, with your palms facing inward and the kettlebells resting on the outside of your forearms. Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat the movement with the opposite arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","traps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Allow the kettlebells to hang in front of your body with your arms fully extended.","In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips, shrug your shoulders, and pull the kettlebells up towards your shoulders.","As the kettlebells reach shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebells in the rack position, with your palms facing inward and the kettlebells resting on the outside of your forearms.","Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat the movement with the opposite arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust oben.","Lass die Kettlebells vor dem Körper hängen, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Strecke in einer fliessenden Bewegung explosiv die Hüfte, ziehe die Schultern hoch und ziehe die Kettlebells zu den Schultern.","Drehe die Handgelenke, sobald die Kettlebells Schulterhöhe erreichen, und fange sie in der Rack-Position auf, Handflächen nach innen, die Kettlebells liegen aussen an den Unterarmen an.","Senke die Kettlebells zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0518.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0518.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0b3cf0db-54f4-5bbd-a31a-a9f5f46a9566', NULL, 'Kettlebell Alternating Press', 'Wechselseitiges Kettlebell-Drücken', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height. Press one kettlebell overhead, fully extending your arm. Lower the kettlebell back to shoulder height. Repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height.","Press one kettlebell overhead, fully extending your arm.","Lower the kettlebell back to shoulder height.","Repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe.","Drücke eine Kettlebell über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0520.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0520.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ea65a99e-1a9d-5b7a-87bf-06135bd86584', NULL, 'Kettlebell Alternating Press on Floor', 'Wechselseitiges Kettlebell-Bodendrücken', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'kettlebell', 'Start by lying on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold a kettlebell in each hand, with your palms facing towards your feet and your arms extended straight up towards the ceiling. Lower one kettlebell down towards your shoulder while keeping the other kettlebell extended straight up. Press the lowered kettlebell back up to the starting position while simultaneously lowering the other kettlebell down towards your shoulder. Continue alternating the press motion with each kettlebell for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start by lying on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a kettlebell in each hand, with your palms facing towards your feet and your arms extended straight up towards the ceiling.","Lower one kettlebell down towards your shoulder while keeping the other kettlebell extended straight up.","Press the lowered kettlebell back up to the starting position while simultaneously lowering the other kettlebell down towards your shoulder.","Continue alternating the press motion with each kettlebell for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken auf den Boden, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell, Handflächen Richtung Füsse, die Arme gerade Richtung Decke gestreckt.","Senke eine Kettlebell Richtung Schulter, während die andere gerade nach oben gestreckt bleibt.","Drücke die abgesenkte Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition, während du gleichzeitig die andere Richtung Schulter senkst.","Wechsle die Druckbewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter zwischen den Kettlebells ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0519.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0519.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4efa8d55-a32a-5748-9b00-a2baa0e061b4', NULL, 'Kettlebell Alternating Renegade Row', 'Wechselseitiges Kettlebell-Renegade-Rudern', 'back', 'upper back', 'kettlebell', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands gripping the kettlebells and your feet hip-width apart. Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to heels. Pull one kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands gripping the kettlebells and your feet hip-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to heels.","Pull one kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in den hohen Stütz, die Hände greifen die Kettlebells, die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Ziehe eine Kettlebell Richtung Brust, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0521.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0521.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4377f612-6a5e-5e11-9a0d-22a6a7bda9d0', NULL, 'Kettlebell Alternating Row', 'Wechselseitiges Kettlebell-Rudern', 'back', 'upper back', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a kettlebell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Pull one kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat with the other arm. Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a kettlebell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull one kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat with the other arm.","Continue alternating arms for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt, und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe eine Kettlebell Richtung Brust, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper, und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Arme ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0522.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0522.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4071ffc8-15b3-5d3e-b8a4-4546100fb9e7', NULL, 'Kettlebell Arnold Press', 'Kettlebell-Arnold-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height with your palms facing towards you. Engage your core and press the kettlebells overhead, rotating your palms to face forward as you extend your arms. Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height with your palms facing towards you.","Engage your core and press the kettlebells overhead, rotating your palms to face forward as you extend your arms.","Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen zu dir gerichtet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und drücke die Kettlebells über den Kopf, während du die Handflächen beim Strecken der Arme nach vorne drehst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und senke die Kettlebells dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0523.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0523.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cfae45bf-d527-57f1-99f5-59277b3d95da', NULL, 'Kettlebell Bent Press', 'Kettlebell-Bent-Press', 'waist', 'abs', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand. Bend your knees slightly and press the kettlebell overhead with your right arm, keeping your elbow locked. Rotate your torso to the left, shifting your weight onto your left foot. Bend your left knee and lower your torso towards the ground, keeping your right arm extended overhead. As you lower, keep your eyes on the kettlebell and your chest lifted. Once your left hand touches the ground, push through your left foot and straighten your left leg, driving your hips forward. As you drive your hips forward, use your core and right arm to press the kettlebell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","obliques"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand.","Bend your knees slightly and press the kettlebell overhead with your right arm, keeping your elbow locked.","Rotate your torso to the left, shifting your weight onto your left foot.","Bend your left knee and lower your torso towards the ground, keeping your right arm extended overhead.","As you lower, keep your eyes on the kettlebell and your chest lifted.","Once your left hand touches the ground, push through your left foot and straighten your left leg, driving your hips forward.","As you drive your hips forward, use your core and right arm to press the kettlebell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in der rechten Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und drücke die Kettlebell mit dem rechten Arm über den Kopf, der Ellbogen bleibt gestreckt.","Drehe den Oberkörper nach links und verlagere das Gewicht auf den linken Fuss.","Beuge das linke Knie und senke den Oberkörper Richtung Boden, der rechte Arm bleibt über dem Kopf gestreckt.","Behalte beim Absenken die Kettlebell im Blick und halte die Brust oben.","Sobald die linke Hand den Boden berührt, drücke dich über den linken Fuss ab, strecke das linke Bein und schiebe die Hüfte nach vorne.","Nutze beim Vorschieben der Hüfte Körpermitte und rechten Arm, um die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu drücken.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0524.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0524.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f8dd557e-0441-5c5b-ba74-21cfb4ae019b', NULL, 'Kettlebell Bottoms-Up Clean from the Hang Position', 'Kettlebell-Bottoms-up-Clean aus der Hängeposition', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Allow the kettlebell to hang down between your legs, with your arm fully extended. In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips and knees while pulling the kettlebell up towards your shoulder. As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrist so that the bottom of the kettlebell is facing up. Catch the kettlebell at shoulder height with your elbow bent and your palm facing up. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position by reversing the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Allow the kettlebell to hang down between your legs, with your arm fully extended.","In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips and knees while pulling the kettlebell up towards your shoulder.","As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrist so that the bottom of the kettlebell is facing up.","Catch the kettlebell at shoulder height with your elbow bent and your palm facing up.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position by reversing the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust oben.","Lass die Kettlebell zwischen den Beinen hängen, der Arm vollständig gestreckt.","Strecke in einer fliessenden Bewegung explosiv Hüfte und Knie, während du die Kettlebell Richtung Schulter ziehst.","Drehe das Handgelenk, sobald die Kettlebell Schulterhöhe erreicht, sodass der Boden der Kettlebell nach oben zeigt.","Fange die Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe auf, der Ellbogen gebeugt, die Handfläche nach oben.","Senke die Kettlebell in umgekehrter Bewegung zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0525.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0525.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a6f264ab-00ae-5998-9786-c69950ceec54', NULL, 'Kettlebell Double Alternating Hang Clean', 'Wechselseitiges Doppel-Kettlebell-Hang-Clean', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Allow the kettlebells to hang straight down in front of your body. In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips and knees while shrugging your shoulders. As the kettlebells rise, pull them up towards your shoulders, keeping your elbows high and out to the sides. Catch the kettlebells at shoulder height, with your palms facing inward and your elbows pointing forward. Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Allow the kettlebells to hang straight down in front of your body.","In one fluid motion, explosively extend your hips and knees while shrugging your shoulders.","As the kettlebells rise, pull them up towards your shoulders, keeping your elbows high and out to the sides.","Catch the kettlebells at shoulder height, with your palms facing inward and your elbows pointing forward.","Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust oben.","Lass die Kettlebells gerade vor dem Körper hängen.","Strecke in einer fliessenden Bewegung explosiv Hüfte und Knie, während du die Schultern hochziehst.","Ziehe die Kettlebells beim Hochkommen Richtung Schultern, die Ellbogen bleiben hoch und seitlich abgespreizt.","Fange die Kettlebells auf Schulterhöhe auf, Handflächen nach innen, die Ellbogen zeigen nach vorne.","Senke die Kettlebells zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0526.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0526.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ed0579db-825c-5f0d-b6e2-d5cad9bb5815', NULL, 'Kettlebell Double Jerk', 'Doppel-Kettlebell-Stossen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms. Bend your knees and quickly drop into a partial squat. Explosively extend your hips and knees, driving the kettlebells overhead. Lock out your arms and catch the kettlebells overhead with your knees slightly bent. Stand up straight and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms.","Bend your knees and quickly drop into a partial squat.","Explosively extend your hips and knees, driving the kettlebells overhead.","Lock out your arms and catch the kettlebells overhead with your knees slightly bent.","Stand up straight and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Drücke die Kettlebells über den Kopf und strecke die Arme vollständig.","Beuge die Knie und senke dich schnell in eine leichte Kniebeuge ab.","Strecke Hüfte und Knie explosiv und treibe die Kettlebells über den Kopf.","Strecke die Arme vollständig durch und fange die Kettlebells über dem Kopf mit leicht gebeugten Knien auf.","Richte dich auf und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0527.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0527.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('92d17506-afaa-598b-81bc-91d63dda5dba', NULL, 'Kettlebell Double Push Press', 'Doppel-Kettlebell-Push-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Initiate the movement by explosively extending your hips, knees, and ankles, driving the kettlebells overhead. As the kettlebells reach the top, press them fully overhead, locking out your arms. Lower the kettlebells back to the starting position by bending your elbows and bringing them back down to shoulder height. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Initiate the movement by explosively extending your hips, knees, and ankles, driving the kettlebells overhead.","As the kettlebells reach the top, press them fully overhead, locking out your arms.","Lower the kettlebells back to the starting position by bending your elbows and bringing them back down to shoulder height.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Leite die Bewegung ein, indem du Hüfte, Knie und Fussgelenke explosiv streckst und die Kettlebells über den Kopf treibst.","Drücke die Kettlebells oben vollständig durch, sobald sie den höchsten Punkt erreichen.","Senke die Kettlebells zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und sie zurück auf Schulterhöhe bringst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0528.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0528.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d1809077-e172-59e2-9522-213863555e93', NULL, 'Kettlebell Double Snatch', 'Doppel-Kettlebell-Snatch', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at arm''s length in front of your thighs. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back flat and chest up. In one explosive motion, extend your hips, knees, and ankles, and simultaneously pull the kettlebells up towards your shoulders. As the kettlebells reach shoulder level, rotate your wrists and punch the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms. Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","forearms","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at arm''s length in front of your thighs.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back flat and chest up.","In one explosive motion, extend your hips, knees, and ankles, and simultaneously pull the kettlebells up towards your shoulders.","As the kettlebells reach shoulder level, rotate your wrists and punch the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms.","Lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell mit gestrecktem Arm vor den Oberschenkeln.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt flach, die Brust oben.","Strecke in einer explosiven Bewegung Hüfte, Knie und Fussgelenke und ziehe gleichzeitig die Kettlebells Richtung Schultern.","Drehe die Handgelenke, sobald die Kettlebells Schulterhöhe erreichen, und stosse sie über den Kopf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Senke die Kettlebells zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0529.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0529.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('71d05c5c-fbab-56b3-a4fb-b672ee2fe3ac', NULL, 'Kettlebell Double Windmill', 'Doppel-Kettlebell-Windmill', 'waist', 'abs', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand. Extend your right arm overhead, keeping your eyes on the kettlebell. Rotate your left foot 45 degrees to the left and your right foot 90 degrees to the right. Bend at the waist to the left, keeping your right arm extended overhead. Lower the kettlebell towards the ground, reaching towards your left foot. Pause for a moment, then engage your core and push through your right foot to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","hamstrings"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand.","Extend your right arm overhead, keeping your eyes on the kettlebell.","Rotate your left foot 45 degrees to the left and your right foot 90 degrees to the right.","Bend at the waist to the left, keeping your right arm extended overhead.","Lower the kettlebell towards the ground, reaching towards your left foot.","Pause for a moment, then engage your core and push through your right foot to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in der rechten Hand.","Strecke den rechten Arm über den Kopf und behalte die Kettlebell im Blick.","Drehe den linken Fuss um 45 Grad nach links und den rechten Fuss um 90 Grad nach rechts.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach links, der rechte Arm bleibt über dem Kopf gestreckt.","Senke die Kettlebell Richtung Boden und greife Richtung linken Fuss.","Halte kurz inne, spanne dann die Körpermitte an und drücke dich über den rechten Fuss zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0530.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0530.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('97f67235-c158-51d6-83b7-1da05680ba10', NULL, 'Kettlebell Extended Range One Arm Press on Floor', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Bodendrücken mit erweitertem Bewegungsradius', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'kettlebell', 'Start by lying on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold a kettlebell in one hand, with your palm facing towards your feet. Extend your arm straight up towards the ceiling, keeping your elbow locked and your wrist straight. Slowly lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position, maintaining control throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start by lying on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a kettlebell in one hand, with your palm facing towards your feet.","Extend your arm straight up towards the ceiling, keeping your elbow locked and your wrist straight.","Slowly lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position, maintaining control throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken auf den Boden, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand, Handfläche Richtung Füsse.","Strecke den Arm gerade Richtung Decke, der Ellbogen bleibt durchgestreckt, das Handgelenk gerade.","Senke die Kettlebell langsam und kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0531.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0531.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('688619ac-d390-530e-a954-9571050714a2', NULL, 'Kettlebell Figure 8', 'Kettlebell-Achterbewegung', 'waist', 'abs', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Pass the kettlebell between your legs, switching hands as it reaches the back of your legs. As the kettlebell comes forward, pass it to the other hand between your legs. Continue passing the kettlebell between your legs in a figure 8 motion. Maintain a steady pace and engage your core throughout the exercise. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Pass the kettlebell between your legs, switching hands as it reaches the back of your legs.","As the kettlebell comes forward, pass it to the other hand between your legs.","Continue passing the kettlebell between your legs in a figure 8 motion.","Maintain a steady pace and engage your core throughout the exercise.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Führe die Kettlebell zwischen den Beinen hindurch und wechsle die Hand, sobald sie hinter den Beinen ankommt.","Übergib die Kettlebell zwischen den Beinen an die andere Hand, sobald sie wieder nach vorne kommt.","Führe die Kettlebell in einer Achterbewegung weiter zwischen den Beinen hindurch.","Halte ein gleichmässiges Tempo und spanne die Körpermitte während der gesamten Übung an.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0532.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0532.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dbd194fc-eca1-5129-bc96-456d20a45194', NULL, 'Kettlebell Front Squat', 'Kettlebell-Frontkniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out. Hold the kettlebell with both hands in front of your chest, close to your body. Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your hips down and back, as if sitting into a chair. Lower until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Drive through your heels to stand back up, squeezing your glutes at the top. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out.","Hold the kettlebell with both hands in front of your chest, close to your body.","Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your hips down and back, as if sitting into a chair.","Lower until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Drive through your heels to stand back up, squeezing your glutes at the top.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte die Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor der Brust, nah am Körper.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, halte die Brust oben und senke die Hüfte nach unten und hinten, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Senke dich, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es angenehm ist.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab, um dich wieder aufzurichten, und spanne oben das Gesäss an.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0533.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0533.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c1b54c60-e07f-506e-a050-da7d5e80bc84', NULL, 'Kettlebell Goblet Squat', 'Kettlebell-Goblet-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell close to your chest with both hands. Keeping your chest up and core engaged, lower your body down into a squat position by bending at the knees and hips. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell close to your chest with both hands.","Keeping your chest up and core engaged, lower your body down into a squat position by bending at the knees and hips.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen nah an der Brust.","Halte die Brust oben und die Körpermitte angespannt, senke den Körper durch Beugen von Knien und Hüfte in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0534.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0534.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('65062e9e-7356-5632-9fc4-9f1614faa543', NULL, 'Kettlebell Hang Clean', 'Kettlebell-Hang-Clean', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your thighs. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Lower the kettlebell towards the ground, allowing it to swing between your legs. Quickly extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height. As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebell in the rack position, with your elbow tucked in and the kettlebell resting on your forearm. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position between your legs, and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your thighs.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Lower the kettlebell towards the ground, allowing it to swing between your legs.","Quickly extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height.","As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebell in the rack position, with your elbow tucked in and the kettlebell resting on your forearm.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position between your legs, and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell vor den Oberschenkeln.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Senke die Kettlebell Richtung Boden und lass sie zwischen die Beine schwingen.","Strecke Hüfte und Knie schnell und nutze den Schwung, um die Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe zu schwingen.","Drehe die Handgelenke, sobald die Kettlebell Schulterhöhe erreicht, und fange sie in der Rack-Position auf, der Ellbogen eng am Körper, die Kettlebell liegt auf dem Unterarm.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück zwischen die Beine in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0535.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0535.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a24e1e63-b700-5574-9636-5155333060bf', NULL, 'Kettlebell Lunge Pass Through', 'Ausfallschritt mit Kettlebell-Durchreichen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands. Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. As you lunge forward, pass the kettlebell under your right thigh and transfer it to your left hand. Push off with your right foot to return to the starting position, while simultaneously passing the kettlebell back to your right hand. Repeat the lunge on the opposite side, passing the kettlebell under your left thigh. Continue alternating lunges and passing the kettlebell between hands for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands.","Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","As you lunge forward, pass the kettlebell under your right thigh and transfer it to your left hand.","Push off with your right foot to return to the starting position, while simultaneously passing the kettlebell back to your right hand.","Repeat the lunge on the opposite side, passing the kettlebell under your left thigh.","Continue alternating lunges and passing the kettlebell between hands for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor der Brust.","Mache mit dem rechten Fuss einen Schritt nach vorne und senke den Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Führe die Kettlebell beim Ausfallschritt unter dem rechten Oberschenkel hindurch und übergib sie an die linke Hand.","Drücke dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren, und übergib die Kettlebell gleichzeitig zurück an die rechte Hand.","Wiederhole den Ausfallschritt auf der anderen Seite und führe die Kettlebell unter dem linken Oberschenkel hindurch.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter zwischen Ausfallschritten und Handwechsel der Kettlebell ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0536.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0536.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eac946eb-a525-5a1d-91af-3d67e9c25368', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Clean and Jerk', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Clean-and-Jerk', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell between your legs. Explosively extend your hips, knees, and ankles, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height. As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrist and punch your hand straight up, locking out your arm overhead. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell between your legs.","Explosively extend your hips, knees, and ankles, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height.","As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrist and punch your hand straight up, locking out your arm overhead.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte, während du die Kettlebell zwischen die Beine senkst.","Strecke Hüfte, Knie und Fussgelenke explosiv und nutze den Schwung, um die Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe zu schwingen.","Drehe das Handgelenk, sobald die Kettlebell Schulterhöhe erreicht, und stosse die Hand gerade nach oben, der Arm streckt sich über dem Kopf vollständig durch.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0537.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0537.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('22aaf047-c52c-548e-849f-6a5435e10571', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Floor Press', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Bodendrücken', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'kettlebell', 'Lie flat on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold the kettlebell in one hand with your palm facing towards your feet and your arm extended straight up towards the ceiling. Slowly lower the kettlebell towards your chest by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm close to your body. Pause for a moment when the kettlebell is just above your chest, then push it back up to the starting position by extending your elbow. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on your back on the floor with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the kettlebell in one hand with your palm facing towards your feet and your arm extended straight up towards the ceiling.","Slowly lower the kettlebell towards your chest by bending your elbow, keeping your upper arm close to your body.","Pause for a moment when the kettlebell is just above your chest, then push it back up to the starting position by extending your elbow.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken auf den Boden, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte die Kettlebell in einer Hand, Handfläche Richtung Füsse, der Arm gerade Richtung Decke gestreckt.","Senke die Kettlebell langsam Richtung Brust, indem du den Ellbogen beugst, der Oberarm bleibt nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne, sobald die Kettlebell knapp über der Brust ist, und drücke sie durch Strecken des Ellbogens zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1298.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1298.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('75daab02-80dd-5ffd-9d4c-64669d2f5c93', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Jerk', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Stossen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder height. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Press the kettlebell overhead in a straight line, fully extending your arm. As you press the kettlebell overhead, simultaneously dip your knees and quickly straighten them to generate momentum. As the kettlebell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it by bending your knees and hips. Catch the kettlebell with a slight bend in your knees and hips, and your arm fully extended overhead. Stand up straight, fully extending your knees and hips, and stabilize the kettlebell overhead. Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by bending your knees and hips, and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder height.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Press the kettlebell overhead in a straight line, fully extending your arm.","As you press the kettlebell overhead, simultaneously dip your knees and quickly straighten them to generate momentum.","As the kettlebell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it by bending your knees and hips.","Catch the kettlebell with a slight bend in your knees and hips, and your arm fully extended overhead.","Stand up straight, fully extending your knees and hips, and stabilize the kettlebell overhead.","Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by bending your knees and hips, and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Drücke die Kettlebell in einer geraden Linie über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Beuge beim Hochdrücken der Kettlebell gleichzeitig die Knie und strecke sie schnell wieder, um Schwung zu erzeugen.","Tauche schnell darunter, sobald die Kettlebell ihren höchsten Punkt erreicht, indem du Knie und Hüfte beugst.","Fange die Kettlebell mit leicht gebeugten Knien und Hüfte auf, der Arm vollständig über dem Kopf gestreckt.","Richte dich auf, strecke Knie und Hüfte vollständig und stabilisiere die Kettlebell über dem Kopf.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du Knie und Hüfte beugst, und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0538.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0538.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4da3bd7d-592b-55b8-9986-3252d9b5aade', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Military Press to the Side', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Military-Press zur Seite', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder height. Engage your core and keep your back straight. Press the kettlebell overhead, extending your arm fully. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder height.","Engage your core and keep your back straight.","Press the kettlebell overhead, extending your arm fully.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken gerade.","Drücke die Kettlebell über den Kopf und strecke den Arm vollständig.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kettlebell dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0539.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0539.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2c63ecd3-a731-583d-a96b-82ee3315ab57', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Push Press', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Push-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder level. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Press the kettlebell overhead by extending your arm and fully extending your legs. Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by bending your knees and bringing the kettlebell back to your shoulder. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand at shoulder level.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Press the kettlebell overhead by extending your arm and fully extending your legs.","Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by bending your knees and bringing the kettlebell back to your shoulder.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand auf Schulterhöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Drücke die Kettlebell über den Kopf, indem du den Arm streckst und die Beine vollständig durchstreckst.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Knie beugst und die Kettlebell zurück zur Schulter bringst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0540.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0540.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('173bf2aa-c8a4-5faa-b68e-3280aacefc47', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Row', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Rudern', 'back', 'upper back', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Pull the kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat with the other arm.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand with an overhand grip.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull the kettlebell up towards your chest, keeping your elbow close to your body and squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat with the other arm."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand im Obergriff.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Kettlebell Richtung Brust, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper, und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kettlebell dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0541.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0541.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5486f737-b038-5134-aa44-338a79a7b375', NULL, 'Kettlebell One Arm Snatch', 'Einarmiges Kettlebell-Snatch', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand between your legs. Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell towards the ground. Explosively extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up towards your shoulder. As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your hand and punch it straight up overhead, fully extending your arm. Lower the kettlebell back down between your legs and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","forearms","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand between your legs.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell towards the ground.","Explosively extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to swing the kettlebell up towards your shoulder.","As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your hand and punch it straight up overhead, fully extending your arm.","Lower the kettlebell back down between your legs and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand zwischen den Beinen.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte, während du die Kettlebell Richtung Boden senkst.","Strecke Hüfte und Knie explosiv und nutze den Schwung, um die Kettlebell Richtung Schulter zu schwingen.","Drehe die Hand, sobald die Kettlebell Schulterhöhe erreicht, und stosse sie gerade über den Kopf, der Arm streckt sich vollständig.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück zwischen die Beine und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0542.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0542.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('41585d6b-f627-5e39-8d66-c118ee251cf6', NULL, 'Kettlebell Pirate Ships', 'Kettlebell-Pirate-Ships', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Raise the kettlebell up to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body. Extend your arm fully overhead, straightening your elbow. Lower the kettlebell back down to shoulder height, then return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in one hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Raise the kettlebell up to shoulder height, keeping your elbow close to your body.","Extend your arm fully overhead, straightening your elbow.","Lower the kettlebell back down to shoulder height, then return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in einer Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Hebe die Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe an, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper.","Strecke den Arm vollständig über den Kopf, der Ellbogen wird dabei gestreckt.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück auf Schulterhöhe und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0543.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0543.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2b9dd063-6a1e-53bc-9ebf-1cd01118d442', NULL, 'Kettlebell Pistol Squat', 'Kettlebell-Pistolenkniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands. Lift your left foot off the ground and extend it forward, keeping it parallel to the ground. Slowly lower your body down into a squat position, keeping your right foot flat on the ground and your left leg extended. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the squat, then push through your right heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands.","Lift your left foot off the ground and extend it forward, keeping it parallel to the ground.","Slowly lower your body down into a squat position, keeping your right foot flat on the ground and your left leg extended.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the squat, then push through your right heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor der Brust.","Hebe den linken Fuss vom Boden ab und strecke ihn parallel zum Boden nach vorne aus.","Senke den Körper langsam in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, der rechte Fuss bleibt flach auf dem Boden, das linke Bein gestreckt.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die rechte Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0544.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0544.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('1d21a1f4-247c-56d5-801e-f70eb475e786', NULL, 'Kettlebell Plyo Push-Up', 'Plyo-Liegestütz mit Kettlebells', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'kettlebell', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands on the kettlebells, shoulder-width apart. Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body. Push through your hands explosively, lifting your hands off the kettlebells and extending your arms fully. Land softly back on the kettlebells and immediately lower your chest back down for the next repetition. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands on the kettlebells, shoulder-width apart.","Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Push through your hands explosively, lifting your hands off the kettlebells and extending your arms fully.","Land softly back on the kettlebells and immediately lower your chest back down for the next repetition.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in den hohen Stütz, die Hände liegen schulterbreit auf den Kettlebells.","Senke die Brust Richtung Boden, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Drücke dich explosiv über die Hände ab, hebe die Hände von den Kettlebells und strecke die Arme vollständig.","Lande weich wieder auf den Kettlebells und senke die Brust sofort für die nächste Wiederholung ab.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0545.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0545.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0f34a92c-18e3-5a17-9dfb-c037e7fcc0ef', NULL, 'Kettlebell Seated Press', 'Kettlebell-Schulterdrücken im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height, palms facing forward. Press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms. Lower the kettlebells back to shoulder height. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height, palms facing forward.","Press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms.","Lower the kettlebells back to shoulder height.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kettlebells über den Kopf und strecke die Arme vollständig.","Senke die Kettlebells zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0546.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0546.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('acd5536a-e173-5f3d-969f-9378289d10ad', NULL, 'Kettlebell Seated Two Arm Military Press', 'Beidarmiges Kettlebell-Military-Press im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward. Press the kettlebells overhead by extending your arms fully. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward.","Press the kettlebells overhead by extending your arms fully.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Bank, halte den Rücken gerade und stelle die Füsse flach auf den Boden.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Drücke die Kettlebells über den Kopf, indem du die Arme vollständig streckst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kettlebells dann langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1438.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1438.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('192b5df5-2ef7-56d8-b191-5a591577aaa5', NULL, 'Kettlebell Seesaw Press', 'Kettlebell-Seesaw-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height. Press one kettlebell overhead while keeping the other kettlebell at shoulder height. Lower the pressed kettlebell back to shoulder height while simultaneously pressing the other kettlebell overhead. Continue alternating the pressing motion, creating a seesaw-like movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder height.","Press one kettlebell overhead while keeping the other kettlebell at shoulder height.","Lower the pressed kettlebell back to shoulder height while simultaneously pressing the other kettlebell overhead.","Continue alternating the pressing motion, creating a seesaw-like movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe.","Drücke eine Kettlebell über den Kopf, während die andere auf Schulterhöhe bleibt.","Senke die gedrückte Kettlebell zurück auf Schulterhöhe, während du gleichzeitig die andere über den Kopf drückst.","Wechsle die Druckbewegung weiter ab, sodass eine wippende Bewegung entsteht.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0547.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0547.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4848c4e7-ad63-5c84-915c-64434b5dce56', NULL, 'Kettlebell Sumo High Pull', 'Kettlebell-Sumo-Hochzug', 'back', 'traps', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing outwards. Hold a kettlebell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended downwards. Bend your knees and lower your hips into a squat position, keeping your back straight. Drive through your heels and explosively extend your hips and knees, pulling the kettlebell up towards your chin. As you pull the kettlebell up, keep your elbows high and wide, and squeeze your shoulder blades together. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing outwards.","Hold a kettlebell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended downwards.","Bend your knees and lower your hips into a squat position, keeping your back straight.","Drive through your heels and explosively extend your hips and knees, pulling the kettlebell up towards your chin.","As you pull the kettlebell up, keep your elbows high and wide, and squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich breiter als schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen nach aussen.","Halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor dem Körper, die Arme nach unten gestreckt.","Beuge die Knie und senke die Hüfte in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab und strecke Hüfte und Knie explosiv, während du die Kettlebell Richtung Kinn ziehst.","Halte die Ellbogen beim Hochziehen hoch und breit und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0548.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0548.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f5e564f8-057d-5982-9558-3e1278f32c52', NULL, 'Kettlebell Swing', 'Kettlebell-Swing', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointed slightly outward. Hold the kettlebell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended. Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, pushing your butt back. Swing the kettlebell back between your legs, keeping your arms straight and maintaining a flat back. Drive your hips forward and swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height, using the momentum generated by your hips. Allow the kettlebell to swing back down between your legs and repeat the movement for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointed slightly outward.","Hold the kettlebell with both hands in front of your body, arms extended.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, pushing your butt back.","Swing the kettlebell back between your legs, keeping your arms straight and maintaining a flat back.","Drive your hips forward and swing the kettlebell up to shoulder height, using the momentum generated by your hips.","Allow the kettlebell to swing back down between your legs and repeat the movement for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte die Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor dem Körper, die Arme gestreckt.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte, schiebe das Gesäss nach hinten.","Schwinge die Kettlebell zwischen den Beinen nach hinten, die Arme bleiben gestreckt, der Rücken flach.","Schiebe die Hüfte nach vorne und schwinge die Kettlebell mithilfe des Hüftschwungs auf Schulterhöhe.","Lass die Kettlebell zurück zwischen die Beine schwingen und wiederhole die Bewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0549.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0549.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ff762cc4-1a44-5087-8eb5-a2c0db655cf0', NULL, 'Kettlebell Thruster', 'Kettlebell-Thruster', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands, palms facing each other. Lower into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back, keeping your chest up and your back straight. As you reach the bottom of the squat, explosively drive through your heels to stand up, simultaneously pressing the kettlebell overhead. Lock out your arms at the top of the movement, fully extending your elbows. Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by reversing the movement, bending your elbows and lowering the weight back to your chest. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","glutes","core"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your chest with both hands, palms facing each other.","Lower into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back, keeping your chest up and your back straight.","As you reach the bottom of the squat, explosively drive through your heels to stand up, simultaneously pressing the kettlebell overhead.","Lock out your arms at the top of the movement, fully extending your elbows.","Lower the kettlebell back to the starting position by reversing the movement, bending your elbows and lowering the weight back to your chest.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor der Brust, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Senke dich in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst, die Brust bleibt oben, der Rücken gerade.","Drücke dich am tiefsten Punkt der Kniebeuge explosiv über die Fersen ab, um aufzustehen, und drücke die Kettlebell gleichzeitig über den Kopf.","Strecke die Arme am Ende der Bewegung vollständig durch.","Senke die Kettlebell in umgekehrter Bewegung zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und das Gewicht zurück zur Brust bringst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0550.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0550.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e4faafa8-2a57-50fb-be5f-8d9e98e8b2c8', NULL, 'Kettlebell Turkish Get-Up (Squat Style)', 'Kettlebell-Turkish-Get-up (Kniebeugen-Stil)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'kettlebell', 'Start by lying on your back with your legs extended and the kettlebell held in your right hand, arm fully extended above your shoulder. Bend your right knee and place your right foot flat on the ground, keeping your left leg extended. Pressing through your right foot, lift your hips off the ground, coming into a bridge position. Slide your left leg underneath your body, bending your left knee and placing your left foot flat on the ground. Rotate your torso to the left, bringing your left hand to the ground for support. Pressing through your right foot and left hand, lift your torso off the ground, coming into a kneeling position. From the kneeling position, stand up, keeping the kettlebell extended overhead. Reverse the movement to return to the starting position. Repeat the exercise on the other side, starting with the kettlebell in your left hand.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","core"]', '["Start by lying on your back with your legs extended and the kettlebell held in your right hand, arm fully extended above your shoulder.","Bend your right knee and place your right foot flat on the ground, keeping your left leg extended.","Pressing through your right foot, lift your hips off the ground, coming into a bridge position.","Slide your left leg underneath your body, bending your left knee and placing your left foot flat on the ground.","Rotate your torso to the left, bringing your left hand to the ground for support.","Pressing through your right foot and left hand, lift your torso off the ground, coming into a kneeling position.","From the kneeling position, stand up, keeping the kettlebell extended overhead.","Reverse the movement to return to the starting position.","Repeat the exercise on the other side, starting with the kettlebell in your left hand."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt, die Kettlebell in der rechten Hand, der Arm vollständig über der Schulter gestreckt.","Beuge das rechte Knie und stelle den rechten Fuss flach auf den Boden, das linke Bein bleibt gestreckt.","Drücke dich über den rechten Fuss ab und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden in eine Brücken-Position.","Schiebe das linke Bein unter den Körper, beuge das linke Knie und stelle den linken Fuss flach auf den Boden.","Drehe den Oberkörper nach links und stütze die linke Hand auf dem Boden ab.","Drücke dich über rechten Fuss und linke Hand ab und hebe den Oberkörper in eine kniende Position.","Richte dich aus der knienden Position auf, die Kettlebell bleibt über dem Kopf gestreckt.","Kehre die Bewegung um, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole die Übung auf der anderen Seite, beginnend mit der Kettlebell in der linken Hand."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0551.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0551.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ccb73bd3-a4ca-57d5-a889-69ba45cd31bf', NULL, 'Kettlebell Two Arm Clean', 'Beidarmiges Kettlebell-Clean', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your thighs with both hands, palms facing towards you. Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell towards the ground. Explosively extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to pull the kettlebell up towards your shoulders. As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebell in the rack position, with your elbows tucked in and the kettlebell resting on the back of your forearm. Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in front of your thighs with both hands, palms facing towards you.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge at the hips, lowering the kettlebell towards the ground.","Explosively extend your hips and knees, using the momentum to pull the kettlebell up towards your shoulders.","As the kettlebell reaches shoulder height, rotate your wrists and catch the kettlebell in the rack position, with your elbows tucked in and the kettlebell resting on the back of your forearm.","Lower the kettlebell back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell mit beiden Händen vor den Oberschenkeln, Handflächen zu dir gerichtet.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich aus der Hüfte, während du die Kettlebell Richtung Boden senkst.","Strecke Hüfte und Knie explosiv und nutze den Schwung, um die Kettlebell Richtung Schultern zu ziehen.","Drehe die Handgelenke, sobald die Kettlebell Schulterhöhe erreicht, und fange sie in der Rack-Position auf, die Ellbogen eng am Körper, die Kettlebell liegt auf der Rückseite des Unterarms.","Senke die Kettlebell zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0552.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0552.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e007349d-ecd3-5a61-981f-e03f0e0aebe4', NULL, 'Kettlebell Two Arm Military Press', 'Beidarmiges Kettlebell-Military-Press', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward. Engage your core and press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in each hand at shoulder level with your palms facing forward.","Engage your core and press the kettlebells overhead, fully extending your arms.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell auf Schulterhöhe, Handflächen nach vorne.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und drücke die Kettlebells über den Kopf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kettlebells dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0553.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0553.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('97d52a48-4620-5484-865a-10aca89bd253', NULL, 'Kettlebell Two Arm Row', 'Beidarmiges Kettlebell-Rudern', 'back', 'upper back', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a kettlebell in each hand with your palms facing your body. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Pull the kettlebells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a kettlebell in each hand with your palms facing your body.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull the kettlebells up towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the kettlebells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt, und halte in jeder Hand eine Kettlebell, Handflächen zum Körper gerichtet.","Beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Kettlebells Richtung Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Kettlebells dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1345.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1345.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0fb8442f-abf3-5286-afc2-095f03dea2d3', NULL, 'Kettlebell Windmill', 'Kettlebell-Windmill', 'waist', 'abs', 'kettlebell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand overhead. Rotate your left foot outwards about 45 degrees and keep your right foot pointing forward. Bend your torso to the left side, keeping your right arm extended overhead and your eyes on the kettlebell. Lower your torso as far as you can while keeping your right arm straight and your left arm extended to the side. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position by pushing through your right foot and engaging your obliques. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a kettlebell in your right hand overhead.","Rotate your left foot outwards about 45 degrees and keep your right foot pointing forward.","Bend your torso to the left side, keeping your right arm extended overhead and your eyes on the kettlebell.","Lower your torso as far as you can while keeping your right arm straight and your left arm extended to the side.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position by pushing through your right foot and engaging your obliques.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte eine Kettlebell in der rechten Hand über dem Kopf.","Drehe den linken Fuss etwa 45 Grad nach aussen, der rechte Fuss zeigt weiter nach vorne.","Beuge den Oberkörper nach links, der rechte Arm bleibt über dem Kopf gestreckt, der Blick auf die Kettlebell gerichtet.","Senke den Oberkörper so weit wie möglich ab, der rechte Arm bleibt gestreckt, der linke Arm seitlich ausgestreckt.","Halte kurz inne und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du dich über den rechten Fuss abdrückst und die seitliche Bauchmuskulatur anspannst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0554.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0554.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('60a30d83-e895-5ea8-b434-6209bc276cd4', NULL, 'Kick Out Sit', 'Kick-out im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Lean back slightly and place your hands on the edge of the bench or chair for support. Engaging your hamstrings, lift your feet off the ground and extend your legs straight out in front of you. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly bend your knees and bring your feet back towards your body. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","glutes"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Lean back slightly and place your hands on the edge of the bench or chair for support.","Engaging your hamstrings, lift your feet off the ground and extend your legs straight out in front of you.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly bend your knees and bring your feet back towards your body.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich an den Rand einer Bank oder eines Stuhls, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden, die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Lehne dich leicht zurück und stütze die Hände an der Kante der Bank oder des Stuhls ab.","Spanne die Beinbeuger an, hebe die Füsse vom Boden und strecke die Beine gerade vor dir aus.","Halte oben kurz inne, beuge die Knie dann langsam und ziehe die Füsse zurück zum Körper.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0555.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0555.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('95f3ec92-e913-5f8e-be73-e0bfd6242ed2', NULL, 'Kipping Muscle-Up', 'Kipping-Muscle-up', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and use a swinging motion to generate momentum. As you swing forward, pull your chest towards the bar, using your lats and biceps to initiate the movement. Continue the upward motion until your chest reaches the bar, then transition into a dip position by pushing down on the bar and extending your arms. Lower yourself back down to the starting position by bending your arms and controlling the descent. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and use a swinging motion to generate momentum.","As you swing forward, pull your chest towards the bar, using your lats and biceps to initiate the movement.","Continue the upward motion until your chest reaches the bar, then transition into a dip position by pushing down on the bar and extending your arms.","Lower yourself back down to the starting position by bending your arms and controlling the descent.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge an einer Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und nutze eine Schwungbewegung, um Schwung aufzubauen.","Ziehe die Brust beim Vorwärtsschwung zur Stange, angetrieben von Latissimus und Bizeps.","Führe die Aufwärtsbewegung fort, bis die Brust die Stange erreicht, und gehe dann in eine Dip-Position über, indem du dich über die Stange nach unten drückst und die Arme streckst.","Senke dich kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme beugst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0558.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0558.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e821bf94-a6dd-5c3b-8482-85602182d9a2', NULL, 'Knee Touch Crunch', 'Crunch mit Knieberührung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, lift your shoulder blades off the ground and reach your right hand towards your left knee. Return to the starting position and repeat, this time reaching your left hand towards your right knee. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, lift your shoulder blades off the ground and reach your right hand towards your left knee.","Return to the starting position and repeat, this time reaching your left hand towards your right knee.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an, hebe die Schulterblätter vom Boden und greife mit der rechten Hand Richtung linkes Knie.","Kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole, diesmal mit der linken Hand Richtung rechtes Knie.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3640.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3640.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d7902f3c-2725-5fe1-96bf-95591d250b64', NULL, 'Kneeling Jump Squat', 'Sprungkniebeuge aus dem Kniestand', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'barbell', 'Start by kneeling on the ground with your feet hip-width apart and your toes pointing forward. Hold a barbell across your upper back, resting it on your shoulders. Engage your core and glutes, then explosively jump up into the air, extending your hips and knees. As you jump, push through your toes and fully extend your ankles, knees, and hips. Land softly back on the ground, bending your knees to absorb the impact. Immediately go into the next repetition, repeating the jump squat motion.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start by kneeling on the ground with your feet hip-width apart and your toes pointing forward.","Hold a barbell across your upper back, resting it on your shoulders.","Engage your core and glutes, then explosively jump up into the air, extending your hips and knees.","As you jump, push through your toes and fully extend your ankles, knees, and hips.","Land softly back on the ground, bending your knees to absorb the impact.","Immediately go into the next repetition, repeating the jump squat motion."]', '["Knie dich auf den Boden, die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Halte eine Langhantel quer über dem oberen Rücken, sie liegt auf den Schultern.","Spanne Körpermitte und Gesäss an und springe dann explosiv in die Luft, während du Hüfte und Knie streckst.","Drücke dich beim Sprung über die Zehen ab und strecke Fussgelenke, Knie und Hüfte vollständig.","Lande weich auf dem Boden und beuge die Knie, um den Aufprall abzufedern.","Gehe sofort in die nächste Wiederholung über und wiederhole die Sprung-Kniebeuge."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1420.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1420.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7f832f6-5a55-5097-8e0f-467d9860bf3c', NULL, 'Kneeling Lat Stretch', 'Latissimus-Dehnung im Kniestand', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Kneel on the ground with your knees hip-width apart and your toes pointing back. Extend your arms overhead and interlace your fingers. Keeping your back straight, slowly lean to the right side, feeling a stretch in your left lat muscle. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position. Repeat the stretch on the left side, leaning to the left and feeling a stretch in your right lat muscle. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Kneel on the ground with your knees hip-width apart and your toes pointing back.","Extend your arms overhead and interlace your fingers.","Keeping your back straight, slowly lean to the right side, feeling a stretch in your left lat muscle.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the stretch on the left side, leaning to the left and feeling a stretch in your right lat muscle.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Knie dich auf den Boden, die Knie hüftbreit auseinander, die Zehen zeigen nach hinten.","Strecke die Arme über den Kopf und verschränke die Finger.","Halte den Rücken gerade und lehne dich langsam zur rechten Seite, spüre die Dehnung im linken Latissimus.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Dehnung auf der linken Seite, lehne dich nach links und spüre die Dehnung im rechten Latissimus.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1346.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1346.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c25e8cf3-445b-5fc1-aa12-8376d218d675', NULL, 'Kneeling Plank Tap Shoulder (Male)', 'Plank im Kniestand mit Schulterberührung (männlich)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a kneeling position with your hands on the ground, shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs behind you, resting on your toes, and lift your body into a plank position. Keeping your core engaged and your hips stable, lift one hand off the ground and tap the opposite shoulder. Return the hand to the ground and repeat with the other hand. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start in a kneeling position with your hands on the ground, shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on your toes, and lift your body into a plank position.","Keeping your core engaged and your hips stable, lift one hand off the ground and tap the opposite shoulder.","Return the hand to the ground and repeat with the other hand.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in eine kniende Position, die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Boden.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Zehen und hebe den Körper in eine Plank-Position.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, halte die Hüfte stabil, hebe eine Hand vom Boden und tippe die gegenüberliegende Schulter an.","Setze die Hand zurück auf den Boden und wiederhole mit der anderen Hand.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3239.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3239.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('26a79a42-cadd-5000-a7b4-3249bfc17314', NULL, 'Kneeling Push-Up (Male)', 'Liegestütz im Kniestand (männlich)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start by kneeling on the ground with your hands shoulder-width apart, fingers pointing forward. Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, so that your body forms a straight line from head to heels. Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Continue lowering until your chest is just above the ground, then push back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start by kneeling on the ground with your hands shoulder-width apart, fingers pointing forward.","Extend your legs behind you, resting on the balls of your feet, so that your body forms a straight line from head to heels.","Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Continue lowering until your chest is just above the ground, then push back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Knie dich auf den Boden, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Strecke die Beine nach hinten aus, stütze dich auf die Fussballen, sodass der Körper eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Ferse bildet.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke den Körper Richtung Boden, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, sie bleiben nah am Körper.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Brust knapp über dem Boden ist, und drücke dich dann durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3211.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3211.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f3b5ed0a-9062-5921-984f-6578423469a5', NULL, 'Korean Dips', 'Koreanische Dips', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms extended and supporting your body weight. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms extended and supporting your body weight.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich zwischen zwei Dip-Barren, die Arme gestreckt, sie tragen dein Körpergewicht.","Senke den Körper, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis die Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3288.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3288.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('34681963-beb9-546a-91a5-b93a036124f4', NULL, 'L-Pull-Up', 'L-Klimmzug', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your lats and biceps to pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your lats and biceps to pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen, der Körper gerade.","Spanne Latissimus und Bizeps an und ziehe den Körper zur Stange hoch, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Ziehe weiter hoch, bis das Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3418.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3418.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('22986040-5dd7-5c1b-ae18-7b94f95d8fe9', NULL, 'L-Sit on Floor', 'L-Sit am Boden', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the floor with your legs extended in front of you. Place your hands on the floor beside your hips, fingers pointing forward. Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight. Try to bring your legs parallel to the floor, forming an ''L'' shape with your body. Hold this position for as long as you can. Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the floor with your legs extended in front of you.","Place your hands on the floor beside your hips, fingers pointing forward.","Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight.","Try to bring your legs parallel to the floor, forming an ''L'' shape with your body.","Hold this position for as long as you can.","Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Stütze die Hände neben der Hüfte auf dem Boden ab, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe die gestreckten Beine vom Boden.","Versuche, die Beine parallel zum Boden zu bringen, sodass der Körper ein L bildet.","Halte diese Position so lange wie möglich.","Senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3419.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3419.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7894ca8-860e-5e6a-9384-37e5378373e2', NULL, 'Landmine 180', 'Landmine 180', 'waist', 'abs', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell with both hands in front of your chest. Bend your knees slightly and rotate your torso to the right, swinging the barbell down towards your right hip. As you reach the bottom of the movement, quickly reverse the motion and rotate your torso to the left, swinging the barbell up and across your body towards your left shoulder. Continue this twisting motion, alternating sides, for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","quadriceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell with both hands in front of your chest.","Bend your knees slightly and rotate your torso to the right, swinging the barbell down towards your right hip.","As you reach the bottom of the movement, quickly reverse the motion and rotate your torso to the left, swinging the barbell up and across your body towards your left shoulder.","Continue this twisting motion, alternating sides, for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin und halte die Langhantel mit beiden Händen vor der Brust.","Beuge die Knie leicht und drehe den Oberkörper nach rechts, während du die Stange Richtung rechte Hüfte schwingst.","Kehre die Bewegung am tiefsten Punkt schnell um und drehe den Oberkörper nach links, während du die Stange über den Körper Richtung linke Schulter schwingst.","Führe diese Drehbewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen abwechselnd auf beiden Seiten fort."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0562.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0562.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6db83aa2-7d1e-5df6-a976-1ad549331f80', NULL, 'Landmine Lateral Raise', 'Landmine-Seitheben', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold the barbell with an overhand grip, resting it on the front of your shoulders. Keeping your core engaged and back straight, lift the barbell up and away from your body, raising it to shoulder height. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold the barbell with an overhand grip, resting it on the front of your shoulders.","Keeping your core engaged and back straight, lift the barbell up and away from your body, raising it to shoulder height.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte die Langhantel im Obergriff, sie liegt vorne auf den Schultern.","Spanne die Körpermitte an, halte den Rücken gerade, und hebe die Stange vom Körper weg auf Schulterhöhe.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3237.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3237.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('132363cb-c356-5d63-95cf-32a531f74741', NULL, 'Lean Planche', 'Geneigte Planche', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body straight. Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, bringing your shoulders past your hands. Keep your elbows slightly bent and your body straight as you lean forward. Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","triceps"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body straight.","Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, bringing your shoulders past your hands.","Keep your elbows slightly bent and your body straight as you lean forward.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander, der Körper gerade.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und verlagere das Gewicht langsam nach vorne, die Schultern kommen über die Hände hinaus.","Halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt und den Körper gerade, während du dich nach vorne lehnst.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3300.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3300.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('38f58517-5e13-5d00-b22c-c1a08cf672a4', NULL, 'Left Hook (Boxing)', 'Linker Haken (Boxen)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Keep your left hand up to protect your face and your right hand by your chin. Rotate your hips and pivot on your left foot as you extend your left arm forward in a punching motion. Twist your torso and engage your core muscles to generate power in the punch. Snap your arm back to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Keep your left hand up to protect your face and your right hand by your chin.","Rotate your hips and pivot on your left foot as you extend your left arm forward in a punching motion.","Twist your torso and engage your core muscles to generate power in the punch.","Snap your arm back to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte die linke Hand oben zum Schutz des Gesichts und die rechte Hand am Kinn.","Drehe die Hüfte und pivotiere auf dem linken Fuss, während du den linken Arm nach vorne in einer Schlagbewegung streckst.","Drehe den Oberkörper und spanne die Körpermitte an, um Kraft in den Schlag zu bringen.","Ziehe den Arm zügig zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2271.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2271.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8a16bde5-9e49-5dba-bccb-5236bae7a0e9', NULL, 'Leg Pull in Flat Bench', 'Beinanzug auf der Flachbank', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on a flat bench with your legs extended straight out in front of you. Place your hands on the bench beside your hips for support. Engage your abs and lift your legs off the ground, bringing your knees towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Sit on a flat bench with your legs extended straight out in front of you.","Place your hands on the bench beside your hips for support.","Engage your abs and lift your legs off the ground, bringing your knees towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine flache Bank, die Beine gerade vor dir ausgestreckt.","Stütze die Hände neben der Hüfte auf der Bank ab.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe die Beine vom Boden, während du die Knie Richtung Brust ziehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0570.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0570.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('59b75d98-3ed3-5011-92ec-4f0d529c30c6', NULL, 'Leg-Up Hamstring Stretch', 'Hamstring-Dehnung mit erhobenem Bein', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended. Bend one knee and bring it towards your chest, holding onto your thigh or shin. Straighten your leg as much as possible while keeping it elevated. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Repeat with the other leg.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended.","Bend one knee and bring it towards your chest, holding onto your thigh or shin.","Straighten your leg as much as possible while keeping it elevated.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Repeat with the other leg."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt.","Beuge ein Knie und ziehe es Richtung Brust, halte dabei Oberschenkel oder Schienbein fest.","Strecke das Bein so weit wie möglich, während es angehoben bleibt.","Halte die Dehnung 20 bis 30 Sekunden.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1576.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1576.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a5761427-9601-57de-b901-df1a3dae829d', NULL, 'Lever Alternate Leg Press', 'Wechselseitige Beinpresse an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat and foot platform of the leverage machine to your desired position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the foot platform. Place your hands on the handles or sides of the machine for stability. Push one foot against the foot platform, extending your leg until it is almost fully straight. Pause for a moment, then slowly bend your leg and return to the starting position. Repeat with the other leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the seat and foot platform of the leverage machine to your desired position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the foot platform.","Place your hands on the handles or sides of the machine for stability.","Push one foot against the foot platform, extending your leg until it is almost fully straight.","Pause for a moment, then slowly bend your leg and return to the starting position.","Repeat with the other leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitz und Fussplattform des Geräts auf die gewünschte Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse auf der Fussplattform.","Stütze die Hände zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts ab.","Drücke einen Fuss gegen die Fussplattform und strecke das Bein, bis es fast vollständig gestreckt ist.","Halte kurz inne, beuge das Bein dann langsam und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Beine ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2287.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2287.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ca6fcd12-faca-5dbe-a989-98ab6f231873', NULL, 'Lever Alternating Narrow Grip Seated Row', 'Wechselseitiges Rudern an der Maschine im Sitzen (enger Griff)', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment. Sit on the machine with your back straight and feet flat on the footplate. Grasp the handles with a narrow grip, palms facing each other. Keep your chest up and shoulders back throughout the exercise. Pull one handle towards your torso while keeping the other handle stationary. Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the end of the movement. Slowly return the handle to the starting position and repeat with the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment.","Sit on the machine with your back straight and feet flat on the footplate.","Grasp the handles with a narrow grip, palms facing each other.","Keep your chest up and shoulders back throughout the exercise.","Pull one handle towards your torso while keeping the other handle stationary.","Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the end of the movement.","Slowly return the handle to the starting position and repeat with the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattenposition für eine korrekte Ausrichtung ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken gerade, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe im engen Griff, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Halte die Brust oben und die Schultern zurück während der gesamten Übung.","Ziehe einen Griff Richtung Oberkörper, während der andere Griff ruhig bleibt.","Ziehe am Ende der Bewegung die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Führe den Griff langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole mit der anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0571.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0571.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0a0caf8b-3ad9-5c0f-a348-318f36eed6f8', NULL, 'Lever Assisted Chin-Up', 'Klimmzug (Untergriff) unterstützt an der Maschine', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the leverage machine to your desired resistance level. Stand on the foot platform and grip the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang with your arms fully extended, keeping your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the handles, leading with your chest. Continue pulling until your chin is above the handles. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the leverage machine to your desired resistance level.","Stand on the foot platform and grip the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang with your arms fully extended, keeping your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the handles, leading with your chest.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the handles.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf den gewünschten Widerstand ein.","Stell dich auf die Fussplattform und greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen, der Körper bleibt gerade.","Spanne die Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe den Körper, angeführt von der Brust, zu den Griffen hoch.","Ziehe weiter hoch, bis das Kinn über den Griffen ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0572.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0572.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('340ad919-d7eb-5902-9c1d-20bc4c251f29', NULL, 'Lever Back Extension', 'Rückenstrecker an der Maschine', 'back', 'spine', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body size and range of motion. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet secured. Place your hands on the handles or grip bars. Engage your core and slowly lean forward, allowing your back to round slightly. Pause for a moment at the bottom position, feeling a stretch in your lower back. Using your back muscles, slowly raise your torso back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body size and range of motion.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet secured.","Place your hands on the handles or grip bars.","Engage your core and slowly lean forward, allowing your back to round slightly.","Pause for a moment at the bottom position, feeling a stretch in your lower back.","Using your back muscles, slowly raise your torso back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deine Körpergrösse und den Bewegungsradius ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, die Füsse fixiert.","Lege die Hände auf die Griffe oder Haltestangen.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und lehne dich langsam nach vorne, der Rücken rundet sich dabei leicht.","Halte unten kurz inne und spüre die Dehnung im unteren Rücken.","Richte den Oberkörper mithilfe der Rückenmuskulatur langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition auf.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0573.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0573.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3ead95cc-e110-53fc-882b-817b23705db3', NULL, 'Lever Bent-Over Row', 'Vorgebeugtes Rudern an der Maschine', 'back', 'upper back', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Pull the barbell towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Pull the barbell towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte die Langhantel im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Brust oben.","Ziehe die Stange Richtung unteren Brustbereich und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0574.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0574.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b05e87d6-a7a3-50a8-b741-4847a6421737', NULL, 'Lever Bent-Over Row with V-Bar', 'Vorgebeugtes Rudern an der Maschine mit V-Griff', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine. Grasp the v-bar with an overhand grip, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent. Pull the v-bar towards your abdomen, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release the weight back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine.","Grasp the v-bar with an overhand grip, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent.","Pull the v-bar towards your abdomen, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release the weight back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich vor dem Gerät.","Greife den V-Griff im Obergriff, der Rücken bleibt gerade, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Ziehe den V-Griff Richtung Bauch und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und lasse das Gewicht dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3200.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3200.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2296eca9-6542-5c80-a429-f3662ed0c2a6', NULL, 'Lever Biceps Curl', 'Bizepscurl an der Maschine', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and keep your elbows close to your sides. Exhale and curl the handles upward, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and keep your elbows close to your sides.","Exhale and curl the handles upward, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Atme aus und curle die Griffe hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0575.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0575.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0b7238f8-1586-52b5-8864-ee2661a732d0', NULL, 'Lever Calf Press', 'Wadenpresse an der Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat of the leverage machine so that your shoulders are aligned with the lever pad. Place your toes on the lever pad, with your heels hanging off the edge. Grasp the handles or side supports for stability. Push the lever pad down by extending your ankles, contracting your calf muscles. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement. Slowly return to the starting position by allowing your heels to rise back up. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the seat of the leverage machine so that your shoulders are aligned with the lever pad.","Place your toes on the lever pad, with your heels hanging off the edge.","Grasp the handles or side supports for stability.","Push the lever pad down by extending your ankles, contracting your calf muscles.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement.","Slowly return to the starting position by allowing your heels to rise back up.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz des Geräts so ein, dass die Schultern mit dem Polster ausgerichtet sind.","Stelle die Zehen auf das Polster, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seitenstützen fest.","Drücke das Polster nach unten, indem du die Fussgelenke streckst und die Wadenmuskulatur anspannst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne.","Kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du die Fersen wieder anheben lässt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2289.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2289.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('82c849da-0f4a-55ed-8b54-bdb31ffef95b', NULL, 'Lever Chest Press', 'Brustpresse an der Maschine', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle. Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement. Pause briefly at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle.","Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement.","Pause briefly at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt flach am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Ellbogen im 90-Grad-Winkel.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, atme dabei aus.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und kehre dann langsam atmend in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0577.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0577.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('29e2b179-7457-5b2a-9877-97fa08e7b42b', NULL, 'Lever Chest Press', 'Brustpresse an der Maschine', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle. Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement. Pause briefly at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle.","Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement.","Pause briefly at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt flach am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Ellbogen im 90-Grad-Winkel.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, atme dabei aus.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und kehre dann langsam atmend in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0576.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0576.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('01bc24f2-ae7e-5e41-ab0d-bffc6e76d713', NULL, 'Lever Deadlift', 'Kreuzheben an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and foot platform to your desired position. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the foot platform. Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability. Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and push through your heels to lift the weight up. Keep your back straight and avoid rounding your shoulders. Extend your hips fully at the top of the movement, squeezing your glutes. Lower the weight back down in a controlled manner, keeping tension on your glutes and hamstrings. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Adjust the seat height and foot platform to your desired position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the foot platform.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and push through your heels to lift the weight up.","Keep your back straight and avoid rounding your shoulders.","Extend your hips fully at the top of the movement, squeezing your glutes.","Lower the weight back down in a controlled manner, keeping tension on your glutes and hamstrings.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattform auf die gewünschte Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplattform.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Sitzes fest.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und drücke dich über die Fersen ab, um das Gewicht hochzuheben.","Halte den Rücken gerade und vermeide es, die Schultern zu runden.","Strecke die Hüfte am Ende der Bewegung vollständig durch und spanne das Gesäss an.","Senke das Gewicht kontrolliert ab, die Spannung bleibt auf Gesäss und Beinbeugern.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0578.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0578.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ab402e0c-1dc1-5c08-8300-4038f3e4b229', NULL, 'Lever Decline Chest Press', 'Negativbank-Brustpresse an der Maschine', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended. Slowly lower the handles back towards your chest, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended.","Slowly lower the handles back towards your chest, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Rückenlehne des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne und vom Körper weg, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Senke die Griffe langsam zurück Richtung Brust, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke die Griffe dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1300.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1300.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f8d78065-2604-55fd-ab01-0bcd43fe74e3', NULL, 'Lever Donkey Calf Raise', 'Donkey-Wadenheben an der Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the leverage machine to the appropriate height for your body. Position yourself facing the machine, with your toes on the foot platform and your heels hanging off the edge. Place your hands on the handles or the support bars for stability. Engage your calves and lift your heels as high as possible, using the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the leverage machine to the appropriate height for your body.","Position yourself facing the machine, with your toes on the foot platform and your heels hanging off the edge.","Place your hands on the handles or the support bars for stability.","Engage your calves and lift your heels as high as possible, using the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf die passende Höhe für deinen Körper ein.","Positioniere dich vor dem Gerät, die Zehen auf der Fussplattform, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Stützstangen fest.","Spanne die Waden an und hebe die Fersen so hoch wie möglich über die Fussballen.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1253.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1253.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a9680784-f814-56ff-ba46-e60a5eb23a90', NULL, 'Lever Front Pulldown', 'Latzug zur Brust an der Maschine', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Sit upright with your chest lifted and your shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back. Engage your lats and pull the handles down towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Sit upright with your chest lifted and your shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back.","Engage your lats and pull the handles down towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, die Knie unter den Polstern, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Sitze aufrecht, die Brust oben, die Schultern zurück, mit leichtem Hohlkreuz.","Spanne den Latissimus an und ziehe die Griffe Richtung Brust, während du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und lasse die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0579.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0579.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cbe20e85-2913-592a-bec9-953f73b89079', NULL, 'Lever Gripless Shrug', 'Schulterheben an der Maschine ohne Griff', 'back', 'traps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine. Grasp the handles with your palms facing inwards and your arms fully extended. Keeping your back straight, exhale and elevate your shoulders as high as possible. Hold the contraction for a brief moment, then inhale and slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine.","Grasp the handles with your palms facing inwards and your arms fully extended.","Keeping your back straight, exhale and elevate your shoulders as high as possible.","Hold the contraction for a brief moment, then inhale and slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät.","Greife die Griffe, Handflächen nach innen gerichtet, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Halte den Rücken gerade, atme aus und hebe die Schultern so hoch wie möglich.","Halte die Anspannung kurz, atme ein und senke die Schultern dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0580.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0580.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dc18c4a6-b1fd-5eee-9c1c-aee290964103', NULL, 'Lever Gripless Shrug V. 2', 'Schulterheben an der Maschine ohne Griff V. 2', 'back', 'traps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles or bars with an overhand grip, keeping your arms straight. Keeping your back straight, lift your shoulders up towards your ears as high as possible. Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles or bars with an overhand grip, keeping your arms straight.","Keeping your back straight, lift your shoulders up towards your ears as high as possible.","Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife die Griffe oder Stangen im Obergriff, die Arme bleiben gestreckt.","Halte den Rücken gerade und hebe die Schultern so hoch wie möglich Richtung Ohren.","Halte die Anspannung kurz und senke die Schultern dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1439.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1439.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c19b5946-7ca1-59ef-8367-8be4678bf3f5', NULL, 'Lever Gripper Hands', 'Handgreifer-Training an der Maschine', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and grip the handles of the leverage machine. Keep your back straight and your feet flat on the ground. Exhale and squeeze the handles, contracting your forearms. Hold the contraction for a second, then slowly release and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps"]', '["Adjust the seat height and grip the handles of the leverage machine.","Keep your back straight and your feet flat on the ground.","Exhale and squeeze the handles, contracting your forearms.","Hold the contraction for a second, then slowly release and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und greife die Griffe des Geräts.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Atme aus und drücke die Griffe zusammen, während du die Unterarme anspannst.","Halte die Anspannung eine Sekunde, löse dann langsam und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2288.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2288.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6d4215fb-8a3f-5b96-a226-9a332950303e', NULL, 'Lever Hammer Grip Preacher Curl', 'Hammergriff-Scott-Curl an der Maschine', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine. Place your upper arms on the preacher pad, ensuring your chest is pressed against it. Grasp the handles with a hammer grip (palms facing each other). Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the handles towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine.","Place your upper arms on the preacher pad, ensuring your chest is pressed against it.","Grasp the handles with a hammer grip (palms facing each other).","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the handles towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät.","Lege die Oberarme auf das Scott-Polster, die Brust liegt fest daran an.","Greife die Griffe im Hammergriff (Handflächen zueinander gerichtet).","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Griffe zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1615.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1615.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bca7dccf-c25a-5008-92b5-7dc034240c09', NULL, 'Lever High Row', 'Hohes Rudern an der Maschine', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and foot platform to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the foot platform. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and foot platform to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the foot platform.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattform auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplattform.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Körper und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Höhepunkt der Bewegung kurz inne und lasse die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0581.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0581.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('65c675e8-1938-5008-88b8-7f53823150e5', NULL, 'Lever Hip Extension V. 2', 'Hüftstrecken an der Maschine V. 2', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest. Place your feet on the footrests and grip the handles for stability. Engage your glutes and hamstrings, then push against the footrests to extend your hips and raise your legs backward. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest.","Place your feet on the footrests and grip the handles for stability.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings, then push against the footrests to extend your hips and raise your legs backward.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und setz dich, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Stelle die Füsse auf die Fussstützen und halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen fest.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und drücke gegen die Fussstützen, um die Hüfte zu strecken und die Beine nach hinten anzuheben.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2286.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2286.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bd56dca5-635b-59a3-bf27-8bb294723cc6', NULL, 'Lever Horizontal One Leg Press', 'Einbeinige horizontale Beinpresse an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat of the machine so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle when your feet are on the footplate. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate. Place your hands on the handles or sides of the machine for stability. Push the footplate away from your body by extending your leg, keeping your back against the backrest. Pause for a moment at the fully extended position, then slowly bend your leg to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat of the machine so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle when your feet are on the footplate.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate.","Place your hands on the handles or sides of the machine for stability.","Push the footplate away from your body by extending your leg, keeping your back against the backrest.","Pause for a moment at the fully extended position, then slowly bend your leg to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stelle den Sitz des Geräts so ein, dass die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel sind, wenn die Füsse auf der Fussplatte stehen.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse schulterbreit auf der Fussplatte.","Stütze die Hände zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts ab.","Drücke die Fussplatte durch Strecken des Beins vom Körper weg, der Rücken bleibt an der Rückenlehne.","Halte in der vollständig gestreckten Position kurz inne und beuge das Bein dann langsam, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2611.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2611.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('119cde8e-0fc6-542e-8ca5-11894a85af7e', NULL, 'Lever Incline Chest Press', 'Schrägbank-Brustpresse an der Maschine', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended. Pause for a moment, then slowly bend your elbows and lower the handles back towards your chest. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Adjust the seat and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended.","Pause for a moment, then slowly bend your elbows and lower the handles back towards your chest.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitz und Rückenlehne des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne und vom Körper weg, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte kurz inne, beuge dann langsam die Ellbogen und senke die Griffe zurück Richtung Brust.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1299.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1299.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('185c45d5-6c5b-5c9b-916d-7cd0d07259f7', NULL, 'Lever Incline Chest Press V. 2', 'Schrägbank-Brustpresse an der Maschine V. 2', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and backrest angle on the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended, but without locking your elbows. Pause for a moment at the fully extended position, then slowly bend your elbows and lower the handles back towards your chest. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and backrest angle on the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles forward and away from your body until your arms are fully extended, but without locking your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the fully extended position, then slowly bend your elbows and lower the handles back towards your chest.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Neigung der Rückenlehne des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne und vom Körper weg, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne die Ellbogen durchzustrecken.","Halte in der vollständig gestreckten Position kurz inne, beuge dann langsam die Ellbogen und senke die Griffe zurück Richtung Brust.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1479.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1479.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('966f26dd-98f2-5180-b3f1-2c94242fd23d', NULL, 'Lever Kneeling Leg Curl', 'Beincurl im Kniestand an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body and select the desired weight. Kneel on the machine facing downwards, with your knees resting on the pad and your feet secured under the footpads. Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability. Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs up towards your glutes by flexing your knees. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your hamstrings. Inhale and slowly lower your legs back to the starting position, fully extending your knees. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body and select the desired weight.","Kneel on the machine facing downwards, with your knees resting on the pad and your feet secured under the footpads.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability.","Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs up towards your glutes by flexing your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your hamstrings.","Inhale and slowly lower your legs back to the starting position, fully extending your knees.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und wähle das gewünschte Gewicht.","Knie dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf das Gerät, die Knie liegen auf dem Polster, die Füsse sind unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts fest.","Halte den Oberkörper ruhig, atme aus und curle die Beine Richtung Gesäss, indem du die Knie beugst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne die Beinbeuger an.","Atme ein und senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Knie vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0582.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0582.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('999105ca-eddb-5fdd-b189-a22478538765', NULL, 'Lever Kneeling Twist', 'Rumpfdrehen im Kniestand an der Maschine', 'waist', 'abs', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees resting on the pads and your upper body facing forward. Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability. Keeping your core engaged, twist your torso to one side as far as comfortably possible. Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat the twist to the opposite side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees resting on the pads and your upper body facing forward.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability.","Keeping your core engaged, twist your torso to one side as far as comfortably possible.","Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat the twist to the opposite side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät, die Knie liegen auf den Polstern, der Oberkörper zeigt nach vorne.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts fest.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und drehe den Oberkörper so weit wie angenehm möglich zu einer Seite.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Drehung zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen weiter die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0583.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0583.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f3b1ad5a-a72d-5a4f-964e-5ea8c8efe1a4', NULL, 'Lever Lateral Raise', 'Seitheben an der Maschine', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms straight. Exhale and raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the floor. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms straight.","Exhale and raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the floor.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und halte die Arme gestreckt.","Atme aus und hebe die Arme seitlich an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0584.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0584.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3dfa2391-6d26-56cc-80ca-3a79522c2d26', NULL, 'Lever Leg Extension', 'Beinstrecken an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and backrest of the machine to fit your body. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footpad. Grasp the handles or sidebars for stability. Extend your legs forward by straightening your knees, lifting the weight. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the weight back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the seat height and backrest of the machine to fit your body.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footpad.","Grasp the handles or sidebars for stability.","Extend your legs forward by straightening your knees, lifting the weight.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the weight back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Rückenlehne des Geräts auf deinen Körper ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse auf dem Fusspolster.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seitenstangen fest.","Strecke die Beine nach vorne, indem du die Knie durchstreckst, und hebe dabei das Gewicht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke das Gewicht dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0585.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0585.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8cf2ff6f-c412-574d-a6f6-88f7d9f82ed9', NULL, 'Lever Lying Leg Curl', 'Liegender Beincurl an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body and select the desired weight. Lie face down on the machine with your legs straight and your heels against the padded lever. Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability. Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs up as far as possible without lifting your hips off the pad. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings. Inhale and slowly lower the lever back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body and select the desired weight.","Lie face down on the machine with your legs straight and your heels against the padded lever.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability.","Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs up as far as possible without lifting your hips off the pad.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings.","Inhale and slowly lower the lever back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und wähle das gewünschte Gewicht.","Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf das Gerät, die Beine gestreckt, die Fersen am gepolsterten Hebel.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts fest.","Halte den Oberkörper ruhig, atme aus und curle die Beine so weit wie möglich hoch, ohne die Hüfte vom Polster zu heben.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und spanne die Beinbeuger an.","Atme ein und senke den Hebel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0586.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0586.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bb78cdb9-9a28-569a-a556-b0d5d182adc4', NULL, 'Lever Lying Two-One Leg Curl', 'Liegender Beincurl an der Maschine (2-1-Technik)', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest. Place your legs on the lever pad, just above your ankles. Grasp the handles on the sides of the machine for support. Keeping your upper body still, exhale and curl your legs up towards your glutes. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest.","Place your legs on the lever pad, just above your ankles.","Grasp the handles on the sides of the machine for support.","Keeping your upper body still, exhale and curl your legs up towards your glutes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und setz dich, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Lege die Beine auf das Polster, knapp über den Fussgelenken.","Halte dich an den Griffen an den Seiten des Geräts fest.","Halte den Oberkörper ruhig, atme aus und curle die Beine Richtung Gesäss.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3195.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3195.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f6b4071a-3d76-57a4-912b-8a72cb7bf007', NULL, 'Lever Military Press', 'Military-Press an der Maschine', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles upward until your arms are fully extended, but do not lock your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper chest"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles upward until your arms are fully extended, but do not lock your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach oben, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne die Ellbogen durchzustrecken.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0587.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0587.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4ca5fd53-64e3-5a05-8a69-8b5611d3b76c', NULL, 'Lever Narrow Grip Seated Row', 'Rudern an der Maschine im Sitzen mit engem Griff', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footrests to ensure proper form. Sit on the machine with your feet flat on the footrests and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the handles with a narrow grip, palms facing each other. Keep your back straight and lean slightly forward. Pull the handles towards your torso, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement. Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footrests to ensure proper form.","Sit on the machine with your feet flat on the footrests and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the handles with a narrow grip, palms facing each other.","Keep your back straight and lean slightly forward.","Pull the handles towards your torso, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement.","Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussstützen für eine korrekte Ausführung ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Füsse flach auf den Fussstützen, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife die Griffe im engen Griff, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet.","Halte den Rücken gerade und lehne dich leicht nach vorne.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Oberkörper und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Höhepunkt der Bewegung kurz inne.","Lasse die Griffe langsam los und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0588.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0588.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3bc3e226-4515-5756-b60a-739ccc0a338d', NULL, 'Lever One Arm Bent-Over Row', 'Einarmiges vorgebeugtes Rudern an der Maschine', 'back', 'upper back', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a barbell with an overhand grip. Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your head up. Let the barbell hang in front of you with your arms fully extended. Pull the barbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the top of the movement. Lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a barbell with an overhand grip.","Bend forward at the hips, keeping your back straight and your head up.","Let the barbell hang in front of you with your arms fully extended.","Pull the barbell up towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Squeeze your shoulder blades together at the top of the movement.","Lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich schulterbreit hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt, und halte eine Langhantel im Obergriff.","Beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade, der Kopf oben.","Lass die Stange mit vollständig gestreckten Armen vor dir hängen.","Ziehe die Stange Richtung Brust hoch, die Ellbogen bleiben nah am Körper.","Ziehe am Ende der Bewegung die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Senke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0589.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0589.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b07471bb-87c5-53d9-81cb-43a28306debc', NULL, 'Lever One Arm Lateral High Row', 'Einarmiges hohes Rudern an der Maschine (seitlich)', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine. Grasp the handle with one hand and keep your back straight. Pull the handle towards your body, keeping your elbow close to your side. Squeeze your back muscles at the top of the movement. Slowly release the handle back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine.","Grasp the handle with one hand and keep your back straight.","Pull the handle towards your body, keeping your elbow close to your side.","Squeeze your back muscles at the top of the movement.","Slowly release the handle back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich vor dem Gerät.","Greife den Griff mit einer Hand und halte den Rücken gerade.","Ziehe den Griff Richtung Körper, der Ellbogen bleibt nah am Körper.","Spanne am Ende der Bewegung die Rückenmuskulatur an.","Lasse den Griff langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1356.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1356.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bda54f66-a99b-5c1c-be2b-f006153daed4', NULL, 'Lever One Arm Lateral Wide Pulldown', 'Einarmiger breiter Latzug an der Maschine', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handle with an overhand grip and fully extend your arm, keeping a slight bend in your elbow. Pull the handle down and across your body towards your opposite hip, squeezing your lat muscle at the bottom of the movement. Slowly return the handle to the starting position, fully extending your arm. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handle with an overhand grip and fully extend your arm, keeping a slight bend in your elbow.","Pull the handle down and across your body towards your opposite hip, squeezing your lat muscle at the bottom of the movement.","Slowly return the handle to the starting position, fully extending your arm.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife den Griff im Obergriff und strecke den Arm vollständig, der Ellbogen bleibt leicht gebeugt.","Ziehe den Griff nach unten und über den Körper Richtung gegenüberliegende Hüfte, spanne dabei am Ende der Bewegung den Latissimus an.","Führe den Griff langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, der Arm streckt sich vollständig.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1347.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1347.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cfb62910-b26e-543c-a1f6-06c5bdafc74c', NULL, 'Lever One Arm Shoulder Press', 'Einarmiges Schulterdrücken an der Maschine', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the lever handle with one hand and position your elbow at a 90-degree angle. Press the lever upward until your arm is fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the lever back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the lever handle with one hand and position your elbow at a 90-degree angle.","Press the lever upward until your arm is fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the lever back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife den Hebelgriff mit einer Hand, der Ellbogen im 90-Grad-Winkel.","Drücke den Hebel nach oben, bis der Arm über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke den Hebel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0590.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0590.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8e6b0b29-8ef4-5fd6-870b-e0d4c058ba2a', NULL, 'Lever Overhand Triceps Dip', 'Trizeps-Dip an der Maschine im Obergriff', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to the appropriate height and secure your body in position. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your body so that your arms are fully extended. Lower your body by bending your elbows, keeping your upper arms close to your sides. Continue lowering until your upper arms are parallel to the floor. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your elbows. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the machine to the appropriate height and secure your body in position.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your body so that your arms are fully extended.","Lower your body by bending your elbows, keeping your upper arms close to your sides.","Continue lowering until your upper arms are parallel to the floor.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your elbows.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf die passende Höhe ein und sichere den Körper in Position.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und positioniere den Körper so, dass die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Senke den Körper, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, die Oberarme bleiben nah am Körper.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis die Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Ellbogen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0591.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0591.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7144a321-848f-52e8-8c5e-57e7597b4102', NULL, 'Lever Preacher Curl', 'Scott-Curl an der Maschine', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine. Place your upper arms on the pad and grip the handles with an underhand grip. Keep your back straight and your elbows positioned on the pad. Exhale and curl your forearms towards your upper arms, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine.","Place your upper arms on the pad and grip the handles with an underhand grip.","Keep your back straight and your elbows positioned on the pad.","Exhale and curl your forearms towards your upper arms, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät.","Lege die Oberarme auf das Polster und greife die Griffe im Untergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade, die Ellbogen bleiben auf dem Polster.","Atme aus und curle die Unterarme Richtung Oberarme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0592.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0592.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('22fb65e3-432d-51d3-b121-36a2f9640807', NULL, 'Lever Preacher Curl V. 2', 'Scott-Curl an der Maschine V. 2', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against the support. Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your upper arms stationary and exhale as you curl the handles towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps. Inhale as you slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your upper arms resting on the pad and your chest against the support.","Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your upper arms stationary and exhale as you curl the handles towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale as you slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät, die Oberarme liegen auf dem Polster, die Brust an der Stütze.","Greife die Griffe im Untergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und atme aus, während du die Griffe zu den Schultern hochcurlst und den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1614.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1614.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d1a4bb1e-6668-5f92-8f5a-47d879a6b183', NULL, 'Lever Pullover', 'Pullover an der Maschine', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat and handles of the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and grasp the handles with an overhand grip. Keep your arms slightly bent and your core engaged. Slowly pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your lats. Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat and handles of the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and grasp the handles with an overhand grip.","Keep your arms slightly bent and your core engaged.","Slowly pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your lats.","Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitz und Griffe des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, und greife die Griffe im Obergriff.","Halte die Arme leicht gebeugt und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Griffe langsam Richtung Brust und spanne dabei den Latissimus an.","Halte an der maximalen Anspannung kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2285.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2285.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('93e89f08-0c24-5a33-967c-0263e724b43b', NULL, 'Lever Reverse Grip Lateral Pulldown', 'Breiter Latzug an der Maschine im Untergriff', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Sit upright with your chest out and shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back. Pull the handles down towards your chest, leading with your elbows and squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Sit upright with your chest out and shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back.","Pull the handles down towards your chest, leading with your elbows and squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, die Knie unter den Polstern, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Sitze aufrecht, die Brust raus, die Schultern zurück, mit leichtem Hohlkreuz.","Ziehe die Griffe, angeführt von den Ellbogen, Richtung Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und lasse die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2736.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2736.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('89714832-b780-581b-8137-7c92a3d2c9b6', NULL, 'Lever Reverse Grip Preacher Curl', 'Scott-Curl an der Maschine im Untergriff', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine. Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Rest your upper arms on the preacher pad, ensuring your elbows are fully extended. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the handles towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your elbows. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine.","Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Rest your upper arms on the preacher pad, ensuring your elbows are fully extended.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the handles towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, fully extending your elbows.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät.","Greife die Griffe im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Lege die Oberarme auf das Scott-Polster, die Ellbogen vollständig gestreckt.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curle die Griffe zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition, die Ellbogen vollständig gestreckt.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1616.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1616.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b08045c0-0198-534b-81a5-c1d73f4846fb', NULL, 'Lever Reverse Grip Vertical Row', 'Vertikales Rudern an der Maschine im Untergriff', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment. Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate. Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment.","Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate.","Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, palms facing up.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattenposition für eine korrekte Ausrichtung ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1348.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1348.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('802c2850-cb92-58d2-8a83-da5fe4c77781', NULL, 'Lever Reverse Hyperextension', 'Reverse Hyperextension an der Maschine', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the leverage machine to fit your body and secure your feet in the foot pads. Lie face down on the machine with your upper body hanging off the edge and your hips resting on the pad. Cross your arms over your chest or place them behind your head. Engage your glutes and hamstrings to lift your legs upward until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Adjust the leverage machine to fit your body and secure your feet in the foot pads.","Lie face down on the machine with your upper body hanging off the edge and your hips resting on the pad.","Cross your arms over your chest or place them behind your head.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings to lift your legs upward until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und fixiere die Füsse in den Fusspolstern.","Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf das Gerät, der Oberkörper hängt über die Kante, die Hüfte liegt auf dem Polster.","Verschränke die Arme vor der Brust oder lege sie hinter den Kopf.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und hebe die Beine, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0593.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0593.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('be6e00d8-826f-5a43-ac99-eea19c145bba', NULL, 'Lever Reverse T-Bar Row', 'T-Bar-Rudern an der Maschine im Untergriff', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footplate position on the leverage machine. Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footplate position on the leverage machine.","Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattenposition des Geräts ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und strecke die Arme dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1349.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1349.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ac9b3cd0-9154-59d8-863c-fa1332ae7c18', NULL, 'Lever Rotary Calf', 'Rotations-Wadenheben an der Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that your knees are slightly bent and your feet are flat on the footplate. Place your toes on the footplate, with your heels hanging off the edge. Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability. Push through the balls of your feet, raising your heels as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'soleus', '["soleus","ankle stabilizers"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that your knees are slightly bent and your feet are flat on the footplate.","Place your toes on the footplate, with your heels hanging off the edge.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the machine for stability.","Push through the balls of your feet, raising your heels as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass die Knie leicht gebeugt sind und die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte stehen.","Stelle die Zehen auf die Fussplatte, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Geräts fest.","Drücke dich über die Fussballen ab und hebe die Fersen so hoch wie möglich.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2315.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2315.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e165fe33-9866-5879-a38b-99e6e7ea0b23', NULL, 'Lever Seated Calf Press', 'Wadenpresse an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat of the machine so that your shoulders are aligned with the lever pad. Place your toes on the lower portion of the platform and position your knees under the lever pad. Grasp the handles on the sides of the seat for stability. Press the lever pad down by extending your ankles, lifting your heels as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'soleus', '["soleus","hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the seat of the machine so that your shoulders are aligned with the lever pad.","Place your toes on the lower portion of the platform and position your knees under the lever pad.","Grasp the handles on the sides of the seat for stability.","Press the lever pad down by extending your ankles, lifting your heels as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz des Geräts so ein, dass die Schultern mit dem Polster ausgerichtet sind.","Stelle die Zehen auf den unteren Teil der Plattform und positioniere die Knie unter dem Polster.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen an den Seiten des Sitzes fest.","Drücke das Polster nach unten, indem du die Fussgelenke streckst und die Fersen so hoch wie möglich hebst.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2335.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2335.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('17b85653-fcb3-500b-94ca-203d93607b78', NULL, 'Lever Seated Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that your knees are slightly bent and your feet are flat on the footplate. Place your toes on the footplate with your heels hanging off the edge. Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability. Push through the balls of your feet to raise your heels as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'soleus', '["soleus","ankle stabilizers"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that your knees are slightly bent and your feet are flat on the footplate.","Place your toes on the footplate with your heels hanging off the edge.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability.","Push through the balls of your feet to raise your heels as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass die Knie leicht gebeugt sind und die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte stehen.","Stelle die Zehen auf die Fussplatte, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Sitzes fest.","Drücke dich über die Fussballen ab, um die Fersen so hoch wie möglich zu heben.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0594.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0594.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1baf65c1-a3a0-57f2-863c-73f64872b91b', NULL, 'Lever Seated Crunch', 'Crunch an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'waist', 'abs', 'leverage machine', 'Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles or place your hands on the side pads for support. Engage your abs and slowly lean back, allowing the pad to move with you. Once your upper body is at a 45-degree angle, contract your abs and crunch forward, bringing your chest towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly release and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles or place your hands on the side pads for support.","Engage your abs and slowly lean back, allowing the pad to move with you.","Once your upper body is at a 45-degree angle, contract your abs and crunch forward, bringing your chest towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly release and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe oder stütze die Hände an den Seitenpolstern ab.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und lehne dich langsam zurück, das Polster bewegt sich mit.","Sobald der Oberkörper in einem 45-Grad-Winkel ist, spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und rolle dich nach vorne, die Brust Richtung Knie.","Halte oben kurz inne, löse dann langsam und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1452.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1452.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1822dce1-9c56-5f92-9cf2-5f51dff5772b', NULL, 'Lever Seated Crunch (Chest Pad)', 'Crunch an der Maschine im Sitzen (Brustpolster)', 'waist', 'abs', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and chest pad position according to your comfort. Sit on the machine with your back against the chest pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles or side bars for stability. Engage your abs and slowly lean back, allowing the chest pad to move with you. Pause for a moment at the maximum contraction, feeling the tension in your abs. Slowly return to the starting position by contracting your abs and pulling yourself back up. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Adjust the seat height and chest pad position according to your comfort.","Sit on the machine with your back against the chest pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles or side bars for stability.","Engage your abs and slowly lean back, allowing the chest pad to move with you.","Pause for a moment at the maximum contraction, feeling the tension in your abs.","Slowly return to the starting position by contracting your abs and pulling yourself back up.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Brustpolster-Position nach deinem Komfort ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Brustpolster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seitenstangen fest.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und lehne dich langsam zurück, das Brustpolster bewegt sich mit.","Halte bei maximaler Anspannung kurz inne und spüre die Spannung in der Bauchmuskulatur.","Kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du die Bauchmuskulatur anspannst und dich zurückziehst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0595.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0595.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('471dae68-482a-5185-8211-8ab2fb4e112d', NULL, 'Lever Seated Crunch V. 2', 'Crunch an der Maschine im Sitzen V. 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'leverage machine', 'Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the pad and your feet secured under the footpads. Place your hands on the handles or the sides of the seat for support. Engage your abs and slowly crunch forward, bringing your chest towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your abs. Slowly return to the starting position, allowing your back to round slightly. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the pad and your feet secured under the footpads.","Place your hands on the handles or the sides of the seat for support.","Engage your abs and slowly crunch forward, bringing your chest towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your abs.","Slowly return to the starting position, allowing your back to round slightly.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Stütze die Hände an den Griffen oder Seiten des Sitzes ab.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und rolle dich langsam nach vorne, die Brust Richtung Knie.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an.","Kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, der Rücken rundet sich dabei leicht.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3760.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3760.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('757ac126-60a0-571f-86d2-d30918871a64', NULL, 'Lever Seated Dip', 'Dip an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that your feet are flat on the ground and your knees are at a 90-degree angle. Grasp the handles of the leverage machine with your palms facing down and your arms fully extended. Slowly lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that your feet are flat on the ground and your knees are at a 90-degree angle.","Grasp the handles of the leverage machine with your palms facing down and your arms fully extended.","Slowly lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass die Füsse flach auf dem Boden stehen und die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel sind.","Greife die Griffe des Geräts, Handflächen nach unten, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Senke den Körper langsam, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis die Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich durch Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1451.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1451.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('23e91e89-4a63-5d70-839c-b1d2d0ed3edd', NULL, 'Lever Seated Fly', 'Fliegende an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles with a pronated grip and keep your elbows slightly bent. Exhale and push the handles forward, bringing them together in front of your chest. Pause for a moment, squeezing your chest muscles. Inhale and slowly return to the starting position, allowing your chest muscles to stretch. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'deltoids', '["deltoids","trapezius"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles with a pronated grip and keep your elbows slightly bent.","Exhale and push the handles forward, bringing them together in front of your chest.","Pause for a moment, squeezing your chest muscles.","Inhale and slowly return to the starting position, allowing your chest muscles to stretch.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Pronationsgriff und halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Atme aus und drücke die Griffe nach vorne, bis sie sich vor der Brust treffen.","Halte kurz inne und spanne die Brustmuskulatur an.","Atme ein und kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, die Brustmuskulatur dehnt sich dabei.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0596.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0596.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('16ae6dbb-e5b4-5cd2-8e2e-3b317c1c46d0', NULL, 'Lever Seated Good Morning', 'Good Morning an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that your hips are slightly higher than your knees. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the footrests. Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability. Keeping your back straight, slowly lean forward from your hips until your upper body is parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position by pushing through your glutes and hamstrings. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that your hips are slightly higher than your knees.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the footrests.","Grasp the handles or the sides of the seat for stability.","Keeping your back straight, slowly lean forward from your hips until your upper body is parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then slowly return to the starting position by pushing through your glutes and hamstrings.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass die Hüfte etwas höher als die Knie ist.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf den Fussstützen.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seiten des Sitzes fest.","Halte den Rücken gerade und beuge dich langsam aus der Hüfte nach vorne, bis der Oberkörper parallel zum Boden ist.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du Gesäss und Beinbeuger anspannst.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3759.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3759.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4245c536-c3d8-5038-a7c7-e969760df8b0', NULL, 'Lever Seated Hip Abduction', 'Hüftabduktion an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'abductors', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footrests. Place your hands on the side handles for stability. Engage your abductors and slowly push your legs apart, away from the midline of your body. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring your legs back together to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footrests.","Place your hands on the side handles for stability.","Engage your abductors and slowly push your legs apart, away from the midline of your body.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring your legs back together to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel sind.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse auf den Fussstützen.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den seitlichen Griffen fest.","Spanne die Abduktoren an und drücke die Beine langsam auseinander, von der Körpermitte weg.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und führe die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0597.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0597.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9ac35ebe-07f2-5e9c-9ee9-955e21ccd461', NULL, 'Lever Seated Hip Adduction', 'Hüftadduktion an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'adductors', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest. Place your feet on the footrests and grasp the handles for stability. Engage your adductor muscles and slowly bring your legs together, squeezing your inner thighs. Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest.","Place your feet on the footrests and grasp the handles for stability.","Engage your adductor muscles and slowly bring your legs together, squeezing your inner thighs.","Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Stelle die Füsse auf die Fussstützen und halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen fest.","Spanne die Adduktoren an und führe die Beine langsam zusammen, während du die Innenseite der Oberschenkel anspannst.","Halte bei maximaler Anspannung kurz inne und kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0598.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0598.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('589d22c1-5fbc-5cda-abca-0b39b96475f3', NULL, 'Lever Seated Leg Curl', 'Beincurl an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest. Place your lower legs under the padded lever, just above your ankles. Grasp the handles on the sides of the machine for support. Keeping your upper legs stationary, exhale and curl your legs up as far as possible. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings. Inhale and slowly lower the lever back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves"]', '["Adjust the machine to fit your body and sit on it with your back against the backrest.","Place your lower legs under the padded lever, just above your ankles.","Grasp the handles on the sides of the machine for support.","Keeping your upper legs stationary, exhale and curl your legs up as far as possible.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings.","Inhale and slowly lower the lever back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deinen Körper ein und setz dich, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Lege die Unterschenkel unter den gepolsterten Hebel, knapp über den Fussgelenken.","Halte dich an den Griffen an den Seiten des Geräts fest.","Halte die Oberschenkel ruhig, atme aus und curle die Beine so weit wie möglich hoch.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und spanne die Beinbeuger an.","Atme ein und senke den Hebel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0599.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0599.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c7aae55b-a2af-52ee-8f19-157694a8eda7', NULL, 'Lever Seated Leg Raise Crunch', 'Crunch mit Beinheben an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'waist', 'abs', 'leverage machine', 'Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footrests. Grasp the handles or sidebars for stability. Engage your abs and slowly raise your legs up towards your chest, curling your torso forward at the same time. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs and torso back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the leverage machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the footrests.","Grasp the handles or sidebars for stability.","Engage your abs and slowly raise your legs up towards your chest, curling your torso forward at the same time.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs and torso back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse auf den Fussstützen.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen oder Seitenstangen fest.","Spanne die Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe die Beine langsam Richtung Brust, während du den Oberkörper gleichzeitig nach vorne einrollst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke Beine und Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0600.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0600.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c56d3ec4-8831-5231-8ef3-03ab3943361a', NULL, 'Lever Seated Reverse Fly', 'Reverse Fliegende an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms slightly bent. Exhale and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull the handles back and outward, away from your body. Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then inhale and slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms slightly bent.","Exhale and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull the handles back and outward, away from your body.","Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then inhale and slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und halte die Arme leicht gebeugt.","Atme aus und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen, während du die Griffe nach hinten und aussen vom Körper weg ziehst.","Halte bei maximaler Anspannung kurz inne, atme ein und kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0602.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0602.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('29a371e5-323c-5c37-9b69-6d4dc6cdeb9f', NULL, 'Lever Seated Reverse Fly (Parallel Grip)', 'Reverse Fliegende an der Maschine im Sitzen (paralleler Griff)', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with a parallel grip, palms facing each other, and keep your arms slightly bent. Exhale and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull the handles back and outward, away from your body. Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then inhale and slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with a parallel grip, palms facing each other, and keep your arms slightly bent.","Exhale and squeeze your shoulder blades together as you pull the handles back and outward, away from your body.","Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then inhale and slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Parallelgriff, Handflächen zueinander gerichtet, die Arme leicht gebeugt.","Atme aus und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen, während du die Griffe nach hinten und aussen vom Körper weg ziehst.","Halte bei maximaler Anspannung kurz inne, atme ein und kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0601.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0601.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a205458b-7f0b-52e2-ae12-b6c34998cc2e', NULL, 'Lever Seated Row', 'Rudern an der Maschine im Sitzen', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footrests to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet on the footrests. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and your core engaged. Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement. Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footrests to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet on the footrests.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement.","Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussstützen auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse auf den Fussstützen.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, schulterbreit auseinander.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Körper und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am Höhepunkt der Bewegung kurz inne.","Lasse die Griffe langsam los und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1350.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1350.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2f8b62eb-6caa-5b74-bcb2-4042aa4a484f', NULL, 'Lever Seated Squat Calf Raise on Leg Press Machine', 'Wadenheben im Sitzen an der Beinpresse-Maschine', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the footplate. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the footplate, shoulder-width apart. Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the footplate, keeping your heels off the edge. Release the safety handles and push the footplate away from you by extending your knees. Once your knees are fully extended, slowly lower your heels by flexing your calves. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the footplate back up by extending your calves. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the footplate.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the footplate, shoulder-width apart.","Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the footplate, keeping your heels off the edge.","Release the safety handles and push the footplate away from you by extending your knees.","Once your knees are fully extended, slowly lower your heels by flexing your calves.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the footplate back up by extending your calves.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Beinpresse so ein, dass die Knie leicht gebeugt sind, wenn die Füsse auf der Fussplatte stehen.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse schulterbreit flach auf der Fussplatte.","Stelle Zehen und Fussballen auf die Fussplatte, die Fersen bleiben über der Kante.","Löse die Sicherheitsgriffe und drücke die Fussplatte durch Strecken der Knie von dir weg.","Senke die Fersen langsam ab, sobald die Knie vollständig gestreckt sind, indem du die Waden dehnst.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke die Fussplatte dann durch Anspannen der Waden zurück nach oben.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1385.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1385.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0393a3bb-f198-5ab3-8855-c68dffeb8070', NULL, 'Lever Shoulder Press', 'Schulterdrücken an der Maschine', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands at shoulder level. Push the handles upward until your arms are fully extended, but do not lock your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the backrest.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands at shoulder level.","Push the handles upward until your arms are fully extended, but do not lock your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände auf Schulterhöhe.","Drücke die Griffe nach oben, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne die Ellbogen durchzustrecken.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0603.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0603.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eb89f2e1-3a02-5e05-9ea0-d9cd475a441d', NULL, 'Lever Shoulder Press V. 2', 'Schulterdrücken an der Maschine V. 2', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles of the machine with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles upward and forward until your arms are fully extended, but not locked. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles of the machine with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles upward and forward until your arms are fully extended, but not locked.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Rückenlehne des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe des Geräts im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach oben und vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne sie durchzustrecken.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0869.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0869.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('498e6c1b-205e-556a-ae64-839310d393a7', NULL, 'Lever Shoulder Press V. 3', 'Schulterdrücken an der Maschine V. 3', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles of the machine with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Push the handles upward and forward until your arms are fully extended, but not locked. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest"]', '["Adjust the seat height and backrest of the leverage machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles of the machine with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push the handles upward and forward until your arms are fully extended, but not locked.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Rückenlehne des Geräts auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe des Geräts im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Drücke die Griffe nach oben und vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne sie durchzustrecken.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2318.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2318.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d77f209c-4dcc-5bf4-b4cf-ce362144f37c', NULL, 'Lever Shrug', 'Schulterheben an der Maschine', 'back', 'traps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms straight. Keeping your back straight, lift your shoulders up towards your ears as high as possible. Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the leverage machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your arms straight.","Keeping your back straight, lift your shoulders up towards your ears as high as possible.","Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich auf das Gerät, der Rücken liegt am Polster.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und halte die Arme gestreckt.","Halte den Rücken gerade und hebe die Schultern so hoch wie möglich Richtung Ohren.","Halte die Anspannung kurz und senke die Schultern dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0604.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0604.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a47bb045-7ac5-5de2-9e6b-58821556378b', NULL, 'Lever Standing Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben an der Maschine im Stehen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the machine to your height and stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Place your shoulders under the pads and hold onto the handles for stability. Raise your heels as high as possible by extending your ankles. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'soleus', '["soleus","ankle stabilizers"]', '["Adjust the machine to your height and stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place your shoulders under the pads and hold onto the handles for stability.","Raise your heels as high as possible by extending your ankles.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle das Gerät auf deine Grösse ein und stell dich schulterbreit hin.","Stelle die Schultern unter die Polster und halte dich zur Stabilisierung an den Griffen fest.","Hebe die Fersen so hoch wie möglich, indem du die Fussgelenke streckst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke die Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0605.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0605.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('47cf569d-b281-51b0-83a2-1e6aaaf52b17', NULL, 'Lever Standing Chest Press', 'Brustpresse an der Maschine im Stehen', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands at chest level. Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the handles back towards your chest, maintaining control throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your hands at chest level.","Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the handles back towards your chest, maintaining control throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf dem Gerät, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände auf Brusthöhe.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Halte kurz inne und führe die Griffe dann kontrolliert zurück Richtung Brust.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3758.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3758.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7a3651b-13e0-5d67-b6f5-35a9547b0593', NULL, 'Lever T-Bar Row', 'T-Bar-Rudern an der Maschine', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment. Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Pull the handles towards your torso, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footplate position to ensure proper alignment.","Sit on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the footplate.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Pull the handles towards your torso, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak contraction, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussplattenposition für eine korrekte Ausrichtung ein.","Setz dich auf das Gerät, die Brust liegt am Polster, die Füsse flach auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne die Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung Oberkörper und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte bei maximaler Anspannung kurz inne und lasse die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0606.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0606.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ccc26905-c817-5109-8dee-bb17b2ccc5f3', NULL, 'Lever T-Bar Reverse Grip Row', 'T-Bar-Rudern an der Maschine (Untergriff)', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and engage your core. Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and engage your core.","Pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich an der Maschine, sodass deine Brust an der Polsterung anliegt und deine Füsse flach auf dem Boden stehen.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Ziehe die Griffe zu deiner Brust, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung, löse dann langsam und strecke die Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1351.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1351.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('954338fd-8a97-5191-89a2-50aa4014c55e', NULL, 'Lever Triceps Extension', 'Trizepsstrecken an der Maschine', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and fully extend your arms in front of you. Keeping your upper arms stationary, slowly lower the handles towards your forehead by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the handles back up to the starting position by extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and fully extend your arms in front of you.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, slowly lower the handles towards your forehead by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the handles back up to the starting position by extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich an der Maschine mit dem Rücken an der Polsterung.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und strecke die Arme vollständig vor dir aus.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig und senke die Griffe langsam in Richtung Stirn ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke die Griffe dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0607.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0607.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bcc0001b-ad24-53f5-a9c0-196b52ea8ab1', NULL, 'Lever Unilateral Row', 'Einarmiges Rudern an der Maschine', 'back', 'upper back', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your back straight. Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the machine.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and keep your back straight.","Pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release and extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich mit Blick zur Maschine.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und halte den Rücken gerade.","Ziehe die Griffe zu deinem Körper, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung, löse dann langsam und strecke die Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1313.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1313.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f528fc13-181f-593a-bd4c-5152180bb9a7', NULL, 'London Bridge', 'London Bridge', 'back', 'upper back', 'rope', 'Attach the rope to a high anchor point. Stand facing away from the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the rope with an overhand grip, palms facing down. Lean forward slightly, keeping your back straight and core engaged. Pull the rope towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the tension and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","biceps","forearms"]', '["Attach the rope to a high anchor point.","Stand facing away from the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the rope with an overhand grip, palms facing down.","Lean forward slightly, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","Pull the rope towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the tension and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Befestige das Seil an einem hoch angebrachten Fixpunkt.","Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zum Fixpunkt, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Greife das Seil im Obergriff, die Handflächen zeigen nach unten.","Lehne dich leicht nach vorne, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe das Seil zu deinem Körper, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung, löse die Spannung dann langsam und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0609.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0609.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('1d129b2d-7720-5d64-9f55-77cabf081872', NULL, 'Low Glute Bridge on Floor', 'Flache Gesässbrücke am Boden', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your arms by your sides, palms facing down. Engage your glutes and core, then lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your glutes. Slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","core"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your arms by your sides, palms facing down.","Engage your glutes and core, then lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your glutes.","Slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Arme neben den Körper, die Handflächen zeigen nach unten.","Spanne Gesäss und Körpermitte an und hebe dann die Hüfte vom Boden ab, bis dein Körper eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern bildet.","Halte kurz inne oben und spanne dabei das Gesäss an.","Senke die Hüfte langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3013.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3013.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a5ca35a7-2378-51e2-be59-34dab4244cef', NULL, 'Lower Back Curl', 'Unterrücken-Curl', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your stomach with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling your back upwards. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Lie flat on your stomach with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling your back upwards.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Bauch, die Beine gestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, indem du den Rücken nach oben wölbst.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke dann den Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1352.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1352.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d66d6751-b25c-5790-b4ec-8ad250626450', NULL, 'Lunge with Jump', 'Ausfallschritt mit Sprung', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart. Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. Push off with your right foot and jump into the air, switching the position of your feet mid-air. Land softly with your left foot forward and immediately lower your body into a lunge position. Continue alternating between lunges and jumps for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","Push off with your right foot and jump into the air, switching the position of your feet mid-air.","Land softly with your left foot forward and immediately lower your body into a lunge position.","Continue alternating between lunges and jumps for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin.","Mache einen Schritt nach vorne mit dem rechten Fuss und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Stosse dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab und springe in die Luft, wobei du die Position deiner Füsse in der Luft wechselst.","Lande weich mit dem linken Fuss vorne und senke deinen Körper sofort wieder in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Wechsle weiterhin zwischen Ausfallschritten und Sprüngen für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3582.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3582.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1a2b0e33-fefc-5b40-8ec4-067348f05a1e', NULL, 'Lunge with Twist', 'Ausfallschritt mit Drehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart. Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. As you lunge, twist your torso to the right, bringing your left elbow towards your right knee. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side, stepping forward with your left foot and twisting your torso to the left. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","As you lunge, twist your torso to the right, bringing your left elbow towards your right knee.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side, stepping forward with your left foot and twisting your torso to the left.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin.","Mache einen Schritt nach vorne mit dem rechten Fuss und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Drehe im Ausfallschritt deinen Oberkörper nach rechts und führe den linken Ellbogen zum rechten Knie.","Halte kurz inne, kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite, indem du mit dem linken Fuss nach vorne trittst und den Oberkörper nach links drehst.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1688.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1688.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('37a7144d-b897-5cd4-a275-e091a33fd4df', NULL, 'Lying (Side) Quads Stretch', 'Quadrizeps-Dehnung im Liegen (seitlich)', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs straight. Bend your top leg and grab your ankle or foot with your hand. Gently pull your ankle or foot towards your glutes until you feel a stretch in your quads. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Release the stretch and repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs straight.","Bend your top leg and grab your ankle or foot with your hand.","Gently pull your ankle or foot towards your glutes until you feel a stretch in your quads.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Release the stretch and repeat on the other side."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine gestreckt.","Beuge das obere Bein und greife mit der Hand deinen Knöchel oder Fuss.","Ziehe Knöchel oder Fuss sanft in Richtung Gesäss, bis du eine Dehnung im Quadrizeps spürst.","Halte die Dehnung für 20-30 Sekunden.","Löse die Dehnung und wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0613.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0613.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('34639d67-b71c-5868-878b-cc0b1d5e5ef7', NULL, 'Lying Elbow to Knee', 'Ellbogen-zu-Knie im Liegen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee. At the same time, extend your right leg straight out and lift it off the ground. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time bringing your left elbow towards your right knee and extending your left leg. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee.","At the same time, extend your right leg straight out and lift it off the ground.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time bringing your left elbow towards your right knee and extending your left leg.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper vom Boden ab, indem du den rechten Ellbogen zum linken Knie führst.","Strecke gleichzeitig das rechte Bein gerade aus und hebe es vom Boden ab.","Halte kurz inne, kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal führst du den linken Ellbogen zum rechten Knie und streckst das linke Bein.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2312.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2312.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f46008bc-0f54-5a0e-818b-699853956ad4', NULL, 'Lying Leg Raise Flat Bench', 'Beinheben im Liegen auf der Flachbank', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on a flat bench with your back pressed against it. Place your hands under your glutes for support. Keep your legs straight and together, and lift them up towards the ceiling. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on a flat bench with your back pressed against it.","Place your hands under your glutes for support.","Keep your legs straight and together, and lift them up towards the ceiling.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Flachbank, den Rücken fest angepresst.","Lege die Hände zur Unterstützung unter das Gesäss.","Halte die Beine gestreckt und zusammen und hebe sie in Richtung Decke an.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke dann die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0620.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0620.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('12d0f42e-c5ba-5981-94f0-9ca955e849b0', NULL, 'Lying Leg-Hip Raise', 'Bein-Hüft-Heben im Liegen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Place your hands under your glutes for support. Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, raising them towards the ceiling. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Place your hands under your glutes for support.","Engage your core and lift your legs off the ground, raising them towards the ceiling.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Lege die Hände zur Unterstützung unter das Gesäss.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine vom Boden ab in Richtung Decke.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke dann die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0865.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0865.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a834f1d0-f074-598c-bfc1-cbca6663e053', NULL, 'Machine Inner Chest Press', 'Innere Brustpresse an der Maschine', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle. Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your back flat against the pad.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and position your elbows at a 90-degree angle.","Push the handles forward until your arms are fully extended, exhaling during the movement.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position, inhaling as you do so.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich an der Maschine mit dem Rücken flach an der Polsterung.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und positioniere die Ellbogen in einem 90°-Winkel.","Drücke die Griffe nach vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind, und atme dabei aus.","Halte kurz inne am Ende der Bewegung, kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück und atme dabei ein.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1301.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1301.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4359daea-0cda-5ea2-98ec-85b86face565', NULL, 'March Sit (Wall)', 'Marschieren im Wandsitz', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your back against a wall and your feet hip-width apart. Slowly slide your back down the wall until your knees are bent at a 90-degree angle. Lift your right foot off the ground and bring your knee towards your chest. Lower your right foot back down and lift your left foot off the ground, bringing your knee towards your chest. Continue alternating between lifting your right and left foot for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your back against a wall and your feet hip-width apart.","Slowly slide your back down the wall until your knees are bent at a 90-degree angle.","Lift your right foot off the ground and bring your knee towards your chest.","Lower your right foot back down and lift your left foot off the ground, bringing your knee towards your chest.","Continue alternating between lifting your right and left foot for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Rücken an eine Wand, die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander.","Rutsche langsam mit dem Rücken die Wand hinunter, bis deine Knie in einem 90°-Winkel gebeugt sind.","Hebe den rechten Fuss vom Boden ab und führe das Knie zur Brust.","Senke den rechten Fuss wieder ab und hebe den linken Fuss vom Boden ab, indem du das Knie zur Brust führst.","Wechsle weiterhin zwischen dem Anheben des rechten und linken Fusses für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0624.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0624.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('27a2b615-b8d5-5ed3-b195-7e4cf9fab7bf', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Catch and Overhead Throw', 'Medizinball fangen und über Kopf werfen', 'back', 'lats', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball in both hands at chest level. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Lower your body into a squat position, keeping your back straight and chest up. Explosively extend your hips and legs, while simultaneously throwing the medicine ball overhead. Release the ball at the top of the movement and catch it on the way down. Lower your body back into the squat position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball in both hands at chest level.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Lower your body into a squat position, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Explosively extend your hips and legs, while simultaneously throwing the medicine ball overhead.","Release the ball at the top of the movement and catch it on the way down.","Lower your body back into the squat position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte einen Medizinball mit beiden Händen auf Brusthöhe.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Brust aufgerichtet.","Strecke Hüfte und Beine explosiv, während du gleichzeitig den Medizinball über Kopf wirfst.","Lass den Ball am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung los und fange ihn auf dem Weg nach unten wieder auf.","Senke deinen Körper zurück in die Kniebeuge-Position und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1353.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1353.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3dd72341-c147-554c-92ae-4783f796e43a', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Chest Pass', 'Medizinball-Brustpass', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball at chest level. Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest with force. As you release the ball, follow through with your arms and torso, transferring your weight from your back foot to your front foot. Catch the ball as it rebounds off the wall or partner, and immediately repeat the movement. Continue for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball at chest level.","Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest with force.","As you release the ball, follow through with your arms and torso, transferring your weight from your back foot to your front foot.","Catch the ball as it rebounds off the wall or partner, and immediately repeat the movement.","Continue for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte den Medizinball auf Brusthöhe.","Strecke die Arme nach vorne und drücke den Medizinball mit Kraft von deiner Brust weg.","Wenn du den Ball loslässt, führe die Bewegung mit Armen und Oberkörper fort und verlagere dein Gewicht vom hinteren auf den vorderen Fuss.","Fange den Ball auf, wenn er von der Wand oder deinem Partner zurückprallt, und wiederhole die Bewegung sofort.","Fahre fort für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1302.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1302.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('56a44187-3a9c-51d1-a0b6-61336ab7e046', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Chest Push from 3-Point Stance', 'Medizinball-Brustdrücken aus dem 3-Punkte-Stand', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Start in a 3 point stance with one hand on the medicine ball and the other hand on the ground. Extend your legs and position your body in a straight line. Lower your chest towards the ground while keeping your back straight. Push the medicine ball away from your body, extending your arm fully. Return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start in a 3 point stance with one hand on the medicine ball and the other hand on the ground.","Extend your legs and position your body in a straight line.","Lower your chest towards the ground while keeping your back straight.","Push the medicine ball away from your body, extending your arm fully.","Return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne im 3-Punkt-Stand, eine Hand auf dem Medizinball und die andere Hand auf dem Boden.","Strecke die Beine und bringe deinen Körper in eine gerade Linie.","Senke die Brust in Richtung Boden ab und halte dabei den Rücken gerade.","Drücke den Medizinball von deinem Körper weg, indem du den Arm vollständig streckst.","Kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1303.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1303.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('100c2585-1138-5d6c-b019-d9e438aad551', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Chest Push Multiple Response', 'Medizinball-Brustdrücken (mehrfache Reaktion)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball at chest level. Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest. Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the medicine ball back to your chest. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball at chest level.","Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest.","Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the medicine ball back to your chest.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte einen Medizinball auf Brusthöhe.","Strecke die Arme nach vorne und drücke den Medizinball von deiner Brust weg.","Halte kurz inne, bringe den Medizinball dann langsam zurück zu deiner Brust.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1304.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1304.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d96c6f0a-9118-554e-b2cb-5be2bef74009', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Chest Push Single Response', 'Medizinball-Brustdrücken (einfache Reaktion)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball at chest level. Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest. Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the medicine ball back to your chest. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball at chest level.","Extend your arms forward, pushing the medicine ball away from your chest.","Pause for a moment, then slowly bring the medicine ball back to your chest.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte den Medizinball auf Brusthöhe.","Strecke die Arme nach vorne und drücke den Medizinball von deiner Brust weg.","Halte kurz inne, bringe den Medizinball dann langsam zurück zu deiner Brust.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1305.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1305.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('59ca578f-e9d6-5ca9-9e2c-3d19fd4dcb70', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Chest Push with Run Release', 'Medizinball-Brustdrücken mit Lauf-Abwurf', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball at chest level. Step forward with your right foot and simultaneously push the medicine ball forward, extending your arms fully. As you push the ball forward, release it and let it roll forward. Quickly run forward and catch the ball before it hits the ground. Once you catch the ball, bring it back to your chest and repeat the movement with your left foot forward. Continue alternating legs and repeating the exercise for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball at chest level.","Step forward with your right foot and simultaneously push the medicine ball forward, extending your arms fully.","As you push the ball forward, release it and let it roll forward.","Quickly run forward and catch the ball before it hits the ground.","Once you catch the ball, bring it back to your chest and repeat the movement with your left foot forward.","Continue alternating legs and repeating the exercise for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte einen Medizinball auf Brusthöhe.","Trete mit dem rechten Fuss nach vorne und drücke gleichzeitig den Medizinball nach vorne, wobei du die Arme vollständig streckst.","Lass den Ball los, während du ihn nach vorne drückst, und lass ihn nach vorne rollen.","Laufe schnell nach vorne und fange den Ball, bevor er den Boden berührt.","Sobald du den Ball gefangen hast, bringe ihn zurück zu deiner Brust und wiederhole die Bewegung mit dem linken Fuss vorne.","Wechsle weiterhin die Beine und wiederhole die Übung für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1312.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1312.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9eff538b-3fe3-5e0d-9fe6-b0e57cc37ef8', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Close Grip Push-up', 'Enger Liegestütz auf dem Medizinball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'medicine ball', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands on the medicine ball, shoulder-width apart. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Push back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands on the medicine ball, shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Push back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer hohen Planke-Position, die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Medizinball.","Senke deinen Körper in Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und eng am Körper hältst.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme vollständig streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1701.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1701.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d2f90924-a7d5-5d9d-b661-98b12d08df21', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Overhead Slam', 'Medizinball-Überkopfslam', 'back', 'upper back', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball with both hands above your head. Engage your core and keep your back straight. Bend your knees slightly and forcefully slam the medicine ball down to the ground in front of you. As you slam the ball down, use your entire body to generate power, including your shoulders and core. Catch the ball on the bounce and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a medicine ball with both hands above your head.","Engage your core and keep your back straight.","Bend your knees slightly and forcefully slam the medicine ball down to the ground in front of you.","As you slam the ball down, use your entire body to generate power, including your shoulders and core.","Catch the ball on the bounce and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte einen Medizinball mit beiden Händen über dem Kopf.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken gerade.","Beuge die Knie leicht und schlage den Medizinball mit Wucht vor dir auf den Boden.","Nutze beim Aufschlagen des Balls deinen ganzen Körper, um Kraft zu erzeugen, einschliesslich Schultern und Körpermitte.","Fange den Ball nach dem Aufprall und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1354.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1354.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a5934921-98f0-5c3e-a9cd-5a2e20ca2c38', NULL, 'Medicine Ball Supine Chest Throw', 'Medizinball-Brustwurf im Liegen (Rückenlage)', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'medicine ball', 'Lie flat on your back on a bench with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold the medicine ball with both hands, extending your arms straight up above your chest. Lower the medicine ball towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Explosively push the medicine ball upwards, extending your arms fully and throwing the ball as high as possible. Catch the medicine ball and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Lie flat on your back on a bench with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the medicine ball with both hands, extending your arms straight up above your chest.","Lower the medicine ball towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Explosively push the medicine ball upwards, extending your arms fully and throwing the ball as high as possible.","Catch the medicine ball and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken auf eine Bank, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte den Medizinball mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme gerade über deine Brust nach oben.","Senke den Medizinball in Richtung Brust ab und halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Drücke den Medizinball explosiv nach oben, strecke die Arme vollständig und wirf den Ball so hoch wie möglich.","Fange den Medizinball und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1750.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1750.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b2d38867-d86a-5883-90ff-15bfcf6df864', NULL, 'Mixed Grip Chin-up', 'Klimmzug im gemischten Griff', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an underhand grip (palms facing towards you) and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your feet off the ground. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position with control. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an underhand grip (palms facing towards you) and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your feet off the ground.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position with control.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Untergriff (Handflächen zeigen zu dir), die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge an der Stange mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und den Füssen über dem Boden.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, wobei die Brust vorangeht.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke deinen Körper dann kontrolliert langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0627.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0627.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('91a84433-f96f-5ac4-8b1f-96534f5131e6', NULL, 'Modified Hindu Push-up (Male)', 'Modifizierter Hindu-Liegestütz (Mann)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet hip-width apart. Lower your body towards the ground, bending your elbows and keeping your core engaged. As you lower your body, shift your weight back and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, creating an inverted V shape with your body. Continue to lower your body until your chest is just above the ground, then reverse the movement, pushing your hips back down and extending your arms to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet hip-width apart.","Lower your body towards the ground, bending your elbows and keeping your core engaged.","As you lower your body, shift your weight back and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, creating an inverted V shape with your body.","Continue to lower your body until your chest is just above the ground, then reverse the movement, pushing your hips back down and extending your arms to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit und die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander.","Senke deinen Körper in Richtung Boden ab, beuge dabei die Ellbogen und halte deine Körpermitte angespannt.","Verlagere beim Absenken dein Gewicht nach hinten und hebe die Hüfte in Richtung Decke, sodass dein Körper ein umgekehrtes V bildet.","Senke deinen Körper weiter ab, bis deine Brust knapp über dem Boden ist, kehre die Bewegung dann um, indem du die Hüfte wieder absenkst und die Arme streckst, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3217.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3217.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3e72d665-c1cb-5514-b9ab-c4bd6f84b4d3', NULL, 'Modified Push-up to Lower Arms', 'Modifizierter Liegestütz zum Unterarmstütz', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line. Lower your body down towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Once your elbows are at a 90-degree angle, lower your forearms to the ground, keeping your elbows directly under your shoulders. Pause for a moment, then push through your palms to lift your forearms back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","chest","shoulders"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line.","Lower your body down towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Once your elbows are at a 90-degree angle, lower your forearms to the ground, keeping your elbows directly under your shoulders.","Pause for a moment, then push through your palms to lift your forearms back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer Liegestütz-Position, die Hände direkt unter den Schultern und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Senke deinen Körper in Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und eng am Körper hältst.","Sobald die Ellbogen in einem 90°-Winkel sind, senke die Unterarme auf den Boden ab, wobei die Ellbogen direkt unter den Schultern bleiben.","Halte kurz inne, drücke dich dann über die Handflächen ab, um die Unterarme zurück in die Ausgangsposition anzuheben.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1421.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1421.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0cfb7b84-fb95-5c93-9019-581db58ea179', NULL, 'Monster Walk', 'Monster Walk', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Place a resistance band around your ankles. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly bend your knees. Take a step to the side with your right foot, maintaining tension on the resistance band. Follow with your left foot, stepping to the side to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Place a resistance band around your ankles.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly bend your knees.","Take a step to the side with your right foot, maintaining tension on the resistance band.","Follow with your left foot, stepping to the side to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege ein Widerstandsband um deine Knöchel.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und beuge die Knie leicht.","Mache einen Schritt zur Seite mit dem rechten Fuss und halte dabei die Spannung im Widerstandsband.","Folge mit dem linken Fuss, indem du zur Seite trittst, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen, wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0628.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0628.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cd2db465-9e4d-5a78-8066-18b010082134', NULL, 'Mountain Climber', 'Mountain Climber', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line. Engage your core and bring your right knee towards your chest, then quickly switch and bring your left knee towards your chest. Continue alternating legs in a running motion, keeping your hips low and your core engaged. Maintain a steady pace and breathe evenly throughout the exercise. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line.","Engage your core and bring your right knee towards your chest, then quickly switch and bring your left knee towards your chest.","Continue alternating legs in a running motion, keeping your hips low and your core engaged.","Maintain a steady pace and breathe evenly throughout the exercise.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer hohen Planke-Position, die Hände direkt unter den Schultern und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und führe das rechte Knie zur Brust, wechsle dann schnell und führe das linke Knie zur Brust.","Wechsle die Beine weiter in einer laufenden Bewegung, halte dabei die Hüfte tief und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Halte ein gleichmässiges Tempo und atme während der gesamten Übung gleichmässig.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0630.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0630.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a86f4420-72a1-5bab-ad38-3f410e66f50d', NULL, 'Muscle-up', 'Muscle-up', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended. Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. As you reach the top of the movement, transition your grip so that your palms are facing towards you. Continue pulling yourself up until your chest is above the bar and your arms are fully flexed. Reverse the movement by slowly lowering yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","shoulders","chest"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended.","Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","As you reach the top of the movement, transition your grip so that your palms are facing towards you.","Continue pulling yourself up until your chest is above the bar and your arms are fully flexed.","Reverse the movement by slowly lowering yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge zu Beginn an einer Klimmzugstange, die Handflächen zeigen von dir weg, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, wobei die Brust vorangeht.","Wechsle am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung deinen Griff, sodass die Handflächen zu dir zeigen.","Ziehe dich weiter hoch, bis deine Brust über der Stange ist und die Arme vollständig gebeugt sind.","Kehre die Bewegung um, indem du dich langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition absenkst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0631.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0631.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1d166bd4-6722-5d90-a7b8-c7441464fce3', NULL, 'Muscle-up (on Vertical Bar)', 'Muscle-up (an der senkrechten Stange)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a vertical bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended. Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. As you pull yourself up, lean back slightly and bring your elbows towards your sides. Continue pulling until your chest reaches the bar and your elbows are fully bent. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","forearms"]', '["Start by hanging from a vertical bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended.","Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","As you pull yourself up, lean back slightly and bring your elbows towards your sides.","Continue pulling until your chest reaches the bar and your elbows are fully bent.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge zu Beginn an einer vertikalen Stange, die Handflächen zeigen von dir weg, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, wobei die Brust vorangeht.","Lehne dich beim Hochziehen leicht zurück und führe die Ellbogen zu den Seiten.","Ziehe weiter, bis deine Brust die Stange erreicht und die Ellbogen vollständig gebeugt sind.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1401.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1401.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e83eb36c-299b-595f-8f7f-f3844f2563fc', NULL, 'Narrow Push-up on Exercise Ball', 'Enger Liegestütz auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the ball, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to toe. Lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the ball, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Stabilitätsball auf den Boden und positioniere dich in einer Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas schmaler als schulterbreit auf dem Ball.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte deinen Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Senke deine Brust in Richtung Ball ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und eng am Körper hältst.","Halte kurz inne unten, drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2328.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2328.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('877aee97-3c22-5b9f-ad93-3f1c63450556', NULL, 'Neck Side Stretch', 'Seitliche Nackendehnung', 'neck', 'levator scapulae', 'body weight', 'Stand or sit up straight with your shoulders relaxed. Tilt your head to one side, bringing your ear towards your shoulder. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds. Repeat on the other side. Perform 2-4 sets on each side.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","sternocleidomastoid"]', '["Stand or sit up straight with your shoulders relaxed.","Tilt your head to one side, bringing your ear towards your shoulder.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds.","Repeat on the other side.","Perform 2-4 sets on each side."]', '["Stehe oder sitze aufrecht mit entspannten Schultern.","Neige deinen Kopf zur Seite und führe das Ohr zur Schulter.","Halte die Dehnung für 15-30 Sekunden.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Führe 2-4 Sätze pro Seite aus."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1403.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1403.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a41e009e-e27e-56e6-8bcf-a7c38ffbcfa8', NULL, 'Negative Crunch', 'Negativer Crunch', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, indem du dich nach vorne einrollst, bis dein Oberkörper einen 45°-Winkel bildet.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke dann den Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0634.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0634.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0326e1bd-65d0-5771-8a88-05bceed26b69', NULL, 'Oblique Crunch V. 2', 'Seitlicher Crunch V. 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your abs and lift your shoulder blades off the ground, rotating your torso to one side. Pause for a moment, then lower your shoulder blades back down to the starting position. Repeat on the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your abs and lift your shoulder blades off the ground, rotating your torso to one side.","Pause for a moment, then lower your shoulder blades back down to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe die Schulterblätter vom Boden ab, während du den Oberkörper zu einer Seite drehst.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Schulterblätter dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1495.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1495.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('db7ad674-52d8-5247-a114-20767fdb7abb', NULL, 'Oblique Crunches Floor', 'Seitliche Crunches am Boden', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your abs and lift your shoulder blades off the floor, rotating your torso to one side. Pause for a moment, then lower your shoulder blades back down to the floor. Repeat on the other side, alternating sides with each repetition.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your abs and lift your shoulder blades off the floor, rotating your torso to one side.","Pause for a moment, then lower your shoulder blades back down to the floor.","Repeat on the other side, alternating sides with each repetition."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe die Schulterblätter vom Boden ab, während du den Oberkörper zu einer Seite drehst.","Halte kurz inne, senke die Schulterblätter dann zurück auf den Boden ab.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite und wechsle die Seite mit jeder Wiederholung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0635.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0635.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('aaaee5fc-58b5-5c44-ad82-22f2aae219b4', NULL, 'Olympic Barbell Hammer Curl', 'Hammercurl mit Olympia-Langhantel', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'olympic barbell', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold an Olympic barbell with an overhand grip. Let the barbell hang at arm''s length in front of your thighs, with your palms facing your body. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps. Continue to raise the barbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the barbell is at shoulder level. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps. Inhale and slowly begin to lower the barbell back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold an Olympic barbell with an overhand grip.","Let the barbell hang at arm''s length in front of your thighs, with your palms facing your body.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the weights while contracting your biceps.","Continue to raise the barbell until your biceps are fully contracted and the barbell is at shoulder level.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your biceps.","Inhale and slowly begin to lower the barbell back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen und halte eine Olympia-Langhantel im Obergriff.","Lass die Langhantel in Armlänge vor deinen Oberschenkeln hängen, die Handflächen zeigen zu deinem Körper.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Arme, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Hebe die Langhantel weiter an, bis dein Bizeps vollständig angespannt ist und sich die Langhantel auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und spanne dabei den Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke die Langhantel langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0636.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0636.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eca89b99-5246-54fe-a3f6-f02ee6993da4', NULL, 'Olympic Barbell Triceps Extension', 'Trizepsstrecken mit der Olympia-Langhantel', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'olympic barbell', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and holding the barbell with an overhand grip. Raise the barbell above your head, fully extending your arms. Keeping your upper arms close to your head, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows. Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and holding the barbell with an overhand grip.","Raise the barbell above your head, fully extending your arms.","Keeping your upper arms close to your head, slowly lower the barbell behind your head by bending your elbows.","Pause for a moment, then extend your arms back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich zu Beginn mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte die Langhantel im Obergriff.","Hebe die Langhantel über deinen Kopf und strecke dabei die Arme vollständig.","Halte die Oberarme nah am Kopf und senke die Langhantel langsam hinter deinen Kopf ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Halte kurz inne, strecke dann die Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0637.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0637.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e0d35bbc-17cb-56fe-bed0-751461725089', NULL, 'One Arm Against Wall', 'Ein Arm gegen die Wand (Latissimus-Dehnung)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a wall with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend one arm straight out in front of you and place your palm against the wall. Engage your core and lean your body forward, keeping your arm straight and your back flat. Slowly push against the wall with your palm, activating your lat muscles. Hold the position for a few seconds, then release and repeat with the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Stand facing a wall with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend one arm straight out in front of you and place your palm against the wall.","Engage your core and lean your body forward, keeping your arm straight and your back flat.","Slowly push against the wall with your palm, activating your lat muscles.","Hold the position for a few seconds, then release and repeat with the other arm."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Gesicht zu einer Wand, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Strecke einen Arm gerade nach vorne aus und lege die Handfläche an die Wand.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und lehne deinen Körper nach vorne, halte dabei den Arm gestreckt und den Rücken flach.","Drücke langsam mit der Handfläche gegen die Wand und aktiviere dabei den Latissimus.","Halte die Position für ein paar Sekunden, löse dann und wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1355.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1355.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('97da403d-7b6d-5b7e-90e4-654fbd3de22f', NULL, 'One Arm Chin-up', 'Einarmiger Klimmzug (Untergriff)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a pull-up bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Reach up and grab the bar with an underhand grip, with one hand gripping the bar and the other hand holding your wrist for support. Hang from the bar with your arm fully extended, keeping your body straight and your core engaged. Pull yourself up towards the bar by bending your elbow and squeezing your back muscles. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand facing a pull-up bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Reach up and grab the bar with an underhand grip, with one hand gripping the bar and the other hand holding your wrist for support.","Hang from the bar with your arm fully extended, keeping your body straight and your core engaged.","Pull yourself up towards the bar by bending your elbow and squeezing your back muscles.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms and repeat."]', '["Stelle dich vor eine Klimmzugstange, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Greife nach oben und fasse die Stange im Untergriff, wobei eine Hand die Stange greift und die andere Hand zur Unterstützung dein Handgelenk hält.","Hänge an der Stange mit vollständig gestrecktem Arm, halte den Körper gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe dich zur Stange hoch, indem du den Ellbogen beugst und die Rückenmuskulatur anspannst.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen, wechsle dann den Arm und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0638.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0638.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ab99c455-6c2e-5ef6-a28e-eba142fc0ded', NULL, 'One Arm Dip', 'Einarmiger Dip', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Stand facing away from a bench or chair, with your feet shoulder-width apart. Place one hand on the bench or chair behind you, fingers pointing towards your body. Extend your legs out in front of you, keeping your heels on the ground. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench or chair. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat with the other arm.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Stand facing away from a bench or chair, with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place one hand on the bench or chair behind you, fingers pointing towards your body.","Extend your legs out in front of you, keeping your heels on the ground.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench or chair.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides and repeat with the other arm."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zu einer Bank oder einem Stuhl, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Lege eine Hand auf die Bank oder den Stuhl hinter dir, die Finger zeigen zu deinem Körper.","Strecke die Beine vor dir aus und halte die Fersen auf dem Boden.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper in Richtung Boden ab, halte dabei den Rücken nah an der Bank oder dem Stuhl.","Halte kurz inne unten, drücke dich dann über die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole mit dem anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0639.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0639.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b0282bb1-c112-5998-ac48-0ceabdf0d0f0', NULL, 'One Arm Slam (with Medicine Ball)', 'Einarmiger Medizinball-Slam', 'waist', 'abs', 'medicine ball', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball with one hand in front of your waist. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Raise the medicine ball above your head, fully extending your arm. Forcefully slam the medicine ball down to the ground, using your core and shoulders to generate power. Catch the medicine ball on the bounce and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding the medicine ball with one hand in front of your waist.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Raise the medicine ball above your head, fully extending your arm.","Forcefully slam the medicine ball down to the ground, using your core and shoulders to generate power.","Catch the medicine ball on the bounce and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte den Medizinball mit einer Hand vor der Hüfte.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Hebe den Medizinball über deinen Kopf und strecke dabei den Arm vollständig.","Schlage den Medizinball mit Wucht auf den Boden, indem du Körpermitte und Schultern zur Krafterzeugung nutzt.","Fange den Medizinball nach dem Aufprall und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0640.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0640.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3c9020fe-7c9d-556e-903e-0d6c763c09ee', NULL, 'One Arm Towel Row', 'Einarmiges Rudern mit Handtuch', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a towel with one hand. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Extend your arm fully, allowing the towel to hang in front of you. Pull the towel towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the towel back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, knees slightly bent, and hold a towel with one hand.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Extend your arm fully, allowing the towel to hang in front of you.","Pull the towel towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the towel back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch arms."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen und leicht gebeugten Knien hin und halte ein Handtuch mit einer Hand.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Strecke deinen Arm vollständig und lass das Handtuch vor dir hängen.","Ziehe das Handtuch zu deiner Brust, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne oben, senke das Handtuch dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen, wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1773.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1773.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('cfc76650-8a1c-598a-9994-d250e226bb8b', NULL, 'One Leg Donkey Calf Raise', 'Einbeiniges Donkey-Wadenheben', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward. Place your hands on a stable surface for support, such as a wall or a bar. Lift one leg off the ground, keeping your knee slightly bent. Raise your heel as high as possible, using your calf muscles. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward.","Place your hands on a stable surface for support, such as a wall or a bar.","Lift one leg off the ground, keeping your knee slightly bent.","Raise your heel as high as possible, using your calf muscles.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Stütze dich mit den Händen an einer stabilen Fläche ab, zum Beispiel einer Wand oder einer Stange.","Hebe ein Bein vom Boden ab und halte das Knie leicht gebeugt.","Hebe die Ferse mit der Kraft deiner Wadenmuskulatur so hoch wie möglich an.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke dann die Ferse langsam wieder ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1386.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1386.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7ff00749-7d37-59cd-bd65-758790d07ca7', NULL, 'One Leg Floor Calf Raise', 'Einbeiniges Wadenheben am Boden', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart and place your hands on a wall or sturdy object for balance. Lift one foot off the ground and balance on the other foot. Slowly raise your heel off the ground, lifting your body up onto the ball of your foot. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles","feet"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart and place your hands on a wall or sturdy object for balance.","Lift one foot off the ground and balance on the other foot.","Slowly raise your heel off the ground, lifting your body up onto the ball of your foot.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Stelle dich hüftbreit hin und stütze dich zur Balance mit den Händen an einer Wand oder einem stabilen Gegenstand ab.","Hebe einen Fuss vom Boden ab und balanciere auf dem anderen Fuss.","Hebe die Ferse langsam vom Boden ab und komm auf den Ballen deines Fusses hoch.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke dann die Ferse langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, wechsle dann das Bein und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1387.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1387.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('547f2aae-8024-54ab-a08a-ca5b305386c8', NULL, 'One Leg Squat', 'Einbeinige Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend one leg forward, keeping it off the ground. Bend your standing leg and lower your body down as if sitting back into a chair. Keep your chest up and your back straight. Push through your heel to return to the starting position. Repeat with the other leg.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend one leg forward, keeping it off the ground.","Bend your standing leg and lower your body down as if sitting back into a chair.","Keep your chest up and your back straight.","Push through your heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat with the other leg."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin.","Strecke ein Bein nach vorne aus, ohne den Boden zu berühren.","Beuge dein Standbein und senke deinen Körper ab, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte die Brust hoch und den Rücken gerade.","Drücke dich über die Ferse ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1476.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1476.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c714c445-53b8-5da5-b950-ed983a3fd201', NULL, 'Otis Up', 'Otis Up', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, bis dein Rumpf einen Winkel von 45° bildet.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke dann den Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0641.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0641.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d501e52c-247a-51f0-b3a5-adbdc7482d18', NULL, 'Outside Leg Kick Push-up', 'Liegestütz mit Beinkick nach aussen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and core engaged. As you push back up, kick one leg out to the side, extending it fully and engaging your glutes. Return your leg to the starting position and repeat the push-up, alternating legs with each repetition. Continue alternating leg kicks and push-ups for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","As you push back up, kick one leg out to the side, extending it fully and engaging your glutes.","Return your leg to the starting position and repeat the push-up, alternating legs with each repetition.","Continue alternating leg kicks and push-ups for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Füsse zusammen.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Während du dich wieder nach oben drückst, kicke ein Bein zur Seite und strecke es vollständig, wobei du das Gesäss anspannst.","Bringe das Bein zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole den Liegestütz, wobei du die Beine bei jeder Wiederholung wechselst.","Wechsle Beinkicks und Liegestütze weiter ab, für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0642.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0642.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('248e8557-6860-5ea0-bd4b-f8614ccef2b3', NULL, 'Overhead Triceps Stretch', 'Trizepsdehnung über Kopf', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Stand or sit upright with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend one arm overhead, bending at the elbow so that your hand reaches towards the opposite shoulder blade. With your other hand, gently pull the elbow of the extended arm towards the opposite side of your head, feeling a stretch in your triceps. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand or sit upright with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend one arm overhead, bending at the elbow so that your hand reaches towards the opposite shoulder blade.","With your other hand, gently pull the elbow of the extended arm towards the opposite side of your head, feeling a stretch in your triceps.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Stehe oder sitze aufrecht mit schulterbreit aufgestellten Füssen.","Strecke einen Arm über den Kopf und beuge ihn im Ellbogen, sodass deine Hand in Richtung des gegenüberliegenden Schulterblatts reicht.","Ziehe mit der anderen Hand den Ellbogen des gestreckten Arms sanft zur gegenüberliegenden Kopfseite, bis du eine Dehnung im Trizeps spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden, löse sie dann.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0643.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0643.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e4862486-a4b3-5928-be8b-b0a36c6d450a', NULL, 'Pelvic Tilt', 'Beckenkippung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands by your sides. Engage your abs and tilt your pelvis upward, pressing your lower back into the ground. Hold this position for a few seconds, focusing on contracting your abs. Release the tilt and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'lower back', '["lower back"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands by your sides.","Engage your abs and tilt your pelvis upward, pressing your lower back into the ground.","Hold this position for a few seconds, focusing on contracting your abs.","Release the tilt and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände neben den Körper.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und kippe das Becken nach oben, wobei du den unteren Rücken in den Boden drückst.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden und konzentriere dich darauf, die Bauchmuskeln anzuspannen.","Löse die Kippung und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3147.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3147.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('10da679c-2e13-5c5e-a14c-322226f8b794', NULL, 'Pelvic Tilt into Bridge', 'Beckenkippung in die Brücke', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your arms by your sides with your palms facing down. Engage your glutes and core muscles. Tilt your pelvis upward, lifting your hips off the ground. Hold the bridge position for a few seconds. Slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","core"]', '["Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your arms by your sides with your palms facing down.","Engage your glutes and core muscles.","Tilt your pelvis upward, lifting your hips off the ground.","Hold the bridge position for a few seconds.","Slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Arme neben den Körper, die Handflächen zeigen nach unten.","Spanne Gesäss und Körpermitte an.","Kippe das Becken nach oben und hebe das Becken vom Boden ab.","Halte die Brücken-Position einige Sekunden.","Senke das Becken langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1422.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1422.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9b534a32-caaa-5cfe-bc4a-f3a9b0ceb2e4', NULL, 'Peroneals Stretch', 'Dehnung der Peronealmuskulatur', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'rope', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Loop the rope around the ball of your foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands. Gently pull the rope towards you, flexing your foot and stretching your calf muscles. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds. Release the tension on the rope and repeat the stretch on the other leg. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles","feet"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Loop the rope around the ball of your foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands.","Gently pull the rope towards you, flexing your foot and stretching your calf muscles.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds.","Release the tension on the rope and repeat the stretch on the other leg.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Lege das Seil um den Fussballen und halte die Enden des Seils mit den Händen.","Ziehe das Seil sanft zu dir, winkle den Fuss an und dehne die Wadenmuskulatur.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden.","Löse die Spannung am Seil und wiederhole die Dehnung am anderen Bein.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1388.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1388.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3ca984ee-8b18-5629-b3c8-d14d31771f24', NULL, 'Pike-to-Cobra Push-up', 'Pike-zu-Cobra-Liegestütz', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Engage your core and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, forming an inverted V shape with your body. Lower your upper body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body. As you lower down, shift your weight forward and transition into a cobra pose by straightening your arms and lifting your chest up. Reverse the movement by bending your elbows and lowering your chest back down towards the ground. Push through your hands to return to the inverted V position. Continue the movement by lowering your hips back down towards the ground, returning to the starting push-up position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Engage your core and lift your hips up towards the ceiling, forming an inverted V shape with your body.","Lower your upper body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body.","As you lower down, shift your weight forward and transition into a cobra pose by straightening your arms and lifting your chest up.","Reverse the movement by bending your elbows and lowering your chest back down towards the ground.","Push through your hands to return to the inverted V position.","Continue the movement by lowering your hips back down towards the ground, returning to the starting push-up position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Füsse zusammen.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe das Becken Richtung Decke, sodass dein Körper ein umgekehrtes V bildet.","Senke den Oberkörper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Verlagere beim Absenken das Gewicht nach vorne und gehe in eine Kobra-Position über, indem du die Arme streckst und die Brust anhebst.","Kehre die Bewegung um, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und die Brust wieder Richtung Boden absenkst.","Drücke dich mit den Händen ab, um in die umgekehrte V-Position zurückzukehren.","Setze die Bewegung fort, indem du das Becken zurück Richtung Boden senkst und in die Ausgangs-Liegestützposition zurückkehrst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3662.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3662.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2ee5ca74-2ef4-5e58-82b9-a9613ece5df0', NULL, 'Plyo Push-up', 'Plyo-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Push explosively off the ground, using your chest muscles to propel your upper body off the ground. Land softly with your hands back in the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Push explosively off the ground, using your chest muscles to propel your upper body off the ground.","Land softly with your hands back in the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der hohen Plank-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt.","Senke die Brust Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei in einer geraden Linie.","Drücke dich explosiv vom Boden ab und nutze die Brustmuskulatur, um deinen Oberkörper vom Boden abzuheben.","Lande weich mit den Händen zurück in der Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1306.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1306.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('56ae779f-4467-5d1e-9731-8aefb55e4da2', NULL, 'Posterior Step to Overhead Reach', 'Rückwärtsschritt mit Überkopf-Reichen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart and your arms by your sides. Take a step back with your right foot, landing on the ball of your foot. Bend your left knee and lower your body into a lunge position. As you lower into the lunge, simultaneously reach your arms overhead. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the lunge, then return to the starting position by pushing through your left heel and bringing your right foot forward. Repeat the movement on the other side, stepping back with your left foot and bending your right knee. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","quadriceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart and your arms by your sides.","Take a step back with your right foot, landing on the ball of your foot.","Bend your left knee and lower your body into a lunge position.","As you lower into the lunge, simultaneously reach your arms overhead.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the lunge, then return to the starting position by pushing through your left heel and bringing your right foot forward.","Repeat the movement on the other side, stepping back with your left foot and bending your right knee.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich hüftbreit hin, die Arme neben dem Körper.","Mache einen Schritt zurück mit dem rechten Fuss und lande auf dem Fussballen.","Beuge das linke Knie und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Strecke beim Absenken in den Ausfallschritt gleichzeitig die Arme über den Kopf.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt des Ausfallschritts, kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du dich über die linke Ferse abdrückst und den rechten Fuss nach vorne bringst.","Wiederhole die Bewegung auf der anderen Seite, indem du mit dem linken Fuss zurücktrittst und das rechte Knie beugst.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter ab, für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1687.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1687.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('d16a19fe-6d52-5577-93fa-d87cb5ab8b17', NULL, 'Posterior Tibialis Stretch', 'Dehnung des hinteren Schienbeinmuskels', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'rope', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Loop the rope around the ball of your foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands. Gently pull the rope towards you, flexing your foot and stretching your calf muscles. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Release the tension on the rope and relax your foot. Repeat the stretch on the other leg.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Loop the rope around the ball of your foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands.","Gently pull the rope towards you, flexing your foot and stretching your calf muscles.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Release the tension on the rope and relax your foot.","Repeat the stretch on the other leg."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Lege das Seil um den Fussballen und halte die Enden des Seils mit den Händen.","Ziehe das Seil sanft zu dir, winkle den Fuss an und dehne die Wadenmuskulatur.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden.","Löse die Spannung am Seil und entspanne den Fuss.","Wiederhole die Dehnung am anderen Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1389.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1389.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4322a0ec-0cb2-5518-9bb9-79cf04fc45c2', NULL, 'Potty Squat', 'Potty Squat', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward. Lower your body down by bending your knees and pushing your hips back as if you were sitting on a chair. Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement. Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward.","Lower your body down by bending your knees and pushing your hips back as if you were sitting on a chair.","Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement.","Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen leicht nach aussen.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Knie beugst und das Becken nach hinten schiebst, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte während der gesamten Bewegung die Brust hoch und den Rücken gerade.","Senke dich ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder so tief, wie es für dich angenehm möglich ist.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3119.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3119.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d546af17-655e-5b62-a6ad-a3cd4272ea07', NULL, 'Potty Squat with Support', 'Potty Squat mit Unterstützung', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward. Hold onto a stable support, such as a chair or wall, for balance. Lower your body down into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold onto a stable support, such as a chair or wall, for balance.","Lower your body down into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen leicht nach aussen.","Halte dich zur Balance an einer stabilen Stütze fest, zum Beispiel einem Stuhl oder einer Wand.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab, indem du die Knie beugst und das Becken nach hinten schiebst.","Halte während der gesamten Bewegung die Brust hoch und den Rücken gerade.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3132.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3132.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9c36971d-b514-59f6-be1f-eb3af9369ff9', NULL, 'Power Clean', 'Power Clean', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'barbell', 'Start with the barbell on the ground in front of you, with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend down and grip the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and chest up as you lift the barbell off the ground, extending your hips and knees. As the barbell reaches your mid-thigh, explosively pull it upwards, shrugging your shoulders and pulling your elbows high and to the sides. As the barbell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it, rotating your elbows around and catching the barbell on your shoulders in a front squat position. Stand up with the barbell, fully extending your hips and knees. Lower the barbell back down to the starting position, keeping control of the weight throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Start with the barbell on the ground in front of you, with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend down and grip the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and chest up as you lift the barbell off the ground, extending your hips and knees.","As the barbell reaches your mid-thigh, explosively pull it upwards, shrugging your shoulders and pulling your elbows high and to the sides.","As the barbell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it, rotating your elbows around and catching the barbell on your shoulders in a front squat position.","Stand up with the barbell, fully extending your hips and knees.","Lower the barbell back down to the starting position, keeping control of the weight throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne mit der Langhantel auf dem Boden vor dir, die Füsse schulterbreit aufgestellt.","Beuge dich hinunter und greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Brust hoch, während du die Langhantel vom Boden hebst und dabei Hüfte und Knie streckst.","Sobald die Langhantel deine Oberschenkelmitte erreicht, ziehe sie explosiv nach oben, ziehe die Schultern hoch und die Ellbogen hoch zur Seite.","Sobald die Langhantel ihren höchsten Punkt erreicht, tauche schnell darunter, drehe die Ellbogen herum und fange die Langhantel auf den Schultern in einer Frontkniebeuge-Position auf.","Richte dich mit der Langhantel auf, strecke dabei Hüfte und Knie vollständig.","Senke die Langhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab und behalte während der gesamten Bewegung die Kontrolle über das Gewicht.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0648.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0648.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3f038667-a556-5a3d-a2b2-a64ab678046d', NULL, 'Power Point Plank', 'Power Point Plank', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line from head to toe. Engage your core and squeeze your glutes to maintain a stable position. Lower your body down onto your forearms, one arm at a time, maintaining a straight line from head to toe. Hold this position for the desired amount of time, keeping your core and glutes engaged. To return to the starting position, push through your forearms and lift your body back up into a high plank position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","glutes"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Engage your core and squeeze your glutes to maintain a stable position.","Lower your body down onto your forearms, one arm at a time, maintaining a straight line from head to toe.","Hold this position for the desired amount of time, keeping your core and glutes engaged.","To return to the starting position, push through your forearms and lift your body back up into a high plank position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der hohen Plank-Position, die Hände direkt unter den Schultern und der Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und presse das Gesäss zusammen, um eine stabile Position zu halten.","Senke deinen Körper nacheinander mit je einem Arm auf die Unterarme ab, wobei du eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss beibehältst.","Halte diese Position für die gewünschte Dauer und halte dabei Körpermitte und Gesäss angespannt.","Um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren, drücke dich über die Unterarme ab und hebe deinen Körper zurück in die hohe Plank-Position.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3665.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3665.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d002a6c1-0290-55bc-ab22-93a1aa5ed825', NULL, 'Prisoner Half Sit-up (Male)', 'Halber Sit-up mit Händen im Nacken (Mann)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, bis dein Rumpf einen Winkel von 45° bildet.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke dann den Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3203.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3203.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b234e799-2c8d-5e84-8aa6-16c4c975bfcd', NULL, 'Prone Twist on Stability Ball', 'Rumpfdrehung in Bauchlage auf dem Gymnastikball', 'waist', 'abs', 'stability ball', 'Start by lying face down on a stability ball with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes touching the ground. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your core muscles and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, keeping your back straight. Rotate your torso to one side, bringing your shoulder towards your hip. Keep your hips and legs stable throughout the movement. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat the rotation to the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Start by lying face down on a stability ball with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes touching the ground.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your core muscles and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, keeping your back straight.","Rotate your torso to one side, bringing your shoulder towards your hip. Keep your hips and legs stable throughout the movement.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the rotation to the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich bäuchlings auf einen Gymnastikball, die Füsse schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Zehen berühren den Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Drehe den Oberkörper zu einer Seite und bringe die Schulter Richtung Hüfte. Halte Hüfte und Beine während der gesamten Bewegung stabil.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Drehung zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter ab, für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1707.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1707.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bafa2055-819d-55f6-a441-a3676194dedf', NULL, 'Pull-up (Neutral Grip)', 'Klimmzug (neutraler Griff)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with a neutral grip (palms facing each other) and your arms fully extended. Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together. Pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbows and driving your elbows down towards your hips. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position with control. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with a neutral grip (palms facing each other) and your arms fully extended.","Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbows and driving your elbows down towards your hips.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position with control.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich mit neutralem Griff (Handflächen zeigen zueinander) an eine Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und sie Richtung Hüfte nach unten führst.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke deinen Körper dann kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0651.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0651.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bfd68f78-cbda-5b84-b646-b4095dc254c5', NULL, 'Pull-in (on Stability Ball)', 'Beine einziehen auf dem Gymnastikball', 'waist', 'abs', 'stability ball', 'Start by sitting on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Place your hands on the sides of the stability ball for support. Engage your abs and slowly roll your hips forward, bringing your knees towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Start by sitting on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Place your hands on the sides of the stability ball for support.","Engage your abs and slowly roll your hips forward, bringing your knees towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Gymnastikball, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und die Knie in einem 90°-Winkel gebeugt.","Stütze dich mit den Händen an den Seiten des Gymnastikballs ab.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und rolle das Becken langsam nach vorne, wobei du die Knie Richtung Brust bringst.","Halte kurz inne am höchsten Punkt der Bewegung, strecke dann die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0650.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0650.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d0a3f27c-2143-51bd-9af2-90bac135a6da', NULL, 'Pull-up', 'Klimmzug', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended. Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together. Pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbows and bringing your chest towards the bar. Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended.","Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbows and bringing your chest towards the bar.","Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an eine Klimmzugstange, die Handflächen zeigen von dir weg, die Arme vollständig gestreckt.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und die Brust Richtung Stange bringst.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke deinen Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0652.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0652.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3d13177e-c98b-5bcc-ba3e-c39bd6a73ee5', NULL, 'Push and Pull Bodyweight', 'Drücken und Ziehen', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line. Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. From the push-up position, pull your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","deltoids"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line.","Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","From the push-up position, pull your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Senke die Brust Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei gerade.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, strecke die Arme und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Ziehe aus der Liegestütz-Position die Brust Richtung Boden, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei gerade.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, strecke die Arme und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1689.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1689.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d98a14d3-2118-5fba-a693-d10b5fea39f7', NULL, 'Push to Run', 'Schieben in den Lauf', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line. Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight. Push through your hands to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Quickly bring one knee towards your chest, then quickly switch and bring the other knee towards your chest. Continue alternating knees as fast as you can while maintaining good form. Continue for the desired duration or number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line.","Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body straight.","Push through your hands to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Quickly bring one knee towards your chest, then quickly switch and bring the other knee towards your chest.","Continue alternating knees as fast as you can while maintaining good form.","Continue for the desired duration or number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände schulterbreit aufgestellt und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Senke die Brust Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei gerade.","Drücke dich über die Hände ab, strecke die Arme und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Bringe schnell ein Knie Richtung Brust, wechsle dann schnell und bringe das andere Knie Richtung Brust.","Wechsle die Knie so schnell wie möglich weiter ab, während du eine gute Ausführung beibehältst.","Führe die Übung für die gewünschte Dauer oder Anzahl Wiederholungen fort."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3638.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3638.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2d3ee370-390a-52ff-9ac9-fa8a9c411072', NULL, 'Push-up on Bosu Ball', 'Liegestütz auf dem Bosu-Ball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'bosu ball', 'Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side facing up. Position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the outer edges of the bosu ball. Engage your core and lower your body down towards the bosu ball by bending your elbows. Push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side facing up.","Position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the outer edges of the bosu ball.","Engage your core and lower your body down towards the bosu ball by bending your elbows.","Push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Bosu-Ball mit der flachen Seite nach oben auf den Boden.","Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände an den äusseren Rändern des Bosu-Balls.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, Richtung Bosu-Ball.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1307.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1307.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('96799a98-68cf-5e0e-aeeb-a132f15b1618', NULL, 'Push-up', 'Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Pause for a moment when your chest is just above the ground, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","deltoids","core"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Pause for a moment when your chest is just above the ground, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der hohen Plank-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Füsse zusammen.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei in einer geraden Linie.","Halte kurz inne, wenn deine Brust knapp über dem Boden ist, und drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0662.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0662.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6ab00dce-cdfa-5427-9f06-7e41dd49df17', NULL, 'Push-up (Bosu Ball)', 'Liegestütz (Bosu-Ball)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'bosu ball', 'Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side facing up. Position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the outer edges of the bosu ball. Engage your core and lower your body down towards the bosu ball by bending your elbows. Push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side facing up.","Position yourself in a push-up position with your hands on the outer edges of the bosu ball.","Engage your core and lower your body down towards the bosu ball by bending your elbows.","Push yourself back up to the starting position by extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Bosu-Ball mit der flachen Seite nach oben auf den Boden.","Gehe in die Liegestütz-Position, die Hände an den äusseren Rändern des Bosu-Balls.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, Richtung Bosu-Ball.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0653.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0653.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0ddb5593-94ff-59d6-be00-51f73574be8f', NULL, 'Push-up (on Stability Ball)', 'Liegestütz auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself facing down with your hands on the ball, shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs straight out behind you, balancing on your toes. Engage your core and lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself facing down with your hands on the ball, shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs straight out behind you, balancing on your toes.","Engage your core and lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und positioniere dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten, die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Ball.","Strecke die Beine gerade hinter dir aus und balanciere auf den Zehenspitzen.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke die Brust Richtung Ball ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei in einer geraden Linie.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0655.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0655.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bb871cdc-b702-5dbe-9082-aafd65665b24', NULL, 'Push-up (on Stability Ball)', 'Liegestütz auf dem Gymnastikball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'stability ball', 'Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself facing down with your hands on the ball, shoulder-width apart. Extend your legs straight out behind you, balancing on your toes. Engage your core and lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Place the stability ball on the ground and position yourself facing down with your hands on the ball, shoulder-width apart.","Extend your legs straight out behind you, balancing on your toes.","Engage your core and lower your chest towards the ball by bending your elbows, keeping your body in a straight line.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Gymnastikball auf den Boden und positioniere dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten, die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Ball.","Strecke die Beine gerade hinter dir aus und balanciere auf den Zehenspitzen.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke die Brust Richtung Ball ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Körper dabei in einer geraden Linie.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0656.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0656.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e15cf1a1-ff90-5128-83e2-439365f2470d', NULL, 'Push-up (Wall)', 'Liegestütz (an der Wand)', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a wall, about arm''s length away. Place your hands on the wall at shoulder height, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Step back a few feet, keeping your body straight and your feet hip-width apart. Bend your elbows and lower your chest towards the wall, keeping your body in a straight line. Push back up to the starting position, straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","deltoids"]', '["Stand facing a wall, about arm''s length away.","Place your hands on the wall at shoulder height, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Step back a few feet, keeping your body straight and your feet hip-width apart.","Bend your elbows and lower your chest towards the wall, keeping your body in a straight line.","Push back up to the starting position, straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich vor eine Wand, etwa eine Armlänge entfernt.","Lege die Hände in Schulterhöhe an die Wand, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Trete einige Schritte zurück, halte dabei den Körper gerade und die Füsse hüftbreit.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke die Brust Richtung Wand ab, während du den Körper in einer geraden Linie hältst.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0659.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0659.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fae761b2-d5ad-5670-8450-6878d340a15c', NULL, 'Push-up (Wall) V. 2', 'Liegestütz (an der Wand) V. 2', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a wall, about arm''s length away. Place your hands on the wall at shoulder height, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Step back with your feet, keeping them hip-width apart. Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to heels. Bend your elbows and lower your chest towards the wall, keeping your body straight. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand facing a wall, about arm''s length away.","Place your hands on the wall at shoulder height, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Step back with your feet, keeping them hip-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to heels.","Bend your elbows and lower your chest towards the wall, keeping your body straight.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich vor eine Wand, etwa eine Armlänge entfernt.","Lege die Hände in Schulterhöhe an die Wand, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Trete mit den Füssen zurück und halte sie dabei hüftbreit.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke die Brust Richtung Wand ab, während du den Körper gerade hältst.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0658.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0658.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('159d1a71-b014-5e6c-93a7-69f321769a4b', NULL, 'Push-up Close-Grip off Dumbbell', 'Enger Liegestütz auf der Kurzhantel', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'dumbbell', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands placed close together, directly under your shoulders. Hold a dumbbell in each hand, resting them on the ground. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands placed close together, directly under your shoulders.","Hold a dumbbell in each hand, resting them on the ground.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände eng zusammen direkt unter den Schultern.","Halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, die auf dem Boden aufliegt.","Senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, strecke die Arme und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0660.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0660.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('880caa14-c6f5-5f68-b491-9ac66341edb3', NULL, 'Push-up Inside Leg Kick', 'Liegestütz mit Beinkick nach innen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. As you push back up, lift one leg off the ground and kick it out to the side, keeping it straight. Lower your leg back down and repeat the push-up, then switch to the other leg. Continue alternating leg kicks with each push-up repetition.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","As you push back up, lift one leg off the ground and kick it out to the side, keeping it straight.","Lower your leg back down and repeat the push-up, then switch to the other leg.","Continue alternating leg kicks with each push-up repetition."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Füsse zusammen.","Senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Während du dich wieder nach oben drückst, hebe ein Bein vom Boden ab und kicke es gestreckt zur Seite.","Senke das Bein wieder ab und wiederhole den Liegestütz, wechsle dann zum anderen Bein.","Wechsle die Beinkicks bei jeder Liegestütz-Wiederholung weiter ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0661.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0661.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a320934a-f6f7-5346-800d-f815b275c2bb', NULL, 'Push-up Medicine Ball', 'Liegestütz auf dem Medizinball', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'medicine ball', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands on the medicine ball, shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands on the medicine ball, shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der hohen Plank-Position, die Hände schulterbreit auf dem Medizinball.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte den Rücken gerade.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, strecke die Arme und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0663.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0663.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('efab83bc-7a05-534d-9e34-d350ef5f0473', NULL, 'Push-up on Lower Arms', 'Liegestütz auf den Unterarmen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Start in a plank position with your forearms on the ground and elbows directly below your shoulders. Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to toe. Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Start in a plank position with your forearms on the ground and elbows directly below your shoulders.","Engage your core and keep your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Plank-Position, die Unterarme auf dem Boden und die Ellbogen direkt unter den Schultern.","Spanne die Körpermitte an und halte den Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Senke die Brust Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Halte kurz inne am tiefsten Punkt, drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1467.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1467.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('071de606-1f67-5c77-b117-911196bc3d36', NULL, 'Push-up Plus', 'Push-up Plus', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line from head to heels. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Once your chest is just above the ground, push through your hands to extend your arms and lift your upper body up. At the top of the movement, protract your shoulder blades by pushing your upper back towards the ceiling. Pause for a moment, then reverse the movement by retracting your shoulder blades and lowering your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line from head to heels.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Once your chest is just above the ground, push through your hands to extend your arms and lift your upper body up.","At the top of the movement, protract your shoulder blades by pushing your upper back towards the ceiling.","Pause for a moment, then reverse the movement by retracting your shoulder blades and lowering your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der hohen Plank-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und der Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Ferse.","Senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Sobald deine Brust knapp über dem Boden ist, drücke dich über die Hände ab, strecke die Arme und hebe den Oberkörper an.","Schiebe an der höchsten Position der Bewegung die Schulterblätter auseinander, indem du den oberen Rücken Richtung Decke drückst.","Halte kurz inne, kehre dann die Bewegung um, indem du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst und deinen Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition absenkst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3145.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3145.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('29e36e58-d56d-591c-9eed-cae1290e6d4c', NULL, 'Push-up to Side Plank', 'Liegestütz in den Seitstütz', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your core engaged. Push back up to the starting position. Shift your weight onto your left hand and rotate your body to the right, lifting your right arm towards the ceiling. Hold the side plank position for a few seconds, then return to the starting position. Repeat the push-up and side plank on the opposite side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","triceps"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your core engaged.","Push back up to the starting position.","Shift your weight onto your left hand and rotate your body to the right, lifting your right arm towards the ceiling.","Hold the side plank position for a few seconds, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the push-up and side plank on the opposite side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände schulterbreit aufgestellt und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte die Körpermitte angespannt.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Verlagere dein Gewicht auf die linke Hand und drehe deinen Körper nach rechts, wobei du den rechten Arm Richtung Decke hebst.","Halte die Side-Plank-Position einige Sekunden und kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole den Liegestütz und die Side Plank auf der gegenüberliegenden Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter ab, für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0664.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0664.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c1af5f4d-ab81-5395-8f05-6ff765be92ce', NULL, 'Quads', 'Quadrizeps', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Lower your body by bending your knees and pushing your hips back as if sitting on a chair. Keep your chest up and your back straight. Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground. Push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body by bending your knees and pushing your hips back as if sitting on a chair.","Keep your chest up and your back straight.","Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground.","Push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Knie beugst und das Becken nach hinten schiebst, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte die Brust hoch und den Rücken gerade.","Senke dich ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3533.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3533.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a1dca0c8-c09a-5be0-9acb-abdbfed3d409', NULL, 'Quarter Sit-up', 'Viertel-Sit-up', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, bis dein Rumpf einen Winkel von 45° bildet.","Halte kurz inne an der höchsten Position, senke dann den Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3201.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3201.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1336311c-970b-5cec-a450-c26eca4ff1d6', NULL, 'Quick Feet V. 2', 'Quick Feet V. 2', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms by your sides. Begin by rapidly moving your feet up and down, as if you were running in place. Keep your movements quick and light, focusing on staying on the balls of your feet. Continue for the desired duration or number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","hamstrings"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms by your sides.","Begin by rapidly moving your feet up and down, as if you were running in place.","Keep your movements quick and light, focusing on staying on the balls of your feet.","Continue for the desired duration or number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich schulterbreit hin, die Arme neben dem Körper.","Beginne damit, deine Füsse schnell auf und ab zu bewegen, als würdest du auf der Stelle laufen.","Halte die Bewegungen schnell und leicht und konzentriere dich darauf, auf den Fussballen zu bleiben.","Führe die Übung für die gewünschte Dauer oder Anzahl Wiederholungen fort."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3552.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3552.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('04e5eb39-5829-5e25-8b71-cdf8c3c71c70', NULL, 'Raise Single Arm Push-up', 'Liegestütz mit angehobenem Arm', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Extend one arm straight out to the side, parallel to the ground. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and core engaged. Push back up to the starting position, using your chest muscles to lift your body. Repeat with the other arm extended.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Extend one arm straight out to the side, parallel to the ground.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","Push back up to the starting position, using your chest muscles to lift your body.","Repeat with the other arm extended."]', '["Beginne in der Liegestütz-Position, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgestellt und die Füsse zusammen.","Strecke einen Arm gerade zur Seite aus, parallel zum Boden.","Senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Drücke dich mit der Kraft deiner Brustmuskulatur zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen ausgestreckten Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0666.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0666.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('41fc23d8-9bb3-58df-93fe-a6d2d2dd89ad', NULL, 'Rear Decline Bridge', 'Rückwärts-Brücke (Negativposition)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent. Place your arms by your sides with your palms facing down. Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Lie on your back with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent.","Place your arms by your sides with your palms facing down.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings, and lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und die Knie gebeugt.","Lege die Arme neben den Körper, die Handflächen zeigen nach unten.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und hebe das Becken vom Boden ab, bis dein Körper eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern bildet.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden, senke dann das Becken langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0668.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0668.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('02316e6a-fe2b-5ddc-9b16-9c5f8fbc9cf3', NULL, 'Rear Deltoid Stretch', 'Hintere-Schulter-Dehnung', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'body weight', 'Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend your right arm across your chest, placing your left hand on your right elbow. Gently pull your right arm towards your left shoulder, feeling a stretch in your right shoulder. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids"]', '["Stand tall with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend your right arm across your chest, placing your left hand on your right elbow.","Gently pull your right arm towards your left shoulder, feeling a stretch in your right shoulder.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Steh aufrecht mit schulterbreit aufgestellten Füssen.","Strecke deinen rechten Arm quer vor deiner Brust aus und lege deine linke Hand auf deinen rechten Ellbogen.","Ziehe deinen rechten Arm sanft in Richtung deiner linken Schulter, bis du eine Dehnung in der rechten Schulter spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden, dann löse sie.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0669.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0669.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e679c05d-43ee-56bb-9be1-5b10f45de50d', NULL, 'Rear Pull-up', 'Klimmzug zum Nacken', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, während du die Ellbogen nah am Körper hältst.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte kurz inne, dann senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0670.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0670.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bcbc1fdb-63af-5757-95c4-f5a87c6d1cd3', NULL, 'Reclining Big Toe Pose with Rope', 'Liegende Grosszehenhaltung mit Seil', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'rope', 'Lie on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Loop the rope around the ball of your right foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands. Slowly raise your right leg towards your chest, keeping your knee straight and your foot flexed. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position. Repeat with your left leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","glutes"]', '["Lie on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Loop the rope around the ball of your right foot and hold the ends of the rope with your hands.","Slowly raise your right leg towards your chest, keeping your knee straight and your foot flexed.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position.","Repeat with your left leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Lege das Seil um den Ballen deines rechten Fusses und halte die Enden des Seils mit den Händen.","Hebe dein rechtes Bein langsam in Richtung Brust an, das Knie bleibt gestreckt und der Fuss angezogen.","Halte die Dehnung ein paar Sekunden, dann senke dein Bein langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole mit dem linken Bein.","Wechsle die Beine für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1582.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1582.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('25c186df-19d8-5a63-9080-27fbec1f2265', NULL, 'Resistance Band Hip Thrusts on Knees (Female)', 'Hip Thrust auf den Knien mit Band (Frau)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'resistance band', 'Start by kneeling on the ground with your knees hip-width apart and your feet flexed. Wrap the resistance band around your thighs, just above your knees. Place your hands on your hips or extend them out in front of you for balance. Engage your glutes and core muscles. Push your hips forward and squeeze your glutes as you lift your knees off the ground, extending your hips until your thighs are parallel to the ground. Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your knees back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Start by kneeling on the ground with your knees hip-width apart and your feet flexed.","Wrap the resistance band around your thighs, just above your knees.","Place your hands on your hips or extend them out in front of you for balance.","Engage your glutes and core muscles.","Push your hips forward and squeeze your glutes as you lift your knees off the ground, extending your hips until your thighs are parallel to the ground.","Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your knees back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne im Kniestand, die Knie hüftbreit auseinander und die Füsse angezogen.","Lege das Widerstandsband um deine Oberschenkel, direkt über den Knien.","Lege die Hände auf die Hüften oder strecke sie zur Balance nach vorne aus.","Spanne dein Gesäss und deine Körpermitte an.","Schiebe die Hüfte nach vorne und presse das Gesäss zusammen, während du die Knie vom Boden abhebst und die Hüfte streckst, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte die Position kurz, dann senke die Knie langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3236.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3236.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('336f3e10-2e34-5144-be77-fcc98ca02824', NULL, 'Resistance Band Leg Extension', 'Beinstrecken mit Band', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'resistance band', 'Attach the resistance band to a sturdy anchor point and secure it around your ankle. Stand facing the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart. Keeping your core engaged and your upper body stable, extend your leg straight out in front of you. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly return your leg to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Attach the resistance band to a sturdy anchor point and secure it around your ankle.","Stand facing the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Keeping your core engaged and your upper body stable, extend your leg straight out in front of you.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly return your leg to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Befestige das Widerstandsband an einem stabilen Ankerpunkt und fixiere es um deinen Knöchel.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen dem Ankerpunkt zugewandt hin.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an, halte den Oberkörper stabil und strecke dein Bein gerade nach vorne aus.","Halte kurz inne, dann führe dein Bein langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, dann wechsle das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3007.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3007.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4acd2279-a0e5-5ce1-a4b0-29626b639f27', NULL, 'Resistance Band Seated Biceps Curl', 'Bizepscurl im Sitzen mit Band', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'resistance band', 'Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold the resistance band with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and arms extended down by your sides. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the resistance band up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the resistance band back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the resistance band with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and arms extended down by your sides.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the resistance band up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the resistance band back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Stuhl oder eine Bank, der Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte das Widerstandsband im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben, die Arme gestreckt neben dem Körper.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und ziehe das Widerstandsband in Richtung deiner Schultern hoch.","Halte kurz inne oben und spanne deinen Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke das Widerstandsband langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3123.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3123.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('07be53e4-6ea1-54b2-afd6-cda2c50e31e1', NULL, 'Resistance Band Seated Chest Press', 'Brustdrücken im Sitzen mit Band', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'resistance band', 'Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold the resistance band handles in each hand, with your palms facing down and elbows bent at a 90-degree angle. Extend your arms forward, pushing the resistance band away from your chest. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the resistance band handles in each hand, with your palms facing down and elbows bent at a 90-degree angle.","Extend your arms forward, pushing the resistance band away from your chest.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Stuhl oder eine Bank, der Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte die Griffe des Widerstandsbands in beiden Händen, Handflächen nach unten, die Ellbogen in einem 90°-Winkel gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme nach vorne und drücke das Widerstandsband von deiner Brust weg.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, dann kehre langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3124.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3124.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7b81fefc-cb4d-5117-8dc7-8d427065a036', NULL, 'Resistance Band Seated Hip Abduction', 'Hüftabduktion im Sitzen mit Band', 'upper legs', 'abductors', 'resistance band', 'Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Wrap the resistance band around your thighs, just above your knees. Place your hands on the sides of the chair or bench for support. Engage your abductors (outer thigh muscles) and slowly push your knees apart, against the resistance of the band. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring your knees back together. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Wrap the resistance band around your thighs, just above your knees.","Place your hands on the sides of the chair or bench for support.","Engage your abductors (outer thigh muscles) and slowly push your knees apart, against the resistance of the band.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring your knees back together.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Stuhl oder eine Bank, der Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege das Widerstandsband um deine Oberschenkel, direkt über den Knien.","Stütze dich mit den Händen seitlich am Stuhl oder an der Bank ab.","Spanne deine Abduktoren (äussere Oberschenkelmuskulatur) an und drücke die Knie langsam gegen den Widerstand des Bands auseinander.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, dann bringe die Knie langsam wieder zusammen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3006.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3006.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8ae98e22-301b-5f1e-be09-805ff7f4df24', NULL, 'Resistance Band Seated Shoulder Press', 'Schulterdrücken im Sitzen mit Band', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'resistance band', 'Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground. Hold the resistance band with both hands, palms facing forward, and bring it up to shoulder level. Press the band overhead, extending your arms fully. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the band back down to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Sit on a chair or bench with your back straight and feet flat on the ground.","Hold the resistance band with both hands, palms facing forward, and bring it up to shoulder level.","Press the band overhead, extending your arms fully.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the band back down to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf einen Stuhl oder eine Bank, der Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte das Widerstandsband mit beiden Händen, Handflächen nach vorne, und bringe es auf Schulterhöhe.","Drücke das Band über den Kopf, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke das Band langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3122.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3122.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('18dd58c6-b9bc-58f9-a124-110d208edf7c', NULL, 'Resistance Band Seated Straight Back Row', 'Rudern im Sitzen mit geradem Rücken (Band)', 'back', 'upper back', 'resistance band', 'Sit on the floor with your legs extended and loop the resistance band around your feet. Hold the ends of the resistance band with your hands, palms facing each other. Keep your back straight and lean slightly back, engaging your core. Pull the resistance band towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly release the tension and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the floor with your legs extended and loop the resistance band around your feet.","Hold the ends of the resistance band with your hands, palms facing each other.","Keep your back straight and lean slightly back, engaging your core.","Pull the resistance band towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly release the tension and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine gestreckt, und lege das Widerstandsband um deine Füsse.","Halte die Enden des Widerstandsbands mit den Händen, die Handflächen zeigen zueinander.","Halte den Rücken gerade, lehne dich leicht zurück und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Ziehe das Widerstandsband in Richtung deiner Brust und drücke dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte oben kurz inne, löse dann die Spannung langsam und kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3144.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3144.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('aeb63be8-1b86-5fd0-a314-74a887987681', NULL, 'Reverse Crunch', 'Reverse Crunch', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your arms extended along your sides. Bend your knees and lift your feet off the ground, bringing your thighs perpendicular to the floor. Contract your abs and curl your hips off the floor, bringing your knees towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your arms extended along your sides.","Bend your knees and lift your feet off the ground, bringing your thighs perpendicular to the floor.","Contract your abs and curl your hips off the floor, bringing your knees towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Arme liegen gestreckt neben dem Körper.","Beuge die Knie und hebe die Füsse vom Boden ab, bis die Oberschenkel senkrecht zum Boden stehen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe das Becken vom Boden ab, indem du die Knie zur Brust ziehst.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke das Becken langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0872.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0872.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('713b977d-5599-59da-9895-aed7afe77024', NULL, 'Reverse Dip', 'Reverse Dip', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself between two parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich zwischen zwei parallelen Barren mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0672.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0672.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('de9214ff-b7d3-5182-98f0-5f320c8584b7', NULL, 'Reverse Grip Machine Lat Pulldown', 'Latzug an der Maschine im Untergriff', 'back', 'lats', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Sit upright with your chest out and shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back. Pull the handles down towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your knees under the pads and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the handles with an underhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Sit upright with your chest out and shoulders back, maintaining a slight arch in your lower back.","Pull the handles down towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setz dich an die Maschine, die Knie unter den Polstern und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Fasse die Griffe im Untergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Sitze aufrecht mit herausgestreckter Brust und zurückgezogenen Schultern, halte ein leichtes Hohlkreuz.","Ziehe die Griffe zu deiner Brust hinunter und drücke dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte am unteren Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, dann führe die Griffe langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0673.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0673.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('46c4ff76-3552-5655-a19a-dfaefd3ce562', NULL, 'Reverse Grip Pull-up', 'Klimmzug im Untergriff', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Untergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, die Brust voran.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte kurz inne, dann senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0674.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0674.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e1f16815-16d1-56ed-8a41-6d7d5139b054', NULL, 'Reverse Hyperextension (on Stability Ball)', 'Reverse Hyperextension auf dem Gymnastikball', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'stability ball', 'Lie face down on a stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your legs extended straight behind you. Place your hands on the ground in front of you for stability. Engaging your glutes and hamstrings, lift your legs up towards the ceiling as high as you can. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Lie face down on a stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your legs extended straight behind you.","Place your hands on the ground in front of you for stability.","Engaging your glutes and hamstrings, lift your legs up towards the ceiling as high as you can.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Bauch auf einen Gymnastikball, sodass deine Hüfte auf dem Ball ruht und die Beine gestreckt nach hinten zeigen.","Stütze dich zur Stabilität mit den Händen vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an und hebe die Beine so hoch wie möglich in Richtung Decke.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0675.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0675.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c93a4a99-83e8-53c1-9b68-7e64436cd077', NULL, 'Reverse Hyper on Flat Bench', 'Reverse Hyper auf der Flachbank', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on a flat bench with your hips at the edge and your legs hanging off the bench. Hold onto the bench for stability. Keeping your legs straight, raise them up towards the ceiling as high as you can. Squeeze your glutes at the top of the movement. Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Lie face down on a flat bench with your hips at the edge and your legs hanging off the bench.","Hold onto the bench for stability.","Keeping your legs straight, raise them up towards the ceiling as high as you can.","Squeeze your glutes at the top of the movement.","Slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Bauch auf eine Flachbank, sodass deine Hüfte an der Kante liegt und deine Beine über den Rand hinausragen.","Halte dich zur Stabilität an der Bank fest.","Hebe die gestreckten Beine so hoch wie möglich in Richtung Decke.","Presse am oberen Ende der Bewegung dein Gesäss zusammen.","Senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1423.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1423.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b32f830f-6887-534a-9b14-e4d806d31fc8', NULL, 'Reverse Plank with Leg Lift', 'Reverse Plank mit Beinheben', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you and your hands resting on the ground behind you, fingers pointing towards your feet. Press through your hands and lift your hips off the ground, coming into a reverse plank position. Engage your core and lift one leg off the ground, extending it straight up towards the ceiling. Hold for a moment, then lower your leg back down. Repeat with the other leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you and your hands resting on the ground behind you, fingers pointing towards your feet.","Press through your hands and lift your hips off the ground, coming into a reverse plank position.","Engage your core and lift one leg off the ground, extending it straight up towards the ceiling.","Hold for a moment, then lower your leg back down.","Repeat with the other leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir gestreckt, und stütze die Hände hinter dir ab, die Finger zeigen in Richtung Füsse.","Drücke dich mit den Händen ab und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, bis du in einer umgekehrten Plank-Position bist.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe ein Bein vom Boden ab, strecke es gerade in Richtung Decke.","Halte kurz, dann senke das Bein wieder ab.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein.","Wechsle die Beine für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3663.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3663.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('994d0c04-9c4b-518c-a873-f0dcff2c596a', NULL, 'Ring Dips', 'Dips an Ringen', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from the rings with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your shoulders are below your elbows. Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Start by hanging from the rings with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your shoulders are below your elbows.","Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge zu Beginn an den Ringen, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und der Körper gerade.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Schultern unter den Ellbogen sind.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0677.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0677.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fcd53708-9694-5940-b56e-080fc27409fe', NULL, 'Rocking Frog Stretch', 'Frosch-Dehnung mit Wippen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start by kneeling on the ground with your knees hip-width apart. Place your hands on the ground in front of you for support. Slowly lean forward, shifting your weight onto your hands and extending your legs behind you. Keep your back straight and engage your glutes as you push your hips back and up towards the ceiling. Hold this position for a few seconds, feeling a stretch in your glutes. Slowly return to the starting position by bending your knees and lowering your hips back down. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Start by kneeling on the ground with your knees hip-width apart.","Place your hands on the ground in front of you for support.","Slowly lean forward, shifting your weight onto your hands and extending your legs behind you.","Keep your back straight and engage your glutes as you push your hips back and up towards the ceiling.","Hold this position for a few seconds, feeling a stretch in your glutes.","Slowly return to the starting position by bending your knees and lowering your hips back down.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne im Kniestand, die Knie hüftbreit auseinander.","Stütze die Hände zur Unterstützung vor dir auf dem Boden ab.","Lehne dich langsam nach vorne, verlagere dein Gewicht auf die Hände und strecke die Beine nach hinten aus.","Halte den Rücken gerade und spanne das Gesäss an, während du die Hüfte nach hinten und oben in Richtung Decke schiebst.","Halte diese Position ein paar Sekunden und spüre die Dehnung im Gesäss.","Kehre langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte wieder absenkst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2571.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2571.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('55627e6f-0913-5e26-a81e-49ebacd5193d', NULL, 'Rocky Pull-up Pulldown', 'Rocky-Klimmzug zum Latzug', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand in front of a pull-up bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Reach up and grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand in front of a pull-up bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Reach up and grab the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor eine Klimmzugstange.","Greife nach oben und fasse die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, die Brust voran.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0678.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0678.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('393b91a9-a4da-518a-bee2-e126310f6688', NULL, 'Roller Back Stretch', 'Rückendehnung mit der Faszienrolle', 'back', 'spine', 'roller', 'Start by sitting on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Place the roller perpendicular to your body, just below your glutes. Slowly roll your body backwards, allowing the roller to move up your back. Continue rolling until the roller reaches your upper back. Pause for a moment, then slowly roll back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Start by sitting on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Place the roller perpendicular to your body, just below your glutes.","Slowly roll your body backwards, allowing the roller to move up your back.","Continue rolling until the roller reaches your upper back.","Pause for a moment, then slowly roll back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir gestreckt.","Lege die Rolle quer zu deinem Körper, direkt unterhalb des Gesässes.","Rolle deinen Körper langsam nach hinten, sodass die Rolle deinen Rücken hinaufwandert.","Rolle weiter, bis die Rolle deinen oberen Rücken erreicht.","Halte kurz inne, dann rolle langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2208.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2208.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('44bce607-2048-5e70-a2bd-3118f38de5f7', NULL, 'Roller Body Saw', 'Body Saw mit der Faszienrolle', 'waist', 'abs', 'roller', 'Start in a plank position with your forearms on the roller and your body in a straight line. Engage your core and slowly roll the roller forward, extending your body as far as you can while maintaining control. Pause for a moment at the furthest point, then slowly roll the roller back towards your starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","core"]', '["Start in a plank position with your forearms on the roller and your body in a straight line.","Engage your core and slowly roll the roller forward, extending your body as far as you can while maintaining control.","Pause for a moment at the furthest point, then slowly roll the roller back towards your starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in der Plank-Position mit den Unterarmen auf der Rolle und geradem Körper.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und rolle die Rolle langsam nach vorne, wobei du deinen Körper so weit wie möglich kontrolliert streckst.","Halte am weitesten Punkt kurz inne, dann rolle die Rolle langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2204.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2204.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4719defa-964e-59e0-80bb-d91ba89b7427', NULL, 'Roller Hip Lat Stretch', 'Hüft- und Latissimus-Dehnung mit der Rolle', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'roller', 'Start by kneeling on the ground with the roller positioned under your hips. Place your hands on the roller for support. Slowly roll the roller forward, extending your hips and stretching your glutes. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then roll back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Start by kneeling on the ground with the roller positioned under your hips.","Place your hands on the roller for support.","Slowly roll the roller forward, extending your hips and stretching your glutes.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then roll back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne im Kniestand, die Rolle unter deiner Hüfte positioniert.","Stütze die Hände zur Unterstützung auf der Rolle ab.","Rolle die Rolle langsam nach vorne, strecke dabei die Hüfte und dehne das Gesäss.","Halte die Dehnung ein paar Sekunden, dann rolle zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2205.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2205.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('96f8ae88-2d79-5644-8a2d-8f416639eaed', NULL, 'Roller Hip Stretch', 'Hüftdehnung mit der Faszienrolle', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'roller', 'Start by sitting on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Place the roller under your glutes, just above your knees. Lean back and place your hands on the ground behind you for support. Engage your glutes and slowly roll the roller forward, bending your knees and bringing them towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, feeling a stretch in your glutes. Slowly roll the roller back to the starting position, extending your legs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Start by sitting on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Place the roller under your glutes, just above your knees.","Lean back and place your hands on the ground behind you for support.","Engage your glutes and slowly roll the roller forward, bending your knees and bringing them towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, feeling a stretch in your glutes.","Slowly roll the roller back to the starting position, extending your legs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir gestreckt.","Lege die Rolle unter dein Gesäss, direkt über den Knien.","Lehne dich zurück und stütze die Hände hinter dir auf dem Boden ab.","Spanne dein Gesäss an und rolle die Rolle langsam nach vorne, beuge dabei die Knie und ziehe sie zur Brust.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und spüre die Dehnung im Gesäss.","Rolle die Rolle langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition und strecke dabei die Beine.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2202.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2202.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e100e691-db98-5237-8d46-ae2283c1c7c0', NULL, 'Roller Reverse Crunch', 'Reverse Crunch mit der Faszienrolle', 'waist', 'abs', 'roller', 'Lie flat on your back with your arms extended straight above your head and your legs straight out in front of you. Place the roller between your feet and grip it with your toes. Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the ground and curl your knees towards your chest, rolling the roller towards your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position, rolling the roller away from your body. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your arms extended straight above your head and your legs straight out in front of you.","Place the roller between your feet and grip it with your toes.","Engaging your abs, lift your legs off the ground and curl your knees towards your chest, rolling the roller towards your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position, rolling the roller away from your body.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Arme gestreckt über dem Kopf und die Beine gerade vor dir ausgestreckt.","Lege die Rolle zwischen deine Füsse und greife sie mit den Zehen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an, hebe die Beine vom Boden ab und ziehe die Knie zur Brust, während du die Rolle zu deinem Körper rollst.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab und rolle die Rolle vom Körper weg.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2206.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2206.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bde54886-87f2-53ee-9960-46f137c8c750', NULL, 'Roller Seated Shoulder Flexor Depressor Retractor', 'Schultermobilisation im Sitzen mit der Rolle', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'roller', 'Sit on a flat surface with your legs extended in front of you. Hold the roller with both hands, palms facing down, and place it on your thighs. Lean forward slightly and roll the roller away from your body, extending your arms straight in front of you. Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the roller back towards your body, bending your arms and bringing the roller back to your thighs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'deltoids', '["deltoids","triceps"]', '["Sit on a flat surface with your legs extended in front of you.","Hold the roller with both hands, palms facing down, and place it on your thighs.","Lean forward slightly and roll the roller away from your body, extending your arms straight in front of you.","Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the roller back towards your body, bending your arms and bringing the roller back to your thighs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine ebene Fläche, die Beine vor dir gestreckt.","Halte die Rolle mit beiden Händen, Handflächen nach unten, und lege sie auf deine Oberschenkel.","Lehne dich leicht nach vorne und rolle die Rolle von deinem Körper weg, bis die Arme gerade vor dir gestreckt sind.","Halte kurz inne, dann rolle die Rolle langsam zurück zu deinem Körper, beuge dabei die Arme und bringe die Rolle zurück auf deine Oberschenkel.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2203.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2203.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('889c9ee4-7bbf-5231-b29f-5b13450e8f54', NULL, 'Roller Seated Single Leg Shoulder Flexor Depressor Retractor', 'Schultermobilisation im Sitzen (einbeinig) mit der Rolle', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'roller', 'Sit on a flat surface with your legs extended in front of you. Hold the roller with both hands, palms facing down, and place it on your thighs. Lean back slightly and engage your core muscles. Raise the roller up to shoulder level, keeping your arms straight. Slowly lower the roller back down to your thighs. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'deltoids', '["deltoids","triceps"]', '["Sit on a flat surface with your legs extended in front of you.","Hold the roller with both hands, palms facing down, and place it on your thighs.","Lean back slightly and engage your core muscles.","Raise the roller up to shoulder level, keeping your arms straight.","Slowly lower the roller back down to your thighs.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine ebene Fläche, die Beine vor dir gestreckt.","Halte die Rolle mit beiden Händen, Handflächen nach unten, und lege sie auf deine Oberschenkel.","Lehne dich leicht zurück und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Hebe die Rolle auf Schulterhöhe an, die Arme bleiben gestreckt.","Senke die Rolle langsam zurück auf deine Oberschenkel ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2209.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2209.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6ac13294-1b9e-5d45-a5fe-65713c523633', NULL, 'Roller Side Lat Stretch', 'Seitliche Latissimus-Dehnung mit der Rolle', 'back', 'lats', 'roller', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the roller with both hands in front of your body. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Extend your arms forward and roll the roller down towards your feet, feeling a stretch in your lats. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly roll the roller back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the roller with both hands in front of your body.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arms forward and roll the roller down towards your feet, feeling a stretch in your lats.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly roll the roller back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin und halte die Rolle mit beiden Händen vor deinem Körper.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Strecke die Arme nach vorne und rolle die Rolle in Richtung deiner Füsse hinunter, bis du eine Dehnung im Latissimus spürst.","Halte die Dehnung ein paar Sekunden, dann rolle die Rolle langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2207.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2207.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('13b48eb1-0e23-5606-8b30-766471b36dae', NULL, 'Rope Climb', 'Seilklettern', 'back', 'upper back', 'rope', 'Stand facing the rope with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grab the rope with both hands, palms facing towards you. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Begin pulling yourself up the rope by alternating hand-over-hand movements. Use your legs to assist in the upward movement. Continue climbing until you reach the desired height or the top of the rope. To descend, reverse the hand-over-hand movement while controlling your descent. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","biceps","shoulders"]', '["Stand facing the rope with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grab the rope with both hands, palms facing towards you.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Begin pulling yourself up the rope by alternating hand-over-hand movements.","Use your legs to assist in the upward movement.","Continue climbing until you reach the desired height or the top of the rope.","To descend, reverse the hand-over-hand movement while controlling your descent.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen dem Seil zugewandt hin.","Greife das Seil mit beiden Händen, die Handflächen zeigen zu dir.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Beginne, dich mit abwechselnden Handbewegungen am Seil hochzuziehen.","Nutze deine Beine, um die Aufwärtsbewegung zu unterstützen.","Klettere weiter, bis du die gewünschte Höhe oder das obere Ende des Seils erreichst.","Zum Abstieg kehrst du die abwechselnden Handbewegungen um und kontrollierst deinen Abstieg.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0680.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0680.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0ebaf541-2835-5d45-9acd-5f17387652cb', NULL, 'Run', 'Laufen', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start by standing upright with your feet hip-width apart. Engage your core and keep your upper body relaxed. Begin jogging in place, lifting your knees up towards your chest and landing softly on the balls of your feet. Maintain a steady pace and continue jogging for the desired duration or distance. Remember to breathe deeply and maintain good posture throughout the exercise.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start by standing upright with your feet hip-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your upper body relaxed.","Begin jogging in place, lifting your knees up towards your chest and landing softly on the balls of your feet.","Maintain a steady pace and continue jogging for the desired duration or distance.","Remember to breathe deeply and maintain good posture throughout the exercise."]', '["Stehe aufrecht mit hüftbreit aufgestellten Füssen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte den Oberkörper entspannt.","Beginne auf der Stelle zu joggen, hebe dabei die Knie in Richtung Brust und lande weich auf den Fussballen.","Halte ein gleichmässiges Tempo und jogge weiter für die gewünschte Dauer oder Distanz.","Denke daran, tief zu atmen und während der gesamten Übung eine gute Haltung zu bewahren."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0685.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0685.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5017bf5f-37a1-5294-a0c6-a5ac4edf9a93', NULL, 'Run (Equipment)', 'Laufen (Gerät)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start by standing upright with your feet hip-width apart. Engage your core and keep your upper body relaxed. Begin jogging in place, lifting your knees up towards your chest and landing softly on the balls of your feet. Maintain a steady pace and continue jogging for the desired duration or distance. Remember to breathe deeply and maintain good posture throughout the exercise.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start by standing upright with your feet hip-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your upper body relaxed.","Begin jogging in place, lifting your knees up towards your chest and landing softly on the balls of your feet.","Maintain a steady pace and continue jogging for the desired duration or distance.","Remember to breathe deeply and maintain good posture throughout the exercise."]', '["Stehe aufrecht mit hüftbreit aufgestellten Füssen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte den Oberkörper entspannt.","Beginne auf der Stelle zu joggen, hebe dabei die Knie in Richtung Brust und lande weich auf den Fussballen.","Halte ein gleichmässiges Tempo und jogge weiter für die gewünschte Dauer oder Distanz.","Denke daran, tief zu atmen und während der gesamten Übung eine gute Haltung zu bewahren."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0684.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0684.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0b97e220-0287-5dee-959a-7baa8ff86fd7', NULL, 'Runner''s Stretch', 'Läufer-Dehnung', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart. Take a step forward with your right foot, keeping your left foot planted. Bend your right knee and lower your body down, keeping your left leg straight. Place your hands on your right thigh for support. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","quadriceps"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart.","Take a step forward with your right foot, keeping your left foot planted.","Bend your right knee and lower your body down, keeping your left leg straight.","Place your hands on your right thigh for support.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat."]', '["Stell dich mit hüftbreit aufgestellten Füssen hin.","Mache einen Schritt nach vorne mit dem rechten Fuss, der linke Fuss bleibt am Boden.","Beuge das rechte Knie und senke deinen Körper ab, das linke Bein bleibt gestreckt.","Stütze die Hände zur Unterstützung auf deinem rechten Oberschenkel ab.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden, dann wechsle die Seite und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1585.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1585.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d5e66df1-3995-5efe-9abb-295388b950ab', NULL, 'Russian Twist', 'Russian Twist', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Lean back slightly while keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Hold your hands together in front of your chest or hold a weight if desired. Lift your feet off the ground, balancing on your sit bones. Twist your torso to the right, bringing your hands or weight towards the right side of your body. Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing your hands or weight towards the left side of your body. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor.","Lean back slightly while keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Hold your hands together in front of your chest or hold a weight if desired.","Lift your feet off the ground, balancing on your sit bones.","Twist your torso to the right, bringing your hands or weight towards the right side of your body.","Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing your hands or weight towards the left side of your body.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lehne dich leicht zurück, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Halte die Hände vor der Brust zusammen oder halte nach Wunsch ein Gewicht.","Hebe die Füsse vom Boden ab und balanciere auf deinen Sitzbeinhöckern.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper nach rechts und bringe die Hände oder das Gewicht zur rechten Körperseite.","Halte kurz inne, dann drehe den Oberkörper nach links und bringe die Hände oder das Gewicht zur linken Körperseite.","Wechsle die Seiten für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0687.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0687.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7167ed34-1db9-52a7-9043-560e59b4b742', NULL, 'Scapula Dips', 'Scapula-Dips', 'back', 'traps', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended in front of you. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Lower your body by bending your elbows and retracting your shoulder blades, as if you are trying to squeeze a pencil between them. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to extend your elbows and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'rhomboids', '["rhomboids","deltoids"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended in front of you.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Lower your body by bending your elbows and retracting your shoulder blades, as if you are trying to squeeze a pencil between them.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to extend your elbows and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin und strecke die Arme vor dir aus.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst, als würdest du einen Stift zwischen ihnen einklemmen.","Halte unten kurz inne, dann drücke dich mit den Händen ab, strecke die Ellbogen und kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3012.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3012.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a42407c5-2682-500b-8dfa-805f60a8c236', NULL, 'Scapula Push-up', 'Scapula-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'serratus anterior', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line. Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body. As you lower, squeeze your shoulder blades together and push your chest forward. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line.","Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body.","As you lower, squeeze your shoulder blades together and push your chest forward.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne im hohen Stütz, die Hände direkt unter den Schultern und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Senke deine Brust in Richtung Boden ab, halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Ziehe beim Absenken die Schulterblätter zusammen und schiebe deine Brust nach vorne.","Halte unten kurz inne, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3021.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3021.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('737864ca-13dc-5e09-bbe1-ddf79855507a', NULL, 'Scapular Pull-up', 'Scapula-Klimmzug', 'back', 'traps', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended. Retract your shoulder blades by pulling them down and back. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, focusing on squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your arms fully extended.","Retract your shoulder blades by pulling them down and back.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, focusing on squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge zu Beginn an einer Klimmzugstange, die Handflächen zeigen von dir weg und die Arme sind vollständig gestreckt.","Ziehe die Schulterblätter nach unten und hinten zusammen.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, konzentriere dich darauf, die Schulterblätter zusammenzudrücken.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0688.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0688.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9dea13e2-7f90-5407-8efa-d861e9e97a59', NULL, 'Scissor Jumps (Male)', 'Scherensprünge (Mann)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Jump off the ground and simultaneously cross your right leg in front of your left leg. As you land, quickly switch legs, crossing your left leg in front of your right leg. Continue alternating legs and jumping as quickly as possible. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Jump off the ground and simultaneously cross your right leg in front of your left leg.","As you land, quickly switch legs, crossing your left leg in front of your right leg.","Continue alternating legs and jumping as quickly as possible.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stell dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin.","Spring vom Boden ab und kreuze dabei gleichzeitig das rechte Bein vor dem linken.","Wechsle beim Landen schnell die Beine und kreuze das linke Bein vor dem rechten.","Wechsle die Beine weiter ab und springe so schnell wie möglich.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3219.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3219.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8d942b41-d606-536c-9fe1-afa0238f7a65', NULL, 'Seated Calf Stretch (Male)', 'Wadendehnung im Sitzen (Mann)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a chair or bench with your feet flat on the ground. Extend one leg straight out in front of you, keeping your heel on the ground. Lean forward slightly, feeling a stretch in your calf muscle. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Switch legs and repeat the stretch.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the edge of a chair or bench with your feet flat on the ground.","Extend one leg straight out in front of you, keeping your heel on the ground.","Lean forward slightly, feeling a stretch in your calf muscle.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Switch legs and repeat the stretch."]', '["Setz dich auf die Kante eines Stuhls oder einer Bank, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Strecke ein Bein gerade nach vorne aus, die Ferse bleibt auf dem Boden.","Lehne dich leicht nach vorne, bis du eine Dehnung in der Wade spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden.","Wechsle das Bein und wiederhole die Dehnung."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1390.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1390.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9f0d697f-b86e-56d4-b4dc-6820cbe9df5c', NULL, 'Seated Glute Stretch', 'Gesässdehnung im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Bend your right knee and cross your right ankle over your left thigh. Place your right hand on the ground behind you for support. With your left hand, gently press down on your right knee to deepen the stretch. Hold the stretch for 30 seconds to 1 minute. Switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Bend your right knee and cross your right ankle over your left thigh.","Place your right hand on the ground behind you for support.","With your left hand, gently press down on your right knee to deepen the stretch.","Hold the stretch for 30 seconds to 1 minute.","Switch sides and repeat."]', '["Setz dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir gestreckt.","Beuge das rechte Knie und lege den rechten Knöchel über den linken Oberschenkel.","Stütze die rechte Hand zur Unterstützung hinter dir auf dem Boden ab.","Drücke mit der linken Hand sanft auf dein rechtes Knie, um die Dehnung zu vertiefen.","Halte die Dehnung 30 Sekunden bis 1 Minute.","Wechsle die Seite und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1424.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1424.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('66bb66f6-3b13-5125-846e-b86bb70353c5', NULL, 'Seated Leg Raise', 'Beinheben im Sitzen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on a flat bench with your back straight and your feet flat on the ground. Place your hands on the sides of the bench for support. Keeping your legs straight, slowly raise them up in front of you until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Sit on a flat bench with your back straight and your feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands on the sides of the bench for support.","Keeping your legs straight, slowly raise them up in front of you until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf eine Flachbank, der Rücken gerade und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Stütze die Hände seitlich an der Bank ab.","Hebe die gestreckten Beine langsam vor dir an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, dann senke die Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0689.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0689.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('933b3e8c-f987-51e6-9c08-7c9717805149', NULL, 'Seated Lower Back Stretch', 'Unterrücken-Dehnung im Sitzen', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a chair with your feet flat on the ground. Place your hands on your thighs or on the sides of the chair for support. Slowly lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight. Feel the stretch in your lower back and hold for 20-30 seconds. Slowly return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the edge of a chair with your feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands on your thighs or on the sides of the chair for support.","Slowly lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight.","Feel the stretch in your lower back and hold for 20-30 seconds.","Slowly return to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setz dich auf die Kante eines Stuhls, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände zur Unterstützung auf die Oberschenkel oder seitlich an den Stuhl.","Beuge dich langsam aus der Hüfte nach vorne, der Rücken bleibt gerade.","Spüre die Dehnung im unteren Rücken und halte sie 20-30 Sekunden.","Kehre langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0690.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0690.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f59689cf-34cd-5fea-9a1a-a156043185a8', NULL, 'Seated Piriformis Stretch', 'Piriformis-Dehnung im Sitzen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Bend your right knee and place your right foot on the outside of your left knee. Place your left elbow on the outside of your right knee and gently twist your torso to the right. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Bend your right knee and place your right foot on the outside of your left knee.","Place your left elbow on the outside of your right knee and gently twist your torso to the right.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then switch sides and repeat."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden mit ausgestreckten Beinen vor dir.","Beuge dein rechtes Knie und stelle deinen rechten Fuss aussen neben dein linkes Knie.","Lege deinen linken Ellbogen aussen an dein rechtes Knie und drehe deinen Oberkörper sanft nach rechts.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden, wechsle dann die Seite und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2567.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2567.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('88607e58-6727-58c7-937c-67f6683e32e3', NULL, 'Seated Side Crunch (Wall)', 'Seitlicher Crunch im Sitzen (an der Wand)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the floor with your back against a wall and your legs extended in front of you. Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the floor, hip-width apart. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engage your abs and lean to one side, bringing your elbow towards your hip. Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Sit on the floor with your back against a wall and your legs extended in front of you.","Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the floor, hip-width apart.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engage your abs and lean to one side, bringing your elbow towards your hip.","Pause for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich mit dem Rücken an eine Wand auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Beuge die Knie und stelle die Füsse hüftbreit flach auf den Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskeln an und neige dich zur Seite, wobei sich der Ellbogen der Hüfte annähert.","Halte kurz inne und kehre dann zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0691.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0691.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4520cd1e-b417-5ed2-aadc-e40095abc660', NULL, 'Seated Wide Angle Pose Sequence', 'Sitzende Grätschhaltung – Dehnsequenz', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in a wide angle. Flex your feet and engage your quadriceps. Place your hands on the ground behind you for support. Keeping your back straight, lean forward from your hips. Continue leaning forward until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings. Hold this position for a few breaths. Slowly release the stretch and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","calves"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in a wide angle.","Flex your feet and engage your quadriceps.","Place your hands on the ground behind you for support.","Keeping your back straight, lean forward from your hips.","Continue leaning forward until you feel a stretch in your hamstrings.","Hold this position for a few breaths.","Slowly release the stretch and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden und strecke die Beine weit gegrätscht aus.","Ziehe die Füsse an und spanne deine Quadrizeps an.","Stütze deine Hände hinter dir auf dem Boden ab.","Halte den Rücken gerade und beuge dich aus der Hüfte nach vorne.","Beuge dich weiter nach vorne, bis du eine Dehnung in den Beinbeugern spürst.","Halte diese Position für einige Atemzüge.","Löse die Dehnung langsam und kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1587.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1587.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ec927d67-f4a4-567e-9c4d-e57e0541d344', NULL, 'Self-Assisted Inverse Leg Curl', 'Selbst unterstützter inverser Beincurl', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back on a mat or bench with your legs extended. Place your hands by your sides or under your glutes for support. Bend your knees and lift your feet off the ground, bringing your thighs towards your chest. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","calves"]', '["Lie flat on your back on a mat or bench with your legs extended.","Place your hands by your sides or under your glutes for support.","Bend your knees and lift your feet off the ground, bringing your thighs towards your chest.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken auf eine Matte oder Bank, die Beine ausgestreckt.","Lege die Hände neben den Körper oder unter das Gesäss zur Unterstützung.","Beuge die Knie und hebe die Füsse vom Boden ab, sodass sich die Oberschenkel dem Brustkorb annähern.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0697.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0697.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6dd8634d-3054-5e56-930e-efa9c3ae2318', NULL, 'Self-Assisted Inverse Leg Curl', 'Selbst unterstützter inverser Beincurl', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on a leg curl machine with your legs extended and your ankles hooked under the padded lever. Place your hands on the side handles of the machine for support. Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs upward as far as possible. Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings. Slowly lower your legs back to the starting position while inhaling. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","calves"]', '["Lie face down on a leg curl machine with your legs extended and your ankles hooked under the padded lever.","Place your hands on the side handles of the machine for support.","Keeping your upper body stationary, exhale and curl your legs upward as far as possible.","Hold the contracted position for a brief pause as you squeeze your hamstrings.","Slowly lower your legs back to the starting position while inhaling.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich bäuchlings auf eine Beinbeuger-Maschine, die Beine ausgestreckt und die Fussgelenke unter dem gepolsterten Hebel eingehakt.","Halte dich mit den Händen an den seitlichen Griffen der Maschine fest.","Halte den Oberkörper ruhig, atme aus und beuge die Beine so weit wie möglich nach oben.","Halte die angespannte Position kurz und drücke dabei die Beinbeuger zusammen.","Senke die Beine beim Einatmen langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1766.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1766.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5e7a7229-73d2-5de3-9a4d-18d7fcd6deaa', NULL, 'Self-Assisted Inverse Leg Curl (on Floor)', 'Selbst unterstützter inverser Beincurl am Boden', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the ground, hip-width apart. Lift your hips off the ground, engaging your glutes and hamstrings. Slowly curl your legs towards your glutes, keeping your hips lifted. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position. Lower your hips back down to the ground. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","calves"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the ground, hip-width apart.","Lift your hips off the ground, engaging your glutes and hamstrings.","Slowly curl your legs towards your glutes, keeping your hips lifted.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly extend your legs back to the starting position.","Lower your hips back down to the ground.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine ausgestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Beuge die Knie und stelle die Füsse hüftbreit flach auf den Boden.","Hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab und spanne dabei Gesäss und Beinbeuger an.","Ziehe die Beine langsam zum Gesäss heran, während die Hüfte oben bleibt.","Halte oben kurz inne und strecke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Senke die Hüfte wieder zurück auf den Boden ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0696.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0696.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('14b19f2d-c5f7-52e3-9649-3f44ba0f4f49', NULL, 'Semi Squat Jump (Male)', 'Halbe Kniebeuge mit Sprung (Mann)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body into a squat position. Jump explosively, extending your hips and knees while swinging your arms for momentum. Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next repetition. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees and lower your body into a squat position.","Jump explosively, extending your hips and knees while swinging your arms for momentum.","Land softly on the balls of your feet and immediately go into the next repetition.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen.","Beuge die Knie und senke den Körper in eine Kniebeuge-Position ab.","Springe explosiv ab, strecke dabei Hüfte und Knie und schwinge die Arme für Schwung mit.","Lande weich auf den Fussballen und gehe sofort in die nächste Wiederholung über.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3222.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3222.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a9a9335f-40ae-5b9e-9560-df5748fb0cc2', NULL, 'Short Stride Run', 'Laufen mit kurzen Schritten', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Find an open space or a treadmill to perform the exercise. Stand tall with your feet hip-width apart. Start jogging in place, lifting your knees high and pumping your arms. After a few seconds, start taking short strides forward, maintaining a quick pace. Continue running with short strides for the desired duration or distance.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Find an open space or a treadmill to perform the exercise.","Stand tall with your feet hip-width apart.","Start jogging in place, lifting your knees high and pumping your arms.","After a few seconds, start taking short strides forward, maintaining a quick pace.","Continue running with short strides for the desired duration or distance."]', '["Suche dir einen freien Platz oder ein Laufband für die Übung.","Stehe aufrecht mit hüftbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen.","Beginne auf der Stelle zu joggen, hebe die Knie hoch an und bewege die Arme aktiv mit.","Nach einigen Sekunden beginnst du mit kurzen Schritten vorwärtszulaufen und hältst dabei ein zügiges Tempo.","Laufe mit kurzen Schritten für die gewünschte Dauer oder Distanz weiter."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3656.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3656.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('523f46bc-41dd-5026-8be1-89ef6c2da33c', NULL, 'Shoulder Grip Pull-up', 'Klimmzug mit Schultergriff', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with a shoulder-width grip, palms facing away from you. Hang freely with your arms fully extended. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with a shoulder-width grip, palms facing away from you.","Hang freely with your arms fully extended.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange schulterbreit, die Handflächen zeigen von dir weg.","Hänge frei mit vollständig gestreckten Armen.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke deinen Körper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1763.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1763.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bf6a2f11-0b8a-5df0-b1d1-c659136bf796', NULL, 'Shoulder Tap', 'Shoulder Tap', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line. Engage your core and lift your right hand off the ground, reaching across to tap your left shoulder. Place your right hand back on the ground and repeat with your left hand tapping your right shoulder. Continue alternating shoulder taps while keeping your hips and torso stable. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands directly under your shoulders and your body in a straight line.","Engage your core and lift your right hand off the ground, reaching across to tap your left shoulder.","Place your right hand back on the ground and repeat with your left hand tapping your right shoulder.","Continue alternating shoulder taps while keeping your hips and torso stable.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Starte in einer hohen Plank-Position mit den Händen direkt unter den Schultern und dem Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe deine rechte Hand vom Boden ab, um damit deine linke Schulter zu berühren.","Setze die rechte Hand wieder auf dem Boden ab und wiederhole mit der linken Hand, die die rechte Schulter berührt.","Wechsle die Schulterberührungen weiter ab, während du Hüfte und Oberkörper stabil hältst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3699.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3699.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7a76cae6-71e2-54f0-a244-351d8f296c95', NULL, 'Shoulder Tap Push-up', 'Liegestütz mit Shoulder Tap', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line from head to heels. Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. As you push back up, lift your right hand off the ground and tap your left shoulder. Return your right hand to the ground and repeat the push-up, this time lifting your left hand and tapping your right shoulder. Continue alternating shoulder taps with each push-up repetition. Maintain a stable core and avoid excessive hip rotation throughout the exercise. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your body in a straight line from head to heels.","Lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","As you push back up, lift your right hand off the ground and tap your left shoulder.","Return your right hand to the ground and repeat the push-up, this time lifting your left hand and tapping your right shoulder.","Continue alternating shoulder taps with each push-up repetition.","Maintain a stable core and avoid excessive hip rotation throughout the exercise.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Starte in einer hohen Plank-Position mit den Händen etwas weiter als schulterbreit auseinander und dem Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fersen.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Während du dich wieder nach oben drückst, hebe die rechte Hand vom Boden ab und berühre damit die linke Schulter.","Setze die rechte Hand wieder auf dem Boden ab und wiederhole den Liegestütz, diesmal hebst du die linke Hand und berührst die rechte Schulter.","Wechsle die Schulterberührungen bei jeder Liegestütz-Wiederholung ab.","Halte deine Körpermitte während der gesamten Übung stabil und vermeide übermässige Hüftrotation.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0699.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0699.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2d8f479d-b339-59d1-b99e-d7298c55c20a', NULL, 'Side Bridge Hip Abduction', 'Hüftabduktion im Seitstütz', 'upper legs', 'abductors', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other. Prop yourself up on your forearm, keeping your elbow directly below your shoulder. Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet. While keeping your core engaged, lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips. Pause for a moment at the top, then lower your leg back down. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","obliques"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other.","Prop yourself up on your forearm, keeping your elbow directly below your shoulder.","Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet.","While keeping your core engaged, lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips.","Pause for a moment at the top, then lower your leg back down.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine ausgestreckt und übereinander.","Stütze dich auf deinen Unterarm, wobei der Ellbogen direkt unter der Schulter bleibt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss entsteht.","Hebe bei weiterhin angespannter Körpermitte das obere Bein so hoch wie möglich an, ohne die Hüfte zu drehen.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke das Bein dann wieder ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1774.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1774.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6a506a03-8414-5396-9297-bb2586597422', NULL, 'Side Bridge V. 2', 'Seitstütz V. 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other. Place your forearm on the ground directly below your shoulder, with your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle. Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet. Hold this position for the desired amount of time. Lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","glutes"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other.","Place your forearm on the ground directly below your shoulder, with your elbow bent at a 90-degree angle.","Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet.","Hold this position for the desired amount of time.","Lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine ausgestreckt und übereinander.","Stelle den Unterarm direkt unter der Schulter auf den Boden ab, der Ellbogen ist im 90°-Winkel gebeugt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss entsteht.","Halte diese Position für die gewünschte Dauer.","Senke die Hüfte zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0705.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0705.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3b1bb7df-d707-5074-8d48-e57537f3eb1e', NULL, 'Side Hip (on Parallel Bars)', 'Seitliches Hüftheben am Barren', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Stand between two parallel bars with your feet shoulder-width apart. Place your hands on the bars and lift your body off the ground, supporting your weight on your arms. Engage your abs and slowly lift your legs to the side, keeping them straight. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Stand between two parallel bars with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place your hands on the bars and lift your body off the ground, supporting your weight on your arms.","Engage your abs and slowly lift your legs to the side, keeping them straight.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich zwischen zwei parallele Barren, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Lege die Hände auf die Barren und hebe den Körper vom Boden ab, das Gewicht auf den Armen abstützend.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe die Beine langsam gestreckt zur Seite an.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Beine dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0709.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0709.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ff5e228e-9ba7-5825-9bd1-00d98f4ae463', NULL, 'Side Hip Abduction', 'Seitliche Hüftabduktion', 'upper legs', 'abductors', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your hands on your hips. Shift your weight to one leg and lift the opposite leg out to the side, keeping it straight. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position. Repeat on the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","quadriceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your hands on your hips.","Shift your weight to one leg and lift the opposite leg out to the side, keeping it straight.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen, die Hände an den Hüften.","Verlagere dein Gewicht auf ein Bein und hebe das andere Bein gestreckt zur Seite an.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke das Bein dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0710.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0710.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('87d14b14-9d8b-5a98-a8ed-8759e5e077bb', NULL, 'Side Lying Floor Stretch', 'Seitliche Dehnung am Boden (Seitenlage)', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs straight and your bottom arm extended straight overhead. Bend your top knee and place your foot on the ground in front of your bottom leg. Reach your top arm over your head and grab onto something stable, like a wall or a piece of furniture. Slowly lift your bottom leg off the ground, keeping it straight, until you feel a stretch in your side. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then slowly lower your leg back down. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","glutes"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs straight and your bottom arm extended straight overhead.","Bend your top knee and place your foot on the ground in front of your bottom leg.","Reach your top arm over your head and grab onto something stable, like a wall or a piece of furniture.","Slowly lift your bottom leg off the ground, keeping it straight, until you feel a stretch in your side.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds, then slowly lower your leg back down.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine gestreckt, und strecke den unteren Arm gerade über den Kopf.","Beuge das obere Knie und stelle den Fuss vor dem unteren Bein auf den Boden.","Strecke den oberen Arm über den Kopf und halte dich an etwas Stabilem fest, zum Beispiel einer Wand oder einem Möbelstück.","Hebe das untere Bein langsam gestreckt vom Boden ab, bis du eine Dehnung in der Seite spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden und senke das Bein dann langsam wieder ab.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1358.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1358.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6adb7e4b-5c03-5a62-99fa-28a63892eb50', NULL, 'Side Lying Hip Adduction (Male)', 'Hüftadduktion in Seitenlage (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'adductors', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs straight and stacked on top of each other. Place your bottom arm under your head for support. Engage your adductors and lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips or leaning backward. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs straight and stacked on top of each other.","Place your bottom arm under your head for support.","Engage your adductors and lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips or leaning backward.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine gestreckt und übereinander.","Lege den unteren Arm zur Unterstützung unter den Kopf.","Spanne die Adduktoren an und hebe das obere Bein so hoch wie möglich, ohne die Hüfte zu drehen oder dich nach hinten zu lehnen.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke das Bein dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3667.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3667.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('76cc3ef3-0673-56a3-b5d7-fe8af7f377b2', NULL, 'Side Plank Hip Adduction', 'Hüftadduktion im Seitstütz', 'upper legs', 'adductors', 'body weight', 'Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other. Prop yourself up on your forearm, keeping your elbow directly below your shoulder. Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet. While maintaining the side plank position, lift your top leg towards the ceiling, keeping it straight. Slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","glutes"]', '["Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other.","Prop yourself up on your forearm, keeping your elbow directly below your shoulder.","Engage your core and lift your hips off the ground, creating a straight line from your head to your feet.","While maintaining the side plank position, lift your top leg towards the ceiling, keeping it straight.","Slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine ausgestreckt und übereinander.","Stütze dich auf deinen Unterarm, wobei der Ellbogen direkt unter der Schulter bleibt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fuss entsteht.","Hebe in der Seitstütz-Position das obere Bein gestreckt in Richtung Decke an.","Senke das Bein langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1775.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1775.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4d52d345-3543-5ad7-af26-08dea0a2cbda', NULL, 'Side Push Neck Stretch', 'Nackendehnung seitlich mit Handdruck', 'neck', 'levator scapulae', 'body weight', 'Stand or sit up straight with your shoulders relaxed. Tilt your head to the right, bringing your right ear towards your right shoulder. Place your right hand on the left side of your head and gently apply pressure to increase the stretch. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds. Repeat on the other side, tilting your head to the left and applying pressure with your left hand. Repeat the stretch 2-3 times on each side.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","sternocleidomastoid"]', '["Stand or sit up straight with your shoulders relaxed.","Tilt your head to the right, bringing your right ear towards your right shoulder.","Place your right hand on the left side of your head and gently apply pressure to increase the stretch.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds.","Repeat on the other side, tilting your head to the left and applying pressure with your left hand.","Repeat the stretch 2-3 times on each side."]', '["Stehe oder sitze aufrecht mit entspannten Schultern.","Neige den Kopf nach rechts, sodass sich das rechte Ohr der rechten Schulter annähert.","Lege die rechte Hand auf die linke Kopfseite und übe sanften Druck aus, um die Dehnung zu verstärken.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite, neige den Kopf nach links und übe mit der linken Hand Druck aus.","Wiederhole die Dehnung 2-3 Mal auf jeder Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0716.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0716.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('83afffdd-5fcd-55d1-9da3-e878dc724aef', NULL, 'Side Push-up', 'Seitlicher Liegestütz', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other. Place your bottom hand on the ground directly under your shoulder, fingers pointing forward. Press through your bottom hand to lift your body off the ground, keeping your legs straight and your core engaged. Extend your top arm straight up towards the ceiling, creating a straight line from your head to your heels. Lower your body back down to the starting position with control. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest","core"]', '["Start by lying on your side with your legs extended and stacked on top of each other.","Place your bottom hand on the ground directly under your shoulder, fingers pointing forward.","Press through your bottom hand to lift your body off the ground, keeping your legs straight and your core engaged.","Extend your top arm straight up towards the ceiling, creating a straight line from your head to your heels.","Lower your body back down to the starting position with control.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine ausgestreckt und übereinander.","Stelle die untere Hand direkt unter der Schulter auf den Boden, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke dich mit der unteren Hand vom Boden ab, halte dabei die Beine gestreckt und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Strecke den oberen Arm gerade in Richtung Decke, sodass eine gerade Linie von Kopf bis Fersen entsteht.","Senke deinen Körper kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0717.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0717.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ee7e0749-2e05-571d-8765-a469bd46078e', NULL, 'Side Wrist Pull Stretch', 'Seitliche Handgelenk-Dehnung', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended in front of you. Extend your right arm out to the side, parallel to the ground, with your palm facing down. With your left hand, grab your right hand and gently pull it towards your body, feeling a stretch in your right forearm. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release. Repeat on the other side.', NULL, 'wrists', '["wrists","hands"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended in front of you.","Extend your right arm out to the side, parallel to the ground, with your palm facing down.","With your left hand, grab your right hand and gently pull it towards your body, feeling a stretch in your right forearm.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release.","Repeat on the other side."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen und den Armen vor dir ausgestreckt.","Strecke den rechten Arm seitlich aus, parallel zum Boden, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten.","Greife mit der linken Hand deine rechte Hand und ziehe sie sanft zu deinem Körper, bis du eine Dehnung im rechten Unterarm spürst.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden und löse sie dann.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0721.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0721.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('972acd42-4788-59d8-a251-cfc2c9d60ba9', NULL, 'Side-to-Side Chin', 'Klimmzug von Seite zu Seite', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body relaxed. Pull yourself up by bending your elbows and bringing your chin towards the bar, while keeping your body straight. Once your chin is above the bar, lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body relaxed.","Pull yourself up by bending your elbows and bringing your chin towards the bar, while keeping your body straight.","Once your chin is above the bar, lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen und leicht gebeugten Knien.","Greife eine Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, die Hände etwas weiter als schulterbreit auseinander.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen an der Stange, der Körper entspannt.","Ziehe dich hoch, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und das Kinn zur Stange bringst, während der Körper gerade bleibt.","Sobald dein Kinn über der Stange ist, senke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0720.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0720.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('780aca20-e79b-5fe3-9e23-3442f464b21c', NULL, 'Side-to-Side Toe Touch (Male)', 'Zehenspitzen-Berühren seitlich wechselnd (Mann)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended to the sides. Bend at the waist to the right, reaching your right hand towards your right foot while keeping your left hand extended to the side. Return to the starting position and then bend at the waist to the left, reaching your left hand towards your left foot while keeping your right hand extended to the side. Repeat the side-to-side bending motion for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended to the sides.","Bend at the waist to the right, reaching your right hand towards your right foot while keeping your left hand extended to the side.","Return to the starting position and then bend at the waist to the left, reaching your left hand towards your left foot while keeping your right hand extended to the side.","Repeat the side-to-side bending motion for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen und den Armen seitlich ausgestreckt.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach rechts und strecke die rechte Hand zum rechten Fuss, während die linke Hand seitlich ausgestreckt bleibt.","Kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück und beuge dich dann in der Hüfte nach links, strecke die linke Hand zum linken Fuss, während die rechte Hand seitlich ausgestreckt bleibt.","Wiederhole die Seitbeugen für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3213.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3213.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5e24593f-d189-5daa-8e8b-ac3b7cb95dbf', NULL, 'Single Arm Push-up', 'Einarmiger Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and one hand placed slightly wider than the other. Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight. As you lower yourself, shift your weight to one side and lift the opposite arm off the ground, extending it straight out to the side. Push through your chest and triceps to raise your body back up to the starting position, while simultaneously lowering your extended arm back to the ground. Repeat the movement, alternating the arm you extend with each repetition.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and one hand placed slightly wider than the other.","Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping your back straight.","As you lower yourself, shift your weight to one side and lift the opposite arm off the ground, extending it straight out to the side.","Push through your chest and triceps to raise your body back up to the starting position, while simultaneously lowering your extended arm back to the ground.","Repeat the movement, alternating the arm you extend with each repetition."]', '["Starte in der Liegestütz-Position mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Händen, wobei eine Hand etwas weiter aussen platziert ist als die andere.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und senke den Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und den Rücken gerade hältst.","Während du dich absenkst, verlagere dein Gewicht auf eine Seite und hebe den anderen Arm gestreckt seitlich vom Boden ab.","Drücke dich mit Brust und Trizeps zurück in die Ausgangsposition, während du gleichzeitig den ausgestreckten Arm wieder auf den Boden absenkst.","Wiederhole die Bewegung und wechsle bei jeder Wiederholung den ausgestreckten Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0725.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0725.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5acfbc80-3638-5855-b7d6-7bb9d48297ca', NULL, 'Single Leg Bridge with Outstretched Leg', 'Einbeinige Gesässbrücke mit ausgestrecktem Bein', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Extend one leg straight out in front of you. Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Hold for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Extend one leg straight out in front of you.","Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Hold for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Strecke ein Bein gerade vor dir aus.","Spanne das Gesäss an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern entsteht.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Hüfte dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3645.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3645.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c45eabed-3fd8-5e1e-b769-923ff05a644c', NULL, 'Single Leg Calf Raise (on a Dumbbell)', 'Einbeiniges Wadenheben auf einer Kurzhantel', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand. Lift one foot off the ground and balance on the other foot. Slowly raise your heel as high as possible, using your calf muscles. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles","feet"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand.","Lift one foot off the ground and balance on the other foot.","Slowly raise your heel as high as possible, using your calf muscles.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other leg."]', '["Stehe mit hüftbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Hebe einen Fuss vom Boden ab und balanciere auf dem anderen Fuss.","Hebe die Ferse langsam so hoch wie möglich an, indem du die Wadenmuskulatur einsetzt.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Ferse dann langsam wieder ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0727.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0727.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('634e85c9-2c58-5c7e-880c-cf1f0896c759', NULL, 'Single Leg Platform Slide', 'Einbeiniges Sliden auf der Plattform', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with one foot on a platform or slide board. Bend your knee slightly and slide the foot on the platform backward, extending your leg. Keep your core engaged and maintain a straight posture throughout the movement. Slowly return to the starting position by sliding your foot back to the initial position. Repeat the movement for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","quadriceps"]', '["Start by standing with one foot on a platform or slide board.","Bend your knee slightly and slide the foot on the platform backward, extending your leg.","Keep your core engaged and maintain a straight posture throughout the movement.","Slowly return to the starting position by sliding your foot back to the initial position.","Repeat the movement for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stehe mit einem Fuss auf einer Plattform oder einem Slide-Board.","Beuge das Knie leicht und schiebe den Fuss auf der Plattform nach hinten, wobei sich das Bein streckt.","Halte die Körpermitte während der gesamten Bewegung angespannt und die Haltung aufrecht.","Kehre langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du den Fuss wieder zurückschiebst.","Wiederhole die Bewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0730.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0730.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e3afe87f-2eaa-5fed-b7a9-c930416254a7', NULL, 'Single Leg Squat (Pistol) (Male)', 'Einbeinige Kniebeuge (Pistol Squat) (Mann)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and arms extended in front of you. Lift your right foot off the ground and extend it forward. Slowly lower your body down by bending your left knee and pushing your hips back. Keep your chest up and your back straight as you lower yourself down. Lower until your left thigh is parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your left heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and arms extended in front of you.","Lift your right foot off the ground and extend it forward.","Slowly lower your body down by bending your left knee and pushing your hips back.","Keep your chest up and your back straight as you lower yourself down.","Lower until your left thigh is parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your left heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen und den Armen vor dir ausgestreckt.","Hebe den rechten Fuss vom Boden ab und strecke ihn nach vorne.","Senke deinen Körper langsam ab, indem du das linke Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Halte die Brust oben und den Rücken gerade, während du dich absenkst.","Senke dich ab, bis dein linker Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden ist, oder so tief, wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die linke Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1759.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1759.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e78c79bd-2be6-5107-9d5d-204c8bfcb31a', NULL, 'Sissy Squat', 'Sissy Squat', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing slightly outward. Hold onto a stable object for balance if needed. Slowly lower your body by bending your knees and leaning back, keeping your torso upright. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as far as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold onto a stable object for balance if needed.","Slowly lower your body by bending your knees and leaning back, keeping your torso upright.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as far as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen, die Zehen zeigen leicht nach aussen.","Halte dich bei Bedarf an einem stabilen Gegenstand fest, um das Gleichgewicht zu halten.","Senke deinen Körper langsam ab, indem du die Knie beugst und dich nach hinten lehnst, während der Oberkörper aufrecht bleibt.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder so weit, wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1489.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1489.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('5ba3488b-2008-5cbb-b1db-ff232568dcc8', NULL, 'Sit-up V. 2', 'Sit-up V. 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your torso is at a 45-degree angle.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper langsam vom Boden ab, bis er sich im 45°-Winkel befindet.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0735.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0735.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c694ed16-5fa7-57a7-a33b-a1e6faa3934c', NULL, 'Sit-up with Arms on Chest', 'Sit-up mit Armen auf der Brust', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Cross your arms over your chest. Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Cross your arms over your chest.","Engaging your abs, lift your upper body off the ground towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Verschränke die Arme vor der Brust.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und hebe den Oberkörper in Richtung Knie vom Boden ab.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke den Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3679.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3679.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('81724c61-f271-5b1d-9cba-e49d9929a417', NULL, 'Skater Hops', 'Skater Hops', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and jump to the right, landing on your right foot. As you land, swing your left leg behind your right leg and tap the ground with your left toes. Immediately jump to the left, landing on your left foot. As you land, swing your right leg behind your left leg and tap the ground with your right toes. Continue alternating sides, jumping and tapping the ground with each leg. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees slightly and jump to the right, landing on your right foot.","As you land, swing your left leg behind your right leg and tap the ground with your left toes.","Immediately jump to the left, landing on your left foot.","As you land, swing your right leg behind your left leg and tap the ground with your right toes.","Continue alternating sides, jumping and tapping the ground with each leg.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen.","Beuge die Knie leicht und springe nach rechts, lande auf dem rechten Fuss.","Beim Landen schwingst du das linke Bein hinter das rechte und berührst den Boden mit den linken Zehen.","Springe sofort nach links und lande auf dem linken Fuss.","Beim Landen schwingst du das rechte Bein hinter das linke und berührst den Boden mit den rechten Zehen.","Wechsle die Seiten weiter ab, springe und berühre den Boden abwechselnd mit jedem Bein.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3361.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3361.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7ae4a2a7-fb79-577c-a868-40ad244d439a', NULL, 'Ski Ergometer', 'Ski-Ergometer', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'skierg machine', 'Adjust the seat height and footrests to a comfortable position. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, palms facing down. Sit up straight with your feet flat on the footrests. Extend your arms straight out in front of you, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Engage your triceps and push the handles down towards your thighs. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","forearms"]', '["Adjust the seat height and footrests to a comfortable position.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, palms facing down.","Sit up straight with your feet flat on the footrests.","Extend your arms straight out in front of you, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Engage your triceps and push the handles down towards your thighs.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitzhöhe und Fussstützen auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Handflächen zeigen nach unten.","Sitze aufrecht mit den Füssen flach auf den Fussstützen.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus, die Ellbogen bleiben leicht gebeugt.","Spanne den Trizeps an und drücke die Griffe in Richtung Oberschenkel nach unten.","Halte unten kurz inne und kehre dann langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2142.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2142.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c7ec7632-01ab-5eb1-ab20-b4d388c6b0e2', NULL, 'Ski Step', 'Ski-Step', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and keep your back straight. Jump to the right, landing on your right foot while swinging your left leg behind your right leg. Immediately jump to the left, landing on your left foot while swinging your right leg behind your left leg. Continue alternating jumps from side to side, mimicking a skiing motion. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees slightly and keep your back straight.","Jump to the right, landing on your right foot while swinging your left leg behind your right leg.","Immediately jump to the left, landing on your left foot while swinging your right leg behind your left leg.","Continue alternating jumps from side to side, mimicking a skiing motion.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe mit schulterbreit auseinander stehenden Füssen.","Beuge die Knie leicht und halte den Rücken gerade.","Springe nach rechts, lande auf dem rechten Fuss und schwinge dabei das linke Bein hinter das rechte.","Springe sofort nach links, lande auf dem linken Fuss und schwinge dabei das rechte Bein hinter das linke.","Wechsle die Sprünge weiter von Seite zu Seite ab und ahme dabei eine Skibewegung nach.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3671.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3671.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('21a20a4e-58d6-5004-8010-d566a6896759', NULL, 'Skin the Cat', 'Skin the Cat', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a bar with your arms fully extended and your body relaxed. Engage your core and lift your legs up, bringing your knees towards your chest. Continue to lift your legs up and over your head, allowing your body to pass through the arms. Once your legs are fully extended over your head, begin to lower them back down towards the starting position. As you lower your legs, allow your body to pass back through the arms until you are hanging with your arms fully extended again. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Start by hanging from a bar with your arms fully extended and your body relaxed.","Engage your core and lift your legs up, bringing your knees towards your chest.","Continue to lift your legs up and over your head, allowing your body to pass through the arms.","Once your legs are fully extended over your head, begin to lower them back down towards the starting position.","As you lower your legs, allow your body to pass back through the arms until you are hanging with your arms fully extended again.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen an einer Stange, der Körper entspannt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Beine an, sodass sich die Knie der Brust annähern.","Hebe die Beine weiter über den Kopf, sodass der Körper zwischen den Armen hindurchgleitet.","Sobald die Beine vollständig über dem Kopf gestreckt sind, senke sie zurück in Richtung Ausgangsposition ab.","Während du die Beine absenkst, lässt du den Körper zurück zwischen den Armen hindurchgleiten, bis du wieder mit vollständig gestreckten Armen hängst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3304.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3304.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('359fbf3e-151e-58f1-823c-4c05c1b78ab0', NULL, 'Sled 45° One Leg Press', 'Schlitten-Beinpresse 45° (einbeinig)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle. Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the footplate. Place one foot on the footplate and extend your leg, pushing the sled away from you. Slowly bend your knee and lower the sled back to the starting position. Repeat with the other leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the footplate.","Place one foot on the footplate and extend your leg, pushing the sled away from you.","Slowly bend your knee and lower the sled back to the starting position.","Repeat with the other leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Beinpresse auf einen 45°-Winkel ein.","Setze dich auf die Beinpresse, der Rücken liegt an der Polsterung an und die Füsse stehen auf der Fussplatte.","Stelle einen Fuss auf die Fussplatte und strecke das Bein, um den Schlitten von dir wegzudrücken.","Beuge das Knie langsam und senke den Schlitten zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein.","Wechsle die Beine für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1425.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1425.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('48a034e4-3ece-5fa5-90e5-7144242b2ece', NULL, 'Sled 45° Calf Press', 'Schlitten-Wadenpresse 45°', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle. Place your feet on the sled platform with your toes pointing forward. Push the sled platform away from you by extending your ankles and calves. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the sled platform back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle.","Place your feet on the sled platform with your toes pointing forward.","Push the sled platform away from you by extending your ankles and calves.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the sled platform back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Beinpresse auf einen 45°-Winkel ein.","Stelle die Füsse auf die Plattform der Beinpresse, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke die Plattform von dir weg, indem du die Fussgelenke und Waden streckst.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Plattform dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0738.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0738.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c3689dcb-588d-510c-9494-2dfd750285f7', NULL, 'Sled 45° Leg Press', 'Schlitten-Beinpresse 45°', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the seat and footplate of the sled machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the sled machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate. Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability. Push the footplate away from your body by extending your legs, keeping your heels on the footplate. Continue pushing until your legs are almost fully extended, but without locking your knees. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the footplate back towards your body by bending your knees. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat and footplate of the sled machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the sled machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate.","Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability.","Push the footplate away from your body by extending your legs, keeping your heels on the footplate.","Continue pushing until your legs are almost fully extended, but without locking your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the footplate back towards your body by bending your knees.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitz und Fussplatte der Beinpresse auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Setze dich auf die Beinpresse, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne an, die Füsse stehen schulterbreit auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe seitlich am Sitz für mehr Stabilität.","Drücke die Fussplatte von dir weg, indem du die Beine streckst, die Fersen bleiben dabei auf der Fussplatte.","Drücke weiter, bis die Beine fast vollständig gestreckt sind, ohne die Knie durchzudrücken.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und senke die Fussplatte dann langsam wieder zu dir zurück, indem du die Knie beugst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0739.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0739.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0ba94830-a380-5a52-8020-0db25f112279', NULL, 'Sled 45° Leg Press (Back POV)', 'Schlitten-Beinpresse 45° (Rückenansicht)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the seat of the sled machine so that your knees are at a 45-degree angle. Sit on the sled machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate. Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability. Push the footplate away from your body by extending your legs, keeping your heels on the footplate. Pause for a moment at the fully extended position. Slowly bend your knees and lower the footplate back towards your body, controlling the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat of the sled machine so that your knees are at a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the sled machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate.","Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability.","Push the footplate away from your body by extending your legs, keeping your heels on the footplate.","Pause for a moment at the fully extended position.","Slowly bend your knees and lower the footplate back towards your body, controlling the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Beinpresse so ein, dass deine Knie im 45°-Winkel sind.","Setze dich auf die Beinpresse, der Rücken liegt an der Rückenlehne an, die Füsse stehen schulterbreit auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe seitlich am Sitz für mehr Stabilität.","Drücke die Fussplatte von dir weg, indem du die Beine streckst, die Fersen bleiben dabei auf der Fussplatte.","Halte kurz inne, wenn die Beine vollständig gestreckt sind.","Beuge die Knie langsam und senke die Fussplatte kontrolliert zurück zu dir.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1464.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1464.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9783d5a5-b3a4-5611-b3a7-184273eda073', NULL, 'Sled 45° Leg Press (Side POV)', 'Schlitten-Beinpresse 45° (Seitenansicht)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the seat of the sled machine so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle when your feet are on the footplate. Sit on the sled machine with your back flat against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate. Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability. Push against the footplate to extend your legs, straightening them completely. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly bend your knees to lower the footplate back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat of the sled machine so that your knees are at a 90-degree angle when your feet are on the footplate.","Sit on the sled machine with your back flat against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate.","Grip the handles on the sides of the seat for stability.","Push against the footplate to extend your legs, straightening them completely.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly bend your knees to lower the footplate back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Beinpresse so ein, dass deine Knie im 90°-Winkel sind, wenn die Füsse auf der Fussplatte stehen.","Setze dich auf die Beinpresse, der Rücken liegt flach an der Rückenlehne an, die Füsse stehen schulterbreit auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe seitlich am Sitz für mehr Stabilität.","Drücke gegen die Fussplatte, um die Beine vollständig zu strecken.","Halte oben kurz inne und beuge die Knie dann langsam, um die Fussplatte zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu senken.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1463.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1463.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b2ffdd21-be30-5fb1-971a-e6eac5f54adb', NULL, 'Sled 45° Leg Wide Press', 'Schlitten-Beinpresse 45° breit', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle. Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the foot platform. Position your feet wider than shoulder-width apart. Push against the foot platform to extend your legs and straighten your knees. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bend your knees to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a 45-degree angle.","Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the foot platform.","Position your feet wider than shoulder-width apart.","Push against the foot platform to extend your legs and straighten your knees.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bend your knees to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Beinpresse auf einen 45°-Winkel ein.","Setze dich auf die Beinpresse, der Rücken liegt an der Polsterung an und die Füsse stehen auf der Fussplattform.","Positioniere die Füsse weiter als schulterbreit auseinander.","Drücke gegen die Fussplattform, um die Beine zu strecken und die Knie durchzudrücken.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne und beuge die Knie dann langsam, um zur Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0740.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0740.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fd6f3b43-f2eb-5c42-aff1-0d30213e4f80', NULL, 'Sled Calf Press on Leg Press', 'Wadenpress an der Beinpresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the sled. Place your feet shoulder-width apart on the sled, with your toes pointing forward. Release the safety handles and push the sled away from you by extending your knees and ankles. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the sled back down by bending your knees and ankles. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps"]', '["Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the sled.","Place your feet shoulder-width apart on the sled, with your toes pointing forward.","Release the safety handles and push the sled away from you by extending your knees and ankles.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the sled back down by bending your knees and ankles.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Beinpresse so ein, dass deine Knie leicht gebeugt sind, wenn deine Füsse auf dem Schlitten stehen.","Stelle deine Füsse schulterbreit auf den Schlitten, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Löse die Sicherheitshebel und drücke den Schlitten von dir weg, indem du Knie und Fussgelenke streckst.","Halte kurz inne am oberen Ende der Bewegung und senke den Schlitten dann langsam ab, indem du Knie und Fussgelenke beugst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1391.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1391.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c669daf1-4c0b-500e-9333-42afec5df04d', NULL, 'Sled Closer Hack Squat', 'Enge Hackenschmidt-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight and position yourself with your back against the pad. Place your feet shoulder-width apart on the platform, toes slightly pointed outwards. Grip the handles on the sides of the machine for stability. Engage your core and slowly lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to extend your legs and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight and position yourself with your back against the pad.","Place your feet shoulder-width apart on the platform, toes slightly pointed outwards.","Grip the handles on the sides of the machine for stability.","Engage your core and slowly lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to extend your legs and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Schlittenmaschine auf ein angenehmes Gewicht ein und positioniere dich mit dem Rücken gegen das Polster.","Stelle deine Füsse schulterbreit auf die Plattform, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Greife die Griffe an den Seiten der Maschine für mehr Stabilität.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper langsam ab, indem du Knie und Hüften beugst, während dein Rücken gerade bleibt.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte kurz inne am unteren Punkt und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um die Beine zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0741.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0741.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5de8391b-2842-5807-bd9f-0052954dab86', NULL, 'Sled Forward Angled Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben vorwärts geneigt am Schlitten', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight and position yourself on the machine with your toes on the platform and your heels hanging off. Place your hands on the handles or the sides of the machine for support. Engage your calves and slowly raise your heels as high as possible, pushing against the resistance of the sled. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight and position yourself on the machine with your toes on the platform and your heels hanging off.","Place your hands on the handles or the sides of the machine for support.","Engage your calves and slowly raise your heels as high as possible, pushing against the resistance of the sled.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Schlittenmaschine auf ein angenehmes Gewicht ein und positioniere dich auf der Maschine, sodass deine Zehen auf der Plattform stehen und deine Fersen frei hängen.","Lege deine Hände zur Unterstützung auf die Griffe oder die Seiten der Maschine.","Spanne deine Waden an und hebe deine Fersen langsam so hoch wie möglich, während du gegen den Widerstand des Schlittens drückst.","Halte kurz inne am oberen Ende der Bewegung und senke deine Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0742.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0742.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6add253f-a6d0-560b-9855-32514ff052bc', NULL, 'Sled Hack Squat', 'Hackenschmidt-Kniebeuge', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable position for your height. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart on the platform, toes slightly pointed outwards. Hold onto the handles or bars for stability. Lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight and chest up. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to raise your body back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable position for your height.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart on the platform, toes slightly pointed outwards.","Hold onto the handles or bars for stability.","Lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight and chest up.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to raise your body back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Schlittenmaschine auf eine für deine Körpergrösse passende Position ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen auf die Plattform, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte dich für mehr Stabilität an den Griffen oder Stangen fest.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du Knie und Hüften beugst, während dein Rücken gerade und deine Brust aufgerichtet bleibt.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um deinen Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0743.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0743.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f44ed1eb-28d0-57b0-b3d6-a5190a219984', NULL, 'Sled Lying Calf Press', 'Wadenpress im Liegen am Schlitten', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight. Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the platform. Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the edge of the platform, with your heels hanging off. Push the platform away from you by extending your ankles, keeping your knees slightly bent. Continue pushing until your calves are fully contracted. Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower the platform back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight.","Sit on the sled machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the platform.","Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the edge of the platform, with your heels hanging off.","Push the platform away from you by extending your ankles, keeping your knees slightly bent.","Continue pushing until your calves are fully contracted.","Hold the contraction for a moment, then slowly lower the platform back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Schlittenmaschine auf ein angenehmes Gewicht ein.","Setze dich auf die Schlittenmaschine, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen auf der Plattform.","Stelle deine Zehen und Fussballen auf die Kante der Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei.","Drücke die Plattform von dir weg, indem du deine Fussgelenke streckst, während deine Knie leicht gebeugt bleiben.","Drücke weiter, bis deine Waden vollständig angespannt sind.","Halte die Anspannung kurz und senke die Plattform dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2334.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2334.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b140f71a-c3eb-5fee-9483-c0b9ca6f21e4', NULL, 'Sled Lying Squat', 'Kniebeuge im Liegen am Schlitten', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight. Lie on your back on the sled machine with your feet on the footplate. Position your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly angled outwards. Grip the handles of the sled machine for stability. Engage your glutes and core muscles. Push through your heels and extend your legs to lift the sled. Lower the sled back down by bending your knees and hips. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the sled machine to a comfortable weight.","Lie on your back on the sled machine with your feet on the footplate.","Position your feet shoulder-width apart and slightly angled outwards.","Grip the handles of the sled machine for stability.","Engage your glutes and core muscles.","Push through your heels and extend your legs to lift the sled.","Lower the sled back down by bending your knees and hips.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Schlittenmaschine auf ein angenehmes Gewicht ein.","Lege dich mit dem Rücken auf die Schlittenmaschine, die Füsse auf der Fussplatte.","Positioniere deine Füsse schulterbreit und leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Greife die Griffe der Schlittenmaschine für mehr Stabilität.","Spanne Gesäss und Körpermitte an.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab und strecke die Beine, um den Schlitten anzuheben.","Senke den Schlitten zurück, indem du Knie und Hüften beugst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0744.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0744.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2a9a95ef-96cc-5a72-aada-1d4863961001', NULL, 'Sled One Leg Calf Press on Leg Press', 'Einbeiniges Wadenpress an der Beinpresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'sled machine', 'Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the sled. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the sled, shoulder-width apart. Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the sled, keeping your heels off. Push the sled forward by extending your ankles, keeping your knees slightly bent. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the sled back down by flexing your ankles. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the seat of the leg press machine so that your knees are slightly bent when your feet are on the sled.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet on the sled, shoulder-width apart.","Place your toes and the balls of your feet on the sled, keeping your heels off.","Push the sled forward by extending your ankles, keeping your knees slightly bent.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the sled back down by flexing your ankles.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Beinpresse so ein, dass deine Knie leicht gebeugt sind, wenn deine Füsse auf dem Schlitten stehen.","Setze dich auf die Maschine, mit dem Rücken an der Rückenlehne und den Füssen schulterbreit auf dem Schlitten.","Stelle deine Zehen und Fussballen auf den Schlitten, die Fersen bleiben frei.","Drücke den Schlitten nach vorne, indem du deine Fussgelenke streckst, während deine Knie leicht gebeugt bleiben.","Halte kurz inne am oberen Punkt und senke den Schlitten dann langsam zurück, indem du deine Fussgelenke beugst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1392.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1392.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ac632ce9-a56c-5f5e-b40f-289ef3eedcae', NULL, 'Sledgehammer', 'Vorschlaghammer-Schlag', 'waist', 'abs', 'hammer', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the sledge hammer with both hands. Engage your core and keep your back straight. Swing the sledge hammer down towards the ground, using your core and upper body strength. As you swing down, pivot your hips and transfer the force to the hammer. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms","shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the sledge hammer with both hands.","Engage your core and keep your back straight.","Swing the sledge hammer down towards the ground, using your core and upper body strength.","As you swing down, pivot your hips and transfer the force to the hammer.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin und halte den Vorschlaghammer mit beiden Händen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken gerade.","Schwinge den Vorschlaghammer mit Kraft aus Körpermitte und Oberkörper nach unten Richtung Boden.","Drehe beim Abwärtsschwung deine Hüften und übertrage die Kraft auf den Hammer.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1496.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1496.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b9825ce0-e276-5b5e-b01e-29dad7ca2545', NULL, 'Smith Back Shrug', 'Schulterheben an der Multipresse', 'back', 'traps', 'smith machine', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your arms straight and allow the barbell to hang in front of your thighs. Lift your shoulders straight up towards your ears, squeezing your traps at the top. Hold for a moment, then lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your arms straight and allow the barbell to hang in front of your thighs.","Lift your shoulders straight up towards your ears, squeezing your traps at the top.","Hold for a moment, then lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und lass die Langhantel vor deinen Oberschenkeln hängen.","Hebe deine Schultern gerade nach oben Richtung Ohren und spanne dabei den Trapezmuskel oben an.","Halte kurz inne und senke die Schultern dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0746.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0746.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('57730a9e-d5a2-5a71-b90b-491bd1557162', NULL, 'Smith Behind Neck Press', 'Nackendrücken an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder level. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lift the bar off the rack and step back, maintaining a stable stance. Lower the bar down to the back of your neck, keeping your elbows pointing forward. Press the bar up overhead until your arms are fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder level.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lift the bar off the rack and step back, maintaining a stable stance.","Lower the bar down to the back of your neck, keeping your elbows pointing forward.","Press the bar up overhead until your arms are fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe der Smith-Maschine so ein, dass sich die Stange auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und trete einen Schritt zurück, wobei du einen stabilen Stand beibehältst.","Senke die Stange bis zum Nacken ab, die Ellbogen zeigen dabei nach vorne.","Drücke die Stange nach oben über den Kopf, bis deine Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0747.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0747.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('08119d77-b47a-55ae-afba-ec57a1aa308b', NULL, 'Smith Bench Press', 'Bankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to chest level. Lie flat on the bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground. Grip the bar with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the bar and lower it towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment when the bar touches your chest. Push the bar back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to chest level.","Lie flat on the bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground.","Grip the bar with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the bar and lower it towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment when the bar touches your chest.","Push the bar back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf Brusthöhe ein.","Lege dich flach auf die Bank, die Füsse fest auf dem Boden.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und senke sie Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne, sobald die Stange deine Brust berührt.","Drücke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition und strecke dabei die Arme vollständig.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0748.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0748.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2fdb506a-f5d1-5942-aa10-e8d63930daea', NULL, 'Smith Bent Knee Good Morning', 'Good Morning mit gebeugten Knien an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward. Place the barbell across your upper back, resting it on your traps. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Lower your torso until it is parallel to the ground, feeling a stretch in your hamstrings. Engage your glutes and hamstrings to raise your torso back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","lower back"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward.","Place the barbell across your upper back, resting it on your traps.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Lower your torso until it is parallel to the ground, feeling a stretch in your hamstrings.","Engage your glutes and hamstrings to raise your torso back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Lege die Langhantel auf deinen oberen Rücken, sodass sie auf dem Trapezmuskel aufliegt.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, während dein Rücken gerade bleibt.","Senke deinen Oberkörper ab, bis er parallel zum Boden ist, und spüre die Dehnung in den Beinbeugern.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinbeuger an, um deinen Oberkörper zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0749.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0749.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4338d7bb-4b1d-591f-8414-5a4dc7b0dc31', NULL, 'Smith Bent Over Row', 'Vorgebeugtes Rudern an der Multipresse', 'back', 'upper back', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height. Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Pull the bar towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height.","Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Pull the bar towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Stange auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Stange.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, während dein Rücken gerade bleibt.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Ziehe die Stange zu deiner unteren Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1359.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1359.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c57fcded-e513-526e-b102-d6b47c82d480', NULL, 'Smith Chair Squat', 'Kniebeuge zum Stuhl an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to a comfortable position. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out. Place the barbell across your upper back, resting it on your traps. Engage your core and keep your chest up as you slowly lower your body by bending your knees and hips. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to a comfortable position.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out.","Place the barbell across your upper back, resting it on your traps.","Engage your core and keep your chest up as you slowly lower your body by bending your knees and hips.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf eine angenehme Höhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Lege die Langhantel auf deinen oberen Rücken, sodass sie auf dem Trapezmuskel aufliegt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte die Brust aufgerichtet, während du deinen Körper langsam absenkst, indem du Knie und Hüften beugst.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder so tief, wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0750.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0750.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ca6feecc-a573-5e4c-81e4-cfc4be7f02e3', NULL, 'Smith Close-Grip Bench Press', 'Enges Bankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the bench with your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart. Lower the barbell towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the bench with your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart.","Lower the barbell towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf der Bank, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Langhantel eng, etwas schmaler als schulterbreit.","Senke die Langhantel Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Langhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0751.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0751.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c750fcb4-804b-5b52-9836-6d323dc5d233', NULL, 'Smith Deadlift', 'Kreuzheben an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward. Bend at the hips and knees, keeping your back straight and chest up, and grip the bar with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and lift the bar by extending your hips and knees, keeping the bar close to your body. Stand up straight, fully extending your hips and knees. Lower the bar back down by bending at the hips and knees, maintaining control and keeping your back straight. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","lower back"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward.","Bend at the hips and knees, keeping your back straight and chest up, and grip the bar with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and lift the bar by extending your hips and knees, keeping the bar close to your body.","Stand up straight, fully extending your hips and knees.","Lower the bar back down by bending at the hips and knees, maintaining control and keeping your back straight.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Stange auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Beuge Hüfte und Knie, während dein Rücken gerade und deine Brust aufgerichtet bleibt, und greife die Stange im Obergriff etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Stange, indem du Hüfte und Knie streckst, wobei die Stange nah am Körper bleibt.","Richte dich vollständig auf, indem du Hüfte und Knie vollständig streckst.","Senke die Stange zurück ab, indem du Hüfte und Knie beugst, kontrolliert und mit geradem Rücken.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0752.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0752.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('00b22526-42fc-5c50-b6d2-8181baefab1e', NULL, 'Smith Decline Bench Press', 'Negativbankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the decline bench to the desired angle. Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the decline bench to the desired angle.","Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Negativbank auf den gewünschten Winkel ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Langhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0753.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0753.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6f6f64dd-5031-59ea-b964-e56844278963', NULL, 'Smith Decline Reverse-Grip Press', 'Negativbankdrücken im Untergriff an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine to a decline position. Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Grasp the barbell with a reverse grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the smith machine to a decline position.","Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Grasp the barbell with a reverse grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine auf eine Negativposition ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Greife die Langhantel im Untergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Langhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0754.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0754.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('470e43ed-3878-531d-8a99-ca45d7327a03', NULL, 'Smith Front Squat (Clean Grip)', 'Frontkniebeuge im Umsetzgriff an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at shoulder height. Stand facing the barbell with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Step back and position the barbell on your front shoulders, resting it on your collarbone and deltoids. Keep your chest up, back straight, and core engaged. Lower your body by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves","core"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at shoulder height.","Stand facing the barbell with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Step back and position the barbell on your front shoulders, resting it on your collarbone and deltoids.","Keep your chest up, back straight, and core engaged.","Lower your body by bending at the knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Langhantel auf Schulterhöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Langhantel.","Greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Tritt zurück und positioniere die Langhantel auf deinen vorderen Schultern, sodass sie auf Schlüsselbein und Deltamuskel aufliegt.","Halte die Brust aufgerichtet, den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du Knie und Hüften beugst, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1433.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1433.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('93d7fa76-0d74-5220-9f91-43b27e4da4d8', NULL, 'Smith Full Squat', 'Tiefe Kniebeuge an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at shoulder height. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out. Step under the bar and position it across your upper back, resting on your traps. Grip the bar with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the bar and take a step back, maintaining a stable stance. Keeping your chest up and core engaged, initiate the squat by pushing your hips back and bending your knees. Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as your flexibility allows. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then drive through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at shoulder height.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out.","Step under the bar and position it across your upper back, resting on your traps.","Grip the bar with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the bar and take a step back, maintaining a stable stance.","Keeping your chest up and core engaged, initiate the squat by pushing your hips back and bending your knees.","Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as your flexibility allows.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then drive through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Langhantel auf Schulterhöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Tritt unter die Stange und positioniere sie auf deinem oberen Rücken, sodass sie auf dem Trapezmuskel aufliegt.","Greife die Stange mit den Händen etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und tritt einen Schritt zurück, wobei du einen stabilen Stand beibehältst.","Halte die Brust aufgerichtet und die Körpermitte angespannt, und leite die Kniebeuge ein, indem du die Hüften nach hinten schiebst und die Knie beugst.","Senke deinen Körper ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es deine Beweglichkeit erlaubt.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3281.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3281.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d17e6315-8b91-5c65-b604-8688818db5b3', NULL, 'Smith Hack Squat', 'Hackenschmidt-Kniebeuge an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the barbell on the smith machine to an appropriate height for your body. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly pointed outwards. Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper traps and shoulders. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and keep your chest up as you unrack the barbell. Take a step back and position your feet slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body down, keeping your chest up and back straight. Continue descending until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the barbell on the smith machine to an appropriate height for your body.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly pointed outwards.","Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper traps and shoulders.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your chest up as you unrack the barbell.","Take a step back and position your feet slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees and lower your body down, keeping your chest up and back straight.","Continue descending until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Langhantel der Smith-Maschine auf eine für deinen Körper passende Höhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Positioniere dich unter der Langhantel, sodass sie auf deinem oberen Trapezmuskel und den Schultern aufliegt.","Greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte die Brust aufgerichtet, während du die Langhantel aus der Ablage hebst.","Tritt einen Schritt zurück und positioniere deine Füsse etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Beuge die Knie und senke deinen Körper ab, während Brust aufgerichtet und Rücken gerade bleiben.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0755.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0755.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('63153189-5d92-5bcb-9451-20a6b83d9b50', NULL, 'Smith Hip Raise', 'Hüftheben an der Multipresse', 'waist', 'abs', 'smith machine', 'Position yourself on the smith machine with your back against the pad and your feet shoulder-width apart. Place your hands on the barbell, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and glutes, then push through your heels to raise your hips off the ground. Continue lifting until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. Hold for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Position yourself on the smith machine with your back against the pad and your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place your hands on the barbell, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and glutes, then push through your heels to raise your hips off the ground.","Continue lifting until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","Hold for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your hips back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich an der Smith-Maschine, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen schulterbreit.","Lege deine Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit auf die Langhantel.","Spanne Körpermitte und Gesäss an und drücke dich dann über die Fersen ab, um die Hüften vom Boden abzuheben.","Hebe weiter an, bis dein Körper eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern bildet.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Hüften dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0756.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0756.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('28a14e8b-295a-5d0d-9136-45b5ccf6cac8', NULL, 'Smith Incline Bench Press', 'Schrägbankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the bench to a 30-45 degree incline. Sit on the bench with your back flat against the pad and feet firmly on the ground. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your upper chest, keeping your elbows slightly tucked in. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Adjust the bench to a 30-45 degree incline.","Sit on the bench with your back flat against the pad and feet firmly on the ground.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your upper chest, keeping your elbows slightly tucked in.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Bank auf eine Neigung von 30-45 Grad ein.","Setze dich auf die Bank, den Rücken flach am Polster und die Füsse fest auf dem Boden.","Greife die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam Richtung obere Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei leicht angewinkelt am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Langhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition, wobei du die Arme vollständig streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0757.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0757.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5f8208a5-2638-537d-aea7-916067c668ab', NULL, 'Smith Incline Reverse-Grip Press', 'Schrägbankdrücken im Untergriff an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat of the smith machine to a comfortable incline angle. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip that is slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the bar and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment when the bar is just above your chest. Push the bar back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat of the smith machine to a comfortable incline angle.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip that is slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the bar and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment when the bar is just above your chest.","Push the bar back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Smith-Maschine auf einen angenehmen Neigungswinkel ein.","Setze dich auf die Maschine, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne, sobald sich die Stange knapp über deiner Brust befindet.","Drücke die Stange zurück in die Ausgangsposition und strecke dabei die Arme vollständig.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0758.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0758.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('846e4c28-9c4e-5078-b1a5-1d105b138684', NULL, 'Smith Incline Shoulder Raises', 'Schulterheben auf der Schrägbank an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'serratus anterior', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine to an incline position. Stand facing the machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and core engaged. Raise the barbell up towards the ceiling, leading with your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'deltoids', '["deltoids","trapezius"]', '["Adjust the smith machine to an incline position.","Stand facing the machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and core engaged.","Raise the barbell up towards the ceiling, leading with your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine auf eine Schrägposition ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Maschine.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Hebe die Langhantel Richtung Decke an, wobei die Ellbogen die Bewegung anführen.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Langhantel dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0759.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0759.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2d35ddcb-b032-527a-95ec-1330170b3280', NULL, 'Smith Leg Press', 'Beinpresse an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat and footplate of the smith machine to a comfortable position. Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate. Grasp the handles or sides of the machine for stability. Push the footplate away from you by extending your legs, keeping your back against the backrest. Pause for a moment at the fully extended position. Slowly bend your knees and lower the footplate back towards you, returning to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat and footplate of the smith machine to a comfortable position.","Sit on the machine with your back against the backrest and your feet shoulder-width apart on the footplate.","Grasp the handles or sides of the machine for stability.","Push the footplate away from you by extending your legs, keeping your back against the backrest.","Pause for a moment at the fully extended position.","Slowly bend your knees and lower the footplate back towards you, returning to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle Sitz und Fussplatte der Smith-Maschine auf eine angenehme Position ein.","Setze dich auf die Maschine, mit dem Rücken an der Rückenlehne und den Füssen schulterbreit auf der Fussplatte.","Greife die Griffe oder Seiten der Maschine für mehr Stabilität.","Drücke die Fussplatte von dir weg, indem du die Beine streckst, während dein Rücken an der Rückenlehne bleibt.","Halte kurz inne in der vollständig gestreckten Position.","Beuge die Knie langsam und senke die Fussplatte zurück zu dir, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0760.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0760.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c84bc2e1-edcc-5958-ab1a-6dd8e80da6a3', NULL, 'Smith Low Bar Squat', 'Low-Bar-Kniebeuge an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at a height that allows you to comfortably rest it on your upper back. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned outwards. Step under the bar and position it across your upper back, resting it on your traps. Grip the bar with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the bar by straightening your legs and stepping back from the rack. Take a deep breath and brace your core. Initiate the squat by pushing your hips back and bending your knees. Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement. Drive through your heels to stand back up, extending your hips and knees. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at a height that allows you to comfortably rest it on your upper back.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned outwards.","Step under the bar and position it across your upper back, resting it on your traps.","Grip the bar with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the bar by straightening your legs and stepping back from the rack.","Take a deep breath and brace your core.","Initiate the squat by pushing your hips back and bending your knees.","Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Keep your chest up and your back straight throughout the movement.","Drive through your heels to stand back up, extending your hips and knees.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Langhantel auf eine Höhe ein, die es dir erlaubt, sie bequem auf deinem oberen Rücken abzulegen.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Tritt unter die Stange und positioniere sie auf deinem oberen Rücken, sodass sie auf dem Trapezmuskel aufliegt.","Greife die Stange mit den Händen etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage, indem du die Beine streckst und einen Schritt zurücktrittst.","Atme tief ein und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Leite die Kniebeuge ein, indem du die Hüften nach hinten schiebst und die Knie beugst.","Senke deinen Körper ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte während der gesamten Bewegung die Brust aufgerichtet und den Rücken gerade.","Drücke dich über die Fersen ab, um dich wieder aufzurichten, und strecke dabei Hüften und Knie.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1434.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1434.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('62f72659-0cd8-529e-b9e6-a9ec9d375eab', NULL, 'Smith Machine Bicep Curl', 'Bizepscurl an der Multipresse', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to be at waist level. Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the bar with an underhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your elbows close to your sides and your upper arms stationary. Exhale and curl the bar up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to be at waist level.","Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the bar with an underhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your elbows close to your sides and your upper arms stationary.","Exhale and curl the bar up towards your shoulders, contracting your biceps.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Smith-Maschine.","Greife die Stange im Untergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper und die Oberarme ruhig.","Atme aus und ziehe die Stange Richtung Schultern hoch, während du den Bizeps anspannst.","Halte kurz inne oben und spanne den Bizeps zusätzlich an.","Atme ein und senke die Stange langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1683.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1683.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('16f5efa5-ce88-5e8f-8e18-57138867fb3a', NULL, 'Smith Machine Decline Close-Grip Bench Press', 'Enges Negativbankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the bench on the smith machine to a decline position. Lie down on the bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground. Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Pause for a moment when the barbell is just above your chest. Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the bench on the smith machine to a decline position.","Lie down on the bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground.","Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Pause for a moment when the barbell is just above your chest.","Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Bank der Smith-Maschine auf eine Negativposition ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse fest auf dem Boden.","Greife die Langhantel eng, etwas schmaler als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne, sobald sich die Langhantel knapp über deiner Brust befindet.","Drücke die Langhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition und strecke dabei die Arme vollständig.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1625.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1625.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e40d6d30-6116-5955-809b-1a7b94dd8af8', NULL, 'Smith Machine Incline Triceps Extension', 'Schrägbank-Trizepsstrecken an der Multipresse', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder height. Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Extend your arms fully, lifting the bar off the rack and holding it directly above your chest. Lower the bar slowly towards your forehead, keeping your elbows close to your head. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the bar back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Adjust the seat of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder height.","Sit on the bench with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Extend your arms fully, lifting the bar off the rack and holding it directly above your chest.","Lower the bar slowly towards your forehead, keeping your elbows close to your head.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the bar back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle den Sitz der Smith-Maschine so ein, dass sich die Stange auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Setze dich auf die Bank, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Strecke die Arme vollständig, hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und halte sie direkt über deiner Brust.","Senke die Stange langsam Richtung Stirn ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Kopf.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Stange dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1752.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1752.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5a5f98e5-f5b0-5ba9-9b39-543ee3d76111', NULL, 'Smith Machine Reverse Decline Close-Grip Bench Press', 'Enges Negativbankdrücken im Untergriff an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine to a decline position. Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the smith machine to a decline position.","Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Grasp the barbell with a close grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the barbell back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine auf eine Negativposition ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Greife die Langhantel eng, etwas schmaler als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Langhantel dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1626.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1626.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2dad4703-9567-50c9-ada9-34eb5d6c30b1', NULL, 'Smith Narrow Row', 'Enges Rudern an der Multipresse', 'back', 'upper back', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and your chest up as you pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly narrower than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and your chest up as you pull the handles towards your body, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the peak of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf der Maschine, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas schmaler als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Brust aufgerichtet, während du die Griffe zum Körper ziehst und dabei die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne am Höhepunkt der Bewegung und lass die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0761.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0761.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f0668e6c-fa6a-55da-b461-35a50159e3ef', NULL, 'Smith One Arm Row', 'Einarmiges Rudern an der Multipresse', 'back', 'upper back', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to waist level. Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Grasp the bar with one hand using an overhand grip, with your palm facing down. Keep your elbow close to your body and pull the bar towards your waist, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the bar back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to waist level.","Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Grasp the bar with one hand using an overhand grip, with your palm facing down.","Keep your elbow close to your body and pull the bar towards your waist, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the bar back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch to the other arm."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Smith-Maschine.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, während dein Rücken gerade bleibt.","Greife die Stange mit einer Hand im Obergriff, die Handfläche zeigt nach unten.","Halte den Ellbogen nah am Körper und ziehe die Stange zu deiner Hüfte, während du die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann den Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1360.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1360.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1413d5de-287e-5d88-8d69-0b7f18fd98d4', NULL, 'Smith One Leg Floor Calf Raise', 'Einbeiniges Wadenheben am Boden an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Position yourself on the floor under the smith machine bar, facing away from the machine. Place the balls of your feet on a raised surface, such as a weight plate or block. Position the smith machine bar across your lower legs, just above your ankles. Hold onto the bar with your hands for stability. Raise your heels off the ground by extending your ankles, lifting your body up. Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Position yourself on the floor under the smith machine bar, facing away from the machine.","Place the balls of your feet on a raised surface, such as a weight plate or block.","Position the smith machine bar across your lower legs, just above your ankles.","Hold onto the bar with your hands for stability.","Raise your heels off the ground by extending your ankles, lifting your body up.","Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich auf dem Boden unter der Stange der Smith-Maschine, mit dem Rücken zur Maschine.","Stelle deine Fussballen auf eine erhöhte Fläche, zum Beispiel eine Gewichtsscheibe oder einen Block.","Positioniere die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf deinen Unterschenkeln, knapp über den Fussgelenken.","Halte dich für mehr Stabilität mit den Händen an der Stange fest.","Hebe deine Fersen vom Boden ab, indem du die Fussgelenke streckst und deinen Körper nach oben hebst.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke deine Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1393.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1393.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c7b77265-d420-5198-8a81-39c80fbed87e', NULL, 'Smith Rear Delt Row', 'Rudern für die hintere Schulter an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and your core engaged as you pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'trapezius', '["trapezius","rhomboids","biceps"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the machine with your chest against the pad and your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and your core engaged as you pull the handles towards your chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top of the movement, then slowly release the handles back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich auf der Maschine, mit der Brust am Polster und den Füssen flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt, während du die Griffe zur Brust ziehst und dabei die Schulterblätter zusammenziehst.","Halte kurz inne oben und lass die Griffe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0762.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0762.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('30b6ef25-409c-51d1-9006-e7e223fa0db7', NULL, 'Smith Reverse Calf Raises', 'Umgekehrtes Wadenheben an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine bar to a height just below your shoulders. Stand facing the bar with your feet hip-width apart and toes pointing forward. Place the balls of your feet on the edge of a step or platform, with your heels hanging off. Hold onto the bar for support, keeping your back straight and core engaged. Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the smith machine bar to a height just below your shoulders.","Stand facing the bar with your feet hip-width apart and toes pointing forward.","Place the balls of your feet on the edge of a step or platform, with your heels hanging off.","Hold onto the bar for support, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf eine Höhe knapp unter deinen Schultern ein.","Stelle dich mit hüftbreiten Füssen vor die Stange, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Stelle deine Fussballen auf die Kante einer Stufe oder Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei.","Halte dich zur Unterstützung an der Stange fest, während dein Rücken gerade und deine Körpermitte angespannt bleibt.","Hebe deine Fersen so hoch wie möglich und verlagere dein Körpergewicht auf die Fussballen.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke deine Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0763.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0763.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7cbf9ea1-8eed-5696-9d13-6450c6063783', NULL, 'Smith Reverse Calf Raises', 'Umgekehrtes Wadenheben an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine bar to a height just below your shoulders. Stand facing the bar with your feet hip-width apart and toes pointing forward. Place the balls of your feet on the edge of a step or platform, with your heels hanging off. Hold onto the bar for support. Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body up onto your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Adjust the smith machine bar to a height just below your shoulders.","Stand facing the bar with your feet hip-width apart and toes pointing forward.","Place the balls of your feet on the edge of a step or platform, with your heels hanging off.","Hold onto the bar for support.","Raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body up onto your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf eine Höhe knapp unter deinen Schultern ein.","Stelle dich mit hüftbreiten Füssen vor die Stange, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Stelle deine Fussballen auf die Kante einer Stufe oder Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei.","Halte dich zur Unterstützung an der Stange fest.","Hebe deine Fersen so hoch wie möglich und hebe deinen Körper auf die Zehenspitzen.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke deine Fersen dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1394.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1394.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('637b5f6a-4620-5cd7-931e-a75a9d84433e', NULL, 'Smith Reverse-Grip Bent Over Row', 'Vorgebeugtes Rudern im Untergriff an der Multipresse', 'back', 'upper back', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height. Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Grasp the bar with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Pull the bar towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the bar at hip height.","Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Grasp the bar with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Pull the bar towards your lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Smith-Maschine mit der Stange auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Stange.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, während dein Rücken gerade bleibt.","Greife die Stange im Untergriff, die Hände schulterbreit.","Ziehe die Stange zu deiner unteren Brust und ziehe dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Stange dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1361.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1361.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('a2cf46dd-ac72-543d-a244-ade2dd3136dd', NULL, 'Smith Reverse-Grip Press', 'Drücken im Untergriff an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to chest level. Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Step back and position yourself with a slight bend in your knees. Keep your chest up and core engaged throughout the exercise. Lower the bar towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the bar back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the height of the smith machine bar to chest level.","Stand facing the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Step back and position yourself with a slight bend in your knees.","Keep your chest up and core engaged throughout the exercise.","Lower the bar towards your chest, keeping your elbows tucked in.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push the bar back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf Brusthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor die Stange.","Greife die Stange im Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Tritt zurück und positioniere dich mit leicht gebeugten Knien.","Halte während der gesamten Übung die Brust aufgerichtet und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Senke die Stange Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei nah am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten und drücke die Stange dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0764.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0764.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('590ac212-007c-5628-86f9-dc0acd9d45ce', NULL, 'Smith Seated One Leg Calf Raise', 'Einbeiniges Wadenheben im Sitzen an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the footrest. Place one leg on the footrest and keep the other leg off the footrest. Using your calf muscles, raise your heel as high as possible. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings"]', '["Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet on the footrest.","Place one leg on the footrest and keep the other leg off the footrest.","Using your calf muscles, raise your heel as high as possible.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heel back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Setze dich auf die Maschine, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen auf der Fussstütze.","Stelle ein Bein auf die Fussstütze und halte das andere Bein davon fern.","Hebe deine Ferse mithilfe deiner Wadenmuskulatur so hoch wie möglich an.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke deine Ferse dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1395.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1395.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5f803e57-4862-5db2-97cb-c01c7456005d', NULL, 'Smith Seated Shoulder Press', 'Schulterdrücken im Sitzen an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height so that the handles are at shoulder level. Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the floor. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and lift them off the supports, extending your arms fully. Lower the handles down to shoulder level, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Press the handles up overhead until your arms are fully extended. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height so that the handles are at shoulder level.","Sit on the machine with your back against the pad and your feet flat on the floor.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip and lift them off the supports, extending your arms fully.","Lower the handles down to shoulder level, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Press the handles up overhead until your arms are fully extended.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the handles back down to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe so ein, dass sich die Griffe auf Schulterhöhe befinden.","Setze dich auf die Maschine, mit dem Rücken am Polster und den Füssen flach auf dem Boden.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff und hebe sie aus der Ablage, wobei du die Arme vollständig streckst.","Senke die Griffe auf Schulterhöhe ab, die Ellbogen bleiben dabei leicht gebeugt.","Drücke die Griffe nach oben über den Kopf, bis deine Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte kurz inne oben und senke die Griffe dann langsam zurück auf Schulterhöhe.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0765.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0765.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c0c6ed9a-1f5a-58ae-9550-4070b40d1736', NULL, 'Smith Seated Wrist Curl', 'Handgelenkscurl im Sitzen an der Multipresse', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'smith machine', 'Sit on a bench in front of a Smith machine with your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off. Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the barbell towards your forearms. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","brachialis"]', '["Sit on a bench in front of a Smith machine with your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the barbell with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Rest your forearms on your thighs, allowing your wrists to hang off.","Slowly curl your wrists upward, bringing the barbell towards your forearms.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich mit flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen auf eine Bank vor einer Smith-Maschine.","Fasse die Langhantel im Untergriff, Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Lege deine Unterarme auf die Oberschenkel, sodass die Handgelenke frei hängen.","Rolle die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und bringe die Langhantel zu den Unterarmen.","Halte kurz oben inne und senke die Langhantel dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1426.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1426.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2003c4d5-23aa-5503-b5e7-c8f0cbd0abeb', NULL, 'Smith Shoulder Press', 'Schulterdrücken an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lift the bar off the rack and position it at shoulder level, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward. Press the bar upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself on the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lift the bar off the rack and position it at shoulder level, with your elbows bent and palms facing forward.","Press the bar upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the bar back down to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und positioniere dich an der Smith-Maschine mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen.","Fasse die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und bringe sie auf Schulterhöhe, die Ellbogen gebeugt und die Handflächen zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke die Stange nach oben, bis deine Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Stange dann langsam wieder auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0766.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0766.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d2a6610a-2dca-5d8d-bfce-49c8031fbd55', NULL, 'Smith Shrug', 'Schulterheben an der Multipresse', 'back', 'traps', 'smith machine', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your arms straight and your shoulders relaxed. Lift your shoulders up towards your ears, squeezing your traps at the top. Hold for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your arms straight and your shoulders relaxed.","Lift your shoulders up towards your ears, squeezing your traps at the top.","Hold for a moment, then slowly lower your shoulders back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Fasse die Langhantel im Obergriff, Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte die Arme gestreckt und die Schultern entspannt.","Ziehe die Schultern in Richtung Ohren hoch und spanne den Trapezmuskel oben an.","Halte kurz inne und senke die Schultern dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0767.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0767.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('89cb9e72-d03b-5d45-ac43-8e2dbe8f0b53', NULL, 'Smith Single Leg Split Squat', 'Einbeiniger Split Squat an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'smith machine', 'Stand in front of the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Place one foot behind you on a bench or step, with your toes pointing forward. Hold onto the smith machine bar for stability. Bend your front knee and lower your body down into a lunge position, keeping your back straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Stand in front of the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place one foot behind you on a bench or step, with your toes pointing forward.","Hold onto the smith machine bar for stability.","Bend your front knee and lower your body down into a lunge position, keeping your back straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen vor die Smith-Maschine.","Stelle einen Fuss hinter dir auf eine Bank oder Stufe, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Halte dich zur Stabilisierung an der Stange der Smith-Maschine fest.","Beuge das vordere Knie und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die vordere Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Beine."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0768.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0768.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b2652cdc-b16e-5497-9e59-2c9da7ae38f7', NULL, 'Smith Sprint Lunge', 'Sprint-Ausfallschritt an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at hip height. Stand facing away from the machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Step back with your right foot and place it on the barbell, resting the top of your foot on the bar. Bend your left knee and lower your body into a lunge position, keeping your back straight. Push through your left heel to return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side, stepping back with your left foot. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at hip height.","Stand facing away from the machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Step back with your right foot and place it on the barbell, resting the top of your foot on the bar.","Bend your left knee and lower your body into a lunge position, keeping your back straight.","Push through your left heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side, stepping back with your left foot.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Langhantel an der Smith-Maschine auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zur Maschine hin, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Trete mit dem rechten Fuss zurück und lege ihn auf die Langhantel, sodass der Spann auf der Stange ruht.","Beuge das linke Knie und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Drücke dich über die linke Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite, indem du mit dem linken Fuss zurücktrittst.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0769.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0769.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d8582f38-a7c5-52be-a79a-b4a375b130a4', NULL, 'Smith Squat', 'Kniebeuge an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at an appropriate height for your squat. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out. Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper traps and shoulders. Grip the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and unrack the barbell, stepping back to clear the rack. Keeping your chest up and back straight, initiate the squat by bending at the hips and knees. Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then drive through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at an appropriate height for your squat.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes slightly turned out.","Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper traps and shoulders.","Grip the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and unrack the barbell, stepping back to clear the rack.","Keeping your chest up and back straight, initiate the squat by bending at the hips and knees.","Lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground or slightly below.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then drive through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Langhantel an der Smith-Maschine auf eine für deine Kniebeuge passende Höhe ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Positioniere dich unter der Langhantel, sodass sie auf deinem oberen Trapezmuskel und den Schultern aufliegt.","Fasse die Langhantel breit, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage, indem du einen Schritt zurücktrittst.","Halte die Brust hoch und den Rücken gerade und leite die Kniebeuge ein, indem du Hüfte und Knie beugst.","Senke deinen Körper ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darunter.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0770.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0770.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('83d858d7-4d57-5767-b5df-2e529d6ea504', NULL, 'Smith Standing Back Wrist Curl', 'Umgekehrter Handgelenkscurl im Stehen an der Multipresse', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'smith machine', 'Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your body. Slowly curl your wrists upwards, bringing the barbell towards your body. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps"]', '["Stand facing the smith machine with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and your elbows close to your body.","Slowly curl your wrists upwards, bringing the barbell towards your body.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Gesicht zur Smith-Maschine hin, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Fasse die Langhantel im Obergriff, Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Rolle die Handgelenke langsam nach oben und bringe die Langhantel in Richtung deines Körpers.","Halte kurz oben inne und senke die Langhantel dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0771.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0771.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ced20b25-959f-5dac-a966-7f86ee270a22', NULL, 'Smith Standing Behind Head Military Press', 'Nackendrücken im Stehen an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the seat height of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder level. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lift the bar off the rack and step back, maintaining a stable stance. Position the bar behind your head, resting on your upper traps. Keep your core engaged and your chest lifted throughout the exercise. Press the bar overhead by extending your arms, fully straightening them. Pause briefly at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Adjust the seat height of the smith machine so that the bar is at shoulder level.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lift the bar off the rack and step back, maintaining a stable stance.","Position the bar behind your head, resting on your upper traps.","Keep your core engaged and your chest lifted throughout the exercise.","Press the bar overhead by extending your arms, fully straightening them.","Pause briefly at the top of the movement, then slowly lower the bar back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe der Smith-Maschine so ein, dass sich die Stange auf Schulterhöhe befindet.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Fasse die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Stange aus der Ablage und trete einen Schritt zurück, dabei bleibt dein Stand stabil.","Positioniere die Stange hinter deinem Kopf, sodass sie auf deinem oberen Trapezmuskel aufliegt.","Halte deine Körpermitte während der gesamten Übung angespannt und die Brust hoch.","Drücke die Stange über Kopf, indem du deine Arme vollständig streckst.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Stange dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0772.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0772.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('adfc3c2d-0adc-5f48-8dc0-d634a4f1b0d7', NULL, 'Smith Standing Leg Calf Raise', 'Wadenheben im Stehen an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine bar to a height that allows you to stand with your feet flat on the ground and your shoulders under the bar. Position yourself under the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing forward. Place your hands on the bar for stability. Engage your calves and slowly raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Adjust the smith machine bar to a height that allows you to stand with your feet flat on the ground and your shoulders under the bar.","Position yourself under the bar with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing forward.","Place your hands on the bar for stability.","Engage your calves and slowly raise your heels off the ground, lifting your body up onto your toes.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf eine Höhe ein, bei der du mit flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen und den Schultern unter der Stange stehen kannst.","Positioniere dich unter der Stange, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander und die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Lege deine Hände zur Stabilisierung auf die Stange.","Spanne deine Waden an und hebe langsam deine Fersen vom Boden ab, sodass du auf den Zehenspitzen stehst.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Fersen dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0773.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0773.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a0ad02f1-7533-5573-b49f-a3878744b6c7', NULL, 'Smith Standing Military Press', 'Schulterdrücken im Stehen an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lift the barbell off the rack and bring it down to shoulder level, with your palms facing forward. Press the barbell upward until your arms are fully extended overhead. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to shoulder level. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Lift the barbell off the rack and bring it down to shoulder level, with your palms facing forward.","Press the barbell upward until your arms are fully extended overhead.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to shoulder level.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Fasse die Langhantel im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und bringe sie auf Schulterhöhe, die Handflächen zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke die Langhantel nach oben, bis deine Arme über dem Kopf vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Langhantel dann langsam wieder auf Schulterhöhe ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0774.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0774.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dbbd75b3-b954-5cce-aa98-7ad05621d213', NULL, 'Smith Sumo Squat', 'Sumo-Kniebeuge an der Multipresse', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'smith machine', 'Set up the smith machine with the barbell at hip height. Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing outwards. Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper back and shoulders. Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your body down into a squat position, pushing your hips back and bending your knees. Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Set up the smith machine with the barbell at hip height.","Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart, toes pointing outwards.","Position yourself under the barbell, resting it on your upper back and shoulders.","Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your body down into a squat position, pushing your hips back and bending your knees.","Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Langhantel an der Smith-Maschine auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit den Füssen breiter als schulterbreit hin, die Zehen zeigen nach aussen.","Positioniere dich unter der Langhantel, sodass sie auf deinem oberen Rücken und den Schultern aufliegt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte die Brust hoch, während du deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge absenkst, die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst und die Knie beugst.","Senke dich ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3142.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3142.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('083c7372-7533-5d44-b10f-ee980b7a4911', NULL, 'Smith Toe Raise', 'Zehenheben an der Multipresse', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the smith machine bar to a height that allows you to comfortably stand with your feet flat on the ground. Position yourself under the bar with your shoulders directly below it and your feet shoulder-width apart. Place the balls of your feet on a raised platform or weight plates, with your heels hanging off the edge. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and keep your back straight throughout the exercise. Slowly raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles","shins"]', '["Adjust the smith machine bar to a height that allows you to comfortably stand with your feet flat on the ground.","Position yourself under the bar with your shoulders directly below it and your feet shoulder-width apart.","Place the balls of your feet on a raised platform or weight plates, with your heels hanging off the edge.","Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and keep your back straight throughout the exercise.","Slowly raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Stange der Smith-Maschine auf eine Höhe ein, bei der du bequem mit flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen stehen kannst.","Positioniere dich unter der Stange, die Schultern direkt darunter und die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Stelle die Fussballen auf eine erhöhte Plattform oder Gewichtsscheiben, die Fersen hängen über die Kante hinaus.","Fasse die Stange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte während der gesamten Übung den Rücken gerade.","Hebe deine Fersen langsam so hoch wie möglich an, sodass dein Körpergewicht auf den Fussballen ruht.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Fersen dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1396.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1396.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9bfd8871-1508-52bc-a60a-4dc4099e930b', NULL, 'Smith Upright Row', 'Aufrechtes Rudern an der Multipresse', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'smith machine', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, facing the smith machine. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your back straight and your core engaged. Pull the barbell up towards your chin, leading with your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'traps', '["traps","biceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, facing the smith machine.","Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your back straight and your core engaged.","Pull the barbell up towards your chin, leading with your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen vor die Smith-Maschine.","Fasse die Langhantel im Obergriff, Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Ziehe die Langhantel in Richtung Kinn hoch und führe dabei mit den Ellbogen.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Langhantel dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0775.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0775.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0c27fa55-c411-5000-a346-68bcebbf6bef', NULL, 'Smith Wide-Grip Bench Press', 'Weites Bankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the bench to a comfortable position on the smith machine. Lie down on the bench with your feet flat on the ground. Grasp the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows out to the sides. Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest. Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the bench to a comfortable position on the smith machine.","Lie down on the bench with your feet flat on the ground.","Grasp the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows out to the sides.","Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest.","Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Bank an der Smith-Maschine auf eine bequeme Position ein.","Lege dich mit flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen auf die Bank.","Fasse die Langhantel breit, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam in Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen zeigen dabei zur Seite.","Halte kurz inne, sobald die Langhantel deine Brust berührt.","Drücke die Langhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition, bis deine Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1308.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1308.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('14f06f7b-ec67-5d21-ae29-d53cfe6f51b5', NULL, 'Smith Wide-Grip Decline Bench Press', 'Weites Negativbankdrücken an der Multipresse', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'smith machine', 'Adjust the decline bench to the desired angle. Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Grasp the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows pointed outwards. Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest. Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Adjust the decline bench to the desired angle.","Lie down on the bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Grasp the barbell with a wide grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Unrack the barbell and lower it slowly towards your chest, keeping your elbows pointed outwards.","Pause for a moment when the barbell touches your chest.","Push the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Negativbank auf den gewünschten Winkel ein.","Lege dich auf die Bank, die Füsse unter den Fusspolstern fixiert.","Fasse die Langhantel breit, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hebe die Langhantel aus der Ablage und senke sie langsam in Richtung Brust ab, die Ellbogen zeigen dabei nach aussen.","Halte kurz inne, sobald die Langhantel deine Brust berührt.","Drücke die Langhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition, bis deine Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1309.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1309.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5deb82e7-d47c-55f0-9218-d62e13649973', NULL, 'Snatch Pull', 'Reisszug', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and the barbell on the ground in front of you. Bend your knees and hinge at the hips to lower into a squat position, gripping the barbell with an overhand grip. Keep your back straight and chest up as you drive through your heels to lift the barbell off the ground, extending your hips and knees. As the barbell reaches hip level, explosively pull it upwards, shrugging your shoulders and pulling your elbows high and to the sides. As the barbell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it, pulling yourself into a deep squat position. Catch the barbell overhead with your arms fully extended and your knees bent. Stand up by extending your hips and knees, keeping the barbell overhead. Lower the barbell back down to the starting position by reversing the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and the barbell on the ground in front of you.","Bend your knees and hinge at the hips to lower into a squat position, gripping the barbell with an overhand grip.","Keep your back straight and chest up as you drive through your heels to lift the barbell off the ground, extending your hips and knees.","As the barbell reaches hip level, explosively pull it upwards, shrugging your shoulders and pulling your elbows high and to the sides.","As the barbell reaches its highest point, quickly drop underneath it, pulling yourself into a deep squat position.","Catch the barbell overhead with your arms fully extended and your knees bent.","Stand up by extending your hips and knees, keeping the barbell overhead.","Lower the barbell back down to the starting position by reversing the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Langhantel liegt vor dir auf dem Boden.","Beuge die Knie und klappe in der Hüfte ein, um dich in eine Kniebeuge-Position abzusenken, und fasse die Langhantel im Obergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Brust hoch, während du dich über die Fersen abdrückst, um die Langhantel vom Boden zu heben, indem du Hüfte und Knie streckst.","Sobald die Langhantel Hüfthöhe erreicht, ziehe sie explosiv nach oben, ziehe die Schultern hoch und führe die Ellbogen hoch und zur Seite.","Sobald die Langhantel ihren höchsten Punkt erreicht, tauche schnell darunter und ziehe dich in eine tiefe Kniebeuge-Position.","Fange die Langhantel über Kopf auf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und die Knie gebeugt.","Stehe auf, indem du Hüfte und Knie streckst, und halte die Langhantel dabei über Kopf.","Senke die Langhantel zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab, indem du die Bewegung umkehrst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0776.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0776.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bc819a26-4501-59f3-9d2b-37eb51561c44', NULL, 'Spell Caster', 'Kurzhantel-Rumpfdrehung (Spellcaster)', 'waist', 'abs', 'dumbbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the waist, keeping your back straight. Extend your arm with the dumbbell towards the opposite foot, rotating your torso as you do so. Return to the starting position and repeat on the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in one hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the waist, keeping your back straight.","Extend your arm with the dumbbell towards the opposite foot, rotating your torso as you do so.","Return to the starting position and repeat on the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte eine Kurzhantel in einer Hand.","Beuge die Knie leicht und klappe in der Hüfte nach vorne, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Strecke den Arm mit der Kurzhantel in Richtung des gegenüberliegenden Fusses und drehe dabei deinen Oberkörper.","Kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0777.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0777.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ecae7505-cece-5f55-928a-4f20472422b9', NULL, 'Sphinx', 'Sphinx-Dehnung', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on the ground with your forearms flat on the floor, elbows directly under your shoulders. Engage your core and lift your chest off the ground, keeping your forearms and toes on the floor. Hold this position for a few seconds, making sure to keep your neck in a neutral position. Slowly lower your chest back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Lie face down on the ground with your forearms flat on the floor, elbows directly under your shoulders.","Engage your core and lift your chest off the ground, keeping your forearms and toes on the floor.","Hold this position for a few seconds, making sure to keep your neck in a neutral position.","Slowly lower your chest back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Boden, die Unterarme flach aufliegend und die Ellbogen direkt unter den Schultern.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die Brust vom Boden ab, während Unterarme und Zehen am Boden bleiben.","Halte diese Position einige Sekunden lang und achte darauf, den Nacken in einer neutralen Position zu halten.","Senke deine Brust langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1362.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1362.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('dc4c85a9-fefb-57f1-bc89-9b13b7b95cfd', NULL, 'Spider Crawl Push-up', 'Spinnen-Liegestütz', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Bring your right knee towards your right elbow, keeping it off the ground. As you bring your right knee back, simultaneously lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows. Push back up to the starting position and repeat with your left knee towards your left elbow. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","chest","shoulders"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Bring your right knee towards your right elbow, keeping it off the ground.","As you bring your right knee back, simultaneously lower your body towards the ground by bending your elbows.","Push back up to the starting position and repeat with your left knee towards your left elbow.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer Liegestützposition, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit und die Füsse zusammen.","Bringe dein rechtes Knie in Richtung des rechten Ellbogens, ohne den Boden zu berühren.","Während du das rechte Knie zurückführst, senke gleichzeitig deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole mit dem linken Knie in Richtung des linken Ellbogens.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0778.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0778.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('625cac18-f498-5668-ae31-064516e12e8c', NULL, 'Spine Stretch', 'Wirbelsäulendehnung', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Place your hands on the ground behind you, fingers pointing towards your body. Engage your core and slowly lean back, keeping your back straight. Continue leaning back until you feel a stretch in your spine. Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Place your hands on the ground behind you, fingers pointing towards your body.","Engage your core and slowly lean back, keeping your back straight.","Continue leaning back until you feel a stretch in your spine.","Hold the stretch for a few seconds, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Stütze deine Hände hinter dir auf dem Boden ab, die Finger zeigen zu deinem Körper.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und lehne dich langsam zurück, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Lehne dich weiter zurück, bis du eine Dehnung in der Wirbelsäule spürst.","Halte die Dehnung einige Sekunden lang und kehre dann langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1363.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1363.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b1b91bff-9b6f-59c9-9c5d-58743fea861a', NULL, 'Spine Twist', 'Wirbelsäulendrehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you. Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the ground, hip-width apart. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engage your abs and slowly twist your torso to the right, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee. Pause for a moment at the end of the twist, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat the twist to the left side, bringing your left elbow towards your right knee. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on the ground with your legs extended in front of you.","Bend your knees and place your feet flat on the ground, hip-width apart.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engage your abs and slowly twist your torso to the right, bringing your right elbow towards your left knee.","Pause for a moment at the end of the twist, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat the twist to the left side, bringing your left elbow towards your right knee.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Beuge die Knie und stelle die Füsse hüftbreit auseinander flach auf den Boden.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und drehe deinen Oberkörper langsam nach rechts, wobei du den rechten Ellbogen zum linken Knie führst.","Halte am Ende der Drehung kurz inne und kehre dann langsam zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Drehung zur linken Seite, wobei du den linken Ellbogen zum rechten Knie führst.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2329.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2329.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('60527de2-0cd5-5ac2-814a-aa8857c2afaa', NULL, 'Split Squats', 'Split-Squats', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Take a step forward with one foot and place it about two feet in front of the other foot. Lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight. Continue lowering until your front thigh is parallel to the ground, and your back knee is hovering just above the ground. Pause for a moment, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Take a step forward with one foot and place it about two feet in front of the other foot.","Lower your body by bending your knees and hips, keeping your back straight.","Continue lowering until your front thigh is parallel to the ground, and your back knee is hovering just above the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push through your front heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs and repeat."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin.","Mache mit einem Fuss einen grossen Schritt nach vorne, sodass sich ein deutlicher Abstand zwischen deinen Füssen ergibt.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du Knie und Hüfte beugst, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis dein vorderer Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden ist und dein hinteres Knie knapp über dem Boden schwebt.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die vordere Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Beine."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2368.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2368.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b8539169-75a5-52ed-8058-7c8d05a2c1b6', NULL, 'Squat Jerk', 'Squat-Stoss', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'barbell', 'Start with the barbell resting on your shoulders, with your feet shoulder-width apart. Lower your body into a squat position, keeping your chest up and your knees tracking over your toes. As you reach the bottom of the squat, explosively drive through your legs and push the barbell overhead. As the barbell reaches its peak, quickly drop into a split position, with one foot forward and one foot back. Catch the barbell overhead with your arms fully extended and your back knee slightly touching the ground. Stand up from the split position, bringing your feet back together. Lower the barbell back to your shoulders and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves","core"]', '["Start with the barbell resting on your shoulders, with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Lower your body into a squat position, keeping your chest up and your knees tracking over your toes.","As you reach the bottom of the squat, explosively drive through your legs and push the barbell overhead.","As the barbell reaches its peak, quickly drop into a split position, with one foot forward and one foot back.","Catch the barbell overhead with your arms fully extended and your back knee slightly touching the ground.","Stand up from the split position, bringing your feet back together.","Lower the barbell back to your shoulders and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne mit der Langhantel auf den Schultern, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge ab, halte die Brust hoch und die Knie über den Zehen.","Sobald du den tiefsten Punkt der Kniebeuge erreichst, drücke dich explosiv über die Beine ab und stosse die Langhantel über Kopf.","Sobald die Langhantel ihren höchsten Punkt erreicht, springe schnell in eine Schrittstellung, ein Fuss vorne und ein Fuss hinten.","Fange die Langhantel über Kopf auf, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und das hintere Knie berührt den Boden leicht.","Stehe aus der Schrittstellung auf und bringe die Füsse wieder zusammen.","Senke die Langhantel zurück auf die Schultern ab und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0786.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0786.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('175ffbad-6c51-5eb0-823f-42376a11159e', NULL, 'Squat on Bosu Ball', 'Kniebeuge auf dem Bosu-Ball', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'bosu ball', 'Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side up. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and position yourself on top of the bosu ball. Lower your body down by bending your knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair. Keep your chest up and your weight on your heels. Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Place the bosu ball on the ground with the flat side up.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and position yourself on top of the bosu ball.","Lower your body down by bending your knees and hips, as if sitting back into a chair.","Keep your chest up and your weight on your heels.","Lower yourself until your thighs are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege den Bosu-Ball mit der flachen Seite nach oben auf den Boden.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen auf den Bosu-Ball.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du Knie und Hüfte beugst, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Halte die Brust hoch und dein Gewicht auf den Fersen.","Senke dich ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1705.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1705.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8bb99260-2f66-50f2-ba2e-a772d46ad0cf', NULL, 'Squat to Overhead Reach', 'Kniebeuge mit Überkopf-Streckung', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and toes slightly turned out. Lower your body down into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. As you come up from the squat, extend your arms overhead, reaching towards the ceiling. Return to the starting position by lowering your arms and bending your knees to squat down again. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and toes slightly turned out.","Lower your body down into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","As you come up from the squat, extend your arms overhead, reaching towards the ceiling.","Return to the starting position by lowering your arms and bending your knees to squat down again.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Während du aus der Kniebeuge nach oben kommst, strecke die Arme über den Kopf in Richtung Decke.","Kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück, indem du die Arme absenkst und die Knie erneut beugst, um wieder in die Kniebeuge zu gehen.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1685.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1685.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2e643c3c-825b-5a68-85cd-9a22e12ebae4', NULL, 'Squat to Overhead Reach with Twist', 'Kniebeuge mit Überkopf-Streckung und Drehung', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and toes slightly turned out. Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back. As you come up from the squat, raise your arms overhead and twist your torso to one side. Return to the starting position and repeat the squat, this time twisting your torso to the opposite side. Continue alternating sides with each squat repetition.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and toes slightly turned out.","Lower your body into a squat position by bending your knees and pushing your hips back.","As you come up from the squat, raise your arms overhead and twist your torso to one side.","Return to the starting position and repeat the squat, this time twisting your torso to the opposite side.","Continue alternating sides with each squat repetition."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge ab, indem du die Knie beugst und die Hüfte nach hinten schiebst.","Während du aus der Kniebeuge nach oben kommst, hebe die Arme über den Kopf und drehe deinen Oberkörper zu einer Seite.","Kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole die Kniebeuge, diesmal mit einer Drehung zur entgegengesetzten Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten bei jeder Wiederholung der Kniebeuge fortlaufend."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1686.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1686.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eb850f3e-1aef-56a3-8681-c2ccf73bc67c', NULL, 'Stability Ball Crunch (Full Range Hands Behind Head)', 'Crunch auf dem Gymnastikball (voller Bewegungsradius, Hände hinter dem Kopf)', 'waist', 'abs', 'stability ball', 'Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, slowly curl your upper body forward, bringing your chest towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, slowly curl your upper body forward, bringing your chest towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Gymnastikball, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und die Knie in einem 90°-Winkel gebeugt.","Lege die Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne die Bauchmuskeln an und rolle deinen Oberkörper langsam nach vorne, sodass sich deine Brust den Knien annähert.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke deinen Oberkörper dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2297.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2297.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fb4d6cf5-84dc-5460-9987-82b86ed6d8c2', NULL, 'Stalder Press', 'Stalder-Press', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended overhead. Bend your knees slightly and engage your core. Lower your body down into a squat position while keeping your arms extended overhead. As you squat down, press your arms down towards the ground, engaging your triceps. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the squat, then push through your heels to stand back up while simultaneously raising your arms back overhead. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended overhead.","Bend your knees slightly and engage your core.","Lower your body down into a squat position while keeping your arms extended overhead.","As you squat down, press your arms down towards the ground, engaging your triceps.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the squat, then push through your heels to stand back up while simultaneously raising your arms back overhead.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Arme über dem Kopf gestreckt.","Beuge die Knie leicht und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Senke deinen Körper in eine Kniebeuge ab, während die Arme über dem Kopf gestreckt bleiben.","Während du in die Kniebeuge gehst, drücke die Arme nach unten in Richtung Boden und spanne dabei deinen Trizeps an.","Halte am tiefsten Punkt der Kniebeuge kurz inne und drücke dich dann über die Fersen nach oben, während du gleichzeitig die Arme wieder über den Kopf hebst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3291.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3291.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8b1287e6-05ab-5ef8-b019-35a3ac9c189d', NULL, 'Standing Archer', 'Rudern im Stehen (Archer)', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Extend your arms straight out in front of you at shoulder height, parallel to the ground. Rotate your torso to the right, keeping your arms extended and your back straight. As you rotate, extend your right arm forward and your left arm back, mimicking the motion of drawing a bowstring. Hold the position for a moment, then return to the starting position. Repeat the motion, this time rotating your torso to the left and extending your left arm forward and your right arm back. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Extend your arms straight out in front of you at shoulder height, parallel to the ground.","Rotate your torso to the right, keeping your arms extended and your back straight.","As you rotate, extend your right arm forward and your left arm back, mimicking the motion of drawing a bowstring.","Hold the position for a moment, then return to the starting position.","Repeat the motion, this time rotating your torso to the left and extending your left arm forward and your right arm back.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus, auf Schulterhöhe und parallel zum Boden.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper nach rechts, die Arme bleiben gestreckt und der Rücken gerade.","Strecke während der Drehung den rechten Arm nach vorne und den linken Arm nach hinten, wie beim Spannen eines Bogens.","Halte die Position einen Moment und kehre dann zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal mit einer Drehung nach links, wobei du den linken Arm nach vorne und den rechten Arm nach hinten streckst.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3669.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3669.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('bbb401cc-de98-50d0-a53e-5647ae068303', NULL, 'Standing Behind Neck Press', 'Nackendrücken im Stehen', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'barbell', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell behind your neck with an overhand grip. Keep your back straight and core engaged. Press the barbell overhead by extending your arms, fully extending your elbows. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold the barbell behind your neck with an overhand grip.","Keep your back straight and core engaged.","Press the barbell overhead by extending your arms, fully extending your elbows.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the barbell back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin und halte die Langhantel im Obergriff hinter deinem Nacken.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Drücke die Langhantel über Kopf, indem du die Arme streckst und die Ellbogen vollständig durchdrückst.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Langhantel dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0788.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0788.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6da8cbf4-0124-5575-a78c-00ba7589a84c', NULL, 'Standing Calf Raise (on a Staircase)', 'Wadenheben im Stehen (auf der Treppe)', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Stand on the edge of a step or a sturdy platform with your heels hanging off and your toes on the step. Hold onto a railing or wall for balance if needed. Slowly raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'ankles', '["ankles","feet"]', '["Stand on the edge of a step or a sturdy platform with your heels hanging off and your toes on the step.","Hold onto a railing or wall for balance if needed.","Slowly raise your heels as high as possible, lifting your body weight onto the balls of your feet.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit den Zehen auf die Kante einer Stufe oder einer stabilen Plattform, die Fersen hängen frei.","Halte dich bei Bedarf zum Gleichgewicht an einem Geländer oder einer Wand fest.","Hebe die Fersen langsam so hoch wie möglich an, sodass dein Körpergewicht auf den Fussballen ruht.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke die Fersen dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1490.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1490.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('027eca04-b739-5e91-be3b-64f834e4d284', NULL, 'Standing Calves', 'Wadenheben im Stehen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward. Raise your heels off the ground as high as possible, standing on your toes. Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing forward.","Raise your heels off the ground as high as possible, standing on your toes.","Hold the position for a moment, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Zehen zeigen nach vorne.","Hebe deine Fersen so hoch wie möglich vom Boden ab und stehe auf den Zehenspitzen.","Halte die Position einen Moment und senke die Fersen dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1397.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1397.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('322f59e9-0218-529a-b4d5-0551366931c5', NULL, 'Standing Calves Calf Stretch', 'Wadendehnung im Stehen', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'body weight', 'Stand facing a wall or sturdy object, about an arm''s length away. Place your hands on the wall or object at shoulder height. Step back with one foot, keeping your heel flat on the ground. Bend your front knee slightly and lean forward, keeping your back leg straight. You should feel a stretch in your calf muscle. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Repeat on the other leg.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand facing a wall or sturdy object, about an arm''s length away.","Place your hands on the wall or object at shoulder height.","Step back with one foot, keeping your heel flat on the ground.","Bend your front knee slightly and lean forward, keeping your back leg straight.","You should feel a stretch in your calf muscle.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Repeat on the other leg."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Gesicht zu einer Wand oder einem stabilen Objekt hin, etwa eine Armlänge entfernt.","Lege deine Hände auf Schulterhöhe an die Wand oder das Objekt.","Trete mit einem Fuss zurück, die Ferse bleibt dabei flach auf dem Boden.","Beuge das vordere Knie leicht und lehne dich nach vorne, das hintere Bein bleibt gestreckt.","Du solltest eine Dehnung in der Wadenmuskulatur spüren.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden.","Wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1398.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1398.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('950c53df-b6fd-5bb4-8bfd-d5fb1b6cdb1f', NULL, 'Standing Hamstring and Calf Stretch with Strap', 'Hamstring- und Wadendehnung im Stehen mit Band', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'rope', 'Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart. Hold the strap with both hands and place it around the ball of your foot. Keep your leg straight and slowly lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight. Feel the stretch in your hamstring and calf muscles. Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds. Release the stretch and repeat with the other leg. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'calves', '["calves"]', '["Stand upright with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Hold the strap with both hands and place it around the ball of your foot.","Keep your leg straight and slowly lean forward from your hips, keeping your back straight.","Feel the stretch in your hamstring and calf muscles.","Hold the stretch for 20-30 seconds.","Release the stretch and repeat with the other leg.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich aufrecht hin, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Halte das Band mit beiden Händen und lege es um den Fussballen.","Halte das Bein gestreckt und lehne dich langsam aus der Hüfte nach vorne, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade.","Spüre die Dehnung in Beinbeugern und Waden.","Halte die Dehnung 20-30 Sekunden.","Löse die Dehnung und wiederhole mit dem anderen Bein.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1599.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1599.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('db5a4a12-603c-5941-b9f6-ba783a5eb532', NULL, 'Standing Lateral Stretch', 'Seitliche Dehnung im Stehen', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Extend your arms straight out to the sides, parallel to the ground. Slowly lean your upper body to one side, feeling a stretch in your side and lats. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds. Return to the starting position and repeat on the other side. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","obliques"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Extend your arms straight out to the sides, parallel to the ground.","Slowly lean your upper body to one side, feeling a stretch in your side and lats.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds.","Return to the starting position and repeat on the other side.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Strecke die Arme seitlich aus, parallel zum Boden.","Lehne deinen Oberkörper langsam zu einer Seite und spüre die Dehnung in der Seite und im Latissimus.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden.","Kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole auf der anderen Seite.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0794.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0794.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1ec55f51-0ba0-5f51-bbfd-4240c2c71569', NULL, 'Standing Pelvic Tilt', 'Beckenkippung im Stehen', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Place your hands on your hips or let them hang by your sides. Engage your core muscles and tilt your pelvis forward, pushing your lower back towards the wall behind you. Hold the position for a few seconds, then release and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'abdominals', '["abdominals"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Place your hands on your hips or let them hang by your sides.","Engage your core muscles and tilt your pelvis forward, pushing your lower back towards the wall behind you.","Hold the position for a few seconds, then release and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Lege die Hände auf die Hüften oder lasse sie seitlich hängen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und kippe dein Becken nach vorne, indem du deinen unteren Rücken in Richtung der Wand hinter dir drückst.","Halte die Position einige Sekunden lang, löse sie dann und kehre zur Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1364.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1364.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('18fa28e5-bce1-509f-8605-d09e551c7cc8', NULL, 'Standing Single Leg Curl', 'Einbeiniger Beincurl im Stehen', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart and your hands on your hips. Shift your weight onto your left leg and lift your right foot off the ground, bending your knee. Slowly curl your right heel towards your glutes, squeezing your hamstring. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your right foot back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart and your hands on your hips.","Shift your weight onto your left leg and lift your right foot off the ground, bending your knee.","Slowly curl your right heel towards your glutes, squeezing your hamstring.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your right foot back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stelle dich mit hüftbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Hände auf den Hüften.","Verlagere dein Gewicht auf das linke Bein und hebe den rechten Fuss vom Boden ab, das Knie dabei gebeugt.","Führe deine rechte Ferse langsam in Richtung Gesäss und spanne dabei deinen Beinbeuger an.","Halte oben kurz inne und senke den rechten Fuss dann langsam wieder in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Beine."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0795.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0795.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eb331f57-5ee1-5649-a41c-f19911ffe1eb', NULL, 'Standing Wheel Rollout', 'Ab-Rollout im Stehen', 'waist', 'abs', 'wheel roller', 'Start by standing tall with your feet shoulder-width apart and the wheel roller in front of you. Bend at your waist and slowly roll the wheel forward, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Continue rolling forward until you feel a stretch in your abs and your body is extended as far as possible. Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the wheel back towards your body, returning to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'lower back', '["lower back","shoulders"]', '["Start by standing tall with your feet shoulder-width apart and the wheel roller in front of you.","Bend at your waist and slowly roll the wheel forward, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Continue rolling forward until you feel a stretch in your abs and your body is extended as far as possible.","Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the wheel back towards your body, returning to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe aufrecht mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen, das Ab-Rad liegt vor dir.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte und rolle das Rad langsam nach vorne, dabei bleibt dein Rücken gerade und deine Körpermitte angespannt.","Rolle weiter nach vorne, bis du eine Dehnung in den Bauchmuskeln spürst und dein Körper so weit wie möglich gestreckt ist.","Halte kurz inne und rolle das Rad dann langsam zurück zu deinem Körper, um in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0796.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0796.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2604f44a-6820-5fee-b22d-6dc9cf50a2d3', NULL, 'Star Jump (Male)', 'Hampelmann (männlich)', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms by your sides. Bend your knees slightly and jump up explosively. As you jump, spread your legs and extend your arms out to the sides, forming a star shape with your body. Land softly on the balls of your feet with your knees slightly bent. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms by your sides.","Bend your knees slightly and jump up explosively.","As you jump, spread your legs and extend your arms out to the sides, forming a star shape with your body.","Land softly on the balls of your feet with your knees slightly bent.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreit auseinanderstehenden Füssen hin, die Arme hängen seitlich herab.","Beuge die Knie leicht und springe explosiv nach oben.","Spreize während des Sprungs deine Beine und strecke die Arme seitlich aus, sodass dein Körper eine Sternform bildet.","Lande sanft auf den Fussballen, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3223.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3223.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ac8ea46a-bf5c-5ff2-854a-d4551be6fa21', NULL, 'Stationary Bike Run v. 3', 'Ergometer-Fahren Variante 3', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'stationary bike', 'Adjust the seat height and position to ensure proper alignment. Place your feet on the pedals and secure them with the straps if available. Start pedaling at a comfortable pace. Maintain a steady rhythm and increase the resistance as desired. Engage your core muscles to maintain stability and proper posture. Continue pedaling for the desired duration of your workout. Gradually decrease the resistance and slow down before coming to a complete stop. Stretch your legs and cool down after the workout.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position to ensure proper alignment.","Place your feet on the pedals and secure them with the straps if available.","Start pedaling at a comfortable pace.","Maintain a steady rhythm and increase the resistance as desired.","Engage your core muscles to maintain stability and proper posture.","Continue pedaling for the desired duration of your workout.","Gradually decrease the resistance and slow down before coming to a complete stop.","Stretch your legs and cool down after the workout."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe und Position so ein, dass eine korrekte Ausrichtung gewährleistet ist.","Stelle deine Füsse auf die Pedale und sichere sie bei Bedarf mit den Riemen.","Beginne in einem angenehmen Tempo zu treten.","Halte einen gleichmässigen Rhythmus und erhöhe den Widerstand nach Belieben.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an, um Stabilität und eine korrekte Haltung zu bewahren.","Trete für die gewünschte Dauer deines Trainings weiter.","Verringere den Widerstand allmählich und verlangsame dich, bevor du vollständig zum Stillstand kommst.","Dehne deine Beine und kühle nach dem Training ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2138.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2138.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('926f615b-8e87-5bd7-92bd-d786eaa7736a', NULL, 'Stationary Bike Walk', 'Lockeres Ergometer-Fahren', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the seat height and position on the stationary bike to ensure proper alignment. Place your feet on the pedals and secure them with the straps if available. Start pedaling at a comfortable pace, keeping your back straight and core engaged. Maintain a steady rhythm and increase the resistance level if desired. Continue pedaling for the desired duration of your cardio workout. Cool down by gradually reducing your pace and resistance level. Stretch your leg muscles after the workout to prevent tightness and promote recovery.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position on the stationary bike to ensure proper alignment.","Place your feet on the pedals and secure them with the straps if available.","Start pedaling at a comfortable pace, keeping your back straight and core engaged.","Maintain a steady rhythm and increase the resistance level if desired.","Continue pedaling for the desired duration of your cardio workout.","Cool down by gradually reducing your pace and resistance level.","Stretch your leg muscles after the workout to prevent tightness and promote recovery."]', '["Stelle Sattelhöhe und Position des Heimtrainers so ein, dass eine korrekte Körperhaltung gewährleistet ist.","Setze deine Füsse auf die Pedale und sichere sie, falls vorhanden, mit den Riemen.","Beginne in einem angenehmen Tempo zu treten, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Halte einen gleichmässigen Rhythmus und erhöhe bei Bedarf den Widerstand.","Trete für die gewünschte Dauer deines Cardio-Trainings weiter in die Pedale.","Kühle dich ab, indem du Tempo und Widerstand schrittweise reduzierst.","Dehne deine Beinmuskulatur nach dem Training, um Verspannungen vorzubeugen und die Erholung zu fördern."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0798.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0798.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9f83f48c-5304-52fa-aee0-8d35818b25aa', NULL, 'Straddle Maltese', 'Malteserkreuz gegrätscht', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start by hanging from a pair of rings with your arms fully extended and your body in a straight line. Spread your legs wide apart, forming a straddle position. Engage your core and slowly lower your body until your arms are parallel to the ground. Hold this position for a few seconds, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest"]', '["Start by hanging from a pair of rings with your arms fully extended and your body in a straight line.","Spread your legs wide apart, forming a straddle position.","Engage your core and slowly lower your body until your arms are parallel to the ground.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an ein Ringepaar, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und der Körper in einer geraden Linie.","Spreize deine Beine weit auseinander, sodass eine Grätschposition entsteht.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper langsam ab, bis deine Arme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte diese Position für einige Sekunden, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3314.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3314.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('61d5171a-6e95-5988-8ed9-b1b8b7eaf8a8', NULL, 'Straddle Planche', 'Planche gegrätscht', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your feet spread wide apart. Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, bringing your shoulders over your hands. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to straighten your arms and lift your body back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps","chest"]', '["Start in a push-up position with your hands shoulder-width apart and your feet spread wide apart.","Engage your core and slowly shift your weight forward, bringing your shoulders over your hands.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your hands to straighten your arms and lift your body back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer Liegestützposition mit schulterbreit aufgesetzten Händen und weit gespreizten Füssen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und verlagere dein Gewicht langsam nach vorne, sodass sich deine Schultern über den Händen befinden.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte die Ellbogen dabei nahe am Körper.","Halte kurz inne in der unteren Position, dann drücke dich über die Hände ab, um die Arme zu strecken und deinen Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition zu heben.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3298.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3298.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0db01986-2a1b-5094-8343-913b467be6d0', NULL, 'Straight Leg Outer Hip Abductor', 'Hüftabduktion mit gestrecktem Bein', 'upper legs', 'abductors', 'body weight', 'Lie on your side with your legs straight and stacked on top of each other. Place your bottom arm under your head for support. Engage your core and lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips or leaning backward. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Lie on your side with your legs straight and stacked on top of each other.","Place your bottom arm under your head for support.","Engage your core and lift your top leg as high as possible without rotating your hips or leaning backward.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your leg back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Lege dich auf die Seite, die Beine gestreckt und übereinander liegend.","Lege den unteren Arm zur Unterstützung unter deinen Kopf.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe das obere Bein so hoch wie möglich an, ohne die Hüfte zu drehen oder dich nach hinten zu lehnen.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke dein Bein langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, dann wechsle die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1427.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1427.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('815e6494-6de5-5ed7-8da1-2c826afe28bc', NULL, 'Superman Push-up', 'Superman-Liegestütz', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides. As you lower your body, simultaneously lift your right arm and left leg off the ground, extending them straight out. Pause for a moment at the top, then lower your arm and leg back down while pushing yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time lifting your left arm and right leg. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'core', '["core","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Engage your core and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your sides.","As you lower your body, simultaneously lift your right arm and left leg off the ground, extending them straight out.","Pause for a moment at the top, then lower your arm and leg back down while pushing yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time lifting your left arm and right leg.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Beginne in einer hohen Plank-Position mit den Händen etwas breiter als schulterbreit aufgesetzt und den Füssen zusammen.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte die Ellbogen dabei nahe am Körper.","Während du deinen Körper absenkst, hebe gleichzeitig den rechten Arm und das linke Bein vom Boden ab und strecke sie gerade aus.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke Arm und Bein wieder ab, während du dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition drückst.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal hebst du den linken Arm und das rechte Bein an.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0803.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0803.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('c47998dc-312b-5222-ba82-5aec3c99f2fa', NULL, 'Suspended Abdominal Fallout', 'Bauch-Fallout am Schlingentrainer', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Attach a suspension trainer to a high anchor point and adjust the straps to waist height. Stand facing away from the anchor point and hold the handles with your arms extended in front of you. Lean forward at the waist, keeping your body straight and your core engaged. Lower your body as far as you can while maintaining control and tension in your abs. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly raise your body back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Attach a suspension trainer to a high anchor point and adjust the straps to waist height.","Stand facing away from the anchor point and hold the handles with your arms extended in front of you.","Lean forward at the waist, keeping your body straight and your core engaged.","Lower your body as far as you can while maintaining control and tension in your abs.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly raise your body back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Befestige einen Sling-Trainer an einem hohen Ankerpunkt und stelle die Riemen auf Hüfthöhe ein.","Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zum Ankerpunkt und halte die Griffe mit ausgestreckten Armen vor dir.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Körper gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Senke deinen Körper so weit wie möglich ab, ohne die Kontrolle zu verlieren, und halte die Spannung in der Bauchmuskulatur.","Halte kurz inne unten, dann hebe deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0805.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0805.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1eb1670f-6c9c-5daa-8bef-be4a32a0c88f', NULL, 'Suspended Push-up', 'Liegestütz am Schlingentrainer', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Find a suspension trainer and adjust it to an appropriate height. Stand facing away from the anchor point and hold the handles with an overhand grip. Walk your feet forward, leaning your body forward until your weight is supported by the suspension trainer. Keep your body straight from head to heels, engage your core, and lower your chest towards the handles. Push through your chest and arms to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders","core"]', '["Find a suspension trainer and adjust it to an appropriate height.","Stand facing away from the anchor point and hold the handles with an overhand grip.","Walk your feet forward, leaning your body forward until your weight is supported by the suspension trainer.","Keep your body straight from head to heels, engage your core, and lower your chest towards the handles.","Push through your chest and arms to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle einen Sling-Trainer auf eine geeignete Höhe ein.","Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zum Ankerpunkt und halte die Griffe im Obergriff.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne und lehne deinen Körper vor, bis dein Gewicht vom Sling-Trainer getragen wird.","Halte deinen Körper von Kopf bis Ferse gerade, spanne deine Körpermitte an und senke deine Brust Richtung Griffe ab.","Drücke dich über Brust und Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0806.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0806.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('b601dfca-b4a1-585e-a62a-ceaeaad3f19e', NULL, 'Suspended Reverse Crunch', 'Reverse Crunch am Schlingentrainer', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your knees up towards your chest, curling your pelvis towards your ribcage. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your knees back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your knees up towards your chest, curling your pelvis towards your ribcage.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your knees back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an eine Klimmzugstange, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und die Handflächen von dir weg zeigend.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deine Knie Richtung Brust, indem du dein Becken zum Brustkorb einrollst.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke deine Knie langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0807.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0807.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ee85157a-c46c-5307-b8c3-b6a7567bc381', NULL, 'Suspended Row', 'Rudern am Schlingentrainer', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Set up a suspension trainer at an appropriate height. Stand facing the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart. Hold the handles with an overhand grip, palms facing each other. Lean back, keeping your body straight and your heels on the ground. Pull your chest towards the handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","shoulders"]', '["Set up a suspension trainer at an appropriate height.","Stand facing the anchor point with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Hold the handles with an overhand grip, palms facing each other.","Lean back, keeping your body straight and your heels on the ground.","Pull your chest towards the handles, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower yourself back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle einen Sling-Trainer auf eine geeignete Höhe ein.","Stelle dich mit dem Gesicht zum Ankerpunkt, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Halte die Griffe im Obergriff, die Handflächen zeigen zueinander.","Lehne dich zurück, halte den Körper gerade und die Fersen am Boden.","Ziehe deine Brust zu den Griffen und drücke dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke dich langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0808.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0808.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ac2dc165-dc59-59b5-bbcf-ad502682d55b', NULL, 'Suspended Split Squat', 'Split Squat am Schlingentrainer', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'body weight', 'Stand facing away from a suspension trainer with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend one leg forward and place the top of your foot in the foot cradle of the suspension trainer. Bend your standing leg and lower your body down into a lunge position, keeping your chest up and your knee in line with your toes. Push through your heel to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand facing away from a suspension trainer with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend one leg forward and place the top of your foot in the foot cradle of the suspension trainer.","Bend your standing leg and lower your body down into a lunge position, keeping your chest up and your knee in line with your toes.","Push through your heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch legs."]', '["Stelle dich mit dem Rücken zum Sling-Trainer, die Füsse schulterbreit auseinander.","Strecke ein Bein nach vorne und lege den Fussrücken in die Fussschlaufe des Sling-Trainers.","Beuge dein Standbein und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab, halte dabei die Brust aufrecht und das Knie in Linie mit den Zehen.","Drücke dich über die Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen, dann wechsle das Bein."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0809.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0809.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('85508f31-9669-5293-9750-bb898b3f1af8', NULL, 'Swimmer Kicks v. 2 (Male)', 'Schwimmer-Kicks Variante 2 (männlich)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on a mat with your arms extended overhead. Engage your core and lift your chest and legs off the ground simultaneously. Kick your legs up and down in a fluttering motion, as if you were swimming. Continue kicking for the desired number of repetitions. Lower your chest and legs back down to the starting position.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Lie face down on a mat with your arms extended overhead.","Engage your core and lift your chest and legs off the ground simultaneously.","Kick your legs up and down in a fluttering motion, as if you were swimming.","Continue kicking for the desired number of repetitions.","Lower your chest and legs back down to the starting position."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf eine Matte, die Arme über dem Kopf ausgestreckt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe Brust und Beine gleichzeitig vom Boden ab.","Bewege deine Beine in einer flatternden Auf- und Abbewegung, wie beim Schwimmen.","Führe die Beinbewegung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen fort.","Senke Brust und Beine zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3433.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3433.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2c2cf2b4-1d95-59dc-b589-89fb75e5f71b', NULL, 'Swing 360', '360°-Swing', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent. Hold your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground. Engage your core and swing your arms in a circular motion, rotating your torso as you do so. Continue the circular motion, swinging your arms and rotating your torso for the desired number of repetitions. Remember to breathe throughout the exercise.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and knees slightly bent.","Hold your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground.","Engage your core and swing your arms in a circular motion, rotating your torso as you do so.","Continue the circular motion, swinging your arms and rotating your torso for the desired number of repetitions.","Remember to breathe throughout the exercise."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Halte deine Arme gerade vor dir ausgestreckt, parallel zum Boden.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und schwinge deine Arme kreisförmig, während du deinen Oberkörper mitdrehst.","Führe die kreisförmige Bewegung mit Armschwung und Rumpfdrehung für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen fort.","Denke daran, während der gesamten Übung gleichmässig zu atmen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3318.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3318.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2db3fad0-9b93-50ef-a494-89393969ec55', NULL, 'Three Bench Dip', 'Dip mit drei Bänken', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward. Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands. Bend your elbows and lower your body until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward.","Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands.","Bend your elbows and lower your body until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank und greife mit den Händen die Kante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schiebe dein Gesäss von der Bank und stütze dein Gewicht mit den Händen ab.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper ab, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1753.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1753.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1ea74398-2de8-5caa-a703-4a104ed32521', NULL, 'Tire Flip', 'Reifen-Flip', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'tire', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, facing the tire. Bend your knees and hinge at the hips, lowering into a squat position. Reach down and grab the bottom edge of the tire with both hands, fingers facing towards you. Engage your glutes and leg muscles, and explosively drive through your legs to lift the tire off the ground. As the tire flips over, use your upper body strength to guide it and maintain control. Once the tire is fully flipped, quickly step back and reset your stance. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","core"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, facing the tire.","Bend your knees and hinge at the hips, lowering into a squat position.","Reach down and grab the bottom edge of the tire with both hands, fingers facing towards you.","Engage your glutes and leg muscles, and explosively drive through your legs to lift the tire off the ground.","As the tire flips over, use your upper body strength to guide it and maintain control.","Once the tire is fully flipped, quickly step back and reset your stance.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen vor den Reifen hin.","Beuge deine Knie und klappe in der Hüfte ein, um in eine Kniebeuge-Position abzusinken.","Greife nach unten und fasse die untere Kante des Reifens mit beiden Händen, die Finger zeigen zu dir.","Spanne Gesäss und Beinmuskulatur an und drücke explosiv durch die Beine, um den Reifen vom Boden abzuheben.","Während sich der Reifen dreht, lenke ihn mit deiner Oberkörperkraft und behalte die Kontrolle.","Sobald der Reifen vollständig gekippt ist, trete schnell zurück und nimm erneut deine Ausgangsstellung ein.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2459.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2459.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('705840fa-92cb-5c5e-a1ed-de33a7237c25', NULL, 'Trap Bar Deadlift', 'Kreuzheben mit der Trap Bar', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'trap bar', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and the trap bar on the ground in front of you. Bend at the hips and knees to lower yourself down and grip the handles of the trap bar with an overhand grip. Keep your back straight and chest up as you begin to lift the trap bar off the ground by extending your hips and knees. As you lift, focus on driving through your heels and squeezing your glutes at the top of the movement. Lower the trap bar back down to the ground by bending at the hips and knees, keeping your back straight throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","quadriceps","lower back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and the trap bar on the ground in front of you.","Bend at the hips and knees to lower yourself down and grip the handles of the trap bar with an overhand grip.","Keep your back straight and chest up as you begin to lift the trap bar off the ground by extending your hips and knees.","As you lift, focus on driving through your heels and squeezing your glutes at the top of the movement.","Lower the trap bar back down to the ground by bending at the hips and knees, keeping your back straight throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Trap-Bar liegt vor dir auf dem Boden.","Beuge Hüfte und Knie, um dich abzusenken, und greife die Griffe der Trap-Bar im Obergriff.","Halte den Rücken gerade und die Brust aufrecht, während du die Trap-Bar durch Strecken von Hüfte und Knien vom Boden abhebst.","Achte beim Anheben darauf, dich über die Fersen abzudrücken und dein Gesäss am oberen Ende der Bewegung anzuspannen.","Senke die Trap-Bar zurück auf den Boden ab, indem du Hüfte und Knie beugst, und halte dabei den Rücken während der gesamten Bewegung gerade.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0811.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0811.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7e1c6b29-8812-59b0-9a62-c8e8222085fd', NULL, 'Triceps Dip', 'Trizeps-Dip', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward. Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward.","Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich an den Rand einer Bank oder eines Stuhls und greife mit den Händen die Kante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schiebe dein Gesäss von der Bank und stütze dein Gewicht mit den Händen ab.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte deinen Rücken dabei nahe an der Bank.","Halte kurz inne unten, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0814.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0814.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2e159d5b-7659-5d27-8cff-34f5d5738ef3', NULL, 'Triceps Dip (Bench Leg)', 'Trizeps-Dip (Beine auf der Bank)', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward. Walk your feet forward, sliding your butt off the bench, and straighten your arms. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench. Push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward.","Walk your feet forward, sliding your butt off the bench, and straighten your arms.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench.","Push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich an den Rand einer Bank und greife mit den Händen die Kante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne, schiebe dein Gesäss von der Bank und strecke die Arme durch.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte deinen Rücken dabei nahe an der Bank.","Drücke dich über die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0812.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0812.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('6882ae3e-ae83-5ffa-94e1-abcefe040925', NULL, 'Triceps Dip (Between Benches)', 'Trizeps-Dip zwischen zwei Bänken', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge of the bench, fingers pointing forward. Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge of the bench, fingers pointing forward.","Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your back close to the bench.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank und greife mit den Händen die Bankkante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schiebe dein Gesäss von der Bank und stütze dein Gewicht mit den Händen ab.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte deinen Rücken dabei nahe an der Bank.","Halte kurz inne unten, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0813.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0813.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('409d9eff-fde7-58db-9d73-690d195366ee', NULL, 'Triceps Dips Floor', 'Trizeps-Dips am Boden', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Sit on the edge of a chair or bench with your hands next to your hips, fingers pointing forward. Slide your butt off the front of the chair with your legs extended in front of you. Straighten your arms, keeping a little bend in your elbows to keep tension on your triceps and off your elbow joints. Slowly bend your elbows to lower your body toward the floor until your elbows are at about a 90-degree angle. Once you reach the bottom of the movement, press down into the chair to straighten your elbows, returning to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a chair or bench with your hands next to your hips, fingers pointing forward.","Slide your butt off the front of the chair with your legs extended in front of you.","Straighten your arms, keeping a little bend in your elbows to keep tension on your triceps and off your elbow joints.","Slowly bend your elbows to lower your body toward the floor until your elbows are at about a 90-degree angle.","Once you reach the bottom of the movement, press down into the chair to straighten your elbows, returning to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich an den Rand eines Stuhls oder einer Bank, die Hände neben der Hüfte, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schiebe dein Gesäss von der Vorderkante des Stuhls, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Strecke deine Arme, behalte dabei eine leichte Beugung in den Ellbogen, um die Spannung im Trizeps zu halten und die Ellbogengelenke zu entlasten.","Beuge deine Ellbogen langsam, um deinen Körper Richtung Boden abzusenken, bis die Ellbogen etwa einen 90°-Winkel bilden.","Sobald du den untersten Punkt erreichst, drücke dich vom Stuhl ab, um die Ellbogen zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0815.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0815.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('68c1f025-aca0-5a77-8226-b31a9e882bbb', NULL, 'Triceps Press', 'Trizepsdrücken', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent. Extend your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground. Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your upper arms close to your sides. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.","Extend your arms straight out in front of you, parallel to the ground.","Bend your elbows and lower your body towards the ground, keeping your upper arms close to your sides.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Strecke deine Arme gerade vor dir aus, parallel zum Boden.","Beuge deine Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper Richtung Boden ab, halte die Oberarme dabei nahe am Körper.","Halte kurz inne unten, dann drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0816.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0816.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('32cd38dd-446e-5081-9a6a-ab69f7020137', NULL, 'Triceps Stretch', 'Trizepsdehnung', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'body weight', 'Stand or sit upright with your back straight. Extend one arm overhead, bending it at the elbow. Place your opposite hand on the bent elbow and gently pull it towards your head. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, feeling a gentle stretch in your triceps. Release the stretch and repeat on the other arm.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand or sit upright with your back straight.","Extend one arm overhead, bending it at the elbow.","Place your opposite hand on the bent elbow and gently pull it towards your head.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, feeling a gentle stretch in your triceps.","Release the stretch and repeat on the other arm."]', '["Stehe oder sitze aufrecht mit geradem Rücken.","Strecke einen Arm über den Kopf und beuge ihn im Ellbogen.","Lege die andere Hand auf den gebeugten Ellbogen und ziehe ihn sanft Richtung Kopf.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden, du solltest einen sanften Zug im Trizeps spüren.","Löse die Dehnung und wiederhole sie mit dem anderen Arm."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0817.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0817.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1ad26984-0e35-5517-b4a0-ec181ff0300a', NULL, 'Tuck Crunch', 'Crunch mit angezogenen Beinen', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards. Engaging your abs, lift your shoulder blades off the ground and bring your knees towards your chest, simultaneously curling your upper body towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your shoulder blades and extend your legs back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands behind your head with your elbows pointing outwards.","Engaging your abs, lift your shoulder blades off the ground and bring your knees towards your chest, simultaneously curling your upper body towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your shoulder blades and extend your legs back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege deine Hände hinter den Kopf, die Ellbogen zeigen nach aussen.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskulatur an, hebe die Schulterblätter vom Boden ab und ziehe die Knie Richtung Brust, während du gleichzeitig den Oberkörper zu den Knien einrollst.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke die Schulterblätter langsam ab und strecke die Beine zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0871.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0871.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('59810fb8-1f3c-5fcd-a643-6a83ef99e7f2', NULL, 'Twin Handle Parallel Grip Lat Pulldown', 'Latzug mit Doppelgriff im Parallelgriff', 'back', 'lats', 'cable', 'Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the cable machine. Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Sit down and position your thighs under the thigh pads, keeping your feet flat on the floor. Lean back slightly and keep your chest up, maintaining a neutral spine. Pull the handles down towards your upper chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together. Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, feeling the contraction in your lats. Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","rhomboids","rear deltoids"]', '["Adjust the seat height and position yourself facing the cable machine.","Grasp the handles with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Sit down and position your thighs under the thigh pads, keeping your feet flat on the floor.","Lean back slightly and keep your chest up, maintaining a neutral spine.","Pull the handles down towards your upper chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together.","Pause for a moment at the bottom of the movement, feeling the contraction in your lats.","Slowly release the handles and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle die Sitzhöhe ein und setze dich mit Blick zum Kabelzug.","Greife die Griffe im Obergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Setze dich hin und positioniere deine Oberschenkel unter den Polstern, die Füsse bleiben flach auf dem Boden.","Lehne dich leicht zurück, halte die Brust aufrecht und die Wirbelsäule neutral.","Ziehe die Griffe Richtung oberer Brust nach unten und drücke dabei die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte kurz inne am unteren Punkt der Bewegung und spüre die Anspannung im Latissimus.","Lasse die Griffe langsam los und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0818.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0818.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('169ccaae-83a3-56b2-be46-595388ad3514', NULL, 'Twist Hip Lift', 'Hüftheben mit Drehung', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Place your hands by your sides for support. Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders. While keeping your hips lifted, twist your lower body to the right side, bringing your knees towards the ground. Return to the starting position and repeat the twist to the left side. Continue alternating twists for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hamstrings"]', '["Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Place your hands by your sides for support.","Engage your glutes and lift your hips off the ground, forming a straight line from your knees to your shoulders.","While keeping your hips lifted, twist your lower body to the right side, bringing your knees towards the ground.","Return to the starting position and repeat the twist to the left side.","Continue alternating twists for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Lege deine Hände zur Unterstützung neben den Körper.","Spanne dein Gesäss an und hebe die Hüfte vom Boden ab, sodass eine gerade Linie von den Knien bis zu den Schultern entsteht.","Drehe deinen Unterkörper bei angehobener Hüfte nach rechts, sodass die Knie sich Richtung Boden bewegen.","Kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück und wiederhole die Drehung zur linken Seite.","Wechsle die Drehrichtung fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1466.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1466.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e6a25e52-3aaf-5045-9f8b-5b9983c96654', NULL, 'Twisted Leg Raise', 'Beinheben mit Drehung', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Place your hands under your glutes for support. Engage your abs and lift both legs off the ground, keeping them straight. As you lift your legs, twist your hips to one side, bringing your legs towards your opposite shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time twisting your hips to the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Place your hands under your glutes for support.","Engage your abs and lift both legs off the ground, keeping them straight.","As you lift your legs, twist your hips to one side, bringing your legs towards your opposite shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time twisting your hips to the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Lege deine Hände zur Unterstützung unter dein Gesäss.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe beide Beine gestreckt vom Boden ab.","Drehe beim Anheben der Beine deine Hüfte zu einer Seite, sodass sich die Beine Richtung gegenüberliegende Schulter bewegen.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke deine Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal drehst du die Hüfte zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2802.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2802.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f2ebc73f-aad5-5dda-9b52-4570a8a8eceb', NULL, 'Twisted Leg Raise (Female)', 'Beinheben mit Drehung (weiblich)', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides. Bend your knees and lift your legs off the ground, bringing them towards your chest. As you lift your legs, twist your hips to one side, bringing your knees towards your opposite shoulder. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat the movement, this time twisting your hips to the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your legs extended and your arms by your sides.","Bend your knees and lift your legs off the ground, bringing them towards your chest.","As you lift your legs, twist your hips to one side, bringing your knees towards your opposite shoulder.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat the movement, this time twisting your hips to the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Beine gestreckt und die Arme neben dem Körper.","Beuge deine Knie und hebe die Beine vom Boden ab, sodass sie sich Richtung Brust bewegen.","Drehe beim Anheben der Beine deine Hüfte zu einer Seite, sodass sich die Knie Richtung gegenüberliegende Schulter bewegen.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke deine Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole die Bewegung, diesmal drehst du die Hüfte zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle die Seiten fortlaufend für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2801.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2801.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f9a7a00c-5b87-5e54-a832-8491d260de8d', NULL, 'Two Toe Touch (Male)', 'Zehenberührung (männlich)', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended out to the sides. Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent. Reach down towards your toes with both hands, keeping your legs straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms extended out to the sides.","Bend forward at the waist, keeping your back straight and your knees slightly bent.","Reach down towards your toes with both hands, keeping your legs straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin, die Arme seitlich ausgestreckt.","Beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, halte den Rücken gerade und die Knie leicht gebeugt.","Greife mit beiden Händen Richtung Zehen, halte die Beine dabei gestreckt.","Halte kurz inne unten, dann kehre langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3231.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3231.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('73897933-b0d3-570c-b8e4-a7fbd9999565', NULL, 'Upper Back Stretch', 'Dehnung des oberen Rückens', 'back', 'upper back', 'body weight', 'Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart. Extend your arms straight in front of you, parallel to the ground. Interlace your fingers and rotate your palms away from your body. Slowly raise your arms overhead, keeping them straight and parallel to each other. As you raise your arms, squeeze your shoulder blades together. Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release and repeat.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders"]', '["Stand up straight with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Extend your arms straight in front of you, parallel to the ground.","Interlace your fingers and rotate your palms away from your body.","Slowly raise your arms overhead, keeping them straight and parallel to each other.","As you raise your arms, squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Hold the stretch for 15-30 seconds, then release and repeat."]', '["Stehe aufrecht mit schulterbreiten Füssen.","Strecke deine Arme gerade vor dir aus, parallel zum Boden.","Verschränke deine Finger und drehe die Handflächen vom Körper weg.","Hebe deine Arme langsam über den Kopf, halte sie dabei gestreckt und parallel zueinander.","Drücke beim Anheben der Arme die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Halte die Dehnung 15-30 Sekunden, löse sie dann und wiederhole."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1365.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1365.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('2433fa3d-e78c-5eb4-b9f5-5e26e7d44224', NULL, 'Upward Facing Dog', 'Nach oben schauender Hund', 'back', 'spine', 'body weight', 'Lie face down on the floor with your legs extended behind you. Place your hands on the floor next to your lower ribs, fingers pointing forward. Press your hands firmly into the floor and straighten your arms, lifting your torso and thighs off the ground. Roll your shoulders back and down, opening your chest and lifting your gaze towards the ceiling. Hold this position for a few breaths, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","chest"]', '["Lie face down on the floor with your legs extended behind you.","Place your hands on the floor next to your lower ribs, fingers pointing forward.","Press your hands firmly into the floor and straighten your arms, lifting your torso and thighs off the ground.","Roll your shoulders back and down, opening your chest and lifting your gaze towards the ceiling.","Hold this position for a few breaths, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Boden, die Beine hinter dir gestreckt.","Setze deine Hände neben den unteren Rippen auf den Boden, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Drücke deine Hände fest in den Boden und strecke die Arme durch, sodass sich Oberkörper und Oberschenkel vom Boden abheben.","Rolle die Schultern nach hinten unten, öffne den Brustkorb und richte deinen Blick Richtung Decke.","Halte diese Position für einige Atemzüge, dann senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1366.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1366.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8c96b564-55b8-5e6e-b7e5-c95cc77949b7', NULL, 'V-Sit on Floor', 'V-Sit am Boden', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Sit on the floor with your legs extended in front of you. Lean back slightly and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight. Simultaneously, lift your upper body off the ground and reach your arms towards your legs. Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the floor with your legs extended in front of you.","Lean back slightly and lift your legs off the ground, keeping them straight.","Simultaneously, lift your upper body off the ground and reach your arms towards your legs.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then slowly lower your upper body and legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf den Boden, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Lehne dich leicht zurück und hebe die gestreckten Beine vom Boden ab.","Hebe gleichzeitig den Oberkörper vom Boden ab und strecke die Arme Richtung Beine.","Halte diese Position für einige Sekunden, dann senke Oberkörper und Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3420.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3420.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3a2b661d-4782-5246-82a9-61f79911992b', NULL, 'Vertical Leg Raise (on Parallel Bars)', 'Vertikales Beinheben am Barren', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Hang from the parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight. Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or slightly higher. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors"]', '["Hang from the parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight.","Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or slightly higher.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an die Barren, die Arme vollständig gestreckt und der Körper gerade.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe die gestreckten Beine vor dir an.","Hebe die Beine weiter an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind oder leicht darüber.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke deine Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0826.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0826.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fa07b2a2-9c57-5555-9cca-2982604c2e4a', NULL, 'Walk Elliptical Cross Trainer', 'Crosstrainer im Gehtempo', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'elliptical machine', 'Adjust the resistance level and incline of the elliptical machine to your desired settings. Step onto the pedals of the machine and grip the handles lightly. Begin by pushing down with your feet and pulling the handles towards your body. Continue this motion, alternating between pushing and pulling, to simulate a walking or running motion. Maintain a steady pace and keep your core engaged throughout the exercise. Continue for the desired duration of your cardio workout. Gradually decrease the intensity and speed of the machine before stepping off.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Adjust the resistance level and incline of the elliptical machine to your desired settings.","Step onto the pedals of the machine and grip the handles lightly.","Begin by pushing down with your feet and pulling the handles towards your body.","Continue this motion, alternating between pushing and pulling, to simulate a walking or running motion.","Maintain a steady pace and keep your core engaged throughout the exercise.","Continue for the desired duration of your cardio workout.","Gradually decrease the intensity and speed of the machine before stepping off."]', '["Stelle Widerstand und Steigung des Crosstrainers auf die gewünschten Werte ein.","Steige auf die Pedale und greife die Griffe locker.","Beginne, indem du mit den Füssen nach unten drückst und die Griffe zum Körper ziehst.","Führe diese Bewegung fort und wechsle zwischen Drücken und Ziehen, um eine Geh- oder Laufbewegung nachzuahmen.","Halte ein gleichmässiges Tempo und spanne die Körpermitte während der gesamten Übung an.","Führe die Übung für die gewünschte Dauer deines Cardio-Trainings fort.","Reduziere Intensität und Geschwindigkeit des Geräts schrittweise, bevor du absteigst."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2141.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2141.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('71ea08bf-e615-558d-86fe-f0354c0ccf99', NULL, 'Walking High Knees Lunge', 'Ausfallschritt mit hohen Knien im Gehen', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet hip-width apart. Lift your right knee up towards your chest as high as you can while balancing on your left leg. Step forward with your right foot and lower your body into a lunge position, bending both knees to a 90-degree angle. Push off with your right foot and bring your left knee up towards your chest. Step forward with your left foot and lower your body into a lunge position. Continue alternating legs and lunging forward, keeping your core engaged and maintaining a steady pace. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet hip-width apart.","Lift your right knee up towards your chest as high as you can while balancing on your left leg.","Step forward with your right foot and lower your body into a lunge position, bending both knees to a 90-degree angle.","Push off with your right foot and bring your left knee up towards your chest.","Step forward with your left foot and lower your body into a lunge position.","Continue alternating legs and lunging forward, keeping your core engaged and maintaining a steady pace.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit hüftbreiten Füssen hin.","Hebe dein rechtes Knie so hoch wie möglich Richtung Brust an, während du auf dem linken Bein balancierst.","Trete mit dem rechten Fuss nach vorne und senke deinen Körper in einen Ausfallschritt ab, beide Knie im 90°-Winkel gebeugt.","Stosse dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab und ziehe das linke Knie Richtung Brust hoch.","Trete mit dem linken Fuss nach vorne und senke deinen Körper in einen Ausfallschritt ab.","Wechsle die Beine fortlaufend und mache weiter Ausfallschritte nach vorne, halte dabei die Körpermitte angespannt und ein gleichmässiges Tempo.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3655.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3655.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('828f505c-75fd-52ae-852a-051c8b1911e4', NULL, 'Walking Lunge', 'Ausfallschritt im Gehen', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'body weight', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Take a step forward with your right leg, lowering your body into a lunge position. Keep your torso upright and your front knee aligned with your ankle. Push off with your right foot and bring your left foot forward, stepping into a lunge position with your left leg. Continue alternating legs and walking forward, maintaining a controlled and steady pace. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Take a step forward with your right leg, lowering your body into a lunge position.","Keep your torso upright and your front knee aligned with your ankle.","Push off with your right foot and bring your left foot forward, stepping into a lunge position with your left leg.","Continue alternating legs and walking forward, maintaining a controlled and steady pace.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen hin.","Mache einen Schritt nach vorne mit dem rechten Bein und senke deinen Körper in einen Ausfallschritt ab.","Halte den Oberkörper aufrecht und das vordere Knie in Linie mit dem Knöchel.","Stosse dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab und bringe den linken Fuss nach vorne, um mit dem linken Bein in einen Ausfallschritt zu treten.","Wechsle die Beine fortlaufend und gehe in einem kontrollierten, gleichmässigen Tempo weiter nach vorne.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1460.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1460.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d3940587-2f1d-5b7a-baa3-f8599568644b', NULL, 'Walking on Incline Treadmill', 'Gehen auf dem Laufband mit Steigung', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'leverage machine', 'Adjust the incline level on the treadmill to your desired intensity. Stand on the treadmill with your feet shoulder-width apart. Start walking at a comfortable pace, ensuring that you maintain proper form. Engage your core muscles and keep your back straight throughout the exercise. Continue walking on the incline treadmill for the desired duration of your cardio workout. Gradually decrease the incline and speed of the treadmill to cool down before stopping.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Adjust the incline level on the treadmill to your desired intensity.","Stand on the treadmill with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Start walking at a comfortable pace, ensuring that you maintain proper form.","Engage your core muscles and keep your back straight throughout the exercise.","Continue walking on the incline treadmill for the desired duration of your cardio workout.","Gradually decrease the incline and speed of the treadmill to cool down before stopping."]', '["Stelle die Steigung des Laufbands auf die gewünschte Intensität ein.","Stelle dich mit schulterbreiten Füssen auf das Laufband.","Beginne in einem angenehmen Tempo zu gehen und achte auf eine korrekte Haltung.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte den Rücken während der gesamten Übung gerade.","Gehe auf dem geneigten Laufband für die gewünschte Dauer deines Cardio-Trainings weiter.","Reduziere Steigung und Geschwindigkeit des Laufbands schrittweise, um dich vor dem Stopp abzukühlen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3666.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3666.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b535797b-87ae-5e94-ba3f-b754a1fec673', NULL, 'Walking on Stepmill', 'Gehen auf dem Stepmill', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'stepmill machine', 'Adjust the stepmill machine to a comfortable level. Step onto the machine and place your hands on the handrails for support. Start walking by placing one foot on a step and then the other, alternating between legs. Maintain an upright posture and engage your core muscles. Continue walking for the desired duration or distance. Gradually increase the intensity or speed as you become more comfortable with the exercise. Remember to cool down and stretch after completing the exercise.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","glutes","calves"]', '["Adjust the stepmill machine to a comfortable level.","Step onto the machine and place your hands on the handrails for support.","Start walking by placing one foot on a step and then the other, alternating between legs.","Maintain an upright posture and engage your core muscles.","Continue walking for the desired duration or distance.","Gradually increase the intensity or speed as you become more comfortable with the exercise.","Remember to cool down and stretch after completing the exercise."]', '["Stelle das Stepmill-Gerät auf ein angenehmes Niveau ein.","Steige auf das Gerät und lege deine Hände zur Unterstützung auf die Handläufe.","Beginne zu gehen, indem du abwechselnd einen Fuss und dann den anderen auf eine Stufe setzt.","Halte eine aufrechte Haltung und spanne deine Körpermitte an.","Gehe für die gewünschte Dauer oder Distanz weiter.","Erhöhe Intensität oder Geschwindigkeit schrittweise, sobald dir die Übung leichter fällt.","Denke daran, dich nach der Übung abzukühlen und zu dehnen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2311.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2311.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ebb34729-d6b1-5771-9117-c02110a23ca7', NULL, 'Weighted Bench Dip', 'Bank-Dip mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'weighted', 'Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward. Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the floor. Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward.","Slide your butt off the bench, supporting your weight with your hands.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the floor.","Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf eine Bank und greife mit den Händen die Kante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Schiebe dein Gesäss von der Bank und stütze dein Gewicht mit den Händen ab.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Drücke dich zurück in die Ausgangsposition, indem du die Arme streckst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0830.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0830.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f2005acc-a3b3-548e-95c7-ece4e4d0c27c', NULL, 'Weighted Close-Grip Chin-up on Dip Cage', 'Enger Klimmzug im Untergriff mit Zusatzgewicht am Dip-Käfig', 'back', 'lats', 'weighted', 'Stand in front of the dip cage and grab the parallel bars with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bars with your arms fully extended, feet off the ground, and body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bars, keeping your elbows close to your sides. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bars, then pause for a moment. Slowly lower your body back down to the starting position, fully extending your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand in front of the dip cage and grab the parallel bars with an underhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bars with your arms fully extended, feet off the ground, and body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bars, keeping your elbows close to your sides.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bars, then pause for a moment.","Slowly lower your body back down to the starting position, fully extending your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich vor den Dip-Käfig und greife die Barrenholme im Untergriff, die Hände schulterbreit auseinander.","Hänge dich an die Holme, die Arme vollständig gestreckt, die Füsse frei über dem Boden und der Körper gerade.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zu den Holmen hoch, halte die Ellbogen dabei nahe am Körper.","Ziehe weiter, bis sich dein Kinn über den Holmen befindet, halte dann kurz inne.","Senke deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab und strecke die Arme dabei vollständig durch.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2987.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2987.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('94910db7-4db6-5f53-af1f-851b692410d8', NULL, 'Weighted Cossack Squats (Male)', 'Kosaken-Kniebeuge mit Zusatzgewicht (männlich)', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart and toes pointing slightly outward. Hold a weight in front of your chest with both hands. Shift your weight to one side and lower your body by bending the knee of the side you shifted towards, while keeping the other leg straight. Go as low as you can while maintaining balance and keeping your chest up. Push through the heel of the bent leg to return to the starting position. Repeat on the other side, alternating between legs.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet wider than shoulder-width apart and toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold a weight in front of your chest with both hands.","Shift your weight to one side and lower your body by bending the knee of the side you shifted towards, while keeping the other leg straight.","Go as low as you can while maintaining balance and keeping your chest up.","Push through the heel of the bent leg to return to the starting position.","Repeat on the other side, alternating between legs."]', '["Stelle dich mit den Füssen breiter als schulterbreit hin, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte ein Gewicht mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust.","Verlagere dein Gewicht auf eine Seite und senke deinen Körper ab, indem du das Knie dieser Seite beugst, während das andere Bein gestreckt bleibt.","Gehe so tief wie möglich, ohne das Gleichgewicht zu verlieren, und halte die Brust dabei aufrecht.","Drücke dich über die Ferse des gebeugten Beins zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole auf der anderen Seite und wechsle die Beine fortlaufend."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3643.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3643.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('667413b7-8def-54b8-87a1-39353be996e2', NULL, 'Weighted Crunch', 'Crunch mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Hold a weight plate or dumbbell on your chest. Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your shoulder blades are off the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques"]', '["Lie flat on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground.","Hold a weight plate or dumbbell on your chest.","Engage your abs and lift your upper body off the ground, curling forward until your shoulder blades are off the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf den Rücken, die Knie gebeugt und die Füsse flach auf dem Boden.","Halte eine Gewichtsscheibe oder Kurzhantel auf deiner Brust.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskulatur an und hebe den Oberkörper vom Boden ab, indem du dich nach vorne einrollst, bis die Schulterblätter den Boden verlassen.","Halte kurz inne oben, dann senke deinen Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0832.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0832.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('b99822f4-4e91-553a-869e-b87a2edb73e7', NULL, 'Weighted Decline Sit-up', 'Negativbank-Sit-up mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Lie flat on a decline bench with your feet secured under the foot pads. Place your hands behind your head or across your chest. Engage your abs and slowly lift your upper body off the bench, curling forward until your torso is perpendicular to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Lie flat on a decline bench with your feet secured under the foot pads.","Place your hands behind your head or across your chest.","Engage your abs and slowly lift your upper body off the bench, curling forward until your torso is perpendicular to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich flach auf eine Negativbank und sichere deine Füsse unter den Fusspolstern.","Lege deine Hände hinter den Kopf oder über die Brust.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskeln an und hebe deinen Oberkörper langsam von der Bank ab, indem du dich nach vorne aufrollst, bis dein Oberkörper senkrecht zum Boden steht.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deinen Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3670.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3670.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('1d56ef2c-77d6-5422-9b14-cb8447ae2217', NULL, 'Weighted Donkey Calf Raise', 'Donkey-Wadenheben mit Zusatzgewicht', 'lower legs', 'calves', 'weighted', 'Stand on a raised platform with your toes on the edge and your heels hanging off. Hold onto a stable object for support. Raise your heels as high as possible by extending your ankles. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hamstrings', '["hamstrings","glutes"]', '["Stand on a raised platform with your toes on the edge and your heels hanging off.","Hold onto a stable object for support.","Raise your heels as high as possible by extending your ankles.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your heels back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stelle dich auf eine erhöhte Plattform, mit den Zehen auf der Kante und den Fersen frei hängend.","Halte dich an einem stabilen Gegenstand fest, um Halt zu haben.","Hebe deine Fersen so hoch wie möglich an, indem du deine Knöchel streckst.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deine Fersen langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0833.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0833.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3fe010a1-e713-5ef8-b113-f8a82c6ca957', NULL, 'Weighted Drop Push-up', 'Drop-Liegestütz mit Zusatzgewicht', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'weighted', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together. Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body. Once your chest is just above the ground, explosively push yourself up, lifting your hands off the ground. As you push up, quickly move your hands out to the sides and slightly forward, allowing your body to drop down towards the ground. Catch yourself with your hands in the wider position and immediately lower your chest towards the ground again. Repeat the push-up motion, dropping down and catching yourself with your hands in the narrower position. Continue alternating between the wider and narrower hand positions for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart and your feet together.","Lower your chest towards the ground, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Once your chest is just above the ground, explosively push yourself up, lifting your hands off the ground.","As you push up, quickly move your hands out to the sides and slightly forward, allowing your body to drop down towards the ground.","Catch yourself with your hands in the wider position and immediately lower your chest towards the ground again.","Repeat the push-up motion, dropping down and catching yourself with your hands in the narrower position.","Continue alternating between the wider and narrower hand positions for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Starte in einer hohen Liegestützposition mit den Händen leicht mehr als schulterbreit auseinander und den Füssen zusammen.","Senke deine Brust Richtung Boden ab und halte die Ellbogen nah am Körper.","Sobald deine Brust knapp über dem Boden ist, drücke dich explosiv nach oben und hebe die Hände vom Boden ab.","Bewege beim Hochdrücken deine Hände schnell seitlich und leicht nach vorne, sodass dein Körper Richtung Boden absinkt.","Fange dich mit den Händen in der breiteren Position ab und senke deine Brust sofort wieder Richtung Boden ab.","Wiederhole die Liegestützbewegung, indem du absinkst und dich mit den Händen in der schmaleren Position abfängst.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen zwischen der breiteren und der schmaleren Handposition ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1310.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1310.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7922c224-3ab1-5100-b50a-7dc3b183ad5f', NULL, 'Weighted Front Plank', 'Plank mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Start by lying face down on the floor. Place your forearms on the ground, with your elbows directly under your shoulders. Extend your legs straight out behind you, with your toes on the ground. Engage your core and lift your body off the ground, balancing on your forearms and toes. Keep your body in a straight line from your head to your heels. Hold this position for the desired amount of time. Lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","lower back"]', '["Start by lying face down on the floor.","Place your forearms on the ground, with your elbows directly under your shoulders.","Extend your legs straight out behind you, with your toes on the ground.","Engage your core and lift your body off the ground, balancing on your forearms and toes.","Keep your body in a straight line from your head to your heels.","Hold this position for the desired amount of time.","Lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf den Boden.","Platziere deine Unterarme auf dem Boden, die Ellbogen direkt unter den Schultern.","Strecke deine Beine gerade nach hinten aus, mit den Zehen auf dem Boden.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe deinen Körper vom Boden ab, indem du dich auf Unterarme und Zehen abstützt.","Halte deinen Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fersen.","Halte diese Position für die gewünschte Dauer.","Senke deinen Körper zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2135.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2135.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('37f772c8-b77f-5936-b27b-0ce4734df0bd', NULL, 'Weighted Front Raise', 'Frontheben mit Zusatzgewicht', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your thighs. Keeping your arms straight, exhale and lift the dumbbells in front of you until they are at shoulder level. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with your palms facing your thighs.","Keeping your arms straight, exhale and lift the dumbbells in front of you until they are at shoulder level.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale and slowly lower the dumbbells back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen zu den Oberschenkeln zeigend.","Halte die Arme gestreckt, atme aus und hebe die Kurzhanteln vor dir an, bis sie Schulterhöhe erreichen.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme ein und senke die Kurzhanteln langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0834.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0834.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a4b60b8e-4a76-51c3-b137-805c6dd545f4', NULL, 'Weighted Hanging Leg-Hip Raise', 'Hängendes Bein-Hüft-Heben mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you. Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight. Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or slightly higher. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hip flexors', '["hip flexors","lower back"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your arms fully extended and your palms facing away from you.","Engage your core and lift your legs up in front of you, keeping them straight.","Continue lifting until your legs are parallel to the ground or slightly higher.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich mit vollständig gestreckten Armen an eine Klimmzugstange, Handflächen von dir weg zeigend.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe deine gestreckten Beine vor dir an.","Hebe weiter an, bis deine Beine parallel zum Boden oder leicht darüber sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deine Beine langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0866.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0866.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e8325fd9-308e-5f44-b4fc-60a49eaba0da', NULL, 'Weighted Hyperextension (on Stability Ball)', 'Hyperextension auf dem Gymnastikball mit Zusatzgewicht', 'back', 'spine', 'weighted', 'Position yourself face down on a stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability. Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest. Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings"]', '["Position yourself face down on a stability ball with your hips resting on the ball and your feet against a wall for stability.","Place your hands behind your head or cross them over your chest.","Engage your core and slowly lift your upper body off the ball, extending your back until your body forms a straight line.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your upper body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Lege dich mit dem Gesicht nach unten auf einen Gymnastikball, sodass deine Hüfte auf dem Ball ruht und deine Füsse zur Stabilisierung gegen eine Wand gestellt sind.","Lege deine Hände hinter den Kopf oder verschränke sie vor der Brust.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und hebe deinen Oberkörper langsam vom Ball ab, indem du den Rücken streckst, bis dein Körper eine gerade Linie bildet.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deinen Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0835.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0835.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('09e31342-7ce1-5953-951e-17590b44db41', NULL, 'Weighted Kneeling Step with Swing', 'Kniender Ausfallschritt mit Schwung und Zusatzgewicht', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'weighted', 'Start in a kneeling position with your knees hip-width apart and your back straight. Hold a weight in each hand, with your arms extended straight down in front of you. Engage your core and swing the weights up and overhead, keeping your arms straight. Lower the weights back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","core"]', '["Start in a kneeling position with your knees hip-width apart and your back straight.","Hold a weight in each hand, with your arms extended straight down in front of you.","Engage your core and swing the weights up and overhead, keeping your arms straight.","Lower the weights back down to the starting position and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Gehe in eine kniende Position mit hüftbreiten Knien und geradem Rücken.","Halte in jeder Hand ein Gewicht, die Arme gerade nach unten vor dir gestreckt.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und schwinge die Gewichte mit gestreckten Armen nach oben über den Kopf.","Senke die Gewichte zurück in die Ausgangsposition und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3641.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3641.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('a82a8453-b594-5f09-b72a-355801c67f86', NULL, 'Weighted Lunge with Swing', 'Ausfallschritt mit Schwung und Zusatzgewicht', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a weight in each hand. Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position. As you lunge forward, swing the weights forward and upward, keeping your arms straight. Push off with your right foot and return to the starting position, swinging the weights back down. Repeat with your left foot and continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a weight in each hand.","Take a step forward with your right foot, lowering your body into a lunge position.","As you lunge forward, swing the weights forward and upward, keeping your arms straight.","Push off with your right foot and return to the starting position, swinging the weights back down.","Repeat with your left foot and continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte in jeder Hand ein Gewicht.","Mache mit dem rechten Fuss einen Schritt nach vorne und senke deinen Körper in eine Ausfallschritt-Position ab.","Schwinge beim Ausfallschritt nach vorne die Gewichte mit gestreckten Armen nach vorne und oben.","Drücke dich mit dem rechten Fuss ab und kehre in die Ausgangsposition zurück, während du die Gewichte wieder nach unten schwingst.","Wiederhole mit dem linken Fuss und wechsle die Beine für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3644.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3644.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5684a889-f92b-5a23-b2d9-92ec8715b85b', NULL, 'Weighted Muscle Up', 'Muscle-up mit Zusatzgewicht', 'back', 'lats', 'weighted', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. As you reach the top of the movement, transition your grip so that your palms are facing towards you. Continue pulling yourself up until your chest reaches the bar, then pause for a moment. Slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position, maintaining control throughout the movement. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","shoulders","chest"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","As you reach the top of the movement, transition your grip so that your palms are facing towards you.","Continue pulling yourself up until your chest reaches the bar, then pause for a moment.","Slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position, maintaining control throughout the movement.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an eine Klimmzugstange, Handflächen von dir weg zeigend, mit den Händen leicht mehr als schulterbreit auseinander.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, angeführt von der Brust.","Wechsle am oberen Punkt der Bewegung deinen Griff, sodass deine Handflächen zu dir zeigen.","Ziehe dich weiter hoch, bis deine Brust die Stange erreicht, und halte dann kurz inne.","Senke dich langsam und kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3286.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3286.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3de07154-16c4-55ea-acb3-3f6c408b384e', NULL, 'Weighted Muscle Up (on Bar)', 'Muscle-up an der Stange mit Zusatzgewicht', 'back', 'lats', 'weighted', 'Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back. Bend your elbows and pull your chest towards the bar, keeping your body straight. Once your chest reaches the bar, push down with your hands and drive your elbows back, lifting your body above the bar. Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps","shoulders","forearms"]', '["Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and pull your shoulder blades down and back.","Bend your elbows and pull your chest towards the bar, keeping your body straight.","Once your chest reaches the bar, push down with your hands and drive your elbows back, lifting your body above the bar.","Pause at the top of the movement, then slowly lower yourself back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an eine Klimmzugstange, Handflächen von dir weg zeigend, mit den Händen leicht mehr als schulterbreit auseinander.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deine Schulterblätter nach unten und hinten.","Beuge die Ellbogen und ziehe deine Brust zur Stange, während du den Körper gerade hältst.","Sobald deine Brust die Stange erreicht, drücke mit den Händen nach unten und schiebe die Ellbogen nach hinten, um deinen Körper über die Stange zu heben.","Halte am oberen Punkt der Bewegung kurz inne, senke dich dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3312.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3312.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8bfd0613-1f62-5dbf-ad70-096765f58771', NULL, 'Weighted One Hand Pull-up', 'Einarmiger Klimmzug mit Zusatzgewicht', 'back', 'lats', 'weighted', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arm fully extended and your body straight. Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbow and squeezing your back muscles. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Lower your body back down to the starting position with control. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arm fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your core and pull your body up towards the bar by bending your elbow and squeezing your back muscles.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Lower your body back down to the starting position with control.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestrecktem Arm und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, indem du den Ellbogen beugst und die Rückenmuskulatur anspannst.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Senke deinen Körper kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3290.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3290.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('f26f6367-605e-50e2-9eee-d276399f0353', NULL, 'Weighted Overhead Crunch (on Stability Ball)', 'Crunch mit Überkopfstreckung auf dem Gymnastikball mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a weight plate or dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms overhead. Engage your abs and slowly curl your torso forward, bringing your chest towards your knees. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your torso back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a weight plate or dumbbell with both hands and extend your arms overhead.","Engage your abs and slowly curl your torso forward, bringing your chest towards your knees.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your torso back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Gewichtsscheibe oder Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen und strecke die Arme über den Kopf.","Spanne deine Bauchmuskeln an und rolle deinen Oberkörper langsam nach vorne auf, sodass sich die Brust den Knien annähert.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deinen Oberkörper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0840.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0840.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e7da6496-d436-5021-8814-9981b8925133', NULL, 'Weighted Pull-up', 'Klimmzug mit Zusatzgewicht', 'back', 'lats', 'weighted', 'Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, keeping your elbows close to your body.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange im Obergriff, etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, wobei du die Ellbogen nah am Körper hältst.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0841.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0841.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('39220e30-9ef6-508a-9528-d349b36cce92', NULL, 'Weighted Round Arm', 'Rundarmheben mit Zusatzgewicht', 'shoulders', 'delts', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight. Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows. Continue lifting your arms until they are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","upper back"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand.","Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at the hips, keeping your back straight.","Raise your arms out to the sides, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.","Continue lifting your arms until they are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your arms back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel.","Beuge die Knie leicht und beuge dich in der Hüfte nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Hebe die Arme seitlich an, mit einer leichten Beugung in den Ellbogen.","Hebe die Arme weiter an, bis sie parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deine Arme langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0844.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0844.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('10fb237a-96c7-5191-9496-8d83d2040058', NULL, 'Weighted Russian Twist', 'Russian Twist mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on the ground with your knees bent and your feet flat on the floor. Hold a weight or medicine ball with both hands in front of your chest. Lean back slightly, keeping your back straight and your core engaged. Slowly twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight or medicine ball towards the floor on your right side. Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight or medicine ball towards the floor on your left side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on the ground with your knees bent and your feet flat on the floor.","Hold a weight or medicine ball with both hands in front of your chest.","Lean back slightly, keeping your back straight and your core engaged.","Slowly twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight or medicine ball towards the floor on your right side.","Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight or medicine ball towards the floor on your left side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich mit gebeugten Knien und flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen auf den Boden.","Halte ein Gewicht oder einen Medizinball mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust.","Lehne dich leicht zurück, halte dabei den Rücken gerade und die Körpermitte angespannt.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper langsam nach rechts und führe das Gewicht oder den Medizinball auf deiner rechten Seite Richtung Boden.","Halte kurz inne, drehe dann deinen Oberkörper nach links und führe das Gewicht oder den Medizinball auf deiner linken Seite Richtung Boden.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0846.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0846.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('0be0848f-4c85-5b71-aed8-78ebe4abd691', NULL, 'Weighted Russian Twist (Legs Up)', 'Russian Twist mit angehobenen Beinen und Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet lifted off the ground, keeping your legs together. Hold the weight with both hands in front of your chest, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Lean back slightly to engage your core muscles. Twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight towards the ground on your right side. Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight towards the ground on your left side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","hip flexors"]', '["Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet lifted off the ground, keeping your legs together.","Hold the weight with both hands in front of your chest, keeping your elbows slightly bent.","Lean back slightly to engage your core muscles.","Twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight towards the ground on your right side.","Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight towards the ground on your left side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich mit gebeugten Knien auf den Boden und hebe die Füsse vom Boden ab, wobei die Beine zusammenbleiben.","Halte das Gewicht mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust, die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Lehne dich leicht zurück, um deine Körpermitte anzuspannen.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper nach rechts und führe das Gewicht auf deiner rechten Seite Richtung Boden.","Halte kurz inne, drehe dann deinen Oberkörper nach links und führe das Gewicht auf deiner linken Seite Richtung Boden.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0845.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0845.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);

INSERT OR REPLACE INTO exercises (id, user_id, name, name_de, category, primary_muscle, equipment, instructions_en, instructions_de, muscle_group, secondary_muscles, instruction_steps_en, instruction_steps_de, thumbnail_url, gif_url, created_at, updated_at, deleted) VALUES
  ('dd981c0e-c05a-51d4-90a9-2ed33f7cde39', NULL, 'Weighted Russian Twist v. 2', 'Russian Twist mit Zusatzgewicht, Variante 2', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Hold the weight with both hands in front of your chest. Lean back slightly to engage your core muscles. Twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight towards the right side of your body. Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight towards the left side of your body. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on the ground with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor.","Hold the weight with both hands in front of your chest.","Lean back slightly to engage your core muscles.","Twist your torso to the right, bringing the weight towards the right side of your body.","Pause for a moment, then twist your torso to the left, bringing the weight towards the left side of your body.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich mit gebeugten Knien und flach auf dem Boden stehenden Füssen auf den Boden.","Halte das Gewicht mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust.","Lehne dich leicht zurück, um deine Körpermitte anzuspannen.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper nach rechts und führe das Gewicht zur rechten Körperseite.","Halte kurz inne, drehe dann deinen Oberkörper nach links und führe das Gewicht zur linken Körperseite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2371.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2371.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('99c9486b-939b-55bf-94df-ddd994706b21', NULL, 'Weighted Seated Bicep Curl (on Stability Ball)', 'Bizepscurl im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'medicine ball', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight. Hold a medicine ball with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and let your arms hang down by your sides. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the medicine ball up towards your shoulders. Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps. Inhale and slowly lower the medicine ball back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your back straight.","Hold a medicine ball with an underhand grip, palms facing up, and let your arms hang down by your sides.","Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale and curl the medicine ball up towards your shoulders.","Pause for a moment at the top, squeezing your biceps.","Inhale and slowly lower the medicine ball back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und den Rücken gerade.","Halte einen Medizinball im Untergriff, Handflächen nach oben zeigend, und lasse die Arme seitlich am Körper hängen.","Halte die Oberarme ruhig, atme aus und curl den Medizinball zu den Schultern hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne und spanne die Bizeps an.","Atme ein und senke den Medizinball langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0847.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0847.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('fd46d046-51eb-5ad1-ad64-19c236c4d01d', NULL, 'Weighted Seated Twist (on Stability Ball)', 'Rumpfdrehung im Sitzen auf dem Gymnastikball mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle. Hold a weight plate or dumbbell with both hands close to your chest. Engage your core and slowly rotate your torso to one side, keeping your hips stable. Pause for a moment at the end of the rotation, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat the rotation to the other side. Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet flat on the ground and your knees bent at a 90-degree angle.","Hold a weight plate or dumbbell with both hands close to your chest.","Engage your core and slowly rotate your torso to one side, keeping your hips stable.","Pause for a moment at the end of the rotation, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat the rotation to the other side.","Continue alternating sides for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, die Füsse flach auf dem Boden und die Knie im 90-Grad-Winkel gebeugt.","Halte eine Gewichtsscheibe oder Kurzhantel mit beiden Händen nah an deiner Brust.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und drehe deinen Oberkörper langsam zu einer Seite, während die Hüfte stabil bleibt.","Halte am Ende der Drehung kurz inne, kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole die Drehung zur anderen Seite.","Wechsle für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen die Seiten ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0849.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0849.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('366a7d8f-c3a4-53d6-8da6-19de8a505b7f', NULL, 'Weighted Side Bend (on Stability Ball)', 'Seitbeuge auf dem Gymnastikball mit Zusatzgewicht', 'waist', 'abs', 'weighted', 'Sit on a stability ball with your feet shoulder-width apart and flat on the ground. Hold a weight in one hand and place your other hand on your hip. Engage your core and slowly bend sideways towards the weighted side, keeping your back straight. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides.', NULL, 'obliques', '["obliques","lower back"]', '["Sit on a stability ball with your feet shoulder-width apart and flat on the ground.","Hold a weight in one hand and place your other hand on your hip.","Engage your core and slowly bend sideways towards the weighted side, keeping your back straight.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then slowly return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, then switch sides."]', '["Setze dich auf einen Gymnastikball, die Füsse schulterbreit und flach auf dem Boden.","Halte ein Gewicht in einer Hand und lege die andere Hand auf die Hüfte.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und beuge dich langsam seitlich zur Gewichtsseite, während du den Rücken gerade hältst.","Halte unten kurz inne, kehre dann langsam in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen und wechsle dann die Seite."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0850.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0850.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7223b733-800c-5f7e-97db-05783b81a0b9', NULL, 'Weighted Sissy Squat', 'Sissy Squat mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper legs', 'quads', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing slightly outward. Hold a weight in front of your chest with both hands, or place a barbell across your upper back. Keeping your chest up and your core engaged, slowly lower your body down by bending at the knees and hips. Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as low as you can comfortably go. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold a weight in front of your chest with both hands, or place a barbell across your upper back.","Keeping your chest up and your core engaged, slowly lower your body down by bending at the knees and hips.","Continue lowering until your thighs are parallel to the ground or as low as you can comfortably go.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push through your heels to return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte ein Gewicht mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust oder platziere eine Langhantel auf deinem oberen Rücken.","Halte die Brust aufrecht und die Körpermitte angespannt, während du deinen Körper langsam absenkst, indem du Knie und Hüfte beugst.","Senke dich weiter ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind oder so tief, wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Halte unten kurz inne, drücke dich dann durch die Fersen zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0851.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0851.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('be7a72b0-6de9-5133-9776-1fbc6818a184', NULL, 'Weighted Squat', 'Kniebeuge mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward. Hold a weight in front of your chest or on your shoulders. Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your hips down and back, as if sitting into a chair. Lower until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go. Push through your heels to stand back up, squeezing your glutes at the top. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, toes pointing slightly outward.","Hold a weight in front of your chest or on your shoulders.","Engage your core and keep your chest up as you lower your hips down and back, as if sitting into a chair.","Lower until your thighs are parallel to the ground, or as low as you can comfortably go.","Push through your heels to stand back up, squeezing your glutes at the top.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen, die Zehen leicht nach aussen gedreht.","Halte ein Gewicht vor der Brust oder auf den Schultern.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und halte die Brust aufrecht, während du die Hüfte nach unten und hinten senkst, als würdest du dich auf einen Stuhl setzen.","Senke dich ab, bis deine Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden sind, oder so tief, wie es für dich angenehm ist.","Drücke dich durch die Fersen nach oben und spanne dabei oben das Gesäss an.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0852.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0852.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('79ceb1a4-0e6d-57bb-a9e7-8a26ae647e6d', NULL, 'Weighted Standing Curl', 'Bizepscurl im Stehen mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'biceps', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward. Keep your elbows close to your torso and exhale as you curl the weights up to shoulder level. Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale as you slowly lower the weights back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'forearms', '["forearms"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a dumbbell in each hand, palms facing forward.","Keep your elbows close to your torso and exhale as you curl the weights up to shoulder level.","Pause for a moment at the top, then inhale as you slowly lower the weights back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte in jeder Hand eine Kurzhantel, Handflächen nach vorne zeigend.","Halte die Ellbogen nah am Oberkörper und atme aus, während du die Gewichte bis auf Schulterhöhe hochcurlst.","Halte oben kurz inne, atme dann ein und senke die Gewichte langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0853.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0853.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('e151006b-bbd4-53a0-ac0a-f1e9f948aafc', NULL, 'Weighted Standing Hand Squeeze', 'Handdrücken im Stehen mit Zusatzgewicht', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a weight in each hand. Extend your arms straight in front of you, palms facing each other. Squeeze your hands together as hard as you can, engaging your forearms. Hold the squeeze for a few seconds, then release. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a weight in each hand.","Extend your arms straight in front of you, palms facing each other.","Squeeze your hands together as hard as you can, engaging your forearms.","Hold the squeeze for a few seconds, then release.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte in jeder Hand ein Gewicht.","Strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus, die Handflächen zueinander zeigend.","Drücke deine Hände so fest wie möglich zusammen und spanne dabei die Unterarme an.","Halte die Anspannung ein paar Sekunden, löse sie dann.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0854.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0854.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('8a075ce4-b816-51d9-ba3c-659a669f5151', NULL, 'Weighted Straight Bar Dip', 'Dip an der geraden Stange mit Zusatzgewicht', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'weighted', 'Position yourself between parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself between parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich zwischen den Barren mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne, drücke dich dann durch das Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3313.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3313.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('43bece7f-8077-50c6-8139-3efd506585e2', NULL, 'Weighted Stretch Lunge', 'Ausfallschritt mit Dehnung und Zusatzgewicht', 'upper legs', 'glutes', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Take a step forward with your right foot, keeping your back straight. Lower your body by bending your knees until your right thigh is parallel to the ground. Push through your right heel to return to the starting position. Repeat with your left leg. Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Take a step forward with your right foot, keeping your back straight.","Lower your body by bending your knees until your right thigh is parallel to the ground.","Push through your right heel to return to the starting position.","Repeat with your left leg.","Continue alternating legs for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen.","Mache mit dem rechten Fuss einen Schritt nach vorne und halte den Rücken dabei gerade.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Knie beugst, bis dein rechter Oberschenkel parallel zum Boden ist.","Drücke dich durch die rechte Ferse zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole mit dem linken Bein.","Wechsle die Beine für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen ab."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3642.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3642.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('d9451e25-6d45-584f-9eb3-118334e0bdcd', NULL, 'Weighted Svend Press', 'Svend Press mit Zusatzgewicht', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'weighted', 'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a weight plate in front of your chest with both hands. Keep your elbows slightly bent and your palms facing each other. Press the weight plate straight out in front of you, fully extending your arms. Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring the weight plate back to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'shoulders', '["shoulders","triceps"]', '["Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and hold a weight plate in front of your chest with both hands.","Keep your elbows slightly bent and your palms facing each other.","Press the weight plate straight out in front of you, fully extending your arms.","Pause for a moment at the end of the movement, then slowly bring the weight plate back to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und halte eine Gewichtsscheibe mit beiden Händen vor deiner Brust.","Halte die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt und die Handflächen zueinander zeigend.","Drücke die Gewichtsscheibe gerade nach vorne, bis die Arme vollständig gestreckt sind.","Halte am Ende der Bewegung kurz inne, bringe die Gewichtsscheibe dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0856.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0856.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3f791675-3959-5c91-9951-2917a5180032', NULL, 'Weighted Three Bench Dips', 'Dip mit drei Bänken und Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'weighted', 'Sit on the edge of a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward. Walk your feet forward, sliding your butt off the bench and supporting your weight with your arms. Lower your body by bending your elbows, keeping your back close to the bench. Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench with your hands gripping the edge, fingers pointing forward.","Walk your feet forward, sliding your butt off the bench and supporting your weight with your arms.","Lower your body by bending your elbows, keeping your back close to the bench.","Pause for a moment at the bottom, then push yourself back up to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich an die Kante einer Bank und greife mit den Händen die Kante, die Finger zeigen nach vorne.","Gehe mit den Füssen nach vorne, sodass dein Gesäss von der Bank rutscht, und stütze dein Gewicht mit den Armen ab.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, und halte deinen Rücken dabei nah an der Bank.","Halte unten kurz inne, drücke dich dann zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1754.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1754.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('9e52d9fb-0e4a-52be-bed9-7400f4744ae7', NULL, 'Weighted Triceps Dips', 'Trizeps-Dips mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'weighted', 'Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge next to your hips. Slide your butt off the front of the bench with your legs extended in front of you. Keep your back close to the bench and your elbows slightly bent. Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the floor. Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Sit on the edge of a bench or chair with your hands gripping the edge next to your hips.","Slide your butt off the front of the bench with your legs extended in front of you.","Keep your back close to the bench and your elbows slightly bent.","Lower your body by bending your elbows until your upper arms are parallel to the floor.","Push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Setze dich an die Kante einer Bank oder eines Stuhls und greife mit den Händen die Kante neben deinen Hüften.","Lass dein Gesäss von der Bankkante rutschen, die Beine vor dir ausgestreckt.","Halte deinen Rücken nah an der Bank und die Ellbogen leicht gebeugt.","Senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Drücke dich durch das Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1755.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1755.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('503333c9-7a3e-5059-a297-665f7444f2ac', NULL, 'Weighted Triceps Dip on High Parallel Bars', 'Trizeps-Dip am hohen Barren mit Zusatzgewicht', 'upper arms', 'triceps', 'weighted', 'Position yourself between two parallel bars with your hands gripping the bars and your arms fully extended. Bend your elbows and lower your body until your upper arms are parallel to the ground. Pause for a moment, then push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'chest', '["chest","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself between two parallel bars with your hands gripping the bars and your arms fully extended.","Bend your elbows and lower your body until your upper arms are parallel to the ground.","Pause for a moment, then push through your palms to straighten your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich zwischen zwei Barren, greife die Holme mit den Händen und strecke die Arme vollständig.","Beuge die Ellbogen und senke deinen Körper ab, bis deine Oberarme parallel zum Boden sind.","Halte kurz inne, drücke dich dann durch die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1767.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1767.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('eda28f5d-d931-54b1-8f92-3209befb26d8', NULL, 'Wheel Rollout', 'Ab-Rollout mit dem Rad', 'waist', 'abs', 'wheel roller', 'Kneel on the floor and place the wheel roller in front of you. Place your hands on the handles of the wheel roller and extend your arms straight out in front of you. Engage your core muscles and slowly roll the wheel forward, keeping your back straight and your abs tight. Continue rolling forward until your body is fully extended and your arms are overhead. Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the wheel back towards your knees, maintaining control and keeping your abs engaged. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'lower back', '["lower back"]', '["Kneel on the floor and place the wheel roller in front of you.","Place your hands on the handles of the wheel roller and extend your arms straight out in front of you.","Engage your core muscles and slowly roll the wheel forward, keeping your back straight and your abs tight.","Continue rolling forward until your body is fully extended and your arms are overhead.","Pause for a moment, then slowly roll the wheel back towards your knees, maintaining control and keeping your abs engaged.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Knie dich auf den Boden und platziere das Rollrad vor dir.","Greife die Griffe des Rollrads und strecke die Arme gerade vor dir aus.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und rolle das Rad langsam nach vorne, während du den Rücken gerade und die Bauchmuskeln angespannt hältst.","Rolle weiter nach vorne, bis dein Körper vollständig gestreckt ist und deine Arme über dem Kopf sind.","Halte kurz inne, rolle das Rad dann langsam kontrolliert zurück zu den Knien, während du die Bauchmuskeln weiter angespannt hältst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0857.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0857.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5e2e27ad-32f7-5978-9b01-9980d9a9820f', NULL, 'Wheel Run', 'Laufen im Rad', 'cardio', 'cardiovascular system', 'body weight', 'Start in a plank position with your hands on the wheel and your body straight. Engage your core and start rolling the wheel forward by extending your arms. Continue rolling until your body is fully extended and your arms are overhead. Reverse the movement by pulling the wheel back towards your body, using your core and arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Start in a plank position with your hands on the wheel and your body straight.","Engage your core and start rolling the wheel forward by extending your arms.","Continue rolling until your body is fully extended and your arms are overhead.","Reverse the movement by pulling the wheel back towards your body, using your core and arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Starte in einer Plank-Position mit den Händen auf dem Rad und geradem Körper.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und rolle das Rad durch Strecken der Arme nach vorne.","Rolle weiter, bis dein Körper vollständig gestreckt ist und deine Arme über dem Kopf sind.","Kehre die Bewegung um, indem du das Rad mit Körpermitte und Armen zurück zu deinem Körper ziehst.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3637.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/3637.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('49cdf9ad-b9a5-5f91-916d-e346b2cf5947', NULL, 'Wide-Grip Pull-up', 'Klimmzug im weiten Griff', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Hang from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands wider than shoulder-width apart. Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together. Pull your body up towards the bar until your chin is above the bar. Lower your body back down to the starting position with control. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Hang from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you and your hands wider than shoulder-width apart.","Engage your core and squeeze your shoulder blades together.","Pull your body up towards the bar until your chin is above the bar.","Lower your body back down to the starting position with control.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Hänge dich an eine Klimmzugstange, Handflächen von dir weg zeigend, mit den Händen breiter als schulterbreit.","Spanne deine Körpermitte an und ziehe die Schulterblätter zusammen.","Ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Senke deinen Körper kontrolliert zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1429.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1429.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('5ec9cdd5-f86f-58da-b00e-b6a73bdc691c', NULL, 'Wide-Grip Rear Pull-up', 'Klimmzug im weiten Griff zum Nacken', 'back', 'lats', 'body weight', 'Grab the pull-up bar with a wide overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight. Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest. Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","forearms"]', '["Grab the pull-up bar with a wide overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.","Hang from the bar with your arms fully extended and your body straight.","Engage your back muscles and pull your body up towards the bar, leading with your chest.","Continue pulling until your chin is above the bar.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower your body back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Greife die Klimmzugstange mit einem breiten Obergriff, die Hände etwas breiter als schulterbreit.","Hänge mit vollständig gestreckten Armen und geradem Körper an der Stange.","Spanne deine Rückenmuskulatur an und ziehe deinen Körper zur Stange hoch, angeführt von der Brust.","Ziehe weiter, bis dein Kinn über der Stange ist.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke dann deinen Körper langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1367.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1367.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7660fe1d-9fed-5589-b554-276db6641703', NULL, 'Wide Hand Push-up', 'Liegestütz mit weitem Handabstand', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Start in a high plank position with your hands wider than shoulder-width apart. Keep your body in a straight line from head to toe. Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides. Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Start in a high plank position with your hands wider than shoulder-width apart.","Keep your body in a straight line from head to toe.","Lower your chest towards the ground by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your sides.","Push through your palms to extend your arms and return to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Starte in einer hohen Liegestützposition mit den Händen breiter als schulterbreit.","Halte deinen Körper in einer geraden Linie von Kopf bis Fuss.","Senke deine Brust Richtung Boden ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst und nah am Körper hältst.","Drücke dich durch die Handflächen ab, um die Arme zu strecken und in die Ausgangsposition zurückzukehren.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1311.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1311.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4747d310-a4be-540d-8a26-36504325ff86', NULL, 'Wide-Grip Chest Dip on High Parallel Bars', 'Weiter Brust-Dip am hohen Barren', 'chest', 'pectorals', 'body weight', 'Position yourself on the parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body suspended in the air. Lean forward slightly and lower your body by bending your elbows until your chest is just above the bars. Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'triceps', '["triceps","shoulders"]', '["Position yourself on the parallel bars with your arms fully extended and your body suspended in the air.","Lean forward slightly and lower your body by bending your elbows until your chest is just above the bars.","Pause for a moment, then push yourself back up to the starting position by straightening your arms.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Positioniere dich auf dem Barren mit vollständig gestreckten Armen, sodass dein Körper frei in der Luft hängt.","Lehne dich leicht nach vorne und senke deinen Körper ab, indem du die Ellbogen beugst, bis deine Brust knapp über den Holmen ist.","Halte kurz inne, drücke dich dann durch das Strecken der Arme zurück in die Ausgangsposition.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2363.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/2363.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('4823c730-35d5-5d6d-8b32-2b0501feff88', NULL, 'Wind Sprints', 'Sprintintervalle', 'waist', 'abs', 'body weight', 'Find an open space or a track to perform the exercise. Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart. Begin running as fast as you can, pumping your arms and driving your knees up. Continue sprinting for a specific distance or time period. Rest and repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'quadriceps', '["quadriceps","hamstrings","calves"]', '["Find an open space or a track to perform the exercise.","Start by standing with your feet shoulder-width apart.","Begin running as fast as you can, pumping your arms and driving your knees up.","Continue sprinting for a specific distance or time period.","Rest and repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Suche dir eine freie Fläche oder eine Laufbahn für die Übung.","Stehe zu Beginn schulterbreit mit den Füssen.","Beginne so schnell wie möglich zu laufen, pumpe dabei die Arme und ziehe die Knie hoch.","Sprinte für eine bestimmte Distanz oder Zeitdauer weiter.","Erhole dich und wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0858.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0858.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('ab463ad9-7de9-5482-a594-27bfe28c25a5', NULL, 'World''s Greatest Stretch', 'Ganzkörper-Dehnung (World''s Greatest Stretch)', 'upper legs', 'hamstrings', 'body weight', 'Start in a lunge position with your right foot forward and your left foot back. Place your hands on the ground on either side of your right foot. Lower your left knee to the ground and extend your right leg, keeping your right foot flat on the ground. Rotate your torso to the right, reaching your right arm up towards the ceiling. Hold this position for a few seconds, then return to the starting position. Switch sides and repeat the stretch with your left foot forward.', NULL, 'glutes', '["glutes","quadriceps","calves"]', '["Start in a lunge position with your right foot forward and your left foot back.","Place your hands on the ground on either side of your right foot.","Lower your left knee to the ground and extend your right leg, keeping your right foot flat on the ground.","Rotate your torso to the right, reaching your right arm up towards the ceiling.","Hold this position for a few seconds, then return to the starting position.","Switch sides and repeat the stretch with your left foot forward."]', '["Starte in einer Ausfallschritt-Position mit dem rechten Fuss vorne und dem linken Fuss hinten.","Platziere deine Hände auf beiden Seiten deines rechten Fusses auf dem Boden.","Senke dein linkes Knie zum Boden und strecke dein rechtes Bein, wobei dein rechter Fuss flach auf dem Boden bleibt.","Drehe deinen Oberkörper nach rechts und strecke deinen rechten Arm Richtung Decke.","Halte diese Position ein paar Sekunden, kehre dann in die Ausgangsposition zurück.","Wechsle die Seite und wiederhole die Dehnung mit dem linken Fuss vorne."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1604.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1604.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('3b7eaf90-1332-58e3-b869-96da4615113f', NULL, 'Wrist Circles', 'Handgelenkskreisen', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'body weight', 'Extend your arms straight out in front of you. Make a fist with both hands. Rotate your wrists in a circular motion, keeping your arms still. Continue the wrist circles for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'hands', '["hands","wrists"]', '["Extend your arms straight out in front of you.","Make a fist with both hands.","Rotate your wrists in a circular motion, keeping your arms still.","Continue the wrist circles for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Strecke deine Arme gerade vor dir aus.","Balle beide Hände zu Fäusten.","Kreise deine Handgelenke, während du die Arme ruhig hältst.","Führe die Handgelenkskreise für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen fort."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1428.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/1428.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0),
  ('7f7ccefd-3e3f-5004-8f17-866171ab2652', NULL, 'Wrist Roller', 'Handgelenksroller', 'lower arms', 'forearms', 'weighted', 'Attach a weight to one end of a rope or bar. Hold the other end of the rope or bar with both hands, palms facing down. Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms fully extended in front of you. Slowly roll the weight up towards your hands by flexing your wrists. Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the weight back down to the starting position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', NULL, 'biceps', '["biceps","triceps"]', '["Attach a weight to one end of a rope or bar.","Hold the other end of the rope or bar with both hands, palms facing down.","Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms fully extended in front of you.","Slowly roll the weight up towards your hands by flexing your wrists.","Pause for a moment at the top, then slowly lower the weight back down to the starting position.","Repeat for the desired number of repetitions."]', '["Befestige ein Gewicht an einem Ende eines Seils oder einer Stange.","Halte das andere Ende mit beiden Händen, Handflächen nach unten zeigend.","Stehe schulterbreit mit den Füssen und strecke die Arme vollständig vor dir aus.","Rolle das Gewicht langsam durch Beugen der Handgelenke zu deinen Händen hoch.","Halte oben kurz inne, senke das Gewicht dann langsam zurück in die Ausgangsposition ab.","Wiederhole für die gewünschte Anzahl an Wiederholungen."]', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0859.jpg', 'https://ascent-api.sweber.workers.dev/media/exercises/0859.gif', 1784612222128, 1784612222128, 0);
